[{"Name":"judy lam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJxQFsQ_JnNA4CIO0ttfhv0mp59ggfnPiiIcA0n0F4ju1lLlg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is the location that I return every year for my Christmas dinner Great atmosphere, great food and inviting customer services, making this a great places for any occasion for hang out. Especially Jennifer, she was a fantastic staff who look after us all the time. Gave us recommendations that exceeded our needs. Thank you for spending the night with us!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOQRHmPptwa-QTYI6RBVTzuf0k2O0LCeiTgymy1&fid=0x0:0x29a9313c1a6dc6ea"],"When":"2024-12-15"},{"Name":"Martin Dichupa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXNDFb5fEpdn1lV1xMh2_IBXJ0jnoQ6_jFy0aGbcE01nG9ImDpM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We recently held our joint Christmas and retirement party at JOEY Coquitlam, and it was an absolutely fantastic experience! From start to finish, the food was exceptional, and the service was top-notch.

A special shoutout to our server, Lexie, who truly went above and beyond to ensure our group felt welcomed and well taken care of. Her attentiveness and cheerful demeanor made the evening even more memorable.

Thank you to the entire team at JOEY Coquitlam for providing a 5-star experience that we’ll all be talking about for a long time! Highly recommended for any special occasion or group gathering.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP3n5_s8dop4ZL1-3yNhteI5QvPuYJCiRWWE2GX&fid=0x0:0x29a9313c1a6dc6ea"],"When":"2024-12-20"},{"Name":"Jennifer Bee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFO0fgPBTIA1yxL3IXSghRJ6EmshLC1YB1a72b-xeg3kpjHx0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My first time at this location and I was happy with everything. My MIL and I were offered sparking wine while we waited for a table - that was a treat! Fish tacos were good and my husband and MIL ended their meals as well. Lovely glass sculpture in the dining room - great atmosphere!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOO8s2wbmxDA3OW_Q-Fei91wBIxqxuBwFkGJq2I&fid=0x0:0x29a9313c1a6dc6ea"],"When":"2024-10-11"},{"Name":"Annie Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXeiXkcyhTInf8H3hsa41qWaj0-pj73GTGWAJSoVjdLilWPzd7b=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Upon arrival, guests are warmly welcomed with complimentary champagne. The service is exceptional, with a team of friendly staff. Our family celebrated a birthday, and the staff went above and beyond to accommodate a small issue with my entrée. They also surprised us with a complimentary birthday dessert, making the experience even more special.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPd2rvjU8Iq0HggwcxRdQ3iUjkHCt1i_xlP_Pk&fid=0x0:0x29a9313c1a6dc6ea"],"When":"2024-11-25"},{"Name":"Kayla Cochrane","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLPCxHm8VITPtk2g9XDHBWfyZtomSP_ai-b0ipoJVYmIOKKEg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had our staff party here tonight; Bianca and Jesse were amazing to us! Bianca was so sweet and attentive - Jesse gave us a great set up and was so welcoming! Food, overall service, and atmosphere 10/10","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO4lMwDnQhZroZ3cc7kUnByVwVgdllfheVWkikv&fid=0x0:0x29a9313c1a6dc6ea"],"When":"2024-11-10"},{"Name":"Jamie Brand","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXKYZgBpqiELo9hDY5N-5k-gorixQvb36QqVW-qrYDjhXG_wuiwQQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of the best dining experiences I’ve had in a long time. We had gone previously and had a subpar experience, but were personally invited back by the general manager for a chance to redo the experience. Everything was incredible from the word go. Our server was extremely personable, and I don’t think I’ve ever had a French dip like that before. Our steaks were done to perfection, and I appreciated a couple of drink recommendations they made. We were treated like royalty, and I can tell the GM takes great pride in her restaurant. After 15 years of enjoying Joey, this is by far the best time I’ve had.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMnXXGCOP-ZGWLV7lPed7ddiNLbfTV_EgEvP9fY&fid=0x0:0x29a9313c1a6dc6ea"],"When":"2024-8-16"},{"Name":"Jim O'Grady","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWJGgsb2sCcFjV1Mve3M5vv3QuR2DK9KBJEfmo_m9dlw5ULu0-QIA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently arranged a birthday lunch for an old friend at Joeys, and the experience exceeded my expectations. From the moment we arrived, the staff demonstrated exceptional hospitality, but it was Sydney who truly stood out. Her attention to detail and professionalism elevated the occasion, ensuring that every request was handled promptly and with a warm friendly demeanor. The manager also made a point to personally check in, adding a level of service that made us feel genuinely appreciated. Their combined efforts made our celebration both memorable and thoroughly enjoyable. I would highly recommend Joeys for any special occasion.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPl7xObgarUbqZ5ioLnryyK2VjAiQ9nUewKH8G-&fid=0x0:0x29a9313c1a6dc6ea"],"When":"2024-8-16"},{"Name":"camille sal.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU7Ks7QNJJsJdwwFb2BHOVyVy0T4aFfD9IIuenSGN5xn7y4mt27=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Joey’s restaurant, specifically this location, is an amazing dining experience! The food is absolutely delicious, with a menu that offers a great variety of options to satisfy any craving. The service is top-notch—friendly, attentive, and efficient. The ambiance is equally impressive, with a clean and welcoming atmosphere that’s perfect for any occasion. Highly recommend this place to anyone looking for great food, excellent service, and a fantastic overall experience!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPEvE0G517vl-jg_1k27I_p0eCrQDbGt4SvClOA&fid=0x0:0x29a9313c1a6dc6ea"],"When":"2024-12-23"}]

[{"Name":"Jack Bi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIZ4Bsv7wnjfj756aRVvVyi5fPfQhBIMCe6kqNdp4pTbIyytg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had the pleasure of trying katsu in Burquitlam recently, and I really appreciated the wonderful service. The food was delicious, and it was lovely to have both a salad and a refill of rice included—such a thoughtful addition! That said, I did notice the music was a bit on the loud side, which made it a little hard to fully enjoy the experience. Overall, though, it was a nice outing.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOGrjvypMFCi2IrGkRiEDeUZr2eyCD4xHboYTPz&fid=0x0:0xc180c2232f3f7e85"],"When":"2024-12-11"},{"Name":"Andy Leung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVBfPzDHg9RmwaF6xT8BiwrCt06LiR0mWps8IZZP7KGtsdBbQne=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Stepped into the restaurant not really looking to eat but found the place open amongst many closed restaurants. Staff greeted me at the door and I asked for a menu which was promptly provided. A staff member (tall young man with perm) provided a thorough explanation of the menu and what different food options was available and the restaurant was about. I opted to dine in after the thorough explanation and genuine service even before I sat. Once I settled on an order the staff loudly shouted to the kitchen staff and proceeded to hand me utensils/water. Moments later I could hear a meat mallet being slammed against what can be presumed to be my order (pork loin cutlet). Not long after I sat down another customer came in asking to look at the menu and explaining they're unfamiliar with the concept. the food came out quickly. The deep fried loin was pleasantly plated; light tasting; and juicy with flavour. 5/5 food. 5/5 service. 5/5 ambiance. Seems like cabbage salad sides are unlimited too! Beginning to end this was 5/5. Came on Tuesday Oct 22nd 3:30pm. Katsuya - Coquitlam if you're reading this please recognize your staff for such outstanding service and delicious food!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMqilRDdGE6NydQWz1wbHRJAZ10XC-zTFgOgoJS&fid=0x0:0xc180c2232f3f7e85"],"When":"2024-10-22"},{"Name":"Kristine Aizle Estrada","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKYbQRMW0sa4F7v9y0xsCWOZxC721h53-90ZVy0Q0mpX6y_Og=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We are greeted by all staff as soon we entered the place and got seated right away. We ordered the special set and it did not disappoint (the katsu is crispy and not greasy 😋). The set was large portion and we end up taking the leftovers to go. Good place to eat variety of katsu. Will come back for sure.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOY-fx02u_VLQCLdpnDytZZVO7vSsU3Eniy5syQ&fid=0x0:0xc180c2232f3f7e85"],"When":"2024-12-17"},{"Name":"TS OS","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIrxJ8Fjd3bGSI8mWbF186RbFWyg_DW73VTS3OIkFaxPfXFBEQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"DonKatsu was pretty good. Pricing is up there with its competitors. Quality of food is comparable too but cabbage salad and rice refills don’t seem to exist at this place at free of charge. We also really liked the pasta, which was surprisingly tasty especially the sauce. Place usually isn’t packed so you should be able to get seated fairly shortly.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOJbZSl1M1e8lL8ztqGh1BRqzbPMALyWsOjK81b&fid=0x0:0xc180c2232f3f7e85"],"When":"2024-11-9"},{"Name":"Ben","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLUPgdSyWZ3aTWwwnESZaSRJf8t_y_oBRQlEfjK-SB4dJfKj64=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The Katsu sauce had a unique taste, but overall it was the best tonkatsu place I've had in Vancouver. The taste was great, and the portion size was very enough for the price, which made it very satisfying. The restaurant had a small number of tables compared to the size of the space, which made it comfortable and pleasant. The staff's service was also excellent.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPtnMx8MZVn9g_Opb-r96C0P49aZ1kpq0KR6bq2&fid=0x0:0xc180c2232f3f7e85"],"When":"2024-11-29"},{"Name":"Karen Abary","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVuR4UCsHnAPqLBeNDszrqXOmjrbOmLQnn5L3CErUSQyQJWrM8qqw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you’re cruising through North Road and craving something beyond the usual Korean fare, Katsuya is where you need to be! 😋 This place has all the mouthwatering options—from rich, savory udon to crispy, golden katsu. 🍛 And when I say the portions are huge, I mean HUGE! 🙌

I went for the Katsu Set, and it was an absolute game-changer. The katsu was perfectly crispy on the outside, tender on the inside, paired with a warm, flavorful bowl of udon, plus a variety of side dishes that kept me coming back for more. 🍜🍤 Every bite was better than the last!

But what really made the experience unforgettable? The service! 🙏 The staff is so friendly, super accommodating, and genuinely makes you feel like you’re right at home. 💖 And the best part? The prices are totally worth it for the big portions and top-notch food you get.

Katsuya is definitely a new favorite, and I’ll be back for sure! 🥳 So if you’re after a cozy, flavorful meal that’ll leave you stuffed and satisfied, this spot is a must-try! #KatsuyaCravings #FoodieHeaven #NorthRoadEats #WorthEveryBite","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNI92G2XWHYPDUt7OD1zn2lu0xp98OwnV25kSEQ&fid=0x0:0xc180c2232f3f7e85"],"When":"2024-11-12"},{"Name":"Cyril","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWK-_ySZg3bQEFmes-BY-8D2FucE-bUlde_oHJOB4IAApjGcLEN=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came on a date with my girlfriend, we were greeted as we stepped into the place and were seated right away, love the atmosphere lovely music that fits the season and also love the bread displays it shows that the breading is authentic. I was overwhelmed in a way in which the food had a excellent presentation and the portions were worth the pricing, also love the sesame seeds which you can grind by yourself it gives it a nice detail to add to the meal. Most importantly the Katsu is cooked just right, my girlfriend got the silver cheese katsu and the cheese was just right melting and not too hot, recommend this place for real, nice little hidden spot for a date or for a filling meal :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOUvIHVBWOi-4eHV9Ift76vddqGCB1k7bOIVPwn&fid=0x0:0xc180c2232f3f7e85"],"When":"2024-12-20"},{"Name":"Anish Banik Arko","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWI0KM6WKbnZVsLpZ9NMfdm_mhCSCv9FEUTS0DOwOV0D99wyYin4A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food has always been amazing here. Have been coming here for a long time. Their special set katsu menu comes with enough food for two and the variety of foods really adds to the dining experience. The presentation is also on point. Would highly recommend to try out their red carbonara katsu with your choice of protein.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPaP-aKaqJ3ToDeKrzL9oDtvbRVJxEmm8p4ZWAp&fid=0x0:0xc180c2232f3f7e85"],"When":"2024-7-23"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Kimberly W","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIyEcFWm9KlF1A5qUr48_2k5NqNkBKB28_JBHp8Hk3SydvKzo4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I haven’t had authentic Singaporean cuisine but I’ve heard good things about Singapore hawker so I finally decided to try. The staff seemed very friendly right upon entering. We ordered the pork belly, beef skewers, and the Nasi Goreng. Everything was very tasty, the Nasi Goreng had still a kick to it despite asking for mild. My complain was that the shrimp chips were a bit stale. The beef skewers were kind of on the skinnier side, but were definitely not dry and the peanut sauce was amazing. The crispy pork belly was probably what shined the most. I’m not a huge pork belly fan but this pork belly was not too fatty, extremely moist and tasty. We even got a free dessert at the end which was a pleasant surprise, and it was a delicious way to cleanse your palate after meat/spice. I can’t speak for how authentic the food is but overall we really enjoyed this place and would come again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP9JNMLelRiisg_saezjbRCw_pidLJCdc5JZuAB&fid=0x0:0xbc7025c18f4ae0f7"],"When":"2024-10-23"},{"Name":"Junyong Hong (Junny)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI68GoItOKY8hE2VMit7EfVOjKre8YhHLAJmsrHl632hIf8sQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"You get big portions of tasty food for decent price. Staffs were friendly and the restaurant was clean. This is our second time coming and we will come back again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOyyfJHeAIV46RNOEis4Klz8lkAy-V4zNstd2SJ&fid=0x0:0xbc7025c18f4ae0f7"],"When":"2024-12-14"},{"Name":"Jack Pajak","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV7kRSq5QM1wGXm36_dbE9YR6CpcUs9VUAhu1SxvpJkrQ-nGO0N=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time trying Singapore Hawker and I have to say that I am impressed! Our food was absolutely delicious, with great portions. I highly recommend the Roti Canai and the Mee Goreng. Great for families and kids. Service here is friendly and our food came out fast! Definitely worth a visit.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPACVFg29cV1QEgOLsn1pyLN7LDEZluy1PFmiTk&fid=0x0:0xbc7025c18f4ae0f7"],"When":"2024-9-2"},{"Name":"Marilyn Mok","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUikqrTCDS8NJxP3Hkk4jQDiHEi8RL4gQluQjwU1f2e462S8t3D=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"First off, I wasn't impressed with the atmosphere. The place looks more like a staff canteen than a cafe.

I ordered the Char Kuay Teow and my friend ordered the fried nonya eggplant.  The Char Kuay Teow had a nice wok flavor but is not as sweet and flavorful as I like. It was fried with only the flat white rice noodle and missing the yellow noodle. The fish cake used did not have the springy texture that is found in Singapore fishballs and fish cake. There's also not enough egg in it. The nonya eggplant was nicely fried but I'm not sure where the nonya reference came in. I was also very disappointed that they do not have Singapore style kopi or teh.

The plus point was that the service staff was nice and friendly. And they offered a free small bowl of burbur chacha for dessert.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPqSwNclcQGOBN5-0DD5v221mnMrRsKq067l4xK&fid=0x0:0xbc7025c18f4ae0f7"],"When":"2024-9-26"},{"Name":"grace","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXclLzFOZebBq0D1P6DXbTNuAdCFzeYlMZFVvgi1A5VbWvym50Z=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"food: really delicious and flavorful. the Singaporean laksa is soo creamy and rich, and the fried squid is super crispy and crunchy

service: the service was okay, but they don't take your orders for food. so you have to either go up to the cashier, or scan the QR code on the table to order.

atmosphere: I really like the atmosphere of this restaurant. it's modern, clean, and simple. there's also a really cool wall with the skyline of Singapore and some famous architecture on it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMypF7B-MThYJHZbwWgKhQ5Kjm7zoNR7XF3LFz0&fid=0x0:0xbc7025c18f4ae0f7"],"When":"2024-7-14"},{"Name":"carol liem","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUUCuYohzwvL-I_7dNVbbjdcGA122HF_X2tQ1V3VyXmvEJB9WWU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We had authentic Singapore food here. My son liked the Hainanese Chicken Rice. I liked the satays and Sayur Lodeh. We will visit this restaurant whenever we miss Singaporean food!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNp0oaI4IOKuEtfewT6MXGHW7pSWDfgMC-pKZ9-&fid=0x0:0xbc7025c18f4ae0f7"],"When":"2024-7-16"},{"Name":"Tony Sebastian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXG7uEWzSX7JHK-BIUyNSlpONTzE37us0aA6AsvFHAQcMKQgAKL=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food is excellent oh my god!!! transit all the way from downtown for this place. been here quite some times. Will be back for sure!!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNfO59HQFIEsZivGR_yrnavTAJt1R2UNQn7Ddbg&fid=0x0:0xbc7025c18f4ae0f7"],"When":"2024-12-11"},{"Name":"Irene Martinez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLLx3-d7cbUWi2OAKcOP1RtCCE35UuLboYj6B1-X-4h1WkqA8nN=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The naan was delicious too. I went with my parents. This is not a restaurant where the waiters necessary wait on your table all the time since you order at the counter and pay upfront; regardless, the delicious food is totally worth it and eating the leftovers the next day was even better.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM5DPjWLhIpFJ3nHNkI3EOtYaVqI8N3PM6TcSBe&fid=0x0:0xbc7025c18f4ae0f7"],"When":"2024-8-24"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Joey Lam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIncJBLfbVzRO24PRdfxE4-hovZn6C_s4RV_vqsGslULP8YEA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Originally we wanted to go to Cactus Club but the line was crazily long. We came to the weekend when there was a festival at the mall.

So we searched for the highest-rating restaurant nearby and found this place. The food was so good, it blew our mind.

We had a spicy shredded potato appetizer. It was spicy but still manageable for us.

Their noodles were very different from what we normally saw at other noodle places, so we just kind of picked two very different ones. One was glassy and in chili oil soup, the other one was thin pull noodles in a relatively clear booth. Both were very flavourful and we were so glad that we found this place. Even though this is far from where we live but we will definitely come back to try other types of noodles.

We were given free dessert in the end! The dessert was some sort of jelly - it was transparent, chill and not too sweet. Lovely! A perfect ending to a delicious meal.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOx7_m78rUA4KWGk0lGb8Ceuohpz_2UmkZrSyss&fid=0x0:0xba62bb428697b557"],"When":"2024-5-23"},{"Name":"charles bai","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVivIWOvTOamsgiucoqI5EKukhiOsZqTk7nog1iV-Y1Xav6PIczow=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really flavorful, really bouncy, chewy noodles! Honestly can’t go wrong with any noodle dish, and they all have a unique flavor! Just don’t expect a lot of toppings - the star of the show is the noodles with the sauce!

I really enjoyed the cold noodle dish, 大拉皮, the sauce was the perfect salty sour spicy combination","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMIQ-D3nMLqaxvfeRc-ihmVJMl9FVF33g1PYhY1&fid=0x0:0xba62bb428697b557"],"When":"2024-7-9"},{"Name":"A. L.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW5TiPH35l6b0Yp0-BDY7r9mxPb2PWCWLOWYg3E7uIKxSRcy84P=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best hidden gem in Coquitlam!! Highly recommend the garlic dumplings (their most popular dish for a reason) and the dry noodle with beef brisket (pay the extra 1$ for the hand made noodles) as well as the red bean pancake. Food was perfectly seasoned and so so delicious !!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPFdK1xNLIAQFO20WtiU_cJl86OvWu0Wb4_XpSh&fid=0x0:0xba62bb428697b557"],"When":"2024-11-2"},{"Name":"Ryan Blight","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbpH73lI2xtK9WJxadw5s8Ist4ItI3NEBYZImc9aopB1Hhs9lf=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We ordered homemade garlic dumpling, Dan Dan noodle and handmade noodle with beef brisket - all dishes with medium heat and it was absolutely delicious! The sauce on those dumplings was incredible! Will recommend to others 🤩","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOjB1-v-OnwdXhOzu-73B0SjDMd1KJI52-XJJYn&fid=0x0:0xba62bb428697b557"],"When":"2024-10-14"},{"Name":"Emily Sanchez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUMrCl__83PRc54jDLOKOkfjwZwBODeNVlQZ-bPXLZAKUk3EboR=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you are looking for some authentic Chinese spicy food, especially noodle, this is the place to go! Reasonable price, good portions and great service! Summer is super nice and helpful! We would totally go again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPOO8qMMgo39RmJ-76A6WtKE1-T8c_Y8nInZxtR&fid=0x0:0xba62bb428697b557"],"When":"2024-5-8"},{"Name":"Kevin Luo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVWJMxLZr-3YvPOYEYkCwOqoRgX8yyWGLPYZ19IJEKzgIUssXc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have not a single bad thing to say about this restaurant. The owner is the nicest lady ever, she kept giving me samples of sweet jelly and milk tea even after I was stuffed by the delicious food here. The food here is absolutely delicious, super authentic and has massive portions. The chitterlings were clean and seriously flavourful in the spicy sauce it came with. The cold shredded chicken salad was also wonderful. The Szechuan hot chili wonton is listed under appetizers, but it is actually a full meal by itself. I couldn't even start it after wolfing down the previous two plates with rice. This place is insane value if you are into spicy food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNGfS9sHXFHX-GIUqaFjaBE0peRj7TE-q4oLmfp&fid=0x0:0xba62bb428697b557"],"When":"2024-3-22"},{"Name":"Andrew Zhou","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXPIxXxmEDjGJcYO362T99oS-5qWMFJgvMbwHh0mGwwfhau82E=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The duck feet, noodles, and glutinous rice cakes were absolutely delicious. The duck feet were tender and flavorful, perfectly seasoned with a hint of spice. The noodles were cooked to perfection, with a wonderful texture that absorbed the rich, savory sauce beautifully. The glutinous rice cakes were a delightful finish, with a chewy consistency and just the right amount of sweetness. Overall, each dish offered a unique and memorable taste experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOzMRBsszdMd9y_Ruutiww3mSpWiPcytluwVi5S&fid=0x0:0xba62bb428697b557"],"When":"2024-6-14"},{"Name":"Sy Y.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWlvv5Hw7BczrB2EJa0tUi7oVzXQrKcexe_QyluaWJfb22gz7A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This cozy spot might be small with just a few tables for various group sizes, but it adds to the charm of the dining experience. I can't emphasize enough how incredible the food was, particularly the garlic dumplings and spicy wontons. The ability to customize the spiciness level for most dishes is a standout feature. The cold dishes like cucumber and potato were refreshing and tasty. Even though there was a short 10-minute wait, the overall experience was definitely worth it. The complimentary desserts provided to combat the heat were a thoughtful touch. This place is a definite must-visit for its mouthwatering food and attentive service.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMTGmEiqiIDhpLZSa5uu6VZhUyjR999Na0YSTOG&fid=0x0:0xba62bb428697b557"],"When":"2023-8-13"}]

[{"Name":"Sarah Hong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKnboqN2ucap2810B74d4ezUYCyFoMSbI2XJPs7KKauWRgM5Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is absolutely delicious! The noodles in the 짜장면 are perfectly balanced—not too thick or thin, and cooked just right. The 짬뽕 has just the right level of spice, full of rich flavor that melts away your stress. As for the sweet and sour pork, it's a perfect combination of textures—crispy on the outside, tender and juicy on the inside. 100% recommend! Definitely worth every penny.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOi-q_1NweNn4z2ThRTUFxzQExHPrQNJtVyh5QC&fid=0x0:0xada9b7037d05e7e9"],"When":"2024-9-23"},{"Name":"David 04 Make the World a Better Place","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXXmkrAyRsAwad4uDl0EKEwpsCVMLq51IOxmbley55h_iwJzGo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"David's Overall Recommendation
★★★★★

● Taste ★★★★★
● Price ★★★★★
● Kindness ★★★★★
● Comfort ★★★★☆
● Cleanliness ★★★★★

I visited this restaurant around 4:30 pm, which is a bit early for dinner. A female server welcomed me, and she was very friendly.

I ordered the combo with Jajangmyeon (black bean noodles), Jjamppong (spicy seafood noodle soup), and Tangsuyuk (sweet and sour pork). About 10 minutes later, all three dishes arrived together. The Tangsuyuk seemed to be fried in clean oil, and both the meat and the batter were exceptional. (Having worked in the restaurant industry, I could tell the frying oil was fresh.)

The Jajangmyeon and Jjamppong were delicious too, but the Tangsuyuk was the highlight.

The portions were generous, with all the food being flavorful and filling.

There were a couple of minor downsides:

1.	After the food was served, although the restaurant wasn’t busy, no one came by to check on the food or refill the side dishes. But with food this tasty, it was easy to overlook.
2.	They were playing a Charlie Puth medley, which didn’t quite match the restaurant’s vibe. (Just a playful comment!)

●There’s parking available, though not a lot.

●The restrooms are separated for men and women.

I highly, highly recommend this restaurant.
The food is incredibly tasty and clean.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPsoYUAAi-S_HgnQg7DpsMimB6vAJ-ixuB9las&fid=0x0:0xada9b7037d05e7e9"],"When":"2024-11-3"},{"Name":"Y Man","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUB62F2-VitrTkpd3TexeBmDt6LJ-Ec6lzQvbbyCIp7HJAIiB3b=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Update:
We went for the second time and we are happy that the food is still great and tasty! Consistency is so important and glad it did not disappoint. We ordered the same dishes plus Jjamppong. The Jjamppong was delicious! The broth was spicy but flavourful.  We will come back and try more dishes.

What a great meal! The food was delicious and the portion is generous. The tangsuyuk coating was light and crispy its sauce in the bowl was sweet and flavourful. The fried chicken's batter was also light and crispy and it was coated with a nice sweet tangy sauce that has a nice kick to it.  The jjajangmyeon was delicious, noodles are nice and chewy, the sauce was good with seafood and waterchestnuts mixed in it. I look forward to try their jjamppong (spicy seafood soup noodles)! We saw another table had it and it looks great!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPYGfyXK9P4bM98bWmhnS-0JPOB5QwstdK4zmYr&fid=0x0:0xada9b7037d05e7e9"],"When":"2024-6-8"},{"Name":"Paula Mari Calip","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUDLGLcegymnTs4tKFxCUQkS77Gpb8Bcit9lJfvZ7dcPzKmO_Ci-Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Home-y atmosphere, big servings, flavourful meal. My family enjoyed our time here. Will come back for sure!

PS: couldn’t take proper photos of our other food lol we were hungry and ready to chow down 😂","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO-fmzFjkrXsDSuD70e4LWu0e4GepaXup02B7aI&fid=0x0:0xada9b7037d05e7e9"],"When":"2024-10-31"},{"Name":"Kenny Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXPZZirBvo0A4h9mBsQTblhWpjRI5s3b9jzZsDmMvuAnSg24xg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We don't often have Korean food but we wanted to try this place since they just opened where Kam Ding used to be. We also didn't know the portion sizes but it turned out to be really big so we ended up with enough leftovers for a second meal! The food was tasty so we enjoyed it. Most of the dishes are spicy but just right for us. A senior couple arrived and sat at the next table. They sounded like they are Italian and were also looking to try Korean food. We helped them choose a non-spicy dish!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMhdTuRlDHKuJZqKozH-SA71Wk1X7IfundtlX5N&fid=0x0:0xada9b7037d05e7e9"],"When":"2023-12-27"},{"Name":"Scott Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXHpW7vGME__Zs4wKjXR04Upnw88bkVVyz-H2288JsHocq9vI3r=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"It's a pretty standard Korean-Chinese restaurant that I'm used to. Their black sauce noodle was pretty good, but what really impressed me was the sweet and sour chicken.

The spicy seafood noodle was also quite tasty and would recommend it if you are into spicy food. I recommend that you go with lots of people so that you can order different things to try!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMVNoe2LTQphTqu1MVyAj3B_wmaTn3z8kg7qon6&fid=0x0:0xada9b7037d05e7e9"],"When":"2024-1-23"},{"Name":"marieXD21","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU-Fu7lpV7ZXo_nlR8y9b6iJvHY1uEHpNZ4ShKlMM_rYkUiQkw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"All food are delicious. We eat here once a month but every time we come back, we still can’t finish the big portions. Undefeated, highly recommend 💯!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOAroCq__K1__QMaOgFHdj2TOTP2iR6IMqfnzCS&fid=0x0:0xada9b7037d05e7e9"],"When":"2024-9-4"},{"Name":"Fanny","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJf8QKhXtO_qInBc0jUDaCE3x1KtIHCwwl5Dp3ugGKzBjub0Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We tried the Jjajangmyun and Jjam Bbong, and we're thrilled to have finally found a good Jjajangmyun! The Jjam Bbong was deliciously spicy. The portions were generous, and the service was excellent!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOFNKr0BhTh7zPnf9l2KU0zrOOR5DhjvZAbQn6k&fid=0x0:0xada9b7037d05e7e9"],"When":"2024-6-25"}]

[{"Name":"Coniah Kim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVRF6exFWLtpR3e9xDEQIA8baJa13bfBk5CzdOsGQJX1lxG9B8F=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A hidden surprise gem!
Came in without any expectations but very pleasantly impressed with the interior.  The food was amazing!  Everything was in balanced.  Truffle Risotto was well cooked with hint of balsamic flavoured mushrooms.  Benedict was creamy and soft.  Seafood linguine was tastefully fusiony spicy.
And the cruffles… what a fine and delicious to finish off a meal.  And yes… all the special coffees were good!

Will definitely recommend this place to anyone.

The restaurant is also family friendly- they have special kids menu.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOzA5sKIVZBj7hdzzdx0dAJrQ6A9GlxkEbKK7DC&fid=0x0:0x8242b04469c5d5af"],"When":"2024-12-16"},{"Name":"Stephie N","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXd0_eqzaDNFpYKxu_At0QKV_opW1IXDZ3BtSf_D5LFw7-X91jS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’m genuinely surprised this fantastic place isn’t packed with people. It feels like sitting at a bistro in Paris, with its beautiful patio and ample space. Unlike other popular brunch spots nearby, you don’t have to overhear conversations from the next table, thanks to the generous spacing between tables. The food was delicious, but I wish the coffee were stronger—it was a bit too weak for my taste. Even the restrooms are stylish! I’ll definitely be visiting again in the near future.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNIPt9HrlVESQ7NWmlger11SRLVUmi3PzCBp7V8&fid=0x0:0x8242b04469c5d5af"],"When":"2024-9-20"},{"Name":"Dahee Sim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUX9xskvqrMlPhfaEjei8fHc2AKp7yd0SfCkRSHV-khbg0nQPk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A gorgeous mid-century-style interior and great food. Honestly, I was surprised to find a brunch spot like this in Coquitlam. It’s not too busy. I enjoyed my meal without rushing. Highly recommended for a date spot. I would love to come back and recommend this place to anyone I know.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMe76FYiQnvzBF7kVx5mnkesf4oadu4dy_tlnyD&fid=0x0:0x8242b04469c5d5af"],"When":"2024-12-9"},{"Name":"Jenna A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLGeR4hbJbNaJlqcXNAxQUrp3QHCCXfRtmHBdhtRlvTl_6ydw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I've visited this restaurant several times and have enjoyed the wonderful ambiance, particularly the patio with its beautiful views. The food is delicious and well-portioned. However, the service quality varies. While most of the staff are courteous, one server was not very friendly and handled things carelessly. With more consistent service, this place could be exceptional.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM6B3d3ldgXF0MjORrSBlg1esfRXZTZl94EWzI4&fid=0x0:0x8242b04469c5d5af"],"When":"2024-10-7"},{"Name":"K’s coffee lover","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW-385uQOflrqOxsV0QWsdIyhv-rxdZ7rLwLnLPmzpfPGzr9P6Z=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dine-in again in August, new menu. Taste is good as usual. Still like it.

Dine-in twice within one week. Very interesting menu. Love their vibes. Service is a bit on the slow side but perfect for me to make up my mind on those interesting dishes. Every dish is a feast for the senses, combining color, aroma, and flavor perfectly. Will definitely return for more. 😋😋😋","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPx9tx4IxpQSmwOcmLv8ddhuFNkeLJXAmiPW7VI&fid=0x0:0x8242b04469c5d5af"],"When":"2024-6-3"},{"Name":"Courtney Pittman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocImDRdaEZ1vUaDf3DGIejVTXETr6R1b9106tf3qLHJFMRHijw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It has a nice atmosphere, and is very spacious inside and has outdoor seating with a beautiful view! I went there with 5 adults and 2 kids under 3, it was accommodating for our kids and they have a kids menu and a high chair. I ordered the tomato seafood pasta, it was delicious! And my husband ordered the salmon eggs Benedict, also very yummy! I especially liked the spices they used! The staff was also kind and very quick to help! For example, my child spilled his water, and they cleaned it up for us right away!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNgjAY09m6k9cxVOG4Az0WqGpq2fFEdBw-FJImn&fid=0x0:0x8242b04469c5d5af"],"When":"2024-7-14"},{"Name":"A Miraji","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVKbtSn1-d3iEkTDQas0xH_xCGg1PKv8z1hKaZIhPkrsgM_kICp=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Loved this place, food was very well prepared and served. The staff were nice, polite and helpful. The place itself is nicely decorated and a appropriate selection of music tracks was playing which made the experience even better. Totally recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMrQC1fF5b3mfJw-XcDL01DLAj6uIxwwrpmTln6&fid=0x0:0x8242b04469c5d5af"],"When":"2024-12-1"},{"Name":"Ruby E.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVTXhvN-EpNac4Qr_mgdf5IDJLY8uKSuinXxuVkhfUtlVyIdrlu=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"If you love bennies, this is your spot!  Spacious with lots of seating and good variety of menu items so there’s something for everyone, including vegetarian & gluten-free options.  Even though brunch is served all day, some other items aren't available until after 5pm.
The coffee was disappointing. Their $4 coffee was in a cup that held less than 6 oz. The flat white was served in a glass without a handle?! & way too creamy (more like a latte).
The "Sunset mimosa" ($12) we ordered was delicious but we suspect we were served their zero proof mocktail instead the "Sunrise Mimosa" (for the same price) as there was a canned cherry on the bottom. The Espresso martini ($14) was too sweet & creamy, opt for the Carajillo instead if you want more coffee flavor.
Overall, we prefer Pur & Simple for brunch & beverages.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMIRn2r-vEtR6XvTYqjnnBoMAcr3moEk50xhb05&fid=0x0:0x8242b04469c5d5af"],"When":"2024-11-3"}]

[{"Name":"Cheryl A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocId3JTMrjtqtdmj_0XOBMchbLGhcrTAO0uBPM1jzlHcNAjL=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I loved my potato Marsala Dosa. The coconut chutney was super delicious. It came with a soup ( spicy) very generous portions . The servers were very friendly & kind . Reasonable prices for what you get . Fresh and not much of a wait .","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPQcIzZnZe-I0wMCOjUfijOQEx2ad0NLGuE3ig&fid=0x0:0xa294bdbddd105db6"],"When":"2024-9-30"},{"Name":"PC","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWnLR6JbppM6GM5nol1xpc9XuPLJD0bzW-RWDiP6CpTO8u6ksE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Desi Dosa Madras is such a great find!  I ordered the lamb shank curry and the spinach chicken dosa, and both were incredible.  The lamb was super tender and juicy, and the curry it came with was full of flavor.  The spinach chicken dosa was so fresh and tasty—it hit the spot perfectly.

The portions were huge, which is always a bonus, and everything tasted fresh and homemade.  The owner and staff were really friendly too, which made the whole experience even better.

If you’re looking for delicious food, big portions, and great service, definitely check this place out.  Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Daniel Jung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFE7g6vnjf23CW6mDeh4anchF8fxBs6O5Nsx0bvhepuO3MVzWa=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Such friendly service :)
My first Dosa experience!!
Got a Lamb Dosa, infused with so many flavors, and boy was it spicy but I enjoyed every bite! Also, it was incredibly filling.
Definitely planning to try other dishes","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNDXHxroDT1KqlQCFEHsYQgPbuYbcZHrChRbnRe&fid=0x0:0xa294bdbddd105db6"],"When":"2023-2-9"},{"Name":"Dora Eng","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUhBtDPoDG5jAGseu0DWPAqVq_MQfyz59Il4JHwDJMLbh2lmpSv=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My family and I recently visited Desi Dosa at the Henderson food court, and I’m so impressed with their customer service! My husband ordered a plain dosa for our son, but I forgot to mention that he doesn’t like cilantro. When we went back, hoping the dosa hadn’t been made yet, we asked if they could leave out the cilantro. Even though it was already cooking with cilantro, the chef went above and beyond by carefully removing most of it to accommodate our request. Such a thoughtful gesture! This kind of service, paired with their delicious food, makes them truly stand out. Highly recommend!"","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"GRoo3Y","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXnyXegPToN37SksvZIxBb7lUyVf07LGjT7LQNGsVWronjLoc58Jw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ordered a lamb Dosa,  First time trying it and it was very delicious.  The staff were very kind and attentive on top of that the kitchen was is probably the cleanest of the food court, something to be very proud of in this restaurant business! Will come back to try other items on the menu.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM-wVJO1_3TV0Tv3jtEGK81kp3EofARuLrvSV4r&fid=0x0:0xa294bdbddd105db6"],"When":"2024-2-29"},{"Name":"Delwin Tan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIyLIbxl3BJt2gOJQPp7WrSxwN1pDT08k_u0WCg3VLt8LjxjQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I usually hit up this food court for something else, but I’ve always been curious about this stall since I’m a big fan of dosai.

Super glad I finally gave it a try today. Ordered the onion potato dosa and was kinda worried it wouldn’t fill me up since I usually need a good-sized portion. Happy to report that the portion was spot on, and they didn’t skimp on the onion and potato, which really made the dish. I’m hoping they keep the portions and fillings generous even as they get more popular, ‘cause it’s part of what made it so good.

The chutneys they served— one coconut and the other tomato ginger—were both killer, and I didn’t leave a drop. Plus, it came with this sambar lentil and veggie soup on the side that was the perfect cap to the meal.

They even threw in 2 napkins, which I really appreciated since I ended up using both! Definitely coming back and telling my friends about this place 💯.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMe-LFG7h3bXAKEr9xgvfWsb79gIMwLvNn9CWHj&fid=0x0:0xa294bdbddd105db6"],"When":"2024-3-9"},{"Name":"CHHAVI VERMA","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKdw4FcCl6_OEFKvnlOn3MBE1LOnnJfyRu1VkXzfRzzlZXglg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hidden Gem - Dosa place in Coquitlam!!
Hands down the best dosa I had in Vancouver. Amazing service and greetings at the counter.
Delicious food & a must try.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOUvWApnNPy4CpzSLB1S_QpSssRjMbElbB_oP4a&fid=0x0:0xa294bdbddd105db6"],"When":"2024-5-7"},{"Name":"Prabhat S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJU26Mv7wrF_kHRTI1pZUcReR7O4NpknuGlRvECZ5U9FquW=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"This is the first visit I had. I would say this is a good place to have a biryani experience for those who like a different flavor. They serve Papad and boiled egg which is an exceptional service. Neat and clean, quick service, the portion was just enough for 2. spice level, salt level are good !, OIL is not good quality, need to improve the oil type and reduce the quantity of oil being used for such small portions. price is higher, it's not a reasonable price I would guess 13 $ is reasonable rate for that. For occasional dinners the price and place shouldn't be hitch.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN06dLvVO7tpIP2nl3Kl5ihXNOl_FGjLqHnKcc&fid=0x0:0xa294bdbddd105db6"],"When":"2023-5-10"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Jessameen Dela Peña","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX9mRpmL8-ZJUG7UPFcnsjzRdxjABif-MswbO1rxgJyyWfns8Jd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We finally discovered the best KBBQ in Coquitlam at Galbi! After trying several spots, this is the only place that truly got my partner excited about KBBQ. What sets Galbi apart is their focus on the quality of the meat rather than just the side dishes—a huge plus in our book.

They handled our reservation quickly, and we were fortunate to snag a table before it got really busy. While the space is a bit cozy, the meal was absolutely fantastic. The marinated beef short ribs were so irresistible that we ended up ordering extra.

We were expecting the bill to be around $200, but were pleasantly surprised when it came out $60 cheaper—even with the tip included. I’m definitely bringing my friends here next time. Can’t wait to come back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOtXU7g1Mdshu7JLv6kgKpUYZu5LSk1yfwe--bA&fid=0x0:0x3acdae584ead321a"],"When":"2024-8-24"},{"Name":"Suzanne Y","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVA92S6YKukSMnbRa5H7tG8jeNNTYeIVRPnSfmNiCXXXyAauEzN0A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Came here on a Thursday evening and thankfully we came early! The place filled up pretty quickly around 7pm. We ordered the fresh beef ribs, pork jowl, and pork belly with skin on (thick cut). Prices are reasonable for the quality of meat and quantity (each portion is by weight). I found the soybean paste soup very salty, but once diluted it was quite tasty! Enjoyed the salad and sides, but they charge for extra side dishes and restrict you to 3 pieces of romaine lettuce per meat order (which seems a bit stingy for a small side item). There was also dirt on the lettuce, which they washed off and returned to us... Rice is ordered on the side for $2 each.

Overall a clean storefront with friendly staff, fresh quality ingredients, and a fun no-frills kbbq experience! We spent around $100 for 3 people.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMolYBIiES1jj5IW8KrAnPCgFR-qT5oYoTiMa20&fid=0x0:0x3acdae584ead321a"],"When":"2023-11-3"},{"Name":"MAY 매이 Elford","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUxJVIiA7BVVmzUGqT6sRzP7-hCdYJttIOnYMeIvWOWZPmq7cr7=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A Saturday evening out with my friends. 4 of us ended up at Galbi. We ordered the pork belly with skin on, Galbi, and the cold noodle. Everything was delicious… the bean paste soup was so yummy.
They gave us side dishes, but to add more, there is an extra fee.
Service was great and there have a lot of parking. Definitely worth going!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOiNt4K-oH50HrFkg3LuUdGSxwY6y2kJMYXzNyD&fid=0x0:0x3acdae584ead321a"],"When":"2023-4-28"},{"Name":"Ananda Enkhtur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVkkmVVa6j0bCuttopPInRikVrpr7LXYSHoZtWk3dhng__J_lZi=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Tried this place the other day and it was pretty good! Not many items on the menu that you can choose from but overall the taste was delicious. Especially the red bean soup and the corn cheese was so good. Like many Korean restaurants there are variety of side dishes that come with the meal and the portions for each one was generous too! Would recommend to come as a big group tho!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOJ-sZtMzSf8pafLObOPwMYuYYoPalr6VIO6Vud&fid=0x0:0x3acdae584ead321a"],"When":"2024-2-20"},{"Name":"Nat A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWnjKr4KNFAObzj2bIvH9BRInxwKsSvEg1PM25bKfvhxtWZTWHoog=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Tried this place out for the first time. We had the marinated beef and pork short ribs. The beef was tasty but the pork was just okay. I had a few pieces of the beef that were hard and fatty. The portion size for the meat was average. The soup appetizer, kimchi, and pickled raddish were good. They provided a pitcher of water, no complimentary tea offered.

The selection on the menu is minimal.

Service was average. We had to wave over to the waiters every time we needed something. They did not come up to us and ask how things were after they gave us our food.

Overall, the food was decent but I wouldn't come back when there are other Korean BBQ restaurants with more selection.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPb8x1RQYXa6xENsHZCT5yvKAqEx9VI05wYGrBK&fid=0x0:0x3acdae584ead321a"],"When":"2022-12-11"},{"Name":"Molly","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLxkBBeHfwDYZEHKteGzubNOwVdGJVg2Kn4pysUcR2QBA2w0w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Jessi was my server tonight she was very friendly and attentive. 5 stars for my experience. Food was great. The free soup was so good I purchased another one! They didn't seem to have the salt soya sauce dip tray that you get in other places. Maybe you have to ask for it? I don't care for it I don't add extra stuff to my meat. I got the short ribs and the prime beef so good!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"S C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVumoVlQ2Nr7knqW9lb01ghVZite-FLKkjhE2dVSofQsuYeSfVW=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Galbi is my best place for Korean BBQ in Vancouver. The meats were fresh, tender and nicely marbled also marinated short ribs were well seasoned. Excellent service and reasonable price. I usually visit 1-2times a week. Try this place if you are meat lover!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO4RXzzsu5isoPwissTXgbEx26fjigui8uk6uai&fid=0x0:0x3acdae584ead321a"],"When":"2023-2-28"},{"Name":"Hwa D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUwQyjGi41SNIX6tVkw-8BfQdSHpbL_wDTFcZShwlM2dHZ3e1AW_w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently visited this restaurant and was thoroughly impressed. The marinated beef short ribs were absolutely delicious.
What made the experience even more enjoyable was the exceptional service. The staff were incredibly friendly and attentive, ensuring that our dining experience was delightful from start to finish. I highly recommend this restaurant","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOklX-zzm88iNsKQfia31-tC_DHWRFqVfVdVqKY&fid=0x0:0x3acdae584ead321a"],"When":"2024-3-17"}]

Our server was super sweet and attentive which made our visit so much better.

Overall experience would be 10/10 for me!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOakjAB5jR58pXpBR9mypeOxWq3xrV4ZO5Z-Asi&fid=0x0:0x15802ca10afa6683"],"When":"2024-7-13"},{"Name":"Byung Gab Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWN7CV-kMCm2w9BNLrj2pNfHwejZE1A5pRZgQwny7Y1RJNutpzL=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We Played Yonsei University : Korea University
OB team at Canustie Golf course ⛳️, After
CM Chicken Coquitlam Centre for dinner.
We ordered for dinner Garlic Spicy Chicken,
Snow Onion Chicken Boneless &Snowcheese French  Fries..Beer's and Others.
Very delicious and economy price
Please refer 9 photos","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPPTmIdyqI1jvDWOgVnQIrTUsPL3fLscFb2kZeZ&fid=0x0:0x15802ca10afa6683"],"When":"2024-9-15"},{"Name":"mostafa akbari","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXQ_bqE7-amFiTG-vBEnmJDI06E0ke8OBen6cVHENKq5-RlKDcc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Overall, we had a good experience at this restaurant. Our server was very friendly and did her best to provide us with all the information we needed. We ordered two dishes—one was a squid dish, but it seemed undercooked and lacked spice. So, if you’re not familiar with Korean cuisine, make sure to ask about the menu items. On a positive note, the chicken portion was really generous!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNSmneURZe-m3d3VZClXuv8OQWBVJvB5XABAzgM&fid=0x0:0x15802ca10afa6683"],"When":"2024-6-22"},{"Name":"J C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVRid-486EHf3vFFlqzxc7hc71kbL9n1FDLFiUelrs10b7uY4If=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Take out only for us original boneless.  It was nice and crunchy but was too hungry to notice if it actually had meat or mostly batter!  They were very busy due to a large group.  Despite that waitress was awesome and order came as promised within 15 min.  Will go back again","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOOz8lYR0xwnpXPXCRNQ31PlWvCyDwt2uWh4ert&fid=0x0:0x15802ca10afa6683"],"When":"2024-5-12"},{"Name":"Jeffrey Sung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI0YkwBbHy0GuRP2WnjEAvBQASVPftDGOH3KQfFCO2eDwSARg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Interior is clean, staff was great and the food was delicious! Oden soup was heartwarming for the rainy day and the snow fries were crispy and cheesy. The fried chicken was amazing! I had Red Hot Pepper Chicken which was spicy, juicy and, crispy and the Bacon Spinach Chicken (an odd combo, I thought, but it was delicious!!!)

They have other flavours like Snow Onion, Soy Garlic, Green onion, and etc. So, I’ll definitely be back to try those dishes as well. My time here has aroused my curiosity to try the rest of the menu at this rising establishment, Highly highly recommend!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN31U2TRK0VsRts81BDX793YX1YTOmVOwuVVfuf&fid=0x0:0x15802ca10afa6683"],"When":"2023-10-25"},{"Name":"Jason Park","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMhOEKKHXAe86LaxehFj_x7OVFNVhnJ9HjVRBWt_-JiYzZSRxP=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent fried chicken, probably one of the best ones in Coquitlam.

Great fried chicken I would recommend to my friends.
The fries were on the house as the opening promo and it was pretty good as well.

Great portion, reasonable price.
I'd usually just get the original and make it large to share between 2-3 people.

Keep up with the quality and I'll be a long time regular for sure.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOJ0jChP4mCoDEU5VdDHk5TJXAr2H9gQSfZP-GL&fid=0x0:0x15802ca10afa6683"],"When":"2023-11-15"}]

[{"Name":"Avis Woo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXh4Pb-SJt2DTMUggN2-tIRxEo8pAErRU5SI_TxM4gC-gvdVBym=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great place for family brunch and dinner! Dishes all come in n big portion! Coffee refilled unlimited times! Tables and environment is hygienic and seating quite spacious and comfortable even for senior citizen with backache like me. Toilet is clean! Waiter and waitress crew are all very nice and professional too! Love this restaurant very much❤️❤️❤️❤️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPza0ew2GjCDcnw3yaVoLhK8iMmk0FFxjlS2rw5&fid=0x0:0x1d1cd1ad544caa40"],"When":"2024-8-10"},{"Name":"Kai-Chun Lin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUjTiDNcTKlmyRrDWdGPFt530dlO3QJbviz_GUObBc3bQ0rNmRp=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is one of my favorite restaurants in Coquitlam as it's a place where I'm guaranteed to have a good time.

Food - the food isn't the most amazing thing I've ever tasted, BUT every single one that I've tried was at least good or better. There's basically no bad choice in the menu.
Service/atmosphere - the seats are spacious and comfortable, the waitresses are always friendly (even more so to kids!), we never had to wait too long for our food... it's just a great experience all around.
Price - with the above points, it would've already been one of my restaurants of choice, but then they went ahead and kept the price reasonable and that just seals the deal for me.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN90L9zlD4vK0EDnXwB3NnlbNYPDfIUE5NcHqHh&fid=0x0:0x1d1cd1ad544caa40"],"When":"2024-9-22"},{"Name":"Omid Dadgari","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWXY5oTTgmTf1M1XQYNbrrLX-SdVGDzUB3Iw3aDSyAgQLf2_BwYgw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I visited Coquitlam Grill for breakfast today and ordered Steak and eggs. The overall quality of the ingredients was very good. However, I ordered my steak medium, but it arrived well-done. Despite this, the quality was still good. The quantity of the food was very generous, offering great value for the price. It made me full, even though I hadn't eaten dinner or supper yesterday. The servers were attentive and friendly. The atmosphere was typical of a North American restaurant and quite enjoyable. Overall, a decent experience with room for improvement on the steak preparation."","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNT61QeH3ufJtT_GqPt1Sg0rufpTlP24BeUhlEu&fid=0x0:0x1d1cd1ad544caa40"],"When":"2024-7-9"},{"Name":"Julie B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW4pd43YT5KSqkORSPaVbra7_KcodZ1kkwID5yaolZD_WuCOEiQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What an amazing restaurant. We went just after noon on a Sunday only waited a few minutes and were seated. The place was packed. Everyone thoroughly enjoyed their meals and beverages.
Food was Ultimate Omelet
Mexican Pulled Pork Hash
Tex Mex Omelet
Eggs Haida Benny
Drinks were margarita, mimosas and a Ceasar.
The service was fantastic and Susan was amazing.
Everyone raved about their dishes and everyone cleaned their plated and both styles of harsh browns by far were the best we have ever had.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNatRTF11J76msxdL31ksun0mlD6h6LFwhaBmNW&fid=0x0:0x1d1cd1ad544caa40"],"When":"2024-7-30"},{"Name":"Thomas Chen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUITuDRjw9J9Us45xAUXKSfp8lG2sJ2s04TW_lNAi_G6a5d62ur=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Just came here for a dinner. Thought it was good overall. Satisfactory but not amazing. I had the steak and it was cooked nicely. I wouldn’t rush back because the value isn’t very good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOJH7QVel_maomATRS9LUNPh_6vm10Rj-xcyjR2&fid=0x0:0x1d1cd1ad544caa40"],"When":"2024-8-19"},{"Name":"Rakin Hassan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXandqMb5qdp3U7pCkKHH5i5AInuGc7KeC3c0mJR9W6MOUUvQAlEw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Don't order the turkey dinner if you like flavor. Its all just a big mush. If there was a physical representation of the emission "sadness" this would be it.

Ps had a taste of my friends burger and it was one of the best ive had. So Im sure their other items on the menu must be good, just not the turkey dinner.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOqodY3fX-WlUgRDwc2Piqi1n1ENVZQ-jAmw5hR&fid=0x0:0x1d1cd1ad544caa40"],"When":"2024-12-2"},{"Name":"Gaelen Norman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXBHJXfwZ66Qec82NI1asE8mxzV5EwKVb0vYtF7rcjFlBcha36q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It's exactly what you expect for a little greasy spoon. The place’s ambience is a bit fast-foody, but they don’t lack in quality of food and effort in service! A gem in Coquitlam 😊😊😊","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO1UCLuJHgTXw-8GkzRrLo28YuQXJMxLzAyuFWH&fid=0x0:0x66fc3602c0cc67ed"],"When":"2024-12-19"},{"Name":"Angus Hardy-Francis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXOtcmYFtll6p-kcABiTyaSvlUBcLetlTn7Oc1ghrcT_-ZvyqXKtQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really tasty. Got the Chicken Katsu U.B.B and the broth was so flavourful. One of the best Ramen places in Coquitlam hands down. Would definitely recommend!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOehz3imBdiTzWxuzqvlxnkhc1wGK3AzUJXvEl6&fid=0x0:0x66fc3602c0cc67ed"],"When":"2024-11-3"},{"Name":"Allen Lau","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUgT6c216gR4aXOZdp51tQMw3SUSSLvDCBkRg7H0SzEcFVDKJU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We had a good time here, broth was rich and delicious. Service was quick and efficient as you would expect.  Served was attentive and courteous!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN9oKhWjY86cmXTrWKTbI47nPnGHGbsDpa9ELzG&fid=0x0:0x66fc3602c0cc67ed"],"When":"2024-11-13"},{"Name":"Jessy J","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLHNRFw0Z_JgaU0TxGr1Pv5X-w9V6JzR0bnCuTDlGr_7pfsbx_k=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Our first visit to this ramen noodle restaurant with the family was delightful! The atmosphere is spacious and welcoming, and even though we had to wait briefly, it was only about 5 minutes, which was very acceptable. The service was excellent, with the staff bringing out kids' utensils right away, which we appreciated.

The highlight of the meal was definitely the noodle soup. The broth was creamy with a distinct bonito fish flavor, making it a unique take on our ramen. We've never experienced a creamy base with shoyu before, so it was quite interesting.

Their Gomae was quite tasty. Instead of using spinach and peanut sauce, they used Choy Sum with sesame paste sauce.

The only minor drawback was the soft-boiled egg, which was slightly overcooked.

Overall, the service was up to par and we had a great experience. We'll definitely be back to try more of their dishes!" the family was delightful! The atmosphere is spacious and welcoming, and even though we had to wait briefly, it was only about 5 minutes, which was very acceptable. The service was excellent, with the staff bringing out kids' utensils right away, which we appreciated.

The highlight of the meal was definitely the noodle soup. The broth was creamy with a distinct bonito fish flavor, making it a unique take on shoyu ramen. We've never experienced a creamy base with shoyu before, so it was quite interesting. The only minor drawback was the soft-boiled egg, which was slightly overcooked.

Overall, the service was up to par and we had a great experience. We'll definitely be back to try more of their dishes!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPovmOXlxrn71FdseJvAjANGOudb6lv_Ph6vheL&fid=0x0:0x66fc3602c0cc67ed"],"When":"2024-4-20"},{"Name":"melissa choi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKPYCcnHjMsXKLjSAR5QRLFI-pwNjpHDAAO3nrNqEuOCcrf9A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I came alone. there were maybe 4 tables with people seated and already eating. One other guest came after me. It took forever them to ask for my order. They got the other table before i did. They never checked up on me after placing my food after me. They were not attentive. Food was okay. Wasn’t amazed by it though. Will not be returning. Overall atmosphere was clean and calming. I personally will not be returning.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOzaN_LsU9Kwak7qgzrRh5nUJIoBMK7KF226Z2f&fid=0x0:0x66fc3602c0cc67ed"],"When":"2024-9-27"},{"Name":"Chi Hsi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWcBbxQUmUDBINWW8gpiVBRZkPGVAvZUVKaxZbYRVQUj9Y0ACg0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We came here with our preschooler on a Thursday night at 6pm and was seated immediately. The service was great and quick in response when we raised our hand when we needed anything. They brought the kids utensils, scissors, bowl and cup right away.

I ordered the U. B. B. extra to share with my preschooler. Rich, flavourful, and creamy broth which I found a bit too salty for my liking. I was able to finish the end of the broth with the extra bowl of free rice. My husband doesn't finish the broth whenever we have ramen so it seemed a shame to dump it. We were able to get a to-go container for his remaining broth.

They also have an universal washroom for handicap and any gender so it was easier for my preschooler to reach the sink to wash her hands or go with my husband instead.

We'd recommend this place for families for sure!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOMye_HMVe1iRiTuUeVDUU-tRMeahxBkdlzSUbA&fid=0x0:0x66fc3602c0cc67ed"],"When":"2024-9-13"},{"Name":"Munchica","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbQ6ACs51IPQJlRLrmnunOErED8bimOf5-y1uov4EWpuZvjQQjrA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Delicious ramen with splendid, rich and creamy broth. Tried the black tan tan men which came with a bowl of rice and the flavours were great. The black sesame ground pork was both sweet and salty and went very well with the rice. The U.B.B. Extra ramen came with thick noodles that had great texture and the broth was so rich and complex. The service was great and the place was clean. Solid and satisfying ramen place. There are also complimentary sesame seed and chili powder toppings on each table.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMOZzYuriQu4IYkOTSb_x2nmC5vxcMD9MWz02sD&fid=0x0:0x66fc3602c0cc67ed"],"When":"2024-3-25"},{"Name":"Megan H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIku9KV44jqgA8L-HCiMZoBBhlSnQF2rqxPqsFbb_vW5iUOog=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Thank you for great experience! :D
Vegetarian ramen coconut soup is new to me it was good.
We loved salt and seaweed sause on table for changing it soup own flavor.
Garlic add on was bit over cooked taste was bitter.. more soft is better.","Images":null,"When":""}]

Came here for lunch, happy hour and dinner! The food here is amazing! All the food is really good and the lunch sets were perfect if you cannot decide what to get as it comes with a bunch of really tasty sides! Happy hour is great value! Service is amazing as always! Definitely better than their original Austin location!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOMZrgb8nkBfx3q9a6LLAn4a33kCVc8ylvJ4WPY&fid=0x0:0x7c8e5688b857cfe7"],"When":"2024-12-3"},{"Name":"I","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLIV6jvas1B0Z6XQk1R-VtBTSMtaFi_LbOwHskdbQ4kyPutgw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"a fantastic spot for authentic and affordable Italian food! I tried their linguine soul bianco, and it was absolutely delicious-perfectly cooked pasta with a generous portion of fresh shrimp and scallops. The garlic bread was the perfect complement, crisp and buttery.
The service was friendly and quick, even though the restaurant was quite busy. The cozy and casual atmosphere made it a great place to enjoy a relaxed meal with friends.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMpsq4YTu4ivkuGsCDt4D3kpUni4tLXnJJTZDv6&fid=0x0:0x7c8e5688b857cfe7"],"When":"2024-12-10"},{"Name":"Tim Cho","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVlAeRGbdix5pzSJ294H4Xr78Nd64DzEa5cdHefPrVDxRdp4rOfSg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an incredible dining experience at Jimoco! The seafood risotto and truffle fries I ordered were absolutely delicious – packed with flavor and cooked to perfection. A special shoutout to the manager, Jessica, for her outstanding service. She was attentive, friendly, and made sure everything was perfect. I left with a great impression of the food and service and will definitely be coming back again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNC3tBpJxJuqxwHlK8VADsEVUfJZr1UY8lxk1__&fid=0x0:0x7c8e5688b857cfe7"],"When":"2024-10-13"},{"Name":"Mei Louis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJgXRRaGeGHZwDQ3Cd4BP54rgwmhE9FWdhKccUqwHk97sb73g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cozy interior with warm lighting. We ordered seafood linguine and shrimp saffron spaghetti. Seafood linguine was so tasty.  Shrimp saffron spaghetti was mild and creamy but delicious.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMU2BuJDja3AMX8kL_4BWSstCTPxry1q6mUZlJF&fid=0x0:0x7c8e5688b857cfe7"],"When":"2024-12-2"},{"Name":"Toyomi Ito","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWnHT9hDBL07ssEAY0cDHGtuqcXk582q7qgw7ilC32d_pL0EQaF=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is place is a gem! Loved everything from service, decor, and atmosphere to the food 😍
Portions were reasonable as well as the price, especially their lunch menu! Each dish was flavorful and was not overpowering or over salty.
I felt welcomed and at east with their friendly and genuine service and attitude.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNpkF0_ft2xTh9nJfLPKphM7a228eRGRU-qC_s4&fid=0x0:0x7c8e5688b857cfe7"],"When":"2024-8-31"},{"Name":"Michael Fierro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXGxPiXz4VjAC2xy7rVHkMhqRHuzRHqAbOMz5r7KH0luLvvpF8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"From the moment I stepped into this restaurant every detail—from the ambient lighting to the attentive service—set the stage for a meal I’ll be dreaming about for years.

I started with the truffle fries. Oh. My. Goodness. These weren’t just fries—they were a transcendental experience. Golden, crispy, and kissed by the divine essence of truffle oil, they practically melted in my mouth. Each fry was a little piece of heaven, perfectly seasoned and dangerously addictive.

Then came the seafood risotto, and let me tell you, it was nothing short of perfection. Each grain of rice was tender, infused with a rich, oceanic symphony of flavors. The seafood? Plump, fresh, and cooked to absolute perfection—like it had been caught that very morning. Every bite was a revelation, a crescendo of tastes that danced on my palate.

And then came the pièce de résistance: the blueberry cheesecake. If angels bake, this is what their desserts taste like. The cheesecake was impossibly creamy, with a luscious texture that felt like silk on my tongue. The blueberries, bursting with freshness, added a vibrant sweetness that complemented the tangy richness of the cake. It wasn’t just a dessert—it was a masterpiece.

I can’t recommend this restaurant enough. Every dish was a love letter to flavor, every bite a testament to culinary brilliance. If you haven’t been yet, drop everything and go—you’re in for the meal of a lifetime!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM58BQjrKJtJ5ufQrfKYQ6aYKuCmRpHzR64I1YM&fid=0x0:0x7c8e5688b857cfe7"],"When":"2024-11-17"},{"Name":"Serena Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV9dCXJiXkT2Yw03SJdaNBPt4M_g0YqE6WK4iltbPxjJjyx6Z3vBw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A cozy, peaceful restaurant with a lovely atmosphere! The pasta and risotto were amazing, especially the seafood risotto and mushroom risotto, which were outstanding! The friendly staff made the whole experience even better.✨🎄","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN7K-XPHQAfDvqnQVfPaCONvx1yxJpMFT68uVhh&fid=0x0:0x7c8e5688b857cfe7"],"When":"2024-12-8"},{"Name":"Daiane zhang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXJbTyILgsCGvUsIB6Mf4Jq2jitpvq5ZkuY2CWHmnknophF745t=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We went there for lunch on a Sunday and It's safe to say we'll definitely be going back because we fell in love with it. The staff are super friendly and professional.  The food has great quality and amazing taste. The restaurant has a cute, bright atmosphere. And the best part is it's quite affordable. We had the lunch box and it had little bits of everything.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOVhgAYwoXb6cpGVF1HsHLb4m1MSUKG3UaP8cZo&fid=0x0:0x7c8e5688b857cfe7"],"When":"2024-6-15"}]
