[{"Name":"Neda G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXcXBADLi2CMhn5hf9f-JdbOlYYM_LHhdjb9JmX03VjxzMph4k=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The reviews are legit! This place is a hidden gem. We had a lovely breakfast with my kids, mom and husband. The service was good despite only one person working, she did awesome and they were very respectful of my daughter's allergies.

More importantly, the FOOD was AMAZING!!! Crispy gorgeous potatoes, really yummy pancake and waffles and great coffee. Will absolutely go back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMZm2JrIJBpWvMNrTgyP1KWz2ol7OXkf14yCZLp&fid=0x0:0xde5d02ec9b39e76b"],"When":"2024-8-23"},{"Name":"Cherilyn Morris","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIFSsTxkRHOvnhVnL21RRcRzjanEDvQ_-BctHEQEFo9i_I6jA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We ordered via a delivery service and were very pleased with the food from PK's Diner. We gave a 5 for atmosphere as we have read reviews stating how comfortable the diner is and therefore had to give a 5 for that reason. We had the Bacon Cheeseburger and Clubhouse sandwich. Both were delicious. My husband said that the burger is one of the best that he has had. The burger was loaded with tomatoes, bacon and onions and he really liked the burger sauce that came with it as well. The bacon was thick and my husband said that the caramelized onions made the burger. I also found my Clubhouse to have been very good also with thick bacon, ham, and a generous amount of grilled chicken. The fries were crispy and the picture with the Clubhouse did not have all the fries that came with the order. We both have left overs for tomorrow. We are always cautiously optimistic when ordering home delivery due to the food not being fresh out of the kitchen. Well, we were so pleased with our meals and will definitely be ordering again. We are looking forward to trying out more items on the menu. Thank you so much PK's.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOLTqRnbF0525X_IBQ69XBMilRq6EUKYroOWi1f&fid=0x0:0xde5d02ec9b39e76b"],"When":"2024-11-3"},{"Name":"Kim Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIR3fyXypuJm8ILEdOCVPODC97_SULpf89BUpmEUxYYnr0uBA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Breakfast tasted great. I had the smoked duck benedict - delicious, tender duck meat. Fluffy pancakes.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNQQTCyuOJoSGd_q3QxCrjr06WtsiKzh8wWmmkI&fid=0x0:0xde5d02ec9b39e76b"],"When":"2024-12-24"},{"Name":"Khwanravee Phajum","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI6GF6hlgxdCI-il-sbuGK3OWdGWyHB-PRNuj8HpNLtL-GTcQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We love PK Cafe’!!! The service is excellent, super friendly staff. Their breakfast menu is almost like desserts, especially waffles and French toasts are unbelievable delicious, moist and crispy at the same time! I love my chicken lemongrass, so tender and flavourful. We can’t wait to try all of their dishes. To add to how wonderful this place is…the price is so affordable!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNfrFZiCKbIhIzaUyEMRXaImFdwP6Ap1U7eiGgh&fid=0x0:0xde5d02ec9b39e76b"],"When":"2024-4-8"},{"Name":"Deborah H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIsXwwC3s9WyQKJ7Zs95PXuhLbAGHn9sk0S1KGXgVkYpWzFwg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What a nice surprise to find this great brunch place! Situated in an unassuming small neighbourhood plaza, PKs Cafe is a very clean cafe with a perfect selection of choices on the menu. We have been here a few times and it is always topnotch and tasty whether its breakfast or burgers. Their breakfast potatoes wedges and fries are just the right crispiness. Coming back to try their sandwiches next! Service is always friendly and love the attentive coffee refills.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP30Phpcy40cKMXuRkCo3k4xseN5ZBjAvd2aWS7&fid=0x0:0xde5d02ec9b39e76b"],"When":"2023-11-18"},{"Name":"Dariia Druzkina","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK1HtrODnJhuv0fWVXjF7xNuGcR7qBMJc7wC52gLfs1dI0JGA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It is a very cute cafe with big portions and amazing staff. The food was delicious and the menu has great options.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP3kHOFd3zoIPRpic-fVDR1pTnhEO9xOU7hJ5GR&fid=0x0:0xde5d02ec9b39e76b"],"When":"2024-9-3"},{"Name":"Nick Tang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVQkP22OPLsbOln7vAD-ae1LRI9zUvNKoMyd5lAIDRgo7JO2KRe=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"HOLY!!! The Smoked Duck Benny was deliciously savoury without compromising too salty/saucy! The lemon truffle had a  crunchy exterior and seasoned perfectly. I ate it so fast that I forgot to take a pic!

The Banana Almond French toast was soooo soft, light and not overly sweet. Most places miss the mark by making them way too sweet (sickening even), but this place made what I can only describe as a fluffy cloud ☁️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMT2ii7umzJELBTgDbzMF4sQHmn-zKGU2LMv4hU&fid=0x0:0xde5d02ec9b39e76b"],"When":"2024-3-9"},{"Name":"Jimmy Huang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVmaQe2WLp7herqsSS6Qbb3TdkPTjO2rKeO4tgMEL6Gag0kIT7k=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sensational breakfast. They served great food with flexible options. The meal was filling. They had adequate condiments. They also make delicious soup. The food is cooked perfectly, therefore, it was a flawless execution. It’s definitely worth its rating, and I would highly recommend eating here.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNfMUQfP_csOgdrXJr2gBcHppoITpsoZIHVL0fd&fid=0x0:0xde5d02ec9b39e76b"],"When":"2023-7-30"}]

Lots of options on the menu too","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPullyZx7AqqrjCoCtY-kUc2duamE-y9zLBYWkt&fid=0x0:0xfe535cce35f49e37"],"When":"2024-9-30"},{"Name":"Saeid MJ","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXcewSnJcAhACCkEWKUQGjPaBy78cIOsSGEe0B0nR_ARAnMiJU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Ordered Koubideh and lamb shank, it was good but lamb taste could be better, needs to have more flavor. Also the Dough was really tasty.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOukA4ha22SFPQ6FAbBVu7NKkVDbpC6zgLzLmQN&fid=0x0:0xfe535cce35f49e37"],"When":"2024-10-26"},{"Name":"abas jalili","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU5-JtiEFM0TKssaNHVpKBJWLNTuIm9OgdKbnu5pCDZzBmdt4ra=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"We ordered lamb muscle. The behavior of the staff was very friendly and polite, thank you. But the taste of the food was not great and it was average. If you are craving funny and excellent food, this place is not recommended for lamb muscle. Of course, the prices were very reasonable, but with payment  For five dollars more, you can have a much tastier meal elsewhere","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ridhwaan Murad","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXZ01NrIJq-bXx2O0TQQ_Nlv3d1BmJDfMG1zJNirVKOrJxl9RtiBQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The restaurant is at its name suggests “Grab and Go” so order and pickup.

It is recommended to order before picking up as you will have a slight wait if you walk in and order.

The food has been great each time I ordered. Portion sizes are not bad and the food is always fresh.

Lots of parking available outside and at times they can get busy.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Candice C.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJwFBBjzDK0K147Ahvw56fgZp0Wzk8W8u0zo_aJQ425Hu_MYA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Take out restaurant, the place appears clean and tidy. The staff are welcoming and friendly. Had the beef kebob small platter and that was more than enough. Lots of options.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOshxNmRcFxtlY7YaQH-8G5BG1zitn4SatKU0Pb&fid=0x0:0xfe535cce35f49e37"],"When":"2024-5-14"},{"Name":"Reza Az","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV8VOIYGmudwFgomghjsI628UIOyauu99PTTRqvMp19GbPgNp4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Grab and go Coquitlam is an unforgettable experience! From the moment I walked in, I was greeted with warm hospitality that made me feel right at home. The ambiance was cozy and authentic, transporting me straight to Iran.
The food was absolutely incredible. Every dish was bursting with rich, authentic flavors, showcasing the true essence of Iranian cuisine.
Whether you’re familiar with Iranian food or trying it for the first time, I highly recommend Grab and go Coquitlam for an authentic and delicious culinary journey. I’ll definitely be returning soon!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Reza Beik","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWAk5FOTBi4eYl4XJK_pY6EefWdKrL0UdJY6hMoW801u1k_XvKn=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I called and ordered 45 minutes before the scheduled pickup time, and the person on the phone assured me that the food would be ready on time. However, for the third time in the last two months, I had to wait an additional 15 to 20 minutes at the restaurant to pick up my order. I understand that they are busy and that it may take longer for orders to be prepared, but when a customer orders ahead, it's because they don't want to wait—they want to pick up their order and go.

The restaurant should ensure that they provide customers with an accurate pickup time. If you're busy and the order can't be ready in less than an hour, just let the customer know. But most importantly, make sure that when the customer arrives, the order is ready and properly packed.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Sandra Tran Do","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV9l6s1YZWB64Ki1thgUudvXKddmLpHe47fEzkyE5Wrayj1VfeG=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"This is a great cozy mom and pops restaurant. it is Italian and Korean fusion. The service here is so good, food was comfort food, it wasn’t bad but it wasn’t the best Italian I have had. Would come back tho","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNl3P0sP9BMO8A7fcAP--OVyqDEiLIOYcwNgSXd&fid=0x0:0xae2442bcec231118"],"When":"2024-12-21"},{"Name":"Darian Yee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVa9tIQQ79AzRLuXQPjOsHXO8XmdfzgC67OKlKFj-Hw13RvVc0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I don’t give many five star reviews, and I hope no one sees this one, because I don’t want my favourite restaurant becoming too busy! The prices are LOW, all plates are around $16. Portion sizes are LARGE, and the food is delicious! We always being left overs home.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO3YidPIFJjE_yahI6LsLC9tA7AzaFHQjR3lrXd&fid=0x0:0xae2442bcec231118"],"When":"2024-11-2"},{"Name":"jen h","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUhCIsdNpI0zn0ln1R2W8y6FEnO7Rpwo3p2N6L3S94WtNoyzHf7=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Truly is a nostalgic joint as I used to go here during high school times. It used to be infamous for their buy two get one free pasta dishes but I believe that deal is no longer available. Regardless of which, they have some great pasta dishes, and are a Korean Italian fusion. You can also adjust spice level if available! They take reservations which is nice for a larger group. Parking is abysmal in that location, but that isn’t their fault. Usually, I just find parking in the back or on side streets. Most pasta dishes are between $16-$20 and have quite hearty portion and you also get a slice of garlic bread for free. Staff is friendly and usually run by one person but very efficiently.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO9jwHT3ikVSlmyrS_uHwj81dsEC0JrFYYYHMr-&fid=0x0:0xae2442bcec231118"],"When":"2024-9-6"},{"Name":"Kamil Chocimski","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJiqh1VSZRODqN-Djl6vCyrZVFOC1F520DSa-G8lhjPI6NkKSg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Ordered the Caprese salad and Linguine Seoul. The Salad had no Basil, but salad instead. The Mozzarella seams to be defrosted. It falls apart and it's grainy and mush. The tomato slices were very thick and were dry. No flavor. Disappointing.
The Linguine was different. Taste was good, especially the Clams. However I asked for Parmigiano I was given the powdered stuff and not fresh. Also the dish was in a very hot pan, and not a bowl. Got burned a bit. Be careful if you have fidgety hands or nerve damage.
I also had the $5 pink lemonade, which was just pure sugar. Had to squeeze my lemon garnish wedge and dunk it. It didn't help

Service was impeccable, food arrived quick and the server lady was friendly and very helpful. She deserves a raise.

Atmosphere was fine. I love little holes in the wall like this. The booth seat was comfortable. The service and seafood makes up, and I rate it 3 stars.

Pity, because I was looking forward to checking this place for a while. I grew up in Italy and was hopeful. However it's a miss.

Maybe other dishes are better

DO NOT RECOMMEND THE CAPRESE SALAD

I wanted to rate it 2 stars because the food was so disappointing, but despite the lack of fresh ingredients","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMGWAfrDYg0ryjkUfLpTX5Rjq44jLrPAuXDilwS&fid=0x0:0xae2442bcec231118"],"When":"2024-8-30"},{"Name":"Caroline *","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU8RSBvHYuwmws6j5XyqmPqw1TITZ2sRj-IIy6vhYkGJqRMUR96=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great little gem! I’ve never had a restaurant provide complimentary items, but the lovely server gave me and my friend complimentary garlic bread! ☺️ fabulous service. They are very polite and respectful. Often times, I get servers from different restaurants constantly checking up on me every 10 minutes and while I appreciate the effort to ensure we are taken care of, it can get a little uncomfortable. The server here was amazing. She gave us time to enjoy our food, and checked up on us once to ensure our needs were met. I can’t wait to come back here again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMl3LyC43s2HkW9spcy0e_cmopO2UBWWXdaJn1O&fid=0x0:0xae2442bcec231118"],"When":"2024-6-5"},{"Name":"Bianca Lok","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWLQf55yrLfuQpaVH5_PAPb-xLqdrIrBA83-7_og5_ndyF7MIm4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They have a good selection of dishes on their menu. Each of them look equally delicious. Been there for 2-3 times for lunch, food quality and deliciousness is consistent. Garlic bread is included which is a nice bonus. Portion is sized just enough. Pricing is reasonable and affordable. Otherwise, overall a good place to go if you are looking for decent pasta in the area.
In terms of service, servers do what they need to do and check in to make sure all is good.
It's a good atmosphere as it is never really busy during lunch time, so you can be seated immediately. Also relatively quiet.
The only thing not great is the parking. There is limited street parking, which is pretty much always occupied, but there is a small lot around the corner you can park at and then walk there.

10/10 would recommend to try at least once as their menu will have you going back to try their other food items","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMvJNi4mXTsFlxlVRLuvhRyzXJNyjs0dJLYCKCl&fid=0x0:0xae2442bcec231118"],"When":"2024-2-8"},{"Name":"Scott Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXHpW7vGME__Zs4wKjXR04Upnw88bkVVyz-H2288JsHocq9vI3r=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"It's a great Italian place that you should check out if you want to try out some authentic pasta and risotto dishes.

My personal favourite is the linguine soul that comes piping hot and spicy. I also enjoy their seafood risotto that almost comes out like a Spanish paella. The calamari wasn't as good as their pasta dish but still quite tasty.

The garlic bread is a nice little bonus but it's not as fresh as other places. The portions in general are decent and enough to fill you up.

If you're in the area, definitely check them out!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP_9EptdbJrgFN-WlFs_67YFedfhPPA-kuow85D&fid=0x0:0xae2442bcec231118"],"When":"2024-4-23"},{"Name":"Janice Ko","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUBZdze8bHRgeZWywjB9B830YGMgauY8dm-JU7cYQGuxIUbSKzC=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My friend brought me here for my birthday last month. The food was surprisingly fabulous. I ordered the seafood pasta, and it was delicious. The staff was very kind. I definitely will bring my family back again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOb1O18YubgKwd-WVhAWpPNuheH-vzqyQjFf9UF&fid=0x0:0xae2442bcec231118"],"When":"2024-5-28"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Dan Yang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWn20SO-hez6CdOPY0et6YJIfsXqZVK2JjuFROy8lc6ciazjVwLCQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We were staying at the Poco Inn for several days and we decided to try Izba. We had gone once last year for breakfast and wanted to try other things on the menu this time.

Food is absolutely amazing here. Service was excellent. We dined in and did take out a few times. We can't wait to come back to dine in when we visit BC again. The Pork Hock was amazing and I had to order it twice.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOkeN1QD0k77gLzuWNTChtSslZ8MsYKszhisKyY&fid=0x0:0xc4417d5c6f1e0d7d"],"When":"2024-9-19"},{"Name":"Ewa Jagla","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJt2Lx4cSyXVMUtHz5GqW2QX5giQiHT25H1LY2KPyEyH86PMQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delicious food freshly cooked from scratch, awesome atmosphere, superb customer service. The best place to have Christmas party as well as small gatherings.
Highly recommend 😊","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNhWkgmxDtyb6rEjrVCF6m82pasIw5N0DVS3SmQ&fid=0x0:0xc4417d5c6f1e0d7d"],"When":"2024-11-22"},{"Name":"Angela Jeffery","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUtGyld6d4wIU2Lb7oe7xsoiq4r77iaBdF6nkFQ8ek01eF1q7c=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We ate here as we stayed at the hotel for work, and I may come back to try some of the other menu items, based on the compliments of the others in the group.

The server was pleasant, as well as enthusiastic and knowledgeable about his menu recommendations. He was courteous about checking in and giving us space for our meeting.

The seating was comfortable, and even when it got busy at dinnertime, the ambient noise level still leant to easy conversation.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNqeLGhHKnP50PS663FCp_-g_jpbS2XjZyg9vTH&fid=0x0:0xc4417d5c6f1e0d7d"],"When":"2024-10-18"},{"Name":"Laura Thomas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXJ1taLWiLR5Kqy6TcBzB6ZWgyoj4UBO3ZptGvBaE7P-Aow2HBl=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We visited Izba last week and while it's a regular in our family gtg's I'd be remiss if I didn't brag about this terrific PoCo restaurant, with its cosy, modern, diner feel. They have booths and tables and they can easily accomodate large groups.

I am hearing sensitive and I find the noise volume in this restaurant to be perfect for my needs. I can hear my company's conversation, while not being too quiet. It's a great place to eat & catch up with family or friends.

While they have a terrific  breakfast & dinner menu, we usually visit at lunch. While we've tried many delicious items (shout out to their pierogies, schnitzel & cream of carrot soup!) we tend to have our favourites on their menu. Their chicken tacos are a huge hit with our family, although I lean towards their chicken club sandwich myself. Yum!  And for the late in the day breakfast lover amongst us, the brie & berries stuffed french toast is ah-mazing.

This is a great lunch spot with great service and great food. We love this local gem.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOR6It5KMGfKdXdWFlwEe9CsEMI6164BfCS_2qP&fid=0x0:0xc4417d5c6f1e0d7d"],"When":"2024-6-22"},{"Name":"K Kunz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVJritYkEeakN5S6DMeaooDNRMG4rg18kYdKvuJy7Hp_4TwqoG2=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It was our first time at Izba Bistro and we loved it! Our server Brenda was great! She was nice, attentive but also let us sit for awhile. Food was excellent. We started with the battered brie that came with fruit and a spicy berry compote. I then had the spinach and feta chicken and it was SO good. I loved that it came with spaghetti squash as well. You don't see that too often. My partner had the Vienna schnitzel with an egg on top. My partner being Austrian said it was different than what he's used to, but still enjoyed it. Lastly we had the sacher Austrian chocolate cake and that was also really fantastic! We definitely will be coming back soon!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPTHEmdhYUMMgbRx5jBghp47Wwy64aw3PImFw7B&fid=0x0:0xc4417d5c6f1e0d7d"],"When":"2024-4-22"},{"Name":"Varoujan Makdesian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKfL2mqaxtwIkiG0HlyGX_xrPtFgM36rEWRUZvaEgqUWz0Duw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"****AVOID AT ALL COSTS****
I was really excited to try Izba, given its reputation for authentic Polish cuisine, but unfortunately, my experience was far from what I had hoped for.

First, the service was extremely slow. Despite the restaurant not being very busy, our server seemed disinterested and hardly checked on us. We had to flag them down multiple times just to get basic things like water refills.

The food, which I was looking forward to the most, was underwhelming. The pierogi were bland, lacking any real flavor or seasoning, and the filling was far too dry. The borscht was greasy and tasted more like something that had been reheated multiple times rather than freshly made. It was also way too salty, which made it hard to finish.

The manager/owner, when I raised my concerns, was dismissive and unhelpful. Rather than apologizing or offering a solution, they seemed indifferent to our experience. It’s always frustrating when management doesn’t take feedback seriously, and it only made the situation worse. It felt like they weren’t interested in improving their service or maintaining customer satisfaction.

Overall, I won’t be returning. There are plenty of other places offering better Polish food and a much more welcoming dining experience. I would not recommend this place to anyone.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tones Jyler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKK4GXgTVLnajqhYm0hfamOs6EgRB-CcfZKNyrEZSlfbU3odg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have driven by this place so many times and wanted to try it. Really glad I finally did and you should too! Had the platter for 2 and it came with everything in the picture for 47$ (2 potatoe pancakes that are so crispy and delicious, polish sausage, a huge amount of perogies with lots of chopped bacon and sausage to go with it, 2 large cabbage rolls, salad, and some kind of carrot mango salad) me and my wife both left stuffed and our baby even had his fill too! It was so delicious and you can tell everything is home cooked with care! I highly recommend it!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNF0XwsVtW1OfgUUiRRKbghfLTu0ovz1VSWdmvU&fid=0x0:0xc4417d5c6f1e0d7d"],"When":"2024-7-6"},{"Name":"Kat s","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV2PheeHlSTOrgESZq7PphUL-4YpUmC6odPCrLoBmlFoDLLyzPn=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had breakfast almost every day here while on our trip. Service was great, waitstaff was kind and accommodating of food allergies, and the food was always high quality. This will definitely be a spot we continue coming back to whenever we're in PoCo!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPKp-lMImM02uuFAI1z4isRNhCXkLkbDt4Yr4Xj&fid=0x0:0xc4417d5c6f1e0d7d"],"When":"2024-7-22"}]

[{"Name":"Madrid Rachel (C)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIvf-PcqiVpvwr8lRb4KDHKMwX0b5MC1Fr-oiihQzWaQrrLLEqr=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"At first, they seated us inside, but I requested if we could be outside, and they told us that it could be arranged. The women working are so nice and accomdating to our needs. They will go at the back and keep checking here and there. We had the whole patio to ourselves, and the weather was perfect for that day! My partner and I would definitely  come back again one day to try the cold noodles. The food proportions and the money we paid for it is worth it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMYWOocxVgzgo0EvR-trYO8V3TgKrbAIvJksmW5&fid=0x0:0x794e2821ebc80351"],"When":"2024-7-13"},{"Name":"Tatiana Kamakura","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWK7ZmVLiCrm06mIZ8nEoydM1aHmV1jz4_Pf0vfjLhNGl4wZBRSUw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We arrived by 6pm and sat in the outside part, which was lovely. The dishes came quickly, even with the restaurant close to full. The staff was super friendly, and the menus had the ingredients in english, making it easier to choose what to order. Everything we ordered tasted amazing. Spicy rice and fish cake was delicious, but really spicy for those not used to spicy food. Trying rice wine for the first time was a nice experience. Would definitely come back to try other dishes.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMa7zy5e2C6GKhrfer3Np3-WiL0StLVOmO6sQtn&fid=0x0:0x794e2821ebc80351"],"When":"2023-5-22"},{"Name":"Patrick Chin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW9837XYJatBhh8uygAXZ5cFqnhdVU7CsJgBMh-TzrJtW8lVns=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food is good... we order seafood pancake, spicy pork bone soup, mixed chicken. Portions were humongous, as we cannot finish it... and this is with  big eaters thats hungry.
Pricepoint is also excellent.
Highly recommended!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOYTx31cP3f85St1FgN0aCUeEb41tC5D8yA5oIf&fid=0x0:0x794e2821ebc80351"],"When":"2023-10-28"},{"Name":"TS OS","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIrxJ8Fjd3bGSI8mWbF186RbFWyg_DW73VTS3OIkFaxPfXFBEQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Splendid Korean restaurant.  A new hot place in town for general Korean food.  I have heard some of the menus were quite good and I wasnt disappointed as I tried aggucim.  Portion was very generous too and ingredient were also great.  I would definitively return and try other menus.  Friendly staff as well.

We tried more dishes in later visits and all dishes were above average.  This is one of better Korean food experience in lower mainland.  Most of dishes are impressive and my companions want to come back for more.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPEGX3dYsN5YxJPJJZn8Jhmzf9LLHHVUo4xNFNX&fid=0x0:0x794e2821ebc80351"],"When":"2022-8-11"},{"Name":"Mary Lam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKTR6oY9lWiiFzO0IMhpp4V_CX15n1cYRzi6LeGXsGPhqIE6g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I was quite disappointed with our visit today, especially as a regular customer of two years. I ordered the spicy stir-fried squid and pork with rice for the first time, but the vegetable portion overwhelmed the pork and squid, and I could hardly find any squid in the dish. The pork consisted of only a few small pieces. Additionally, the stone bowl for the bibimbap was not hot enough, which was quite surprising given the usual consistency.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"TIM C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXsL9NSrG8jjAVNG-x9rN6XSoaFI_Viwwt29jo0hKnGaLtx37Tb=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"First time trying, we ordered the fried squid and beef bone soup w ox knee

Taste 0.5/1*
Fried squid was over cooked, quite dark with a bitter taste
Bone soup was creamy and watery at the same time, lack of depth, wife liked the fact that they don’t season it, but instead gives you side of S&P

Value 0.5/1*
For $19.95 was expecting a larger bowl of soup not gonna lie

Speed 1/1*
Order was prep’s & received on time

Presentation 1/1*
Delivered well, presentation on point, always appreciate being able to eat with eyes first

Overall/Revisit 0/1*
Personally think there’s many better choices of Korean food at this price, even just in the same area

Above and beyond? 0/+1*
A side note: we originally wanted some spicy stir fry pork, but there’s no option to order that as a dish, only on top of rice…","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPickoA8wJ9bWiggT5M5spTQboUX0nkdKLU_qhr&fid=0x0:0x794e2821ebc80351"],"When":"2024-1-29"},{"Name":"Ariana Abedini","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUKNjWemH3JT4c-lZV9IuSCGGzTuGZDPVm9u6xasU8uvx3gj15E=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Authentic Korean food, very very delicious! It was my first time there yesterday and I have to admit that, when I walked in, I became kinda sceptical with my choice, as the interior looks old and not very well taken care of. I’m glad I nevertheless decided to have dinner there, because the food was ABSOLUTELY DELICIOUS! And very good prices too, considering their generous portions. Definitely recommend!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOP5F7y2D0tgvW4XgukYKMK6MVZhovx29fE6HH5&fid=0x0:0x794e2821ebc80351"],"When":"2023-12-17"},{"Name":"Scott Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXHpW7vGME__Zs4wKjXR04Upnw88bkVVyz-H2288JsHocq9vI3r=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"It was a pet decent Korean restaurant. The staff were very friendly and accommodating and would visit again! We only had 2 dishes shared between 3 people - we got the pork katsu and the intestine soup.

It’s an authentic Korean restaurant so they will have dishes that might be a bit too adventurous for a typical diner but I think that you should venture out of your comfort zone because you’ll never know what you like!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP4s1reJqggGcJ8xhRwjOyuJ9l5GhK5RspyRH8e&fid=0x0:0x794e2821ebc80351"],"When":"2022-11-11"}]

[{"Name":"Syed Zakir Beyabani","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUqokDOKSfoe3V-nhx9gaqbXkG51P6yrEBIDLQV-o0Qtu2F32xzPg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A hidden gem. They serve Halal & tasty food freshly made. Pricing is worth the taste although it’s a little costly. The staff is very friendly, well dressed & professional. The new Mandi spot in the restaurant is perfectly placed with the view of whole restaurant. Nice ambiance. The owner was friendly & gave us complimentary rice as well.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN_P0WnqZelv_ukHDqvcD6HgILav3coYUuMHUaj&fid=0x0:0x453913a4dd6ab0c8"],"When":"2024-9-21"},{"Name":"Jennifer Daase","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLBwt1y__ieOQ6rtxWrbLx79gFmQDxZHTIlyMirneXVdm7BEw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Loved the food!! Delicious! Wish they had alcohol options too. the service was lacking (barely saw our waitress after ordering )  but I would go back for food and atmosphere for sure .","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPs0SQJDPn_ZvzHKH-x-fByVyWR0Uph3NkLHK4G&fid=0x0:0x453913a4dd6ab0c8"],"When":"2024-12-19"},{"Name":"Jaihoon Samizada","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXHItuhjLVDM5jWI_kVFDHBHiNtZPqPV4Gtdh2DEA3uAhTKylGr=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"The Aria Afghan Grill restaurant hasn’t the Afghani tasting kebabs, but it’s definitely on the pricey side. For $24, you get just four small pieces of kebab with a piece of bread and a small portion of salad. While the flavor isn’t really enjoyable, the size doesn’t seem to justify the high price. It’s hard to feel like you’re getting good value here.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNuEpoHRbRsmSPF6tjM2X1imV1Dd4XPOMwsfFfA&fid=0x0:0x453913a4dd6ab0c8"],"When":"2024-11-12"},{"Name":"Lahoucine Zaama","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUr0NtHkkklLaFXzATLKk0BHNbNwdaRCjZkySrZiKWfhiMXxk7V=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently visited Aria Afghan Grill, and it was a wonderful experience! From the moment I walked in, the staff welcomed me with warm smiles, and the cozy Afghan-inspired decor made the place feel very inviting.

I ordered the famous "Qabili Palau," and it was absolutely delicious. The basmati rice with raisins and carrots was perfectly cooked, and the meat was tender and full of flavor. I also tried the grilled kebab, which was soft and had a great taste – one of the best kebabs I've had!

The service was excellent. The staff made sure I was comfortable throughout my meal and were happy to answer any questions I had about the dishes.

The prices were reasonable, especially for the quality of food and service. Overall, it was a fantastic experience, and I highly recommend Aria Afghan Grill to anyone looking for a cozy place with authentic and tasty Afghan food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMdMOTr-0WNYxsRbn7JBt2KMoxhKV64ivr7n9cZ&fid=0x0:0x453913a4dd6ab0c8"],"When":"2024-11-6"},{"Name":"Veronica Belle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW6pFvHRP0mjMqe62e_f_QKYo-a3lm9h9SR8Vn0pi8n-fCD4bJS=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food blew me away 😭🫶🏽 we had the Mantu to start — amazing 😭.
The chicken kebab and Qabeli rice as a main — when I tell you that chicken was melt in your mouth good, I am NOT kidding. It was amazing. 😭 And last, we had the Sheer Yakh. I cannot say enough good things, the food was amazing. Wait time was great!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOX4fEVdgLRjoMbDPi5oFFnYDLQy1nRjNbyp9Aw&fid=0x0:0x453913a4dd6ab0c8"],"When":"2024-9-8"},{"Name":"suki kuramoto","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJjVxKokdh92B4IkfWX1wqB7Z5fz7cqqwhltPqBJs0g8q3DBg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a really great experience at Aria this weekend. We dropped in for an early dinner while we were in the area. We quickly noticed it wasn’t a very casual dining spot, but even so, the prices were entirely reasonable for the quality and quantity of food.

We shared a plate of mantu -  the best mantu I’ve ever had probably. Deliciously seasoned, and served with chutney and a spicy sauce. Every bite was incredibly satisfying. The entrees were just as good. The lamb fell off the bone, and the ground beef kebobs were succulent and perfectly seasoned. The side of vegetables transformed each bite. Get the fresh lemon juice in their drinks menu - it’s absolutely refreshing.

Service was friendly and efficient. Overall, great dinner! We would be happy to dine there again if we’re in the neighbourhood.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipML56otr3CAj-dfyYUxqu1RAKCZKNxVd8hnsrlw&fid=0x0:0x453913a4dd6ab0c8"],"When":"2024-9-2"},{"Name":"Kasra Rayani","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIdIiPWSpcAx9BqVRsEdkAGO9Cua53EaxS6lGtlui6McfZz=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We went to Aria for the first time, and it was incredible. We had the Mantu, the Naan and the Chopan & Chicken Kebab. The live music was a nice touch. Couldn’t recommend any higher. Must try.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNnuyZJJpyl5U7G007CDTIf1VI9kHnUK2Zq-Ko&fid=0x0:0x453913a4dd6ab0c8"],"When":"2024-11-10"},{"Name":"Neena Siddiqui","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL2pdLyW6VB_yGefegDLXCVkOee4Wto0dJjoFFQijHYz6Xqwg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a lunch at this wonderful restaurant and ordered a roll, chicken Kebab with Kabuli plao, mutton kebab with Naan , Mantu with minced beef and fresh dough. We had the best mantu and kabuli plao of our lives. Simply delicious. Dough was also very refreshing.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP-x2oDXqWoxrSS2xUCofBeNvtNT2LbYtmuSNsO&fid=0x0:0x453913a4dd6ab0c8"],"When":"2024-7-6"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Shiva Y","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVzd9PGyiNJmwLm5yfA-sJl4BpBMAnWlGsSejcj9DY235f2_ZWo4g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you’re looking for a place to enjoy delicious food and create lasting memories, this is where you need to be. Every visit feels like a treat, and the experience is as wonderful as the food.

Having visited many Persian restaurants in Greater Vancouver, I can confidently say this one is unmatched. From the moment you step inside, you’re greeted by a warm and inviting atmosphere that immediately sets the tone for a memorable dining experience. The decor reflects Persian culture beautifully, creating a cozy yet sophisticated vibe.

Our friends and family come from all different backgrounds, but this restaurant has a way of bringing us together. No matter where we’re from, we all share a love for the incredible food and the warm, welcoming atmosphere here. It’s a place that feels like home for everyone.

The food is absolutely outstanding—every dish bursts with authentic flavors, from the tender, perfectly seasoned kebabs to the aromatic saffron rice and hearty stews. The side dishes, like eggplants dips, fresh salads, and tangy yogurt dips, are equally delicious and pair perfectly with the main courses.

What truly sets this restaurant apart is the exceptional service. The staff are genuinely friendly, attentive, and always ready to make thoughtful recommendations. The chef’s skill and attention to detail are evident in every bite, and the management ensures everything runs smoothly, adding to the stress-free, enjoyable experience.

Whether you’re dining with family, celebrating a special occasion, or simply enjoying a night out, this restaurant delivers in every way. It’s not just a meal—it’s a journey into Persian culture and cuisine that leaves you excited to return for more.

We have dined here countless times, and each visit feels as special as the first. This place has never once disappointed us, consistently delivering a dining experience filled with warmth, flavor, and care.

The cleanliness of this restaurant, including its washrooms, is truly unmatched. It’s a reflection of the care and respect the team has for their guests, and it’s something we deeply appreciate. It’s rare to find such attention to detail, and it makes every visit even more comfortable and enjoyable.

A heartfelt thank you to the owners, the talented kitchen team, and all the lovely staff who make this place so special. Your hard work, kindness, and passion shine through in every detail, and we’re so grateful for the memorable experiences you create for us each time we visit.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMczAwKj4A_k1Za0keZhy-d5RactAuJsjO8MIQs&fid=0x0:0xa44f41c917c99255"],"When":"2024-12-22"},{"Name":"Mucahit Mert Alagoz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUlZFzlr8OmJ6ReNSeqILjiXkPYOR-Wi6HlJhjaTTE_xGsRl7kohA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"As a Turkish citizen, I decided to try this restaurant on the recommendation of my Iranian friend.
The dish we tried is called “Kale Pache.” At first, it seemed like an unappealing meal, but with lemon and garlic, it was truly delicious. This restaurant prepares it exceptionally well. I’ve had the chance to try it a few times in Turkey, but nowhere was as good as this place.
Secondly, I’d like to mention the cleanliness of the restaurant. Restaurants reflecting Middle Eastern culture usually look a bit shabby and not very modern. This restaurant was different; it was both very modern and very clean. When I asked to see their kitchen, I saw that everyone was working according to hygiene rules. Additionally, their kitchen was spotless.
Lastly, the owner of the restaurant hosted us wonderfully; he was very attentive. I haven’t had such delicious Iranian food in a long time.
I tried to think of a negative aspect, but honestly, there isn’t any. You must try this place.
They also offer other dishes besides Kale Pache.
Once again, I thank them for a lovely breakfast and their customer satisfaction-focused service.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOlo2r94f53qdKhg2n2HBwk-rYqotX-tFDPbO_5&fid=0x0:0xa44f41c917c99255"],"When":"2024-12-14"},{"Name":"JOANNE KADIR","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK5FtQlTqwnaEemJG-2BJY5ImgYhsbRGNlAyMyitnPajXzAiw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My husband and I went to Shemroon for lunch yesterday and I have to say, it was some of the best Persian food i've ever had! It was flavourful and authentic. My husband got the daily special, which was the celery stew with a bed of rice & I got the walnut stew, also with a bed of rice. We also tried their cucumber yogurt appetizer and it was so tasty! The atmosphere was so cute, I love the decor the owner chose for the store and the staff are so friendly. I was extremely happy with the service, and will definitely be back with my friends and family.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNPee-OFDpK2K4OsrZmG9aXxnyS5qydV-KqprIc&fid=0x0:0xa44f41c917c99255"],"When":"2024-12-12"},{"Name":"Sean Lin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLa2nbdhfTAJwsejRS86C7FhvPUumsFGv-cHzJUBYr2iFqGJw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great food, warm ambiance, and awesome service. I ate here with two other friends and we all thought it was a great meal! Our server was very friendly and we enjoyed her suggestions.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM0PQ8ffrhN-6hmRD6tNqY-y4-Szyqo9npip6YC&fid=0x0:0xa44f41c917c99255"],"When":"2024-12-13"},{"Name":"pegah sedghi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWJLiNV-UWi9udm3iXnF_xdi5sUEh1p7ESZZP-b8NmmVZr9yzw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had kalepache here, and I could say it was one of the most delicious one, the meat was well cooked, tasty and there was no bad smell. The bread was fresh, and the service was great, they behaviour was really friendly, and the tea after that in those glasses was great.
We are so thankful, Shemroon.
Unfortunately I forgot to take photo of the food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOCVHQxwknBRTr0bE_MH-4hgypr0zWsGChTL15M&fid=0x0:0xa44f41c917c99255"],"When":"2024-12-22"},{"Name":"amirali soltaniseresht","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI4NItNzqz4vIRAjofhZXUA96PRthiJElTa31nxJnQMi0lTxQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently dined at Shemroon and had the pleasure of trying their Vazirzi, and it was absolutely phenomenal!
The dish was a perfect blend of flavors—juicy, tender skewers of lamb and chicken, beautifully seasoned and cooked to perfection. The saffron rice that accompanied it was fragrant and fluffy, making it a perfect pairing.

The ambiance of the restaurant was warm and inviting, with a traditional Persian touch that really enhanced the dining experience.
The staff was friendly and attentive, ensuring we had everything we needed.

Overall, if you’re looking for authentic Persian cuisine at Port Coquitlam, Shemroon is a must-visit. I’ll definitely be back to try more of their menu!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPP9kL87qKmKK1n-61Jx0xpsXZEMkXmALk_GWih&fid=0x0:0xa44f41c917c99255"],"When":"2024-10-10"},{"Name":"Nima Ashrafkia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIhCeBQhzwCFMHTX293urOtHgPZvp1N4dhP07LmlghewE6qkg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently dined at Shemroon restaurant and was blown away by the authentic Persian cuisine. Every dish was a flavor explosion, from the perfectly grilled kebabs to the aromatic saffron rice. The atmosphere was warm and inviting, making it the perfect spot for both casual dinners and special occasions. The service was top-notch—attentive, friendly, and knowledgeable about the menu. If you're looking for a true taste of Persian culture, this is the place to be. Highly recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPfSvJnEkKP4h3Re6vWbBWdluHObgKKQtAkA5cn&fid=0x0:0xa44f41c917c99255"],"When":"2024-8-27"},{"Name":"Ferial Kabiri","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVNJSEzvc4IEHA3ToX2itau1biTjLXsZQYy6l6I_VjTX2j8eqY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Tonight was my birthday at Shemroon restaurant 🥳I can’t say enough about the incredible experience we had at this restaurant! From the moment we arrived, the service was outstanding—attentive, warm, and truly personalized. The staff went above and beyond to ensure everything was perfect.

The food? Simply phenomenal. Every dish was prepared to perfection, with flavors that left us speechless. You can tell they put thought and heart into every bite.

What made our evening even more special was the DJ they arranged just for us. It created the perfect ambiance and added so much fun to our celebration. It’s rare to find a place that nails the trifecta of amazing service, mouthwatering food, and exceptional entertainment.

Thank you for making our night unforgettable. I highly recommend this place to anyone looking for a truly remarkable dining experience. We’ll definitely be back!","Images":null,"When":""}]

I enjoyed the classic spicy broth and my husband and kids loved the beef bone broth. So rich and flavourful. The service was also very kind and prompt. We went at 5pm and there was plenty of seating but it quickly filled in at 6pm.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN3mdK8wqUvywrbjqRgGWp5aHwenjRA6FbozF-s&fid=0x0:0xbbb2db8c40d16ac2"],"When":"2024-12-21"},{"Name":"Hadjer Aoufi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUH99dV5yRFKWLUL64N7AAdLAz9CXJlAZU-5tvJ55X8-tguqb4i=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fantastic Hot Pot Spot! exceeded all expectations! The broths were rich and flavorful, with a great variety to choose from. The ingredients were fresh, and the sauce bar added a fun, personal touch.
Ask “Lilly “ for anything about the restaurant and food ,she is very friendly and helpful , and made the meal even Can’t wait to come back!
Thanks","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOTCRPL4LjZecSPBjRmM6y-e_UvXYBu2z1yRDQa&fid=0x0:0xbbb2db8c40d16ac2"],"When":"2024-11-29"},{"Name":"J C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJuz6MjJRGuK58voTnnaV-4We982kehC8yI8eBro-zEfCAGwg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They took over my favourite Chinese restaurant, but they're a good addition to the neighborhood. Very friendly and quick service. They're always cleaning and smiling, and now I'm addicted and come here multiple times a week 😆 They seem busy and I wish them great success.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPF2Mb8K2_MSjZIRoZhtN34vtY266agPzhSV0PM&fid=0x0:0xbbb2db8c40d16ac2"],"When":"2024-12-16"},{"Name":"Grace H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXXJyvF5Y-P5TM_kUaS64jljD1P1SvGaYty3_AOiG-z1kQWRVyL=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time here and Miki and Harry were super helpful.  I almost ordered medium but trusted their advice and ordered less spicy and it was still quite hot.

The ice cream was very different from other places but was so good. It’s become my favorite 🤩 Definitely coming back again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO0s9SIEJ3SzNPY_0TtF6cLo166am3jF6feGp9s&fid=0x0:0xbbb2db8c40d16ac2"],"When":"2024-11-7"},{"Name":"Janica Kwon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKU1cJy-kQLw2_cLn0VcIOSBXRZ0__JNr0PduU1kiwzJu9zIg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"YGF Hot Pot is our new favorite! The restaurant is so clean and organized and the ingredients are very fresh! Love how you can customize everything exactly to your liking and they have a great variety for everyone. The free ice cream is a nice way to finish the meal! Highly recommend!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPQA3Ln7rl3vpvo0BDhgYcxcTpdWYEhB4U0pIoU&fid=0x0:0xbbb2db8c40d16ac2"],"When":"2024-12-14"},{"Name":"Samantha Chow","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJb14piHhrv9m6QfSj83-RTeq5x1xtSBXCe3_gj-f4GSQShHA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We love visit YGF especially enjoy a pot of hot noodle soup in cold/rain days
We tried few of their soup base and all taste lovely.
All staff are super friendly and helpful.
Feel so satisfying with free ice cream after","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP3C5GvaCkCPIw9vchXocTN-nFmfFSGiddE8dv1&fid=0x0:0xbbb2db8c40d16ac2"],"When":"2024-12-22"},{"Name":"Shiki Chan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX1sS7tz7QyhMk5leHHLZOGpXjbE0oOVzsTkOhWQkSzoQjYtWV7ZQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nice hot pot, typically for the potato noodles and the Mala soup base (Set 1). The creamy style with the spicy creates good vibe in enjoying the noodles and ingredient. The fish ball with salted egg inside deserve a merit.

Quite a number of choices of ingredient and noodles that you can do you own mix and match.

Environment is neat and clean which makes a comfortable place to enjoy your food. Server are all nice and polite too.

Typically will come once again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNTEbU5Y1O7JSdHj4XhDQ5CtLL-x6r6tPzXIR0T&fid=0x0:0xbbb2db8c40d16ac2"],"When":"2024-7-28"},{"Name":"Sheryl Zulueta","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXm8ZpPG0fhrDifuXYNAgUyQU36ee1c0FHBQ2redFh16L0S64SmfQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We visited on a Tuesday evening about an hour before closing. There was no line. There were a couple tables occupied. As soon as we entered, a staff member approached to help us. They must have been able to tell it was our first time there. They quickly explained, and we went on our hot pot adventure.
There is a minimum 1 lb weight. As of Sept 2024, the price was $19.90 /lb. I was careful in my choices as I didn't want to end up with a 50 dollar bowl. I got a range of items from meat to tofu to fish balls and noodles. I didn't meet the weight requirement the first time, which was a bit of a relief. I was able to go and put more stuff in that I hesitated on the first time.
I chose the Beef Broth. It was delicious! I'm still thinking about it the next morning. I will definitely be back and try some of the other items.
The service was friendly and they helped explain and I didn't feel rushed at all making any decisions. The food also came out quite quick.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPvXsK3ooVHrnDWw5w-HAyYGFJMJmfi_NzmqBmF&fid=0x0:0xbbb2db8c40d16ac2"],"When":"2024-9-4"}]

Delivery driver Jason is incredible as well.  Their extensive menu is sure to please any cravings.    5 stars…. Come see for yourself.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tracey Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUJZu7Wd-0W8AR1ietbb55MsCEMTW14qREJAaK2bKSh0mIGR3lmBQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Booked a reservation here for 10 at 8pm. Service was great and the server was a great helping us figured out what to order for our group.

We ordered a combo B for 8 ppl and some extra dishes. The food was amazing ! Really loved the fried rice, ginger beef, green beans, and fried squid ! I also love that they have seasoning at every table. I am a sucker for their hot sauce.

We noticed that they had an extra room with a bar , tables, and a karaoke system. Looks like a great place to book an event/ gathering.

Would definitely come back here again for some comfort canadian chinese food. I'm also interested in trying their breakfast in the near future :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOqd9fV6wMT1TELGzoTSGTelTMfPiwt0tnUEvag&fid=0x0:0x318b3df216b4a874"],"When":"2024-3-19"},{"Name":"Truckloadofrhymes canada","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXkND8fxIF1Oqb83wPDair5hXJ85P4wpjp70bDsHPXiyojrgbkuIQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place always has good food. Definitely will compete with wherever you've been going.  All the non-asian dishes. It's not just filler. It's actually good food as well. Highly recommended been coming here for years","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPl6gwoIGVtCq4dV_NqTeIpYWkmUwSbC9aIaxdk&fid=0x0:0x318b3df216b4a874"],"When":"2024-8-24"},{"Name":"Amy Lau","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUMShEyNaVyqkg_udSZIL6AtgBldvcAt4vOmvtftAdUJi-LcA7I=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food was delicious! We ordered the beef with soy sauce noodles and spicy squid for our company’s event. Service was great! Portions were on the larger scale for our corporate events! Lady over the phone was super helpful!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Stacy Purum Jeon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXJokIsJGL-fv0gSK_iI4jQxVk_jmrb_b6s-LN0DAYOqzSpY2xQLw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Combination of western and Chinese!
Servers were super friendly and food is so good. Given the fact that you cannot really find the restaurant this affordable this good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMT4_PggqssU5QpyUWU0Ylqz8PNHV91LwR0XZsh&fid=0x0:0x318b3df216b4a874"],"When":"2024-3-16"},{"Name":"kiana Liu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWKoxfjAHBiXenysk2Q-KlulFH1fxjGp6FrGPGGTkK41ibofwbwig=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I got food poisoning from this place and been living in the washroom for past 7 days. We ordered 3 dishes which they got 2 of them wrong. One dish we realized it’s wrong, when we asked her, she was like “what about this dish? Do you want to try this instead?”
My husband can’t have seafood and the dish had shrimps in it, that’s how I knew for sure we didn’t order that dish.
The second dish we didn’t realize until the end.
The quality of their food was really bad. We went there for all the good reviews and we were super disappointed. Will never return.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO-wQu4pwQGfRKnSX8sP3y7dUGvJGajvqAJG35E&fid=0x0:0x318b3df216b4a874"],"When":"2023-8-5"},{"Name":"KA T","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVaR7ml2dkrIOrwgU_-kQ-HRh1gdXFY-Mwfz5VTGuLsK_EtLSkR=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"We stopped in here for breakfast as we were staying at the attached Ramada. There was 4 of us (two young kids and two adults). The breakfast itself was ok, nothing special at all. The coffee was really good though. The service was embarrassing. The server walked away without taking one of our orders and seemed almost bothered that we would come in to have breakfast. The prices are definitely not worth the quality of food. When we received the our bill, the prices were higher than what was noted on the menu, so this was quite alarming. They need to update their menu to reflect what they charge because that was really shady. Our bill was over $80 for four simple breakfasts. Save your money and go somewhere else.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mike Medcalf","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU1rixyxiw07idcZpYCUo6royGxGKqfnZDSFo9vAAuERRuqgDflAA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing prices. Great western classics with good portions. Also good Chinese food. Nice owners. You will not leave hungry 😋","Images":null,"When":""}]

Modern ambience, but you can definitely feel the warm Italian hospitality here. Friendly staff and good food. Recommend to book a table.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMnhm0MuEeApdX4PY7B_Xhwv6eNgtqcD0gFQtDg&fid=0x0:0xf2949084e08f7717"],"When":"2024-6-10"},{"Name":"P C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL88eGEDtgHkBgqL891vvj7LFnoV5_8VQFpZ1gQaT540IRImA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely fantastic! Customer service was great and food was phenomenal. The prices for Tuesday pasta night were amazing, deals like that for such high quality food are hard to find! Even at full price I definitely recommend checking this spot out for dinner with family or date night.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Elizabeth Lo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVPl6fiur4C23qnNmuemdRGEXafuu9PoCts6x4CUY75Jkk5idyUOw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had their Hula pizza. I don't really like pizza that much, but That Place's was delightful! It's not quite a Napoleon pizza (puffy, chewy crust), I'm not sure what style it is but I loved it, as it is super thin.

The pineapples that accompanied the cures meats on my pizza were not sour, juicy but not dry, and had a sweetness that paired well with the meat.

Got to try my friend's pizzas as well, and everything we ordered was so delicious. I have to come back for their pasta dishes!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMWWN42pLsLaryVZ2ISyc8jvsBx4vKIJP1k6_9g&fid=0x0:0xf2949084e08f7717"],"When":"2024-6-25"},{"Name":"Marie Amin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIKR0qp3fose5GsYts0dtMeJqwXo1MWNFSPwo4SjCtJGEbgYA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":""First time at THAT PLACE, Went here for dinner with my boys and husband to celebrate his birthday. Great food and amazing service. Highly recommend checking them out!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOg-CDNNf8gHM4MeYnGtflN94bgoqf6INfVWNcn&fid=0x0:0xf2949084e08f7717"],"When":"2024-6-11"},{"Name":"Karen Jones","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ6IC1wpFEjyCTx3FWQ_sOYFSAr6w5s8xxxgofCEztXjk_-KQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love the staff at this place. Vanessa is always so welcoming and a hoot to talk to. It's like that family-owned restaurant in your neighborhood that you keep on wanting to go back to. They make an excellent Caesar salad and our favorites are their Wood-Fired pizzas and of course Pat's cheesecakes!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Monica","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLGgIU2jvOA6dZo_R-fDScmbPQKFMa9bNbD6fpKC_vMNnPtfA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time eating at this restaurant and wow! I ordered their duck fettuccine, and chocolate peanut butter cheesecake both were a 10/10.  I have tried a lot of pasta at many different restaurants (including upscale) and this place was significantly better.  It reminded me of the pasta I ate when in Rome and Florence.

I am a desert person and am very critical of desserts. The chocolate peanut butter cheese cake was airy and the best dessert I had in a long time. It was not dense as your typical cheese cake dessert.

The pasta I ate was very well priced. The wine was well priced and dessert.  The excellent quality and taste for the food for the price is unheard of these days.

The customer service was amazing. I believe it was the owners. They were funny and kind and made the experience even more enjoyable.

Overall, I had a great experience. This will be my go-to pasta place. Only “negative”  is that this place is 30 minutes from my home. The food I ate was so delicious that I purchased take out for the same order (pasta and dessert) so that I could eat it the next day without driving back….I’ve never done that before.

Edit: the takeout was not as good for some reason. I would recommend eating in.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO0w4UOCi_NGKNz3P-A1Pjm1_xxTI9oMai9fOpN&fid=0x0:0xf2949084e08f7717"],"When":"2024-4-28"},{"Name":"Michael and Heather Davis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXAR2awDwwg40UXDk37cVoc0wbldzi0KXyWx4JXALGtSKDUndD1=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The food was good but this is a very NOISY restaurant on the small side with reflective walls and floors. There was a table full of very loud family members and friends of the owner that made it impossible to hear people sitting at your own table. Several customers left because of the noise. Instead of addressing the issue, the owner laughed it off (favoring his friends and family above customers) stating "they're from East Van". I thought he would knock off the price of an entree because of the noise but it was full fare. I would't recommend dining in.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Thomas Tricarico","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKhws5bVYDwmrI4nzI8NtjFY5tCFNmhM_PZ57tj9M9bdO7Dag=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a Great dinner last night at That Table..a real family based restaurant with great, friendly, accommodating service and the food was very good. The porrions were generous and very tasty. The Alfredo was not quite to my wife's liking but they immediately made it right to her liking and it turned out great. My Spaghetti Amalfi was excellent. We had a great Sangria too. The best..was their cannoli for dessert.  They were The Best cannolis we have ever had in Vancouver..home made..and we told them so. We will be back..and you should give them a try. Thanks for an enjoyable evening.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOWZ5ULwwW8hMgXeHSDkXmGLNmZEyZJKNch3euT&fid=0x0:0xf2949084e08f7717"],"When":"2021-11-5"}]

[{"Name":"Daniel Jung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFE7g6vnjf23CW6mDeh4anchF8fxBs6O5Nsx0bvhepuO3MVzWa=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came here with the fam for Father's day.
1st time trying Philippine cuisine and what an exceptional experience. Kind and attentive staff and most importantly the food was incredible. This was actually one of my favorite dining experience.
Food was exceptional! Thank you","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMU95rTTAV0BK_cbFii3d-jihpq23PAOpy9xa0y&fid=0x0:0xad7ac43de48b0ec0"],"When":"2024-6-18"},{"Name":"Julie Yan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWfTkMTfEdPNgUhYXY4I0LrmLHMmd9enIo7z2jv5BbsNTul6Qf7=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing food and friendly staff. The Vegetable Kare Kare is divine and get some rice with that. The BBQ pork ribs were an easy runner-up, charred in the best way. Definitely a healthier option if you’re eating out.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOCb3iU50OU-tLuL6jf7CVMEQ2_QnwtSdpzDiR5&fid=0x0:0xad7ac43de48b0ec0"],"When":"2024-10-13"},{"Name":"LSP LSP","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW4u7ZczctbKDKn8CXvFXOwDtsUnW_BDkhdSdynFH0H1WLLxvs=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"For someone who cannot cook or even attempt to cook Filipino food but still misses eating good home cooked meal this place is a "God of Happy Tummies" sent. I visited the Coquitlam branch of Kulinarya. They don't skimp on food portions or presentation for to go orders. I have tried many Filipino restaurants in lower mainland but we always leave disappointed or underwhelmed. The food tasted freshly cooked, homey and quite nostalgic and there's no feeling of "Tirang ulam" from the previous day like most Filipino restaurants we have tried. I highly recommend this place. Worth the price and the team who works at the front are friendly as well. Will return again for more happy tummy days.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMk6DJZJCSJedM8CG8N-34GOqp-B3UnV0nhJJu7&fid=0x0:0xad7ac43de48b0ec0"],"When":"2024-6-16"},{"Name":"Jessameen Dela Peña","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX9mRpmL8-ZJUG7UPFcnsjzRdxjABif-MswbO1rxgJyyWfns8Jd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"As a Filipino residing in Coquitlam, I’m delighted to have this place so conveniently nearby. My partner and I continue to favor the sisig, and we love the store’s ambiance, which wonderfully showcases Filipino culture.

UPDATE: We recently dined in to savor the experience, and it genuinely felt like home with its authentic Filipino atmosphere. The adobo served in a wok was a highlight, and we also loved the lumpiang shanghai. Although they removed the canton from the menu (which was my favorite), my partner tried the bihon and found it delicious. We’re still loving it here!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOCb7sUWiebYL7XEM_jEOXkmRJ2oLf7OB8OBjAP&fid=0x0:0xad7ac43de48b0ec0"],"When":"2024-8-24"},{"Name":"Mav Bayer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU7pHDDvwX22QLIg_Qg1Pd0y5ez5B3UjogKyDHPkds6Co5966k=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I recently ordered the pancit canton platter from Kulinarya  Coquitlam for a party, and I was quite disappointed. The menu indicated it would include a mix of chicken, shrimp, and veggies, but there was no chicken in the dish at all. The topping only had about 6-8 medium-sized shrimp, which felt inadequate for the price. Overall, it didn’t live up to our expectations, and I don’t feel it was worth what we paid. I hope they can improve their portions and accuracy in the future.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMjJR7sTInjkmRWeZrEMluZvnGV1z71iHTrtvKb&fid=0x0:0xad7ac43de48b0ec0"],"When":"2024-9-25"},{"Name":"8T8","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLaHAe29LTwj-kDB4Rxp2LPyCtNn-xUw5U4xwT2905ny-JNkA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"You'll be happy!  Each dish prepared with much attention and care.  Had a wonderful dining experience.  The place is small and just perfect, gives them more opportunity to pay close attention to you.  They'll come over and ask you how your meal was, very hospitable and beautiful atmosphere.   A definite great experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPWFkcyhOUeQnxgY1JQAY3t3VydDgxTDn9_oz2O&fid=0x0:0xad7ac43de48b0ec0"],"When":"2023-6-26"},{"Name":"Arjun Tyagi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWopm7CB27Brsn2nZf_ZcGMYA1rC2xZn0gFS2Ev_B4zUk8mX8MoIQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a great meal and experience here, a hidden gem I didn’t realize was 15 mins from my house, will definitely be back. Came by recommendation of my Filipino friends so I already expected it to be good and it didn’t disappoint. I had the Manok sa Gata with Garlic Rice upgrade and it was absolutely delicious 😋. Finished off with my favourite Halo-halo and it was fantastic as well. Cozy old school style family restaurant vibes with great service. Plenty of free parking outside in the plaza and directly in front of the restaurant as well.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNM3Zt6AMTJSHSA1TqVXRm03Np3YoxVKdfPoUq4&fid=0x0:0xad7ac43de48b0ec0"],"When":"2024-6-11"},{"Name":"Kevin Luo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVWJMxLZr-3YvPOYEYkCwOqoRgX8yyWGLPYZ19IJEKzgIUssXc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"This appears to be the only place serving Filipino food in downtown Coquitlam. I started my meal by trying Talong Salad for the first time, it was amazing! The grilled eggplant added a meaty texture to the raw pineapple, tomato, and onions. The grilled squid was good too, but hindsight I should have ordered something else as the flavours overlapped with the salad. Their house-made vinegar is probably one of the best condiments ever, it will go well with pretty much anything. Halo-halo is super sweet and refreshing. The restaurant is fairly small and the tables are closely placed, making space quite tight.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP0cQnjf8fh_fY4nULnWtnvDlSWVvnao3F1-E1P&fid=0x0:0xad7ac43de48b0ec0"],"When":"2024-3-27"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Kevan Bonn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJvNnHmBNFG_G3ySw9mP3BZPzSJjPIurU1Hy79afN_SrMR1Zg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Ordered online a Cajun chicken sandwich with no Cajun, upgrade the side to yam fries, tofu lettuce wraps and an eggnog cheese cake for dessert. I got a notification that the food was ready for pick up 40 minutes later, my boyfriend went inside to pick up the food but was told it wasn’t ready yet… when he finally got home with our much excited take out date night dinner, we started to dig in. The first couple of bites were yummy, nothing out of the ordinary, but it didn’t take long before my boyfriend noticed that his chicken was not fully cooked through and still very pink. He refused to eat anymore and then we had to make dinner, which negated us buying take out and waiting for it. We wanted to treat ourselves to dinner that we did not have to make or clean up after. Over all we were very disappointed.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO_E3fTpJJdLK0kMeulnj-eqylf46yXWbc1CBWM&fid=0x0:0x5a740195b1b5f06d"],"When":"2024-12-20"},{"Name":"Mur L'Amour Beauty","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLWRTv6Ucl2AQriy5TjtYYVHeEv9CMDUYjKrDpm4hOiOHfpNg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was pleasantly surprised by the carpaccio at your cafe Very fresh and thinly sliced pieces, perfectly balanced with sauce and spices. The presentation was also impressive everything looked very appetizing. I’ll definitely be back for this dish again! Thank you for such a delicious 🫶","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOYN6ShhxADOvPzWTa-wOUvGPBNjzR5tP_ZWxM6&fid=0x0:0x5a740195b1b5f06d"],"When":"2024-11-7"},{"Name":"Danilo Teodoro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU_rV4_xok36vIezJ6uAhpzSfyECA8ogmjA4ehyXVTr4dBqIAFv=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The ceviche was very good, and so was the service. But the main dish was really disappointing! The burger's meat was basically burnt. Both. The beef patty was thin, which helped to make it dry. In the end, it was just an expensive Big Mac.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNWeu7fZGthlPgUHdyxdo79Wu7OuNy5G0EJICj1&fid=0x0:0x5a740195b1b5f06d"],"When":"2024-9-1"},{"Name":"Amanda S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKfFdUftfUOx33L8DAwQyclFhJteI62arLCkWITYeGsgp-LQw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Maria was probably one of the nicest servers I’ve ever had in my life. She’s was sooo warm, kind and bubbly. I was having a bad day and she turned it around with her positivity and attentiveness. The atmosphere on the patio was just perfect too and her recommendation for the Mediterranean bowl is now one of my favorites. Thanks again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOlD5hznwGa7DOTpstaj4P0zPs_a4_CQ2gRi6UK&fid=0x0:0x5a740195b1b5f06d"],"When":"2024-11-22"},{"Name":"Lex","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVIOoTFR1sL0065mPU_AeAGgpwzqHssyGAT0I917Apw20TmHTg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Highly recommend for group (work) lunches. Gluten free, vegan and vegetarian options available. The crispy tofu was so delicious.

5 stars for the food & service. Our team will definitely be back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOyRhebp-rXmnYbmBl2L3bBgxAdFwumqf3-XiKh&fid=0x0:0x5a740195b1b5f06d"],"When":"2024-9-1"},{"Name":"Naz Khan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXRq8l2FAHrB_BVK6IQu7kkBhuqAvVszlJ_x3nATjhjB42KboI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our first server was great, super sweet and kind.  She made sure to make us feel comfortable and helped us decide what to order.  After her shift ended, the new server introduced herself and took over in the same friendly and helpful manner.  The best part was, the manager came over to check on us and was an absolute delight!  She chatted with us for a bit and made us feel so welcome and appreciated.  During a busy time, they all took the time to interact with us on a personal level while still making sure the food was on time and done right.  Overall, my best experience at CC which is almost always wonderful.  Kudos to management for hiring great staff and training so well.  I felt almost like I was at a small, family owned restaurant!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"dawn lopez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVN4Fd7SxUXBbHiu42-5cl9bOQZMv8_jHLVnj32nQgkACFpiRI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went mid day on a Monday
Food was excellent 😋
Was recommended a substitution when asked to have ravioli without prawns . Excellent choice!
Both server and hostess were wonderful","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOhYJd9bcx4x_09onaD0dUnluMyTyys_3o4IGAP&fid=0x0:0x5a740195b1b5f06d"],"When":"2024-10-8"},{"Name":"Linh Tran","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUbP3plInkqXVOA2XJc8czoQ80aWBGnT8WS-yMiUPgvNShtt-y90A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We tried the Vancouver Dining Out 3 course meal, $45/EA and ordered another salmon belly sushi. Ravioli shrimp & fried chicken were the set appetizers that we chose, the ravioli was amazing but the chicken batter was too thick and hard compared to the ones I had at other Cactus Club. I chose steak while my husband got the Creole chicken, both were great, but my husband thought the asparagus was a bit overcooked. There were only 2 options for dessert so we ordered both, cream cheese and chocolate bar, well, we didn't like either of them. In general, the quality met the expectation at the pricing. The kids at another table were too noisy but well, what can they do about it? I wish the light was brighter, it was too dark in the restaurant.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN2pjoMgbvtOo7ShfHUVzqISv7Mmrfu3zzrkBJf&fid=0x0:0x5a740195b1b5f06d"],"When":"2024-1-23"}]
