user_reviews:
[{"Name":"K’s coffee lover","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW-385uQOflrqOxsV0QWsdIyhv-rxdZ7rLwLnLPmzpfPGzr9P6Z=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"After not visiting Denny’s for over a year, we were happy to find that they still offer a free birthday treat. So, we headed there on a Saturday morning. Judging by the packed parking lot, it’s clear Denny’s remains a popular spot, bustling with customers all enjoying their meals.

Our server was lovely and attentive, adding to the warm atmosphere. Although there was a bit of confusion when we arrived, with some customers who arrived after us being seated first, it didn’t affect our mood. According to the official website, the birthday treat includes a Build Your Own Grand Slam, but we overheard from the next table that Denny’s will deduct the equivalent cost if you choose something else from the menu. That’s a thoughtful way to offer flexibility for customers with dietary needs.

Our breakfast arrived hot and well-presented, and the buttermilk pancakes were soft and buttery—just the thing to kick off a great birthday morning!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipORkvKT7-OLSChxlnmYvfSbHoRXFcgK_vhOiG7Y&fid=0x0:0xce11d22c64824992"],"When":"2024-11-3"},{"Name":"Aarna","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIyKiPt9xTa8ZNQM2KUPVsXHP40b2Zu4rW1CyCzcZ5rQDcsYM8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I went on a breakfast date with my mom and we both ordered french toast slams. We got the original and berry filled ones with the side of hashbrows and mozzarella sticks. Everything was SPOT ON. Denny’s is our favourite place for breakfast dates and they never disappoint. Our server Eddy was very kind and service was very fast. We would definitely recommend Denny’s!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO_qJ-w91clOxBAJdKrVA-RZgWjHUEdBKIwXNOz&fid=0x0:0xce11d22c64824992"],"When":"2024-8-24"},{"Name":"Thomas de Zwart","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXZ1Z_rmvSk8qqeJbFDCeuAPhmCK9Dxs-uwyheqZ1TJ_gHr2LQi=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Showed up at 11:15 PM, place was absolutely bustling! Laughed with the host as we were walked towards a booth in the back listening to stories of Denny’s at 3 AM. Then we were greeted by our server, Hans(?), who was such an awesome dude and made great conversation.

I really can’t say much beyond the fact that the vibes were immaculate, service was extremely friendly, and as someone who hasn’t been to Denny’s in over a decade, the food was exactly what we were hoping for at 11:30 PM on a Saturday.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMu_Xljlkh_GXcW3KH-QfYSG9w7AzYzPTau0dld&fid=0x0:0xce11d22c64824992"],"When":"2024-9-1"},{"Name":"Younghee Cho","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLVBDA1ifmp5Ei23MdOWn9Unvt88HUqhpY476Z8yOdP8XHYNw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I visited new location here it is my first time visiting this location. I had a wonderful breakfast! It was tasty And Donna our server was soooo nice and attentive made sure my coffee cup was never empty which was my favorite part of her service and her smile. And she took special order for me instead serving me cheese steak omelette, she changed to three over-easy eggs cheese steak meal. Thank u!  I definitely visit again","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN3HAO-KuBWtrK4Lul0A9PMCzeW4FvfXOKt6RZa&fid=0x0:0xce11d22c64824992"],"When":"2024-10-14"},{"Name":"Ember N","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVAOVVSRZSBJ6e5O5jUUtiBAq23q-FcEx-8tVq1hmthlfDRNYcfgw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"typical Denny’s franchise. Less busy but today is extra busy for Christmas season. we usually go for each of my family’s Bday free grandslam. i chose the fried steak slam cz usually i do the all american but i knew i couldn’t finish even half of it. my husband chose the 55+ veggie omlet. all was good and not too salty! yey! they have condiments and sauces if you wish to make it more salty. so that’s a good thing.

our server was the best. he was asian with great english. didn’t get his name sadly. he always had a smile, he gave us water while we were just browsing. he helped the other family with their teetering table which usually be over seen by any other person. he took my husbands order when he knew the order was wrong and was smiling about it the whole time. i even asked about an old 55+ fish that was not on the menu AND HE KNEW ABOUT IT! waw! he talked to the kids when he said the liked wolverine, said sorry to the mom when he mentioned deadpool cz he didn’t know if it was appropriate for these set of kids to know. mom said they loved deadpool. he was the best AND I HOPE HE GETS A RAISE !!  you hear that!!??? GIVE THIS GUY A RAISE!!! He searved the tables near the washroom and it was really a tight place but he was so smooth with everything.

WE WILL NOW COME BACK HERE instead of Burnaby one bec of the server period.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOYQpyydpBoO865BuaEPT1TzBoBqpkZ4vhzWI7-&fid=0x0:0xce11d22c64824992"],"When":"2024-12-15"},{"Name":"Jacob Tong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXnY0cs4wU4BO3GrJtuGsP4uKk2H9IJcja2Nfyeq_gGo82pzZni=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Denny’s is always a nice diner to read a book at.

The breakfast with pancakes or French toast are usually solid after a late night of studying.

I probably wouldn’t recommend the eggs Benedict though. The English muffin is soggy and overall it’s not that great flavour wise. For the same price you can get a better eggs Benedict elsewhere.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipORRrs2aPZTMQeO1S3i3Khm3MIfwRnXAz_S-TI_&fid=0x0:0xce11d22c64824992"],"When":"2024-10-23"},{"Name":"Grace","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLzCME5X_uS8bQpkwinHDNntk06MLZt48Bbv3csROQbZmIDfg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We ordered bacon ranch sandwiches and coffees early in the morning.
This atmosphere was quite classic!
Even service was also perfect!
I like the Rick’s humorous vibe.
I highly recommend Coquitlam Denny’s.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPTG0wC8O0J3F0X5RhOR8mOW-Vb6HjD-WiXCisD&fid=0x0:0xce11d22c64824992"],"When":"2024-7-1"},{"Name":"Fernando Napoles","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXcZeDf9_r93PjmOj5cU5-zN-CFQNXNCYB-lFZhDkDewNTSBGVy=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It was great! I visited for my birthday :) the waitress, Donna, was very friendly and she guessed it was my bday before I even said it lol delicious breakfast :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPWhYeWZXJvSSFxn6RJuxN3g8OkAvz1VKMZuwQ8&fid=0x0:0xce11d22c64824992"],"When":"2024-11-4"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Ping D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV-_KBk5-yIGzGmKAkX1L-6QPRrz_RZKkgRnIY4il5exhoL_sw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It was a perfect lunch. Kids menu pizza was the same size as the regular pizza. Food and service were both very good. I’d suggest they offer more selections of pizza flavours at lunch time. It’s definitely a good deal to go at lunch. The comfortable meal started with complimentary dinner rolls with garlic oil.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN47_Do9ZdDwPr-MU16mYYSZu6ND1uoZmOWqwg4&fid=0x0:0xcb392bf507fb5484"],"When":"2024-9-29"},{"Name":"Amanda Green","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWX2-QkU6r0X4DLM6-w27hOoQabXaFOXnHBh92gU3KWWKAd6KWGjA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We have ordered takeout before and loved it, so we decided to dine in this time. Very cozy atmosphere and lovely service. The food was so, so fresh and the flavours were outstanding. I ordered the Scusa Mi Pomodoro and I understand now why it's a challenge winner - it was to die for, and I can't remember the last time I had such good, fresh, perfectly cooked prawns. Will definitely be back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO0E5mjnxKtwgfWXwsftGkVtde8Fcyw_qHRefWm&fid=0x0:0xcb392bf507fb5484"],"When":"2024-12-20"},{"Name":"Jessameen Dela Peña","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX9mRpmL8-ZJUG7UPFcnsjzRdxjABif-MswbO1rxgJyyWfns8Jd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a wonderful family dinner at this restaurant! The ambiance is truly lovely, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The staff went above and beyond, being both accommodating and welcoming throughout our meal. We highly recommend the Baked Chicken Parmesan—it was absolutely delicious! A great experience all around!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMC3AKdGWBqxc-jukm25cD5f_HXE9kVmRakX-oM&fid=0x0:0xcb392bf507fb5484"],"When":"2024-12-8"},{"Name":"Nathan Ferlan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUBBwm7N9m9VsEZe8oXWT3QVjEQHlJhduQ22vfMGOziLtc2Ouo=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A Culinary Experience to Remember!

⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️

If you’re looking for a dining experience that leaves you craving more, look no further. I recently had the pleasure of indulging in the most exquisite Pasta & Prawns, and I’m still savoring every memory of it. Each bite was a masterpiece—perfectly cooked pasta with tender, flavorful prawns, all bathed in a rich, savory sauce that danced on my palate. The balance of flavors was simply divine, making it one of the best dishes I’ve ever had.

But what truly made the night unforgettable was the outstanding service. From the moment we arrived, the staff made us feel like we were more than just customers—they made us feel like family. Our server was down-to-earth, warm, and attentive in a way that made the whole evening feel special. Every request was met with a genuine smile and care that is rare to find.

The ambiance, the incredible food, and the impeccable service all came together to create a perfect dining experience. I had such a great time, and I’m already counting down the days until my next visit. Highly recommend!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP6ocpt4jzjfqUqjB2OE7Fa55VrOmI8L5U_KNDR&fid=0x0:0xcb392bf507fb5484"],"When":"2024-9-30"},{"Name":"James Mendonca","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKDOYVs1G-8iT9QF6Fj3_nUauDo1DS6zISrEp3lZ9wij4inDQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Pasta Polo is an exceptionally great Italian restaurant that serves quality food. You know the workers take pride in their food and service when they post the restaurant's review articles on the walls.

I ordered the Osso Bucco with the Virgin Purple Sour drink. I was served complimentary bread with my entrée that included butter and a bottle of fermented garlic. The bread tasted pretty great on its own while the garlic made it taste much better. The Osso Bucco was delicious with the Bolognese sauce. The side pesto pasta was very good and was well seasoned with parmesan. The non-alcoholic Purple Sour tasted excellent with its exceedingly sweet flavours.

The servers were very formal with their customers when it comes to preparing their tables. They check on me as often as possible during busy hours while maintaining a positive attitude. The establishment was dark yet classy and clean.

I look forward to eating as this restaurant again to try their other entrees.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNXlV9QLG73dgmJm2MgWDAp3IaT80Wb7UqKSEgR&fid=0x0:0xcb392bf507fb5484"],"When":"2024-12-15"},{"Name":"S Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWDCpcHtfixdQ1nlZ-cnjxErMYcSiJY3vif9B2kRQjg0W11mPsG=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It’s been a few months since we were here last. We ordered the chicken Marsala and gnocchi.  Both were delicious!  I love the Marsala sauce!  My husband enjoyed the garlic oil that was served with a bun.  The bun was ok. Could have been tastier.  I enjoy good bread and this wasn’t anything to write home about.  Service was excellent. We had Thea and she was great!  I also enjoyed their art gallery.  So much talent.  We will definitely be back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPZaMW99B_vyd2v_54Cdz758FoKxJtAP-r08b85&fid=0x0:0xcb392bf507fb5484"],"When":"2024-12-1"},{"Name":"Y Man","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUB62F2-VitrTkpd3TexeBmDt6LJ-Ec6lzQvbbyCIp7HJAIiB3b=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lovely Italian restaurant. The carbonara was tasty and creamy,  pasta is fresh and the sauce was enough to cover all the pasta and not drenched in it.  The meatballs were tender and mixed with fresh herbs,  a perfect meat side to the pasta.  The tiramisu was delicious,  creamy melts in your mouth.  Definitely coming back to try other dishes","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOdg_N9cATCFpMd2RK_yR7Qj4KSOp6mP1XOgxD7&fid=0x0:0xcb392bf507fb5484"],"When":"2024-9-20"},{"Name":"Marnie Eudela-Umlas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXg_gVRD_Hd9V3XIUh6_P71KHCryea9xsHYGqrZHTuXW_jdxEU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Spent our Mother’s Day celebration in this restaurant and we had a great time. Everything was awesome from food to their service. Our server even took our photos, too bad I forgot his name. The pizzas were all soo good and my fave was the Anchovy pizza. Pastas were yummy and their desserts too were all a treat. We will surely be back :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPbGw58cAzM4X4wXEw-LloHV5v2YTXfNlioydQo&fid=0x0:0xcb392bf507fb5484"],"When":"2024-7-2"}]

1 star - do not go here!  Stay away!!

3 stars - alright to good. I would not return here but you MAY enjoy it.
4 stars - I recommend it!  Yes, I’d like to return.
5 stars - drop everything now and come here!  You are missing out fo shizzle!!

The best SoonDae ever!!!!!! Just order #1 from the menu.
We paired GamJaJeon and MakGeolLee. An excellent choice.

The parking in the front is very limited. We would have been better  served if there were signs informing of more parking underground behind the building.

However, the best SoonDaeKook was sure worthy it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMbYdlDDSJuAYWhFaOmPLFNHnEzk8Q8diLg33uI&fid=0x0:0xbe37361ceb424bbb"],"When":"2023-8-31"},{"Name":"Winston D'souza","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUVogTkVZcv0-nP_G5TXVzg5jg606UQFZgLHkNtppuVrLRIwybg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"We are regular to this place. Pitcher is cheaper than other places and the  restaurant seems very clean and tidy.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNBfCPEFYk7SLJCSMZ7uqWLkpNEtQ8xyTd2rZ-M&fid=0x0:0x8696cccf7f56bf5a"],"When":"2024-11-6"},{"Name":"Eva Tong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUbdn1JwTeGwTMz4zaH_aM0s2MjqUg4f-ith9g4COdwAGXFieA4Ow=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My hubby’s sister came to visit us, she would like to try Korean food. We came across this restaurant. We ordered the pork hocks with oriental herbs, boiled squid, army soup and honey butter chicken. I would strongly recommend the pork hocks, even I’m not a fan of pork hocks but this is one of the best hocks I have tried so far.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMaH_QLO9UiZ7nKCsLgpkQH3VYH7w8288s5QBVf&fid=0x0:0x8696cccf7f56bf5a"],"When":"2023-4-12"},{"Name":"Pedram Habibzadeh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXnlNsGOq0wOKaUh-lvc2DG1IOnzI0Mdb7JS13yIyMx5GMRTfI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Of the -many- Korean restaurants I've tried, this place has my favorite iteration of Army Stew (budae-jjigae) so far. I usually enjoy it with their pa dak chicken. Always hits the spot!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jessameen Dela Peña","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX9mRpmL8-ZJUG7UPFcnsjzRdxjABif-MswbO1rxgJyyWfns8Jd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Ideal for late-night hangouts with its midnight closing time. This place exceeded our expectations with the delicious cheese buldak and beef yakiudon we tried. However, it's a bit on the pricey side!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMkxNxgFvFB-gbT0yy33CiMdQqbyy3GIOzCNjno&fid=0x0:0x8696cccf7f56bf5a"],"When":"2024-2-4"},{"Name":"Chloe D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUQcQz8Kl8hKO23hZqVCOss3Om6Wt10FQPjv4VNUIFeAKqYp8i8Ig=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The jokbal (pork hock) salad with jellyfish was very unique and tasty. It is the dish that sets this restaurant apart from others in my opinion. However, everything else I’ve tried at this restaurant were average and didn’t stand out to me","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNaKEoDKgTiQM_cdt32ylrlt3cATsWacFa6MbR7&fid=0x0:0x8696cccf7f56bf5a"],"When":"2023-5-2"},{"Name":"v l","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUdZvJxBhGRMKAh6ZoV-1pNG0RsqEMX0Q7xeTmMWZiQ1-rLiRu7Rg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Very authentic.  Feels like a small diner in Korea, even has the call bell button at the table.  Food was authentic too... really well rounded spicy dishes.  Spaced out, cozy seating, private.  Dishes are large, for sharing family style.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNh47H4b5M3p4oLwEBzGBMrbzU3qK2h-KPSu2KN&fid=0x0:0x8696cccf7f56bf5a"],"When":"2021-3-29"},{"Name":"John Mavrick","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWtlxEpvwpVyyZ_gqkRZIRms95G82FFcYgvYajFPC85ahCpMFWw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Friendly staff and good portions, perfect for a late night out with friends or family :) We had the padak, army soup, cheese corn with butter, kimchi pancakes, and galbi !","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNvz-HlCZdR0BcWNOBwpX0B07pAr6Lg5gumGyf7&fid=0x0:0x8696cccf7f56bf5a"],"When":"2021-9-25"},{"Name":"Minipa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXLkpsoXCUt-uCoPDrB_Mv40ZqSioejOqdNEdMQaklHEBDE1W1x=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I went to this restaurant with a few buddies after exercising at the aquatic center. It was about a 2 minute walk from the nearest free parking around 7:00pm. It was decently cold but I was well-dressed so it was okay.

We sat down and got the booth which had more than enough room for our party of four and the menu was very easy to understand with pictures and a small but tasty selection. We ended up getting the Tebboki or however you say it, some honey butter chicken, some fried squid, as well as the kimchi.

The chicken gave me a mouth orgasm, although, this could have been because I was rather inebriated on various cannabis products. However, I blinked and the food was gone. My spice tolerance is also decently high, so beware people that are not used to spicy food the tebboki might be a bit much. However, the rice offset the spicy flavour and made the meal a very good combo to eat together.

5/5 would recommend to people. Good service as well.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOQw8Rxz6aZZbrvFM_nKo_4BWjpM-J0jxH9gM-o&fid=0x0:0x8696cccf7f56bf5a"],"When":"2023-1-21"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Kaylee Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUrnelwesLWszVvjanLNlsfSIxKVIQPnh9SEyYTfIQJ3XkS9yt8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A great Italian spot near Como Lake area! The pizza with its thin crust and fresh ingredients is fantastic—definitely the best I've found within a 15-20 minute drive from Surrey. The carbonara is okay, but I'm hoping to try a better pasta option in their menu. The service is always friendly and welcoming. I visit almost every month for the excellent pizza and warm atmosphere!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPEuS0Mu6EwQyj-eOwZklsK5XdyKwUeWnRSKQ5P&fid=0x0:0xec9b84a60327fe07"],"When":"2024-11-5"},{"Name":"Tyler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX5pgqDcV4jXxCDs44gFpKqBE7-kpDe9pqH0qySpykt9h70rZWn=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"If you’re craving authentic Italian cuisine, The Golden Boot in Coquitlam is a must-visit. We recently dined there and had the Ferrari Pizza and the Funghi Pasta, and both dishes exceeded our expectations.

The Ferrari Pizza was a masterpiece of fresh ingredients and perfect execution. The thin, crispy crust paired beautifully with its rich toppings, striking the perfect balance between flavor and texture. It was clear that great care and quality ingredients went into every bite.

The Funghi Pasta was equally outstanding. The earthy richness of the mushrooms combined with a creamy sauce created a dish that was both comforting and indulgent. The pasta was perfectly cooked, and the flavors were well-balanced, making it one of the best pasta dishes we’ve had in a long time.

The Golden Boot offers more than just great food; it provides an inviting and cozy atmosphere that enhances the dining experience. The staff were warm, attentive, and knowledgeable, making our evening even more enjoyable.

If you’re looking for a fresh and authentic Italian experience in Coquitlam, The Golden Boot is a gem worth discovering. We can’t wait to return and explore more of their menu!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNBr1HapyFm5MQNZ6xipl9yNR8QHro3gqqHsWMA&fid=0x0:0xec9b84a60327fe07"],"When":"2024-12-11"},{"Name":"Jamie K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLbJ2U1LY4qMlQOmrUVddM2YAaHlcLuD0VLF8l26mbYtDI6YXU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Food was good especially pizza was delicious. I would love to come back to try different menus! We were not greeted by whoever was at cash desk but our server was very kind and friendly (was a young male, didnt grab his name)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNGWVloDIoqugcX7cgGNXPcXNx_7E-rP1ybD7lq&fid=0x0:0xec9b84a60327fe07"],"When":"2024-9-6"},{"Name":"Stephie N","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXd0_eqzaDNFpYKxu_At0QKV_opW1IXDZ3BtSf_D5LFw7-X91jS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Although I had heard about the Golden Boots restaurant from my friends and acquaintances for a long time, I finally had the chance to visit it with a friend yesterday. The place has a cozy, ‘hole in the wall’ atmosphere, and the food feels homemade. I especially enjoyed the lasagna and penne alla vodka. The service was prompt and kind. I will definitely keep going back to this restaurant.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMZDk4LyqX01zLqd_7wvJhWV6ZoirX1krVr-mP9&fid=0x0:0xec9b84a60327fe07"],"When":"2024-7-26"},{"Name":"Nathan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW6aOctokU9KmE5fwo6-6THfOky0imQyJSKP9b0jCAM3iXNSZtK=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"My wife and I came here for a date but left with a bittersweet taste. The staff are friendly and the sauce was amazing, but the pasta was quite hard and felt undercooked - I’m not sure if it’s supposed to be that way. For two dishes, we spent almost $60, hence the three star rating.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipModeQECB1BLCY6b-NGSlZLF_OwAKKZPDxognru&fid=0x0:0xec9b84a60327fe07"],"When":"2024-7-6"},{"Name":"Afreen J","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWL1ZeweaycOte33MDbmpSg8MtgerWXZP23M-ogg8fCZaa9zvz8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I discovered this place while in the neighbourhood. Great Italian place that is family owned.

Their food is amazing. The service is great and a great recommendation by the server for the pasta I had.

Will be back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPZJZ68qRTqpsh_LiMfgCNh5hjdJ0CnDClvi4V9&fid=0x0:0xec9b84a60327fe07"],"When":"2024-9-15"},{"Name":"Rick Z","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWc1RB-9qyXWMnytRLNxhH7YaYW62JkQs6KrpP4vpe5CjfhN98MBw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came here for dinner tonight and we were impressed. We got lucky as we showed up early without a reservation and someone left as we walked in and got the only available table. The service was excellent. The pasta was really really good. Fresh made hot and lots of flavourful sauce. We will for sure be back to this family run restaurant. You can see they have pride in their food.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Darryn Tsuen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKbDcjC9Ga-8tH4ExWmugm3iFb6E8r94-zSVfwYhntq2jgWeiA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Delicious Italian cuisine 😋. One of my favorite spots in Coquitlam. Everything is spot on taste, portion and pricing isn't bad. Highly recommend.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMG11zyOX96tJIT3Djhz-EM-uVWkZRWZGbFEXum&fid=0x0:0xec9b84a60327fe07"],"When":"2024-6-10"}]

[{"Name":"A F Sidd","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVGDYN08fV6LM29cRcSDRaG5MvFASAFkWejOMDKL0j-lPeMRYj3rg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"5 Stars - delicious Kabab and rice
This place serves the best halal Persian kebab cuisine in town! The food was incredibly fresh and flavorful. We tried a variety of kebabs, including lamb, beef, chicken, and the lamb shank, and everything was juicy, tender, and absolutely delicious. The Qabli rice and white rice were standout dishes—perfectly cooked and full of flavor.

Although the seating area is small, the quality and taste of the food make it well worth the visit. Prices are very reasonable for the generous portion sizes. To top off our meal, we enjoyed their refreshing saffron tea, which was the perfect ending.

A big shoutout to the lady who served us—she was so polite, kind, and attentive, making our experience even better.

We’ll definitely be coming back soon. Highly recommended for anyone looking for amazing Persian food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPfTL7e6UuXBTlcSNnnx7QWZmgQTbOrInlGgi9h&fid=0x0:0x525b8aa9fd0793d"],"When":"2024-12-17"},{"Name":"James Chen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXwJo6T4E0NKsKnDpsBZaZfvtpSMVqQgbfnZDp8I06YSjhudP1t=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our first time having Persian food. Of course I have no way to tell if it's authentic or not but I must say it is very very good. The kebabs were tender and flavourful. The lamb shank was falling off the bone and packed with spices. Food is made to order so there's a little bit of a wait but it's well worth it. Oh and the portion sizes are very generous.

Would definitely eat here again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOGemjXRvrtqK-6E1iW1NhUw1DDH5UKpmlG8tEe&fid=0x0:0x525b8aa9fd0793d"],"When":"2024-7-8"},{"Name":"Sai Vignesh Vaidyam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjViQZ0ANuA-DlocAip5YGRdcMfgbQgwg6LWcYBm8LjEAQA4WcqA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fantastic Persian food. We visit there every other week. We always get the Vaziri kebab and Jojoeh kebab plates. Their kebab are delicious, fresh, tender, and rich in flavor. The rice is fluffy and mildly flavored. Overall recommend it for their food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPfY3HmLR-uDptnM_Jkk14P9iCBSQIcOLgo8x46&fid=0x0:0x525b8aa9fd0793d"],"When":"2024-10-19"},{"Name":"Shay Azizi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKjipKjRGya7wl8SRyI-u7R2Sb2ASl_o0vT2bXwYLUdB_zUmA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We tried their catering services, it was phenomenal, and I was able to customize the menu for my event.
Everyone loves the food, and the kids love the pizza. It was very delicious, the price is amazing for the quality and the portion you get. A 10/10😋","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOQzHF74zx9wql6ymdX_PiSMBbI4AIO6O7Z4Z5G&fid=0x0:0x525b8aa9fd0793d"],"When":"2024-10-11"},{"Name":"Jaime Ricafrente","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXAJwwcGATN2RuHMthkyt1rjxVqb7NF_uxVYPAzS1OSfFJWO9Wn6g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love this place and the family that runs it.  Everytime I buy dinner the family makes me feel like I am part of them family.  I am not exaggerating, they really do.  The food is already AMAZING.  I don't really eat Lamb but the daughter recommended it.  I tried it.  Mic drop.  IT F'N DELICIOUS!   I take it home amd every bite is heaven.  Stop reading this and order their food already.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO5f5JVOBbsBXRJJ-gDwCvARVv-pVD5sislK-EB&fid=0x0:0x525b8aa9fd0793d"],"When":"2024-10-31"},{"Name":"Yosuf Naseri","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUwnDuPqbfHpu2ivNEx7g3C8JM4pgykFcmQ2olsxYMtp3M2014=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"“5/5 - Hands down, the best kabob and pizza I’ve ever had! You can feel the passion and pride they have in their work. Whether you’re a local or just passing through, this place is a must-visit. Incredible people, incredible food. Highly recommended!”","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"S K (OxtailGravy)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIINjUguJePPet75HTnX-unbS8rsk4LQ_Ku9eCz7eh0Wy--ZQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great service and super tasty food. Everything was seasoned perfectly. The meat was so tender and juicy. I really enjoyed my meal. Thank you.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM_a2n6mG1aRa1dVhpkKCujmxzIkGP6FTMWAs4J&fid=0x0:0x525b8aa9fd0793d"],"When":"2024-8-29"},{"Name":"Daniyal Ganatra","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVrce7kOVSHZWu0BGXNifFqnhrhZt0zVPIrDt4lja-Oz-58eu04=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our go to place when we are craving for Juicy Persian Kebabs and don't want to dine in!!

[{"Name":"P Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVlXs2TzM2uknqo2ufsT0wYUNB2JKpkK3UD6GmafGZl0UHRXQ4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Great cozy place. The donairs were average. The chicken was the tastiest. Very expensive for what it was. $43 for 1 large and 2 small donairs and a drink. Tried it but unfortunately we will not go back. The customer service could improve, we were not met with much kindness. I even got in trouble for trying to leave a google review and snapping some pictures being kind and saying nice things about this restaurant. FYI it is a public place and there are no laws to prevent filming. There is no washroom which I believe is against code. There is sign saying nobody is allowed in there and not out of service. Strange. Nice place though. Cozy. Your welcome for the review. Cheer up guys!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPmGfiiXHKopalUlXtDyjXwojwbcUZNpwl9joX8&fid=0x0:0xc69486f80adfef38"],"When":"2024-8-18"},{"Name":"Kate Choi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIjE4MSAa0c4Uqc8iOt1LfqIkJDL1ULa2Z17gRh4YDWMExQ1A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Small parkling lot right beside it which is convenient. It is tucked away from the main spots for restaurants though so not a lot of traffic here.

The prices are fantastic. Around 12 something for a platter. These days it's up to 15-17. I expected less quantity but they give big portions.

The lady serving me was very detailed oriented, slowly stacking the salad making sure pieces dont fall over. The hummus was in a small plastic container that is put into one section of the platter plate. It'd be less waste if they just plopped on the hummus like other places. They give plenty of meat to cover the rice. I asked for extra garlic sauce and they were happy to give it.

The chicken was nice. Not dry. The lamb however was soggy like it was steamed too long after shaving the pieces. The rice was also disappointing and was way overcooked and soggy.

I think they could be a really great place if they can fix the sogginess of the rice and lamb.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPzkx4A3-Rbt5Xe_z2vW_fcA9kqhZGNyS4NzZ8C&fid=0x0:0xc69486f80adfef38"],"When":"2024-4-19"},{"Name":"May Zhagro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU9KviWdU_UGm6yjKPv-6aFaljm1EC_ecrxYhnt_LO3duiyBNho=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Small take out / sit down venue with a good one page of selections. Reasonable prices with reasonable portions. Food is made fresh. Platter can choose between rice and fries. Rice was a bit spicy but very flavourful. Fresh veggies on the side. Dining area is clean and not overcrowded. Small parking lot shared with adjoining businesses but not very busy. Overall great experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOB81_UEOFRfGn1VICD0_80zei-owiO4A3E_AwM&fid=0x0:0xc69486f80adfef38"],"When":"2023-6-5"},{"Name":"David Durango","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV_2PesKmt-cFSjzAWF8ZpvzKFIQfYWeYB7sfNc7YronxWjhwaDKw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"To be honest, I couldn't finish my donair.  It was DELICIOUS but TOO BIG!!
I got the smaller lamb fries donair so I can't imagine how big the "large" must be. The price is very good too. Also, this is the best looking donair place I have ever been to in the tri-cities. It's tastefully decorated with real plants and great art. A very relaxing and excellent place. However I do suggest they add a bit more sauce to the donairs. If you come, ask for that! Apart from this, it is very recommended.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNDqphhv6OjweUv5cVW4wGn53ipIAMcGYBsayRz&fid=0x0:0xc69486f80adfef38"],"When":"2023-10-3"},{"Name":"Rich B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVoQ-WXqpj4r3w8UAKcm_AnoI410Sm3LNTYN6x5shslunTgL988=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Where I grew up we only had Subcity’s for donairs… I half heartedly didn’t want to post this review just so I could keep this place for myself lol.  These donairs aren’t for the faint hearted and this place means some serious business.  So either try them out or just leave them to rest of us! Haha","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNEjX2AfRPdAJ1VRgisBYnYwHMWWF7TcGYxws4h&fid=0x0:0xc69486f80adfef38"],"When":"2024-6-22"},{"Name":"Nika Moeini","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVsFWIuYGkU_vQ-SNFAaTjcl5dIFjZe-4IFc2dLJ4QKoHNKEpklHw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really lovely service from Uncle Moe at Uncle Moe’s donair. Grateful for the vegan option of the felafel plate! Hope they can add more vegan and vegetarian options in the future.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP4jtK9sC9_UujXlTiUWlsHe528b9Ey8aYPE6ij&fid=0x0:0xc69486f80adfef38"],"When":"2024-5-31"},{"Name":"Rachel Fontinha","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUWNj7fASKyewm3nmFMWCcFvbVg-ooLx-XqWjzN_sPfW-srGks=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A gem.

This was our first time trying Uncle Moe's and we had such a great experience. We were warmly welcomed by every face in there, each person said hello with a smile. The lady behind the counter (I'm assuming the owner?) welcomed us as if we were long-time customers and because of this we instantly knew the food here would be made with love. The atmosphere was very warm and family-oriented. It makes you feel like you're in a safe space and it is very comfortable in there.

We ordered the donair combos, I had beef with everything and all sauces and my partner had chicken with everything but no hot sauce. The combos came with fries and a can of pop.

These are some of the best donairs we've ever eaten! And they were huge! The beef and the chicken were season nicely and they were very juicy and fresh. They load it up with meat! The vegetables were fresh, crunchy, and juicy.. it was pleasant. And the sauces were flavourful and delicious. They put just the right amount of everything in these donairs, all of the flavours balance out perfectly.

The fries are their own catagory- they are so fresh and crispy! Wow! No seasoning or salt is needed on these fries, they are delicious by themselves. We did, however, put the last few bites of our donairs into the fries and mixed it up. And it was a fantastic combination. Highly recommend.
We will be back to try the poutine when we are in the area.

My partner has their heart set on 1 donair place in vancouver as their all-time favorite but they said Uncle Moe's is easily the next pick. As for myself, I say Uncle Moe's has the best donair.

All in all I would highly recommend this place to any donair lover, you will not be disappointed in any aspect! 5 stars all across the board. Good job guys, thank you so much for the hospitality and delicious, filing food. We will be back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNy9QCYzXdNPS2y__RbiYDi7vhKRc91NqytLnRe&fid=0x0:0xc69486f80adfef38"],"When":"2023-9-24"},{"Name":"Vikrant Patel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUptTxISAEHRdbzBbZSuM8ZHn-RjdVeH08Qt7ghgs8AUKHbEiwgTA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Family run business serving the local community with great service. They have a nice selection of Donner with veg and non veg options.

We really enjoyed our wraps and rice dishes.

If passing through this town or live around it then definitely try it and you wont be disappointed.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPU2ba-5S3zhgWWbVEpb9Q0uT3X7EcFL-W-xrIA&fid=0x0:0xc69486f80adfef38"],"When":"2022-7-23"}]

[{"Name":"Jessameen Dela Peña","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX9mRpmL8-ZJUG7UPFcnsjzRdxjABif-MswbO1rxgJyyWfns8Jd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The food was decent, and the experience was enjoyable, but I’m unsure if it’s worth a return visit. The service also took a bit longer than anticipated.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM4ROFsnf93KhJeqBR3yZh_LOKAdmCTo8PR3XU0&fid=0x0:0x44571a2bfa63ef77"],"When":"2024-12-8"},{"Name":"james findlay","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLt84_RgdMpRogmDX-lDIyrbCZ45814V53LA5wsiIYzjATJeQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This restaurant will never challenge for anything more than authentic clutter of trays of dirty dishes stacked by the bar and a very ordinary seating area that makes no illusions about being decent and nice. The ladies who are both front and back are not English speaking but we are okay with the idea that they don't cater to a Caucasion crowd that much (but they should try to). We have gone there 4 times now and the first two the food justified the sparse interior.  But the last visit about 9 months ago for take out dinner not so much. We live a 30 minute drive away so we expect a special feast when we go there and the prices are not cheap. They charge as if they are top drawer and they have been in the past in my opinion. Their take out this time was skimpy!!!  The deep fried won ton is now some store bought cheap and frugal version and the portion we received was unsatisfying for us three. It was not the robust and plentiful won ton we received on our first visit. And for twenty bucks we get a meagre portion. Sweet and sour really not great either and again for the price why go so cheap! Lastly our fish dish was bland and boring and served in a medium takeaway plastic bowl that could have been a good meal for one, but was rationed out by the spoonful to be fair.
So what is your attraction Deer Garden? Friendly welcoming service from your ladies? No thank yous and we didn't feel like our business was appreciated. Good food in portions that justified our 60 bucks?  Nope.  Or maybe I should exercise your tip option....what a joke!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Daniel Jung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFE7g6vnjf23CW6mDeh4anchF8fxBs6O5Nsx0bvhepuO3MVzWa=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Did takeout, fried rice tasted great just not sure if it was worth $20 but I still enjoyed it.
Place was busy and service was normal standards.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM5lWG8kBGGZq2ozzxm8mJdeCEN8z-hUL73EFSA&fid=0x0:0x44571a2bfa63ef77"],"When":"2024-11-11"},{"Name":"Anna Zhu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ02jEC0GbE8rA7lyoVVPGxTbOAvDoh1bAmNxeRbS-LbgtI4w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had takeout order of one of their speciality sweet and sour pork, which had thin batter and good quality of pork. Also beef fried rice was unexpectedly delicious. Both were outstanding. Surely will return and order again.

And very friendly customer service!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMepgu3BLhdoIeLn80Zj61C3rF69WMzkgHlml3Q&fid=0x0:0x44571a2bfa63ef77"],"When":"2023-12-24"},{"Name":"CASEY LU","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLgeCpn0LhtSJ0EVTEqBJLUv8bYrl0aK4SzX8G4nXXW8dcHtA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We rushed in for a late lunch almost 3pm  The owner recommended us to try their Four meat balls noodle which was absolutely delicious. The thin noodle just tasted like Hong Kong’s.  The curry beef brisket also just the right taste.  Next time we will definitely go back try their sweet and sour pork.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alvin Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUpasldH6X4K8TtkMbIbac-orAN0Eb0jJ-m74oWvWE0xRNC-us=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"All servers are very friendly! Glad to taste the best handmade noodle in Metro Vancouver so far! Tripe is soft and very tasty, not to mention the wonton, beef balls and HK-styled milk tea. Prices are very reasonable given the quality and generous portion of dishes! Will come back for sure!😋😋","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPcVzaxAPM2faZ5kI0H2ZsmesWqEHnxZo6snzg1&fid=0x0:0x44571a2bfa63ef77"],"When":"2021-9-19"},{"Name":"J C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVRid-486EHf3vFFlqzxc7hc71kbL9n1FDLFiUelrs10b7uY4If=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Interesting resto that seems to be doing well from take out business.  Big space but they only use maybe a quarter of it with two waitresses.  We tried their curry beef and it seems off compared to when they were at their old location outside of the mall.  Still good but just off and the pieces are higher.  I didn’t expect to pay almost $60 for two simple dishes.  Will come back if I’m craving curry.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOaP67dvqo2sdyYwP142fhxisNr-DWWBZECcjiV&fid=0x0:0x44571a2bfa63ef77"],"When":"2023-4-14"},{"Name":"v l","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUdZvJxBhGRMKAh6ZoV-1pNG0RsqEMX0Q7xeTmMWZiQ1-rLiRu7Rg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really friendly service. The food is typical HK/Chinese cafe -- noodles, congee, milk tea...etc.  Lobster and crab special meals available but must order in advance.  Love the steam milk dessert!

Update... been back several times and the food, service are consistently excellent!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMYf29Z5mZxMwxqKILN1Kol-IYrxi33V6oBbcRo&fid=0x0:0x44571a2bfa63ef77"],"When":"2021-6-7"}]

[{"Name":"Ca Media","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVrWY3NtfDMrrfIyiF99Bkud8n1enS71zA5IqjAZySXq1LlIpY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I am deeply disgusted and upset by my experience at this restaurant, both due to what I found in my food and the owner's rude response. While we were halfway through our fries, waiting for the main course, we discovered a chicken bone among them—something that appeared to be part of someone’s leftovers.

When I brought this to the owner's attention, rather than apologizing, she attempted to justify the contamination. She argued that the chicken bone might have ended up in our fries because the same deep-fry basket and oil were used for both chicken and fries. Even if this explanation were accurate, it is entirely unacceptable and unhygienic.

We left the restaurant without receiving a proper apology, feeling unheard and disrespected. This experience was not only unpleasant but also concerning from a food safety perspective.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN6dC70QDNbKSMRKLJ3G9IecJr0_mOmJ0pXMDMB&fid=0x0:0xae7b86714c63c62f"],"When":"2024-12-6"},{"Name":"peyman alamesh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIh14BLAkO2Ok8oQuCYa5ZqPQcRZqabouP1Xpr0AFYX6chAaA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"“An Unforgettable Culinary Experience!”
I recently had the pleasure of dining at [restaurant name], and it was truly a memorable experience. From the moment we walked in, the warm and welcoming ambiance set the tone for a perfect evening.

The food was absolutely incredible—every dish was a celebration of authentic Iranian flavors. The kebabs were perfectly grilled, tender, and flavorful, while the saffron rice and tahdig were cooked to perfection. The appetizers, especially the kashk-e bademjan and mast-o khiar, were a delightful start to the meal.

The service was exceptional, with friendly and attentive staff who went above and beyond to make sure everything was perfect. The attention to detail in both the food presentation and hospitality was impressive.

If you’re looking to enjoy a taste of Persian culture and cuisine, this restaurant is a must-visit. I can’t wait to come back and try more dishes!

Feel free to personalize it based on your specific experience!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPRC2TAD0zbwIAOV3v0qY2ELBDr7kKstsL-psxY&fid=0x0:0xae7b86714c63c62f"],"When":"2024-12-18"},{"Name":"Limping Ninja","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVEnsg6wB_b4XFmIHZf5Dk-Fs3hq6WGzzbCBHgVgDVv5FAQ28Bfqg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Lovely atmosphere, very nice tasting lamb and well cooked rice, with a smile and attentive staff - what more can you ask for!

The food took longer to come out, but it was freshly made and the portions are fantastic. Thank you TiTi!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPicqUikH6VXF3GIAu3yXi5zt6IDGwGQyrDIY5U&fid=0x0:0xae7b86714c63c62f"],"When":"2024-8-22"},{"Name":"Negin Rahimi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV4DUUoCWRf2VeIHKqwIhVGBDp6aPH06WL8KyLGIL_eC6FWBXb5=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently had an intense craving for Persian-style pizza, and my taste buds were blown away when a friend suggested I try Titi Restaurant. This is not only offers a diverse range of delectable dishes, including pizza and chicken kebab, but their cooking is simply divine. The quality, portion size, and flavors of the dishes were absolutely fantastic. Everything exceeded my expectations in terms of taste and presentation. On a late-night pickup, I was pleasantly surprised by the warm hospitality of the owners and the kind-hearted staff, who despite their exhaustion, treated me with the utmost kindness. While waiting for my order, I engaged in a delightful conversation with them. I cannot emphasize enough how highly I recommend this restaurant. You simply have to try their entire menu. Congrats to the team at Titi Restaurant!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMZsaf4OS_S22DuA5YJPzW5ZXnDbZvrVOomD8v2&fid=0x0:0xae7b86714c63c62f"],"When":"2024-6-16"},{"Name":"Brian Krause","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWdP7woIjNOL63V37wHT09kxdTUjnvdRus14yp9YD6p7IyLBnc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Big portion and pizza was tasty. Bathrooms very clean. Ambience a bit slow/laid back but enjoyed experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipON0WnxfAezTu8bYRSgHFC7uG10zBcIDAE_unuC&fid=0x0:0xae7b86714c63c62f"],"When":"2024-11-25"},{"Name":"Nazanin Eskandari","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUTrW5zYZ1EYPClt_zOeVHFz8Qz1spDq65vXAskRtnqhRxUqSQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently visited this Iranian restaurant in Canada multiple times, and I have to say, their "Fesenjan" stew and kebabs are amazing! Each dish is packed with authentic flavors and beautifully presented. Highly recommend it!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPjFexRAsQK7DJsb-rw9XpWJ3eeYhPLAbh7z9gQ&fid=0x0:0xae7b86714c63c62f"],"When":"2024-9-23"},{"Name":"zey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLQZkkgMj8lJ8cQAPaQLN0nMqKvKWJRbFjom0wk11K44rygyw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The quality, quantity and price of food was excellent, fair and competitive. But when u order by Skip the Dishes expect delay more than half an hour. It takes more than an hour when it should be less than 30 minutes. I know this is not Titi fault but this impacts on restaurant reputation and they have to follow up the reason and fix the issue.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ali Shirazi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWzf4KVzISXZ9WpQa0kDI1joNREQjKZOjIp2Zn0BKoJ3Gs3_hvq=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I visited TiTi  a few months ago with my non-Persian colleagues and unfortunately, our experience was not as positive as expected. Despite the restaurant's good reputation, we encountered several issues during our visit.
1.	Pricing Confusion: The price for a specific dish was different for takeout compared to dining in, which wasn’t clearly indicated in the advertisement outside. This led to some confusion and disappointment considering the service fee and expected tips.
2.	Service Issues: The waitress was not as friendly as we had hoped, and her attitude was noticeably different when serving non-Persian guests. Additionally, she insisted that I speak in Persian with her, which felt inappropriate.
3.	Order Mistake: One of our orders was initially incorrect. Although the correct dish was eventually brought to us, the delay was inconvenient.
4.	Tea and Dessert: When ordering tea and dessert, we were told the tea pot was only enough for two people, despite it being sufficient for our group of five. Also, when we asked for extra candy, the waitress’s attitude seemed unwelcoming, even though the candy was a minor request.
5.	Billing Process: The process of splitting the bill for tea and dessert was not accommodated. We were told that one person must pay the entire bill, and we would need to settle among ourselves later. This was quite odd and embarrassing, especially since splitting bills is a common practice.
6. The quality of food was fair.
While we appreciate the restaurant's efforts to provide a unique dining experience, these issues made our visit less enjoyable. We hope these points can be taken into consideration to improve the overall service and ensure a better experience for future guests.
Thank you.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Ping D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV-_KBk5-yIGzGmKAkX1L-6QPRrz_RZKkgRnIY4il5exhoL_sw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"There was only one staff in the early morning but he was extremely efficient. The cranberry turkey sandwich was surprisingly delicious. Cream inside pistachio bun was on the sweeter side but would be a good choice as dessert. Wish price can be lower, so that I can come back regularly.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNxEsqgdYQlHDlZlCYuy0cl7Drwho52YwlHjKCh&fid=0x0:0xda419efba462c144"],"When":"2024-9-7"},{"Name":"Danilo Teodoro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU_rV4_xok36vIezJ6uAhpzSfyECA8ogmjA4ehyXVTr4dBqIAFv=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"First time I tried their bun with pistachio and the turkey bagel, and they were good! The cappuccino was good as well. I tried the Turkish coffee just because it's been years since the last one, and it was very strong, as usual. I'm glad I knew how this type of coffee is made and didn't stir the liquid.
The toilets needed some love..","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNHVVDDLtjxI1rM7Dy_3mg1tubzrGtmjT7wNGaz&fid=0x0:0xda419efba462c144"],"When":"2024-6-11"},{"Name":"Alecia Hack","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU0y1s7Bm_wrj5Zk4QFomT2h-qOh3c4CJw37lBhykQlV1HXtuw4ww=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve come here a couple of times and I’m completely obsessed with this place! Cant wait to go back soon, thanks for a great experience!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMyHEfOUN4bSSLdn0q7eE6t88Gu1R7qdGPR22CG&fid=0x0:0xda419efba462c144"],"When":"2024-11-6"},{"Name":"Mavis Gevido","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVC-AP02ZE-ah41YCH68XbacnGEFbWfIc3R3T9FQiOBp_VcLYiP_A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great selection of coffee buns and the ones we tried were all so good! Relaxing atmosphere, good space. Highly recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMUNszxgua9dx1DrmJ42Rm939D2PVomTSIp69Fc&fid=0x0:0xda419efba462c144"],"When":"2024-8-23"},{"Name":"Ray","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXGVd5s-06Fr3JDo-bYWWNiziS7uiGN7g2hEorOk1Vp-qtDK_-cTg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love the concept of their buns. They have a lot of different flavors, and I tried the pistachio one. The bun is better than what I expected-- I expected a flavorless, chewy/tough bun but it had a great fried flavor and chew to it, made indulgent by the toppings of cream and pistachios.
I also had a toasted salmon lox bagel which had a generous amount of cream cheese, I loved every bit of it.
Very friendly and welcoming service!
It was quite busy.
I would definitely come back if I were in the area 😆","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPMEcOHD1pKqbcUepyj1ihb-fvVuAsZ3n-9iqr_&fid=0x0:0xda419efba462c144"],"When":"2024-1-15"},{"Name":"Zaayer Nasib","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVkh0fpj6mvCROx8j1Ux0TdNtszR1GgFfGTRvlt6JMDCheOJwvK=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ratings Scale 0 - 10
Variety: 8
Service or Product: 8
Customer Service: 8
Environment: 8
Cleaning: 8
Washroom: 7
Cost: 7

Tried a few of the buns, all of which were served fresh and hot! The ice cream bun was a delightful experience of warm bun and cold ice cream, but you have to be a little quick otherwise it starts melting really fast. The drinks were equally yummy. I had the hot chocolate which was perfect!
They have plenty of tables which was pretty good since there were quite a few people. There's only paid parking nearby though which was the only negative I see.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN0IOQFvGUF-_OZnnytcmsz4gQreANuw04M0Tk6&fid=0x0:0xda419efba462c144"],"When":"2021-5-16"},{"Name":"La Mc","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ3bmuxSiXCjm1iot5JpVUU_Lxxw4iPTmDpAUVL9Q9e-760ag=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cute place with fresh buns!

Very bright location with a few tables outside.

Need to come back and try other flavours!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOQryY1DW2BwXBGxMAb_y7tat0BDpJD4G0vlOCs&fid=0x0:0xda419efba462c144"],"When":"2024-8-4"},{"Name":"Rochelle Barrett","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWfUfMrQqNwSQLSz_oSIsTrz93OXwAr4KrdgHWS4xUKxTxBh4cgIQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This was my first visit, despite living at the opposite end of the block!

I was there just after open and it was very quiet. I was able to stare at the menu without pressure, which I appreciated.

I got their Spanish latte. I'm not sure I have ever loved a coffee more. It was so dark and rich coffee flavours. I considered proposing to the barista, it was that good.

I hear their Turkey sandwich on cranberry sourdough, absolutely drool worthy!!! Creamy, savoury and sweet, perfect balance and the sour of the sourdough came through just enough.

Lastly, I had the gluten ginger cookie they out sourced from Wendell's. I did not love it. It was grainy but not their fault and I really appreciate they bring in options for multiple dietary requirements.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPvTAeW_Ad9YU9AOS6XyvZZ8C-blZKGBy516Jo6&fid=0x0:0xda419efba462c144"],"When":"2021-6-13"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Yeshvi Mehta","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVVHHFZUwt0pnim38TVGVDQUhu3Obi33NtK1Ek9rBbru761t74M=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I happened to be in the area, and was craving some thing Indian. Found this place nearby and we chose to dine in.
The service was super quick and kind, even though we were pretty close to last call on a weekday. The interiors are cute & cozy, felt like I was sitting comfortably at home.

The food was also great! We licked our plates clean!! I would totally come back.
We ordered:
- Daal makhani
- malai kofta
- paneer tikka

The only thing I wouldn’t order again is the masala papad, it’s a simple dish and I feel like I’ve had it better and so worth a try here, but not worth ordering again. I could recommend using better quality papad (this tasted like the microwavable ones I buy) and adding cilantro on top!
I can also suggest skipping the rasamalai and gajar ka halwa.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNSDjFW06q2OYUYcOeDlM0qXqAsx7PriBcfC29x&fid=0x0:0x35dd030f9f55b602"],"When":"2024-11-15"},{"Name":"Y L.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKV887-1nS5R1_0KzCym2KWUc3U6pndK939JM55kJWey6Ce8Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time we tried this place from map search. We ordered Chicken vindaloo and Kadai Paneer and some fish and veggie sidedish. Everything was very tasty, and the curry had lots of stuff inside. Their galric naan was very savory. The service was amazing! Sunday mid afternoon, and most tables were full. Will come back with family.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNOELPHUm52kqW3zDV3koxo5VImAINHyx18l_Jm&fid=0x0:0x35dd030f9f55b602"],"When":"2024-7-21"},{"Name":"Katie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJN3p8cZHE5md15OEErKZKNn97Wi4lfH4nosGtOcXvlYGz2XA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The sauce is delicious but I can definitely tell the chick is not fresh. I really want to like this place. I ordered butter chicken many times but the chicken*always* doesn't taste fresh. It tasted like they used frozen chicken or old chicken. Please make this place better!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"陈晓景","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKGC0re95jO_hDOolePpTdMH_6cWbYDgFuh210eUCCpyMpiSQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Food is delicious and service is quick and good. Backgroud music volume could be a little lower. Nice a small but clean spot with a beautiful Indian style chandelier.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM-JksCwe0tHsc-A7xhUiCTe9CsUtM0Cyc1Kmfg&fid=0x0:0x35dd030f9f55b602"],"When":"2024-7-7"},{"Name":"Linda N","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIuD1_pd2ly4vtFhb8M-kjUT3J9JuCYtyHfu9UlF8IRT0IUpuI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cute and cozy Indian restaurant. I absolutely love their food! Their butter chicken is so mouth-watering good. Service was great and staff is extremely friendly. 10/10 recommend and will definitely be coming back for more :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMXf8xMYxAiAkIocwrP_DFEwgjR_QP6IvaAPonY&fid=0x0:0x35dd030f9f55b602"],"When":"2023-7-16"},{"Name":"Dennis Chinatambi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIGLJfwmSynbs1NwEL5QNU9ukic8SU2FJpZcOR9o9KT1JGzLQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Milaap Indian Kitchen has become our goto spot for Indain food in the Tri-Cities. We mostly do take out and found the food to be tasty, authentic  and good portions. The food is aways ready on time for pickup and the staff is friendly and welcoming. Highly recommended!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nat A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWnjKr4KNFAObzj2bIvH9BRInxwKsSvEg1PM25bKfvhxtWZTWHoog=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"This is a small restaurant with about 4 tables. It wasn't too busy inside. They were able to put two tables together to accommodate our group of 5 adults and 4 kids. More customers were coming in for pick up.

My favorite dish was the Palak Paneer. The flavor was so good! The honey garlic cauliflower was something different which was also very good. I preferred the Butter Chicken rather than the Butterica. The Butter Chicken had a lot more flavor and spice. My main dish was the Goat Curry. The goat was nice and tender but I found the sauce a little salty. The garlic naan was very fresh tasting and had good flavor.

Overall, many of the dishes were good and the server was friendly and helpful with describing dishes.

I would definitely come back to try more.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMjVHWe5_Z1UvW7YTHaCkuTZGDbrNMCiP5Dy9-2&fid=0x0:0x35dd030f9f55b602"],"When":"2022-12-23"},{"Name":"wilsonjoshwilson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVPoK02al9DYZ9GLC0wDSU4FEAZAAPuuG6qlzOOh_26eyk877fT=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Ordered Milaap via UberEats.

I ordered the butter chicken, rice, garlic naan and two samosas.

Let’s start with the samosas..not great. I’ve had a lot of samosas in my day, but unfortunately these are some of the worst.

Tasted like unseasoned potatoes with a slight hint of masala..Very underwhelming.

As for the butter chicken, it had a decent flavour. I ordered hot and the sauce had a good amount of kick. The taste itself was a bit lacking in the depth department, but still satisfied my craving.

Some chicken pieces were a tad dry and it felt like the chicken wasn’t overly seasoned. Again, I ordered via Uber, so the quality could be better if the food didn’t have to travel.

As for the rest of the food, I enjoyed the garlic naan and didn’t have issues with the rice.

If you do end up dining here, I would suggest eating at the establishment for a fresher experience.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Rachel R.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV8jVjnRga5YL7aTezZpTCt_6ZsgK_4rtqhAOo2ynzGa5S3gkVauA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food was excellent and very tasty. The prices and portion sizes were reasonable, and the ambiance was perfect. However, the service could have been improved; our server didn’t check on us frequently enough to refill our water or offer us additional drinks. On a positive note, she did give us a complimentary dessert—a slice of cake with a candle—since I was celebrating my birthday. Overall, it was a great choice for a dining experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOQMZ8Ffd-cqer3BB8ck4z2tpthF000_2uW65dk&fid=0x0:0x8a834a2eb78c2221"],"When":"2024-11-28"},{"Name":"John Cantillas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXcyiYFg8BGPrNb-kZxFHp3rbTEqWVw5CXGDd2KlPDKQrWr3m8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Me and my wife celebrated our wedding anniversary here at The Keg last night. It was our first time dining in into this restaurant. The experience was so great. The food and drinks was phenomenal, the Prime ribs was so good that I finished all the 14oz steak. The complimentary Billy Miner Pie was so freaking good that I want to order another one.

Also, that awesome guy Alex, he is very informative and his service was great. We had an awesome night because he always provide what we need.

To sum up everything, we just had a great experience and definitely going back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMf39Ur7X14QdujZ1BLpm4yOKMxM-heMK5-5tlC&fid=0x0:0x8a834a2eb78c2221"],"When":"2024-7-10"},{"Name":"May Zhagro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU9KviWdU_UGm6yjKPv-6aFaljm1EC_ecrxYhnt_LO3duiyBNho=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The Keg is our go-to to celebrate special occasion in our lives. We love the ambiance, the servers, and the way that they cook their steak. Appetizers are also great like the oysters which came with three sauces to try. The potato mash is a great side dish with your steak. The Caesar salad this time around wasn’t as good though, which was a little bit disappointing as I was looking forward to it. Otherwise, we had delicious food and an enjoyable time at The Keg.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP3_RBZeeep_5_lgaUQa4EBUD2lBOw9rDMwVK4s&fid=0x0:0x8a834a2eb78c2221"],"When":"2024-8-24"},{"Name":"Penny Rusty Sophie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUkGfXMIDqwS_yD1axTk6tkHoLsnybE2ErvKrHMoMIElMJWekI_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"One of the many Keg locations - we visited in mid-September.

Here's what we had:
Agua Fresca ($7) - not bad.
French Onion Soup ($14) - I liked this and it was cheesy but it was a bit light with the actual amount of onions in the soup.
10 Oz Prime Rib ($42) - Super thin slice of prime rib. They said they were running out if prime rib and I'm wondering if this was actually 10 oz or if they were just trying to stretch it out so bit.
Brussels Sprouts - One of the better items we had on this day.
Sticky Toffee Pudding - A bit of a let down as it wasn't really sticky. It felt more like eating a dense cake. I really wish they would bring back the brownie sundae.

Service was slow","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOqac-co_Pn31iQgOAY87hCJ3joU7ZRzuoy23j_&fid=0x0:0x8a834a2eb78c2221"],"When":"2024-10-22"},{"Name":"Jessameen Dela Peña","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX9mRpmL8-ZJUG7UPFcnsjzRdxjABif-MswbO1rxgJyyWfns8Jd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We were quickly accommodated and seated in a nice, cozy booth. The staff was friendly and attentive. While the steak was a bit rarer than we ordered, the lobster was absolutely outstanding—one of the best we've had! We also really enjoyed the generous calamari servings. Overall, a great dining experience!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNtIMhIcglzxiTk1_p7t0oojF32vDHS7aNAPWKq&fid=0x0:0x8a834a2eb78c2221"],"When":"2024-8-24"},{"Name":"Supanun Ploy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLD8x1Dkib5UdzUFO77N8E3T_ZS53RX2FTmd37gugrcEvk9Yw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"It was our anniversary and we went on Saturday night without booking as we forgot.  Luckily we didn’t have to wait for a long time coz someone cancelled their reservation. In terms of food, onion ring was not seasoned and bbq ribs smell a little but we really enjoy our steak and calamari.

However, before we leave our server try to clear our table but he carry to many stuff at once then he drop cultery on my back. He did apologize and said sorry it’s only a fork. However, once i got up i also found a knife and the back of my shirt is dirty!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNSbRX3nEUs1B5S1OV0vyO9agkfQf7a-0VyVeNe&fid=0x0:0x8a834a2eb78c2221"],"When":"2024-11-23"},{"Name":"Amir Heidari","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVhtGF44y-l1pQZ17Cs4MnWp1KWCMVfN_sfbl-_OCbn3gyQLgGR=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"“The atmosphere of the restaurant was nice, 🤓but the food quality didn’t meet expectations and was average. 😒We ordered lobster, American steak, and French onion soup. The staff weren’t very friendly, and it seemed like they were not in the mood. 😣Overall, it wasn’t bad for trying once.”","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPLcuPlcBy7mVZb2T4r6UZaN-1KvPOqSiSixTM0&fid=0x0:0x8a834a2eb78c2221"],"When":"2024-9-23"},{"Name":"Morteza Khoramshahi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWXteADRppBLe3Hw2555GOmIwdeoF4ju3YY6aXL5EdFqkJ30LWz=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The best appetizer in town: baked shrimp
Options for all tastes, Steak, seafood and for vegetarian.
Usually I order 2 plates of baked shrimp for start.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOJEyvRrSf7WY14KXQHGEJcvplwZltjyoVzgyQx&fid=0x0:0x8a834a2eb78c2221"],"When":"2024-12-9"}]

Despite the bacon, the overall meal was satisfying.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMWNn48FSQQq24jLQ-BEBeHk-JWoL8sBAKVBQB-&fid=0x0:0x364e4f3b56cfa8f4"],"When":"2024-10-23"},{"Name":"Sam B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLLBuz42uqfzXB3ElZGqaH5wSIVnQ8rMsu03T_blBqmnMaxLQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I get dinner with friends here about every two weeks, and it’s great every time. I usually get the steak frites or the Cajun fish. Both are delicious.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNoMTdvmaIx_HV4hHW1L9RcoVy_mAYZIpasPt-f&fid=0x0:0x364e4f3b56cfa8f4"],"When":"2024-10-24"},{"Name":"Daniel Jung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFE7g6vnjf23CW6mDeh4anchF8fxBs6O5Nsx0bvhepuO3MVzWa=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Update: They now have Vegan Cheese option, Queen Bee Pizza was delicious!

Old Posts:Great experience every time I have been here to dine-in! Thank you Earls Team! Love that this location is a Test Kitchen.

Tacos were absolutely delicious along with the margaritas!! Fantastic service as usual!

Had an amazing dining experience on New Years Day thanks to our server Tess as she had great personality, provided quick service, accommodated to our needs and followed up appropriately! Been dining here for over 5 years and she was the best!
Food was delicious and drinks were mint!
What a great way to start the New Year!!
Thanks Tess and Earls Team!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOrRfJzQdZ0inB94JqpPn9HmUKjzUAU8BKVRSjV&fid=0x0:0x364e4f3b56cfa8f4"],"When":"2022-1-2"},{"Name":"장민","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK90us3Gcwq48qfQCsSB0ooW1tkDEG9RtVDQtgcR-Sa57rtyQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It has good vive. The food wasn’t same that I expected but it was good. Especially risotto with chicken! The price was quite expensive I think because of the popularity.

Next time I wanna try Seafood tower or platter.😋","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMgc5VeZj9HIQegM8b3ZzwlG3BzI2Ncv0TGHnCG&fid=0x0:0x364e4f3b56cfa8f4"],"When":"2024-7-11"},{"Name":"Paul Legge","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKuepvhLXnwipKN8-zUF6NvDdgI9arbvikVkH_erBG_iDKrpA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I am exhausted by chain restaurants and their quality of cooking and food. We ordered burgers for delivery from the Earls in Port Coquitlam. It is 5 minutes from our house. We have 2 young kids so we just wanted an easy, no-think meal. My wife and I had ordered two burgers. Everything was cold which is what it is. Could have been late delivery. We accept that. What we do not accept is undercooked pink burgers. It doesn’t take much. Like I said, we have two young kids. We don’t want to be bent over a toilet while taking care of kids. The delivery service cannot be blamed for undercooked burgers. Absolutely disappointing.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNNc0BXWfSPP9NqoUqBdqTcC04bIOmWl2Jvpd4i&fid=0x0:0x364e4f3b56cfa8f4"],"When":"2024-10-1"},{"Name":"Ariana Abedini","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUKNjWemH3JT4c-lZV9IuSCGGzTuGZDPVm9u6xasU8uvx3gj15E=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great food, very warm and friendly atmosphere, staff very polite. [{"Name":"Mahsa Haghjoo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXRSnT0Wip7Pbg6Z8m0cglGHkWd61YfkTkUIlG6b0IkPWIUcJi2=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The staff are friendly, but they might not check on you often, so they may miss refilling your water. The quality and taste of the food are okay. However, the gheimeh stew on tahdig was served cold, some parts of the meat were still cold, suggesting it wasn't freshly made or properly warmed up. Kashke bademjon was beautifully designed. The menu offers a good variety of options. Overall, it was an okay experience, with some room for improvement. The portions are big, and there's plenty of space to seat large groups. Plus, there's free parking right in front.The decor is nice, featuring some traditional Persian carpets on the walls.

Totally recommend ordering the dogh. It was so creamy and delicious","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMS8kS3M67NNGNn9x3D7RRXzV_nyU5m94YWXi-w&fid=0x0:0xb534928a10c38264"],"When":"2024-9-2"},{"Name":"Vahid Heydarinia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUm3lYhqP-_BPvMwccMRgnhyMaGZHw9udBZ7-ueoyezFBzXZaWT=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Good service, decent portions and tasty food.
