[{"Name":"Ann Badjura","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVf1oROONtXShauxBz8Kbl0XDKTAr0Sjwkq1X29oWc2s6lLWbaZug=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My friend and I enjoyed a lunch here last month and it was our first time here.  We ordered 2 fried rolls and 2 salad rolls as an appetizer.  For the main meal we ordered the Banh Mi sandwich combo with bread and a pop for $11.25.

The rolls were very good and tasty.  The Banh Mi sandwich was really delicious, packed with lots of veggies and grilled chicken.  We really enjoyed these sandwiches a lot.  Service was good, atmosphere was nice but most important of all the food was good.  Will definitely come back here.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPeNPI8IA7C4y_u2HTv-YOswI7YUYg6HKGbFE8N&fid=0x0:0x36f73a9a7e0be3e8"],"When":"2024-9-19"},{"Name":"Prima Primavera","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVgviOjcAerRoNVlGDMxdWH5dK-NAzgYaRM-V8_yzCd5gUIyVaI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My friend and I stopped for dinner, I had veggie tofu pho, and it was really good. My friend had traditional beef pho and really liked it. The service was nice, and the restaurant itself and its washrooms were clean.  We will be back to try more dishes.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP01iUwjZucTlMrL8UiJmRM_vqrir_vnN5KMDFn&fid=0x0:0x36f73a9a7e0be3e8"],"When":"2024-10-11"},{"Name":"Hiep Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMRHHZ7t798igHqhwEObqqiXXBYRe7_vTRRS3-gXG7fOgZlXSH=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ordered the nem sandwich combo with a pop for $11.95. I really enjoyed it! Lots of veggies and the meat was sliced up. Service could have been friendlier because that's what I'm used to. Maybe because this is my first time here and it seems like a new establishment.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPyzWeMmAeqNRVdRJv9-fulKjt1KsiYsgoQoGCf&fid=0x0:0x36f73a9a7e0be3e8"],"When":"2024-4-10"},{"Name":"Helen Wang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKdJPTSymalOucXYUPLOv6ycg7-T2RTYsNMkdaUWaGjWfYnIQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"My husband and I went there to have dinner last night (June 11) Tuesday night around 6 pm. The restaurant is  getting busy at that time  and we understand;however ,only 2 waitress working at the peak hours.
The waitress was very nice and friendly and we don’t have any problem with the service .
We were not impressed for the length of the time we have to wait for our food
I ordered spicy soup and my husband got his rare beef soup
We did not order any appetizer
So we don’t know why it took 35 mins for us to wait for our bowls of soup which normally it might only take 5-10 mins

The staff whom working in the kitchen have to manage their time how to make time more efficiently and the customer have not to wait for a long time

The food is okay,not anything special
The waitress was super nice but if asking me to come back then I won’t cause waiting for a long time for our food
The owner has to figure it out how to tell the staff in the kitchen how to mange their time and it’s not fair to complain to the waitress cause it’s not their fault at all

I hope the restaurant can read this review
It wasn’t a good experience for us

This is my third time posted it
I don’t know why it’s disappeared
Everyone has different opinions and pls respect all opinions
Tks","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMviKTdYWjY7KC_IM3GwKHuuaR1DHxgcwZC7r2S&fid=0x0:0x36f73a9a7e0be3e8"],"When":"2024-6-13"},{"Name":"J C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVRid-486EHf3vFFlqzxc7hc71kbL9n1FDLFiUelrs10b7uY4If=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Sooooo very close to a 4 star if only they you a few more pieces of meat!  The hot sauce was one of the better ones and the soup had the cinnamon smell.  You have to ask for the basil leaves tho.  The salad roll is as good but the fried one is a bit on the smaller side.  Would come back again.  Fairly priced and clean.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN58YfHzFsWY8YMcpQWeAU_2y4wsv2LseMAfQpn&fid=0x0:0x36f73a9a7e0be3e8"],"When":"2023-5-6"},{"Name":"Marcie Kim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUt9D7XuETM6lN9dgpP3G7IQIDDAZYQ-03T2OvXE9TvM6YEYQIY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The waitress was super rude for no reason. Please educate your staff on basic respectfulness surrounding gender identity along with dietary choices. Inexcusable. I should not be interrogated for choosing a dish. Just a weird and frustrating interaction overall. Also, you don't get that much noodles for a 'large' size portion.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ray Chow","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWnHoKzUHN2laU2bSp7bGdZulx8wlTrl7fcyIV2n_GmA8fi001AHw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very good Pho here dry dishes taste great. Kim Ph.D.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWlXOLSBLykfAfenb8ga5US9_f65v2jn1FOUXFVC189lXL5D-M=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently heard rave reviews about Fat Tuna Sushi, so I decided to check it out myself. And wow, it exceeded all expectations! The ambiance was delightful, with such a welcoming atmosphere created by the owner and staff. But let's talk about the food – absolutely divine!

As a sushi and udon enthusiast, I've never experienced rolls as generously sized and delicious as theirs. And the udon? It was so flavorful and comforting that I forgot to snap a picture before devouring it. That's how good it was!

Normally, I'm not a big fan of tempura due to its greasiness, but theirs was a game-changer. It was so fresh and perfectly crispy, leaving me thoroughly satisfied.

I can't recommend this place highly enough. If you're in the mood for an unforgettable culinary experience, Fat Tuna Sushi is the place to be!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNx4TYytKicft437YXnREUt9rdkoxxtWxcg_z6v&fid=0x0:0xfbd1ecee64f77724"],"When":"2024-4-21"},{"Name":"Weston Vanderveen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLS6afXRggtPviK257JTqRh3pnSMCLG-uwi790OfBAR24N5-Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Such a cute, intimate sushi experience.

It’s incredibly fresh, and the presentation is beautiful. The prices are fair as well!

10/10, would recommend. Definitely our go to local spot.","Images":null,"When":""}]

Bur for good reason.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMGSnA4lOBbl9_OITOUk-uDm3EmclsgwsnOvFrF&fid=0x0:0xc045733293aaced8"],"When":"2024-6-18"},{"Name":"Nat A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWnjKr4KNFAObzj2bIvH9BRInxwKsSvEg1PM25bKfvhxtWZTWHoog=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Update:
Came back to try more food. Quality was still very good!

So good! I came here on a Friday night around 7:40pm and there was no wait. We didn't have to wait long for our food to be served either. We ordered the Sashimi sample set and it was so fresh! This place has gomae with okra and tuna. The sauce was soo... good. More pricey than regular gomae with spinach but it was so much better! I enjoyed the Scallop roll and the special roll with Mango salsa on top. There was plenty of seating for small and large groups. It was clean, modern and had a fun vibe to it. I will definitely come back to try more!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOPEJ5JLS8UmtGSSi9dnvc3fmV8eMmEQLkIDCRE&fid=0x0:0xc045733293aaced8"],"When":"2023-7-30"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Sam Goh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKE5mTKD61HIgHQk8dxPyuoRqeGbk2g-M7HwnIwadO5n9CEZ1k=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hons is an authentic casual Chinese restaurant. They make everything to order and have an extensive menu. When we go, our fav 3 dishes are the BBQ fried rice, tofu with rock salt as well as the black pepper chicken with broccoli.  When ordering we usually ask them to withhold the black pepper sauce on the chicken with broccoli as sometimes we find that it’s too much sauce.

We have previously had other dishes such as wontons, sweet and sour pork, eggplant, hot and sour soup, mixed veggies, Shanghai noodles etc and have enjoyed those as well. There really isn’t anything we didn’t like.

Service is typical Chinese restaurant style so don’t be shy to flag the servers down as they can get busy.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNSoq4VSBcm5D9NiPXkZE-eK_-qTsSJ4cK7Mq7j&fid=0x0:0x95ff28cd48bec56f"],"When":"2024-11-9"},{"Name":"A.J. Canadian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU0mITu_1OR_MuXzhVIkPjHjZnimy2Y-mI64r72OA1Zbucah6-N=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Hon's on Coquitlam is one of my go to to pick up a quick dinner. I usually pop in and check out the presented BBQ and roasted duck, pork and chicken in the display. I am always greeted by friendly staff and my food is always up to standard.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMYt6ZGXk07h2TuGo8zKEaxdScTRMp_5YeuJkyR&fid=0x0:0x95ff28cd48bec56f"],"When":"2024-7-21"},{"Name":"Damaris Ibarra","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX94ja2TK604xuamsF18bxzGKPd7B1_MlnXlwCnslYshD_71-qX=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I went to Hon’s Wun-Tun House yesterday for the first time in about a year or two. I was very disappointed and surprised when I had realized the flavour of the food had gone downhill. I used to love Hons cause they used to have Good portions and amazing flavour for a good price however, things have turned for the worse recently and now even the cheaper TNT meals you can get at the mall tastes better than the food on this day.

The wonton soup was super salty and tasted very fishy which i’ve never experienced in a wonton soup before (i love wonton soup so that was surprising that it tasted so wierd). I also ordered the beef and brocoli crispy Chow Mein, which is no longer on their menu but the lady said they could make it which is why I gave them a high rating for the service. The chow mein (the whole thing including the beef) tasted a bit wrong like if it shouldn’t be eaten. Not sure how to describe the flavour but it just tasted off and wrong to eat. It was not the flavour I had known and loved hons for, instead it tasted wierd. I am incredibly disappointed that one of my previous favourite chinese food spots no longer have good flavour and have gone downhill. We did order other things as well and honestly the only thing i liked from this whole meal is the rice.

I will be on the search for better chinese food restaurants because i’m so sad and disappointed that this one won’t hold up to a good standard anymore. The service was really good however and they were very quick, efficient and kind so good job on the service. It was the food that was a big turn off. I hope they are able to bring back their old good flavour they used to have in their food and improve on the quality and flavour.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOeS2mABL7p7eLR9gTvg-74i-iEn4ZW4T_qAG3o&fid=0x0:0x95ff28cd48bec56f"],"When":"2024-9-13"},{"Name":"Nona SM","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIfjTMq2ZKlGJ4Ldu_6g6I_gZ33bv-9-UjHyDYxTjehH_EmHBBS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"We would rate this restaurant 0 star if we could, The portions are big, but the smell of the food is horrendous so you will not even get to eat the food. It’s sticky and the vegetables are discoloured (the broccoli is grey and yellow…)
We ended up letting them know how bad everything was and it was definitely a health hazard to consume and still had to pay full price which is very disappointing.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOo4rv95AaM88dKIuaKfG1oWNhlnzblsWhNADeb&fid=0x0:0x95ff28cd48bec56f"],"When":"2024-9-28"},{"Name":"Maxine Noël","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLQMYs4r5B33gJ34fAugWWfmH6Yn9m7uwjCQYiizbCj9u8j9fk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"So delicious, definitely authentic quality Chinese food and the best sweet and sour pork you'll ever have. It's crunchy on the outside and coated in that sticky sweet sauce. The way they flame wok their dishes just adds so much flavour.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNT4VmTkah8-MppOfU_gvgGtyfVeJikEwnT9Pr4&fid=0x0:0x95ff28cd48bec56f"],"When":"2023-8-3"},{"Name":"Alissa willman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXEDSWOUv6R8DeP9mxksuJk54LZ_0QYAbltxQmHt531hSIGfalIYA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ohmygosh I almost don't want to leave a review as if I do it will bring attention to this secret gem and possibly drive the price up. The food is sooo good! And the servings are HUGE!!! DEFINITELY coming back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNDvBEFlpu-jSgA6qY8f_CpsWkpIMw0YDcxqRiW&fid=0x0:0x95ff28cd48bec56f"],"When":"2024-3-31"},{"Name":"Daniel HAN","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIChGR0mPBUiK47gPt8g99ilcJC6KXSWmFux6ml52TbewOKlQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This restaurant uses low quality ingredients and the food smells weird.

The worst problem is that the servers are very rude. If you order a little bit, they keep staring at you and being rude. I will never go to this restaurant again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMeR1bHYASQgCSg0QnrgKxMtvU9u-NClGdjdbCU&fid=0x0:0x95ff28cd48bec56f"],"When":"2024-9-1"},{"Name":"Candice C.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJwFBBjzDK0K147Ahvw56fgZp0Wzk8W8u0zo_aJQ425Hu_MYA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Haven't ordered from Hons in a long time, decided to get food through uber eats. The food was delivered well within the estimated time and the food was very good. Not a lot of places offer a cod and tofu (bean curd) hotpot but this place does. 👌","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMix90dzMRR_ADqZX-pPRXF85N35NSNq9TqWZbe&fid=0x0:0x95ff28cd48bec56f"],"When":"2023-5-22"}]

[{"Name":"Jessameen Dela Peña","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX9mRpmL8-ZJUG7UPFcnsjzRdxjABif-MswbO1rxgJyyWfns8Jd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food was good, though we would have preferred more meat and fewer side dishes. The space is limited, so expect a queue. Overall, it was a pleasant experience, but it can be a bit pricey.

UPDATE: We gave this place another try and have since become regulars! The atmosphere and menu have improved, with better servings and side dishes. My new favorites are the seafood pancake and soybean paste soup. Can’t even count how many times we’ve come back now!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN9p1vKrQTNJUY8mnBHspHSs3XqMG8w74KLRKZo&fid=0x0:0x2ab3aeb548bc78f7"],"When":"2024-6-13"},{"Name":"Linda Vu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW4Mt-fIM1ZKQuO_Y2ib9yo6xFV3B1mBRBjrbB_M80tp5QNaP0e=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ordered the lunch combo beef ssam bob for $62

It came with a soup of your choice (we got seafood), marinated raw crab, steamed egg, stone rice, cheese corn, 2 salads, and a selection of beef meats.

Of course you get all the banchans as well.

Soup was very flavourful and the meat was so tender.

It was my friends first time having marinated raw crab and it was a very good experience. It would be better if it was a spicy flavor instead of just soy.

Service was very good, she was very attentive.

Highly recommend.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPHjlsvMS8DFN8cJel4S05z6iwrwUs1W46b4iMV&fid=0x0:0x2ab3aeb548bc78f7"],"When":"2024-2-10"},{"Name":"Nancy Zhao","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJy5Qf1QbM0_c1L-F7OulUL2yIwJwQ1TDUbUpgT-AhPSJuxhQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently visited this Korean BBQ restaurant.The quality of the meat was outstanding, everything was incredibly fresh and well-marinated. They had a wide selection, including beef, pork, chicken, and even seafood. As the meat sizzled on the grill, the aroma was irresistible, and every bite was tender, juicy, and flavorful. The side dishes were equally impressive, with unlimited refills of classic Korean banchan like kimchi, pickled veggies, and potato salad.

The service was exceptional! The staff were so friendly and attentive, greeting us warmly as we arrived. They explained how to use the grill, adjusted the heat when needed.This Korean BBQ spot is definitely worth visiting!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Danielle Tan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJmVYhJdAokXRNv0OeadwE83uAo9bdT8RA0Z1YdZz0bhl9Lbg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love this place so much, they have an iPad on the table for you to order what you want and you can call the staff from it and ask for the bill. The food is amazing, a bit pricey but definitely worth it. The raw marinated crab and shrimp are to die for. So is the raw beef, this is a place I come to for a lot of my special occasions. Definitely recommend this restaurant to anyone who wants good Korean food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNK1OwkuN24TX2BsitRX1Wq5_Ks8DylnjH27lpT&fid=0x0:0x2ab3aeb548bc78f7"],"When":"2024-2-14"},{"Name":"Michael Truong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIjodCmziTtCatwb_ZSLMhHV7xv-2xqC3YmbW-x4NUcQBKWBg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My family visited here several times and this is one of our favourite places. The food is delicious. Lunch package is abundant and affordable. So good!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPUO__lX-boW6gXktTJbuci3zfNRQLMxZ9HP5Kj&fid=0x0:0x2ab3aeb548bc78f7"],"When":"2024-10-25"},{"Name":"Ryan Mark","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU-8gTPutAprYAFgA5zkcbXP0HUJcGjXs78lAmbmJUW2gOGY-oj=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The menu features a fantastic selection of premium meats, all marinated to perfection and grilled right at your table, ensuring a fresh and interactive dining experience. The side dishes are plentiful and complement the main offerings wonderfully. Additionally, the attentive and friendly staff enhance the overall experience, making sure every guest feels well taken care of.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMKJXwovheJuCvHDZH6B7-CUNLG9Jr6CQ8MowZ0&fid=0x0:0x2ab3aeb548bc78f7"],"When":"2024-6-10"},{"Name":"Zian “Angel” Chen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUpHlaKmldB-xjFqyb4TkGc38CZDagtkPZhKF3jb0zpQWB9Qtw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Gooi-Ga (구이가) Korean BBQ has various weekday promotion events going on, $44 for 600g pork belly on Thursday, 10% off on all menu on Wednesday. We happened to come here for dinner on a snow day and was so impressed with the quality of food, so surprised that they were still open!!
We ordered - hot stone rice and the pork belly, it’s big portion of food that can serve three people.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN4RFGDDMCDjQcVhitSyDPRlXQo0KzG_a7aK7g5&fid=0x0:0x2ab3aeb548bc78f7"],"When":"2024-1-20"},{"Name":"James H Terre","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXQe3cD2OAW2WicJ2iFvBRW7BSYgRuA0F0JJhj-r3nWIlovZFE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"pork collar combo - grilled marinated pork collar + assorted soy sauce marinated seafood + spicy cockle bibimbap + grilled mackerel + spicy beef tofu soup + steamed eggs + stone pot rice (63) / pork jowl bbq (23) x2","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPK3EwfTQSOTPvURKAhlCOMrHJKFWXILlJxtNft&fid=0x0:0x2ab3aeb548bc78f7"],"When":"2024-11-12"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Jason Tribbiani","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXXpvlAY0NULhaj1b4k1yZZtRXFlzsqxg5gIO8-kzQ1-Qy-iq7d=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is the best Korean restaurant I've visited so far. I've been to many Korean restaurants across Vancouver, Burnaby, Coquitlam, Port Coquitlam, New Westminster, and more, but this one stands out as my favorite. It seems like a hidden gem, as during my visit, I only saw Korean customers. The food is excellent, the service is good, and the prices are fair. A nice touch is the Asian yogurt drink they give you after the meal—my kid absolutely loved it. We'll definitely be coming back again soon!"","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO23awN-dQ3bi0FKJ5yAWbbs8DflyRWk_O6oFCK&fid=0x0:0x132cccb52a4527c8"],"When":"2024-9-8"},{"Name":"Snoopy Kitchen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU3h-I-trbYva-Tzrs-UNhkQe4Nn1jgsblAcoQ0hPrnUWvugM3Y=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nice food. Good service and big portion. Little highlight is small bottle drink when pay bill 🥰","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNpvleOX52Vc9_WylUP3np4rjV6QUxRVLcmYxpU&fid=0x0:0x132cccb52a4527c8"],"When":"2024-12-22"},{"Name":"Monique","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUQcAgOL4v2U_VirmCaadFrb2IzIMWiSeW-tX_pA5B7GcJn2vN8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you’re craving comfort food and Korean food, this place is amazing!

We went on a cold rainy day, and the food was super filling!

The sogogi soontubu was my personal favourite as it was so flavourful especially when mixed with rice! Highly recommend it if you like beef stews and soups.

When you’re done with your meal you get a complimentary yogurt drink which pairs perfectly with the dishes and is super cute. 🥰","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPEiOwpPj8MDmPUHPnWL3zZrJe9UBD_A4dugiYw&fid=0x0:0x132cccb52a4527c8"],"When":"2024-8-27"},{"Name":"Linda Vu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW4Mt-fIM1ZKQuO_Y2ib9yo6xFV3B1mBRBjrbB_M80tp5QNaP0e=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Visited on a quiet evening, got seated quickly with plenty of available tables.

The menu was straightforward; we ordered soups. Side dishes came first, followed by the flavorful soup and not-too-spicy stew.

We were able to opt out of the side rice for noodles free of charge which was nice. There wasn’t much meat in mine, but the issue I had was the amount of onions in the soup, it occupied most of the space in the stone bowl so it wasn’t enjoyable.

Reasonable prices, no rush to leave – great for both small and large groups. A delightful surprise was the complimentary yogurt drinks at the end, a nice touch after a satisfying meal.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMefnWlAUNY_NGLLZAMm4yO6acdkPD-6bSxHwnY&fid=0x0:0x132cccb52a4527c8"],"When":"2024-2-1"},{"Name":"YVR Duke","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVbrjJ5U6gKw7Gn1zE_GlxhUndims9WHlh7sVaHLXVrjOFlYd_B=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"- Very spacious, comfortable seating.
- Friendly and attentive staff
- Delicious BIBIMBAB and seafood pancake
- generous refill of Kimchi and Bean sprouts side dishes

This store is highly recommended","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPVXN7JwN8WX1o98OuOToYl6i_D0JTxQ6G7adEq&fid=0x0:0x132cccb52a4527c8"],"When":"2024-9-2"},{"Name":"M Mark","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJh32lM4t_7cX4VsExqacG-T8y6qepgXVVz9NQxEaNR5c4_HHo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Came for a late lunch. Big restaurant with booths and buttons to call for service. Small parking lot shared with several businesses.

I ordered the gal-bi tang $22.95 - beef back rib and beef brisket in medicine beef broth. It came with free side dishes that were a bit sus tasting. Not the freshest.

Soup came bubbling to the table! Two large bones. It was tender, but lacked that fatty, juicy beef flavour. The beef brisket was dry as per the norm in these soups. Soup was seasoned well. Ended dinner with a free yakult (yogurt drink) which was a nice way to wrap up the meal.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO9Qe0JCF6w16VUJbCbv86S78gX2_U55tXLse1T&fid=0x0:0x132cccb52a4527c8"],"When":"2024-6-28"},{"Name":"Sara Chan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVlSF6ADXHgyatqSj3RdRyjxWuJp2qz8rnQN-QdhLw0IaUlXFq2=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We fall in love with this restaurant since the 1st time we visit 2 months ago, my hubby found his long lost flavour of Seol Leong Tong, here, all their soup rice set is very tasty, the environment is clean & neat, quite comfy to dine in, and their service is very sincere too, very friendly and attentive, I introduced this restaurant to my sisters and they love it too, price is very reasonable, feel free to drop by anytime 😆

Tried their Gamja Tang yesterday (Nov17, 2024) that was really good, it contained 3 big pork bone stew as u can see in the photo, the spiciness of the soup is just right to go with the rice, yummy  😋","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP-23ZXh-8gejMkZpPJXqrpa8RWsEQ6O3sHK_04&fid=0x0:0x132cccb52a4527c8"],"When":"2024-10-28"},{"Name":"Annie Chu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWsXi8Is5QB-hGp8e4gCUiJFiV4Pu0iMPFA2Oi2wm3py-Xxlqfh=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Quite enjoyed the gamjatang and seafood soondubu (tofu soup)! Side dishes were pretty average. Spacious restaurant and plenty of free parking.

They use the service button which you press to get service. Would return again if I was craving!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOo6twih_bB3X46-45qtZs85Qci7K2gp2cYZIdY&fid=0x0:0x132cccb52a4527c8"],"When":"2024-9-14"}]

[{"Name":"Fat Cook Papa (Fat Cook Papa)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJUpgi6nqSgMlDhQ45Yjl_gk21krVh2zgBl_CxlCp6gK1X_Jg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Coming from Toronto..

Love and enjoy great views from the patio.

Fish and Fries - both of their batter and fries were overpowdered and little salty. Also, I'm quite disappointed with the fries portion.
Unfortunately, two pieces of COD were first serving. Apparently, they looked like cooking with different preparation timing. One was great with thick cut crunchy exterior and soft interior, other piece hasn't fully fried to perfection. It's greasy and less crispy.

The Downtowner Pizza - pleasantly surprised by the amazing flavor honey drizzle on pizza. The heat of the pizza then warm the honey as it mixed with the sauce and toppings.

Wings - no impressed.  Originally ordered with Honey garlic sauce toppings style.
Unfortunately, wings were made with buffalo style and tasted like they half coated them with tobasco by mistaken.

We have to say they were by far some of the worst wings I have ever eaten. It's tasted like korean BBQ fried chicken wing.

A little bit pricey and service does need a lot of improvement.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP0be5JHmIITlNBtCmwiDVXPzfNar9iOeCiuLah&fid=0x0:0xbbadd84419ac02a9"],"When":"2024-6-4"},{"Name":"Amy Adams","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWyVH38TT4RWGwG_4hraWZRuXvb1BELFJJQ_LmMrQJEwE8qxzQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Salted and pepper Wings are hard and dried, only drumette, no wingette. So disappointed.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOR5_ZcPVXhC0Wp4WEPzD8P0o66YgMQsBgVyxdG&fid=0x0:0xbbadd84419ac02a9"],"When":"2024-12-15"},{"Name":"Bekah French","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJiYLh-7emQ9AthzE2N_CGxwmtRUdZguPeMRuVIWmhyOtllxQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Views and location are amazing. Would love to visit again in the summer and sit out on their big patio we ordered the soup of the day (chicken and vegetable), it was okay. And we shared a meat lovers pizza. We requested half with no cheese (for me) but the pizza came out first time incorrect (it was half cheese only, half meat). They quickly remade the pizza and the base was very yummy. I’d rate the pizza as a whole 3/5. We found the service very friendly and welcoming.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNwfumHC1VMOXhld8Vw1mT60IYGLKPdkLMIuntT&fid=0x0:0xbbadd84419ac02a9"],"When":"2022-11-16"},{"Name":"Ali Mehrizi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXWq9cg0fjpkngwNGme387YM4kRUdnI6Pf_Z33gzbG1mkoqze49=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Beautiful views of town (all the way to Burnaby) and good pub food. Fries were one of the best I have had. Drinks are good and beer flights are generous. A quick and good place if you’re in the more residential part of northern Coquitlam.

I just wish the service was more courteous. We had to wait quite a bit to get our server’s attention when we wanted to order extra food and drinks. When the food came (in reasonable time), she came to check on us only when we were almost done. On the bright side, I don’t think this is the service culture at Fairways; the two other persons who helped us sit and get a clean/sanitized table were very nice.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP4yxOEC8MmM2niMejhmuf8tooer3a0pejf_8Sj&fid=0x0:0xbbadd84419ac02a9"],"When":"2020-10-22"},{"Name":"Janice Robinson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWwXAghB0kKeZJUcp8jSMN3IavGDPtUMtF57yQo1h9gD5800GlzTg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The last time I dined at this restaurant, it was called Hazards, and we lived 5 minutes away.  Having moved 10 years ago, it was nice to return to a familiar place. The service was pleasant and timely, and the 3 of us really enjoyed our meals.  I had the blackened salmon tacos, which were very flavourful and expertly prepared. I will definitely be back!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Eun R","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUtFP78dUqzbrC3sUP2EUQ7OgKF-9eTaViByIOG1MgbwrrOyEABLw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food quality is good, portion is generous, and servers are friendly and attentive.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMYiB0HybsweJ0t28YswxQYL6q4xyemOS01_F9f&fid=0x0:0xbbadd84419ac02a9"],"When":"2024-7-23"},{"Name":"Ve7123","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI37Dp_jMOGKDkNZyR_8bRIASwIfCrsxmFZJBEVbUjSJ5H-kA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I am living nearby ,we're always coming here.
Today, we ordered the pizza of The downtowner, and it looks like only the dough, where the cheese and meat are.
I suggest that if there is no price increase, please cancel this item, because it is like deceive  customers, the goods are not right.
Quality has no standard

Yesterday we came again.
Because the design and atmosphere of the restaurant are good. However, we only ate for half an hour, and the waitress often came to urge and disturb the guests. Points will be deducted for this.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPFDpA3izzm0cCAL6kBKdFvDio1yiFbqIA-zvUu&fid=0x0:0xbbadd84419ac02a9"],"When":"2023-7-28"},{"Name":"Reza Abbaszadeh Hassiri","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK26XcBa9A6TQLl_HXySTSrhIoetCnYiLUxzi8E55Bm8P9Z1A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Just started hanging out there, I tried soup and fries twice already and Today I took coffee and cheesecake. Never got disappointed so far. You can put nice service and staff on top of that. Ariana is one of the best! Good atmosphere and view as well!!","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Scott Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXHpW7vGME__Zs4wKjXR04Upnw88bkVVyz-H2288JsHocq9vI3r=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"It's a pretty typical dim sum restaurant with decent food and service. I appreciate the speed of the service and the value for all the food. It can get pretty busy, especially during weekends so be prepared to wait if you didn't make a reservation.

We got the lotus leaf wrapped sticky rice with pork, some steamed pea shoots, vegetable porridge (congee) and good selection of dumplings. It's not anything to write home about, but it's hardy and gets the job done. Solid experience overall and I would give them the thumbs up.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNldHIuVK-fsR57KEsIFq08_KeBGOEZKK1j8FvJ&fid=0x0:0xe8960ddf73ad1704"],"When":"2024-9-17"},{"Name":"Grace Wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJv2Qb5BK8BlHD8B-fNqpMIiwBP96of3n6s7qsHpu4xPXVSJg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delicious and cute dim sum! Food was fresh and fast. We made reservations as it can get busy. Staff were friendly and attentive. I do speak Chinese as well. The kids love the food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOqxd3kLGHCrMQedJ1T0fOAbSmVa-M_lHRR3aR-&fid=0x0:0xe8960ddf73ad1704"],"When":"2024-9-26"},{"Name":"Celina Wright","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXh2wmxFC5Utlekpzdr2MpXFcBCcrOSjcqSIoXPM9bCTR9ROXAVjw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The food was fantastic and the staff were polite.  We visited for dim sum on a weekend. Seating took some time (10-15 minutes) even with a reservation, but I find that to be normal at most dim sum restaurants.

For those unfamiliar with a dim sum restaurant: just make sure you flag down the wait staff if you need anything and they'll head over to you quickly - don't wait for them to check in on you.

We had about 6 dishes among 4 people and were very satisfied with all of them 😌

We had an overall great experience and will visit again soon!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPEjZuQIZKRlmVGxE6oDTnZ2lj9iQ_fe2zH2aWD&fid=0x0:0xe8960ddf73ad1704"],"When":"2024-9-1"},{"Name":"Annia Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLCmNf-6kVgoV3z2v1rhLUKPIXQtdwZxPsOxdlb6pZhbXP-BQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Enjoying some yummy 😋 dim sum for brunch.

A culinary tradition that has captured the hearts and palates. The term “dim sum” translates to “touch the heart,” a phrase that encapsulates the essence of these bite-sized delights.  So many different varieties of special Chinese dishes, served in small portions for all to share.
Dim sum has always been a symphony of colors, textures, and flavors in each dish to share amounst friends.

Food was fresh and fast service provided. Staff was attentive.  They were busy today luckily made reservations.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPBhObly0gYODvg08E6vPpciOoSHEghCgOJz5-x&fid=0x0:0xe8960ddf73ad1704"],"When":"2024-12-21"},{"Name":"K 2","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWCr90XQEGh_XW_dogXGAOrNDNdWl4oto2DcQXyO8hGv5A6DKrVWQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I recently had an incredibly disappointing lunch here. We ordered four dishes, but after waiting for more than an hour, only three arrived. The last dish never came despite us repeatedly asking about it. When we requested to cancel the order after an hour, the server responded with an attitude, insisting it was coming. After waiting an additional 20 minutes with no sign of the dish, we had no choice but to cancel it for good.

To make matters worse, the food that we did receive was subpar, tasting like frozen dim sum from T&T rather than freshly made. Seafood roll was.. speechless.. since when the imitation crab became seafood????
The entire experience—from the long wait times to the poor service and bland food—was awful. After spending an hour and a half there and only eating three dishes, I was left feeling frustrated and dissatisfied.

I definitely won’t be returning, and I would not recommend this place to anyone looking for quality dim sum or good service.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO797XW5ANvImlqxiyC1g_s4CcDzQenFyWjxZsG&fid=0x0:0xe8960ddf73ad1704"],"When":"2024-9-26"},{"Name":"J T","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJhlRzWDXzdsN5IEg7ILK_EQ56zA9jcQ-fPPr3cS5cgV1YVlw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Another Neptune afternoon…

I think this is the only Neptune I haven’t been to yet? Anyways, in the area taking care of some business so decided to try this location out.

It’s located on the front side of Coquitlam Center and facing the new Cactus Club, plentiful of parking is available up front in the malls parking lot.

Inside is separated into to section; Neptune Wonton for fast casual dishes and Neptune Seafood for more of a formal dining. It’s kind of a smaller place and pretty basic to me.

Anyways, here were the dim sum I ordered;

1. Seafood dumpling in soup. The imitation crab being used made the broth a bit overly sweet, was too unpleasant to finish it.
2. Steamed spicy beef tripe. It wasn’t tender enough, needed to steam it a bit longer.
3. Steamed chicken feet with special sauce. It wasn’t tender enough for the skin to fall off the bone, needed to run through the deep fryer a bit longer during the prep process.
4. Turnip cake with XO sauce. It’s almost a joke, my 10 year old nephew could’ve done better with this dish especially its presentation. Failed!
5. Baked preserved egg and ginger pastry. Absolutely horrible, the preserved egg was rubbery and the whole pastry crumbled along with its ginger paste. Failed!
6. Fried vegetables with shrimp paste. An alternate version of the deep fried eggplant with shrimp paste. It was so so.
7. Baked bbq pork buns. It was okay, the bbq pork could be less sweet.
8. Purple rice roll with fish paste. It was okay, the super jumbo size was unexpected.
9. Stir fry udon with live lobster. Surprisingly it was pretty good, enough wok hay to really bring out the flavours.
10. Little white rabbit pudding. Not bad, cute little treats.

Overall, I wasn’t too impressed with the layout and atmosphere of the restaurant. It portray itself as a mid class Chinese seafood restaurant, but felt l like a simple family restaurant with mid level prices.

The service was okay, enough to satisfy the basics, don’t expect anything more than that.

As for the food, honestly it was probably one of the most disappointing experience I had so far out of all the Neptunes I’ve been to.

Not a repeat or recommendation from me anytime soon… 1.5 stars","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOQR35TFh2sABn6mWQv4-F7inIjdWxHkqeXqX1w&fid=0x0:0xe8960ddf73ad1704"],"When":"2024-6-3"},{"Name":"Danny Y","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX8eoyUE6az-FmQo7i2mVq5z64Ow48sgKu1EmLZc0zWWN6DMy5asw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Came for dimsum. The portions here are pretty big and taste fresh. Lots of menu items to choose from. We had a larger party (11 people) and they had our table ready on time. However they forgot 3 of our items which we ended up cancelling. Overall good food and friendly service.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM2zar_Z9-rBEtiUz29w_-7yCkOfWbkH7rr9FO8&fid=0x0:0xe8960ddf73ad1704"],"When":"2023-10-9"},{"Name":"CY","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIyAWoVXS2wSYA_X8YaMHwhMb74Th2juKHatcW6zvf48kBI0A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Been here twice, once in July 2024, once in Nov 2024. Quality difference between a couple months was huge. (Much better food quality and taste now).

Clean and spacious environment.

Food was served a bit slowly though.

Dim Sum dish variety is quite limited on the menu.

Price is a bit higher than mid tier

Over it is decent","Images":null,"When":""}]

title: Woking Dragon Chop Suey House
descriptions: Long-standing restaurant featuring a variety of standard Chinese dishes in an unpretentious setting.

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Robert Trzcinski","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVjvBxe6tzSkzBsCzfDWOgFDumFdZh6OAIOTPWchqGyhFuBAJ72=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We come here over and over again, yes the food is western style Chinese but we like that. Great quality and never disappoints. The Combos are good because you get a bit of everything.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOLcyXB15QxU_xtLk10NRcRcx7yt0dX5KagChb1&fid=0x0:0x898188a487161c37"],"When":"2024-7-26"},{"Name":"Esther W.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWZ44_CjQ6-wehLPc33Ng17kPOWOSFrXqo3jg5WgP7CtwNUYUeR=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Asian Canadian styled food.
All the servers I saw were Caucasian. Food is ok a sauce is a little too sweet for my preference.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNiI6uZM2QAOCWBAY7bqQbTClAUhHM8lxPPzZMa&fid=0x0:0x898188a487161c37"],"When":"2024-12-6"},{"Name":"Jennifer Bee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFO0fgPBTIA1yxL3IXSghRJ6EmshLC1YB1a72b-xeg3kpjHx0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We like ordering Chinese food for New Year’s Eve and after seeing positive comments on the local Facebook groups, I thought I’d try Woking Dragon. I called a bit after 4pm and was surprised to hear we could pick up our order (seven dishes) in twenty minutes, or delivery before 5pm.

All dishes were perfect, and good portions too. The ginger beef, crispy breaded prawns, and dragon mixed greens were stand outs. We have lots of leftovers which means I don’t have to cook for a while. ;-)

We will definitely order again and I can’t wait to get my leftovers for lunch tomorrow!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOvoll5x-ugmDwlCnBNcz1AEX7mNqnRA8VRWng2&fid=0x0:0x898188a487161c37"],"When":"2024-1-1"},{"Name":"Brittany G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVRln3edCQZy4eIJWxl6Z_lj8lSlxw4wvRKO5IkeK_2Xd1MZTZURQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our usual go to was closed when we wanted to order. We ordered 4 individual meals and one of them was missing a sweet and sour order. With paying $90 for feeding my family I called in and let them know not expecting them to only replace my item but they exceeding it with great service. They didn’t just give an individual serving of the pork but an entree portion and fried rice to compensate! The service and phone service was amazing! Will be ordering again","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Frank Reiter","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW15lY4LVpS801XttkePhwWnIgWbJbkUqbRqcmq17Hr9jQY8EeN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food and service were both very nice.  I love the garlic calamari and the hot sauce (not part of the dish, but a nice combination if you enjoy some heat).","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNpNO5wwTmiIQs4xcAobMPYPvawIkSkE5I5ze2u&fid=0x0:0x898188a487161c37"],"When":"2024-5-10"},{"Name":"Ed Saxton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWNb4QcEnLutDQ1n6BX1NRrkvTayY3wJJFW3Qi0N3gL0iuAYAA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Prices at this place have gone up 40% in 3 years and the portions have gotten a lot smaller. Just let that sink in.. The food here used to be worth the price but it really isn’t anymore.
Something that used to be a rare treat has become unjustifiable/ unaffordable.
If someone can explain to me how these prices make sense I will be more than happy to remove this review, however the math ain’t mathin’.
Unless someone tells me eating this food will cure my knee pain, I will not be coming back.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Marly Sas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJDkU3WXHU8p4mUFPDAgNwKlyF9aXYw-JJYUVo7s3-y7grmZA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"we ordered a variety of dishes off Uber eats! We loved the Szechuan Fiery beef,Szechuan Fiery chicken, combo 3&4 and potstickers! It was absolutely delicious and fantastic ! We will be ordering again in the future!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMuz49HMyVmg8hQyjaN-3AodOU6Eq875CwgNZf7&fid=0x0:0x898188a487161c37"],"When":"2024-3-8"},{"Name":"Rick Arnau","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWO_R3g3kpaxvSzjraNuTgc5gUMEYQHlh6bzCz4SjcCsMzUPxkAlw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We came on a Sunday night, no reservation with an 8 person party. They accomodated us in excellent fashion. Very good service, typical Sechuan/Chinese fare. Food was not exceptional, but well seasoned, fresh and tasty. I would go back.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Jessameen Dela Peña","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX9mRpmL8-ZJUG7UPFcnsjzRdxjABif-MswbO1rxgJyyWfns8Jd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A true hidden gem in Coquitlam. My partner can't get enough of their extra spicy chicken, and I thoroughly enjoyed their fries too. Highly recommend checking this place out!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNt9f88ndaRd036qoohrw_t3ZPHje_k5haQCOSq&fid=0x0:0x37a99b2a94c8acc5"],"When":"2024-5-5"},{"Name":"argh c","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX2c34N4-KZC9sfBqKbqJSYJcFxkP3ce_vYTvsj7Y6T7ga6urdW=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The food was generally fine. Things were still crisp when they arrived. The soy garlic chicken was sweeter than I prefer and the original recipe chicken a little bland, but that’s just nitpicky personal preference.

Watched the Door Dash driver, on the app, circle the neighborhood a few times before finding our house, so we know why the food was cool-ish.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNVDNEQpXxKKZfsQLkRk4icrTxRH467vpVhg0gJ&fid=0x0:0x37a99b2a94c8acc5"],"When":"2023-3-4"},{"Name":"Belinda Jin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVQN2pGhoNzK76Clox_ElaIbflMT40WxZHUMqKpCiI5FtnukLZ6Zw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The biggest advantages living in the Coquitlam is that you can have authentic Korean food. GOGO Chicken & BBQ is one of my favorite Korean Chicken Restaurant. I'm highly recommend everyone to give this place a try.

GoGo Chicken & BBQ is a small Korean Restaurant, located on 105-2973 Glen Dr, Coquitlam. Since it's small and on the street, it's very easy to pass by if you are driving. Inside the restaurant, only few tables are there.  This place is better for grab food to go.

My husband and I have ordered food from this place so many times. The Chicken here are good, crispy, flavourful, juicy and succulent inside. The most important is fresh fried chicken! The portions are huge.  Normally, we ordered 1/2 Original KFC and 1/2 Soy Garlic  Chicken boneless as well as the Go Go Fries. It will take us more than three meals to finish all these food. So, when you are ordering the food, please be careful. It will be a lot of food.

Highly Recommend this place !","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOUn21xEnFKANZEbRy7Qq97dAtQw7Cbc9L1rx-D&fid=0x0:0x37a99b2a94c8acc5"],"When":"2021-5-23"},{"Name":"Elnaz Etminan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWmz21sbX2OgbPxtYDJY17TDDX2tdEpJRPILPXCRlOuUkYQWC0X=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Good location and 2 tables outside for use. Ordered Chicken Bao and Chiken BBQ bowl.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNe8yi7a9udBBcI1HqFYM29iKsRbiOR5od9uQdi&fid=0x0:0x37a99b2a94c8acc5"],"When":"2024-10-13"},{"Name":"Dasha Melnik","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXL2jlFLZHs9ZwNN5ssey6RDI1bggc2Q8OBg2ZHd1-2oyzkn1XB=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Half size box of deep fried chicken. I should admit it is tasty, but the box wasn't fully packed for $16+taxes. I will be back when it gets warmer to eat outside. The place is nice.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPYqRgQeWDTdQiANZJjZ7-V8QoXhl4pq6v76nfm&fid=0x0:0x37a99b2a94c8acc5"],"When":"2024-2-29"},{"Name":"Teeka Nedilenka","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW2T28buTAQlAhyk_WUlnanatMQSqwCz9P8Q45ikEbQ9lxEJf50=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"You can't even comprehend how amazing this food is, seriously juicy amazing chicken with the most crispy crust on the outside. The staffer are always so friendly, one mistake I should have gotten the cilantro spicy sauce to dip this in because I had it last time and it was absolutely mind blowingly delicious!!! 🤤🤤 The prices are unbelievably reasonable for how amazing their food/chicken is. I'm sad that they're not open on Wednesdays/ chicken wing Wednesdays here would be my all-time favorite go-to!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPcLj2UIW_Ii0cHrEJPz9DyyrI7-lTeup7pvAl8&fid=0x0:0x37a99b2a94c8acc5"],"When":"2023-9-21"},{"Name":"Jiwon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVIsZg-pNG4lb9PqK7xCUlXSaQxpd3Jdf6ktNLgUMoYNFrnzim8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am SO stoked about this one! LOCAL, CRISPY, DELICIOUS & JUICY!

Although we had dinner ready to be eaten at home, we couldn't help trying out a couple items. We decided on 2 pieces of regular fried chicken ($5.99) and pork belly bao bun ($3.50).

As we was waiting, the owner was talking to us and let us know that they make their own special brine for their chicken to make it more juicy and flavourful. He also said that it's mainly a take out restaurant but people can eat in if there are spots. He was a very lovely guy and you can tell that he really cares about his business and his customers.

It did take a while to get our food but they make everything to order. I hate when you go to a fried chicken place and they give you fried chicken that has been siting there for who knows how long. So I didn't mind waiting.

The fried chicken was extremely crispy, juicy and flavourful! It wasn't too greasy and didn't make me feel sick afterwards either. The bao bun was just okay, I wouldn't order it again.

I am a huge fan of Church's but Go Go possibly has taken over to the #1 spot. I will most definitely be returning to try out everything else on the menu!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMwr_oYJunwJKKPjS5cIBewFtCO3gdOcftXIE4C&fid=0x0:0x37a99b2a94c8acc5"],"When":"2019-11-10"},{"Name":"Iris","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVuI2UF9tE3ZrxOyUZSh_nizM_Sr9TFUm8fPaLEBlASv1eRDOW2=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ordered the Skirt Steak Bowl and I was really impressed. The steak was very flavourful and tender. I loved how the sides were roasted brussel sprouts and kale, very different from regular rice bowls that you see. I will be back next time to try their chicken!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNdYbiAVLNG0w44siPkTs4GPKpuk1ci7o1W9Uj3&fid=0x0:0x37a99b2a94c8acc5"],"When":"2019-11-8"}]

[{"Name":"Olya","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVuljIiKlDUrPITFddmFs3zyev4mYxdf2HUixB81rOEFGv2L00G=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have never tried Persian food before, so I can’t compare, but it was the best food court experience for a while! Kebabs were juicy and delicious, rice was crumbly and fragrant. We could not eat everything and took left overs home. The staff was very nice! We met Varan, it was very interesting to chat with her about their cuisine. We will definitely come again and try other meals. Recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNUh1u_cR-LbaYJn0zzwRm-UT5_IK7yYDeIUqxv&fid=0x0:0xc4a5aadb0e7a117c"],"When":"2024-10-10"},{"Name":"Michelle Whiting","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLmss_OEESK8x1d2pEnsJo89h8T20_Ft18qRE00KpBNnMnF5Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The most delicious Persian food I have ever tasted! The lamb was so tender it fell off the bone. Very lovely staff, too. Thank you for a delicious meal!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN8-kirEBruI8gCjSp-JvXmKh0_C7DAk6bpjMJw&fid=0x0:0xc4a5aadb0e7a117c"],"When":"2024-12-3"},{"Name":"Armin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUVKfPvn-jqW8hTOlU1VeElw6vFvjre9PTWSba_96soEJn4hAFVjA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"It's cheap Persian fast food restaurant. You really get what you pay for. The quality is low and the kebabs are usually uncooked. It's the only Persian restaurant that I have to ask for my kebabs to be well done. But never the less it is still a better option compared to the other restaurants in the food court.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN9fY94w5MHLs6he5LwSy1h6lQRFTvSLzbGpw-J&fid=0x0:0xc4a5aadb0e7a117c"],"When":"2024-9-19"},{"Name":"sina alizadeh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKSC-qOWc2GiQiv5hVq0Qj8qebxMFe41pWOC8rfJ3jR-i_vYg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My wife and I recently visited Cazba Restaurant, and we had an outstanding experience. Baran was incredibly patient and took the time to explain the entire menu to us, which we greatly appreciated. We decided on the tachin, and it was absolutely amazing! Exceptional service and delicious food—highly recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMOPrh5iw-1DV7Fodv88jQ3DF3Hy2OebTHbgl3y&fid=0x0:0xc4a5aadb0e7a117c"],"When":"2024-12-3"},{"Name":"Kavosh Kln","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWlfB9EgU9YnNPo13doTycsdypjxUXFct9EaV5C94Dq3F3Ewyug=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Shahriar is an amazing chef at Cazba! The food is always delicious and cooked to perfection. The whole team is great — everyone there provides excellent service and makes the experience even better. It’s definitely one of the best Persian restaurants I’ve been to in Vancouver. Highly recommend! 😍","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sina Davoodi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVsrtSBz--2gJPVnH9uOwP4TtQcMb0EOF2s0Imz8ul5N4xxXGA9=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great! Compared to other options in the food court, in my opinion, the money you pay is reasonable and you get delicious food.
Try at least once and enjoy!
One of my fave’s!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOXg9onzo0tABvKQEaVv5tTs-LJi0vmLKGCKgmt&fid=0x0:0xc4a5aadb0e7a117c"],"When":"2024-8-1"},{"Name":"Parisa Parisa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXiqvy4f3Zh-Hle5yXFRmNoQv42eDGnEFF3-BLvXVbsX9fq-zKasQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The staff is so friendly and the food feels like home 💌 Kabobs were juicy! For the taste and portion at that price was a steal","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPqBUjbqAn2q6XV0ebDrQ0dnWO3wEG0MAGP4T8z&fid=0x0:0xc4a5aadb0e7a117c"],"When":"2024-12-13"},{"Name":"Mary K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLM32L-upYYQa_ml8TrN7nODFH_dv8dTRlYkW-KTO7iQeVXbOw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I recently dined at Cazba Persian Restaurant in Loughedd Center, and unfortunately, my experience was far from satisfactory. To begin with, the food was served cold, which significantly diminished the overall enjoyment of the meal. One of the key aspects of Persian cuisine is its rich and aromatic spices, but the dishes I received were notably lacking in this regard, making the flavors quite underwhelming.
The rice, a staple in Persian dining, was of low quality. It was pale and utterly tasteless, which was a major letdown. Good quality rice should be fluffy and fragrant, but what was served fell short of these basic expectations. The overall quality of the food was poor. When dining out, especially at a cuisine-specific restaurant like Cazba, one expects a certain level of authenticity and quality, which, regrettably, was not met. It's disappointing to see such a lack of attention to detail and quality in a restaurant that has the potential to offer a rich culinary experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNIUx4MiuyTlwhy5p4lu3D8qhXoTD3kf6_x30lr&fid=0x0:0xc4a5aadb0e7a117c"],"When":"2024-2-27"}]

title: Lee Garden Seafood Restaurant
descriptions: Chinese place offering a wide selection of traditional dim sum in a relaxed, elegant dining room.

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"May Zhagro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU9KviWdU_UGm6yjKPv-6aFaljm1EC_ecrxYhnt_LO3duiyBNho=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Delicious food but service was a letdown. We arrived in time for our reservation but no one was at the front to bring us in so we had to go into the restaurant itself to tell them that there are customers waiting at the entrance. We also got scolded by one of the servers for leaving the teacup lid open as were trying to let out a bit of steam so it wouldn’t be so hot to drink the tea straight away.

Food wise, we came for the dim sum and everything tasted. My favourite was definitely the shrimp with eggplant. The seafood congee was also flavourful but it was a bit lacking in the seafood. Overall, it came to less than $100 for 4 people before tips for a weekday lunch.

Be sure to make reservations as it was very busy for a regular weekday lunch time.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMSZfN6QZQKtTQjGvhORwCxQmETX0WOfGF2i1LN&fid=0x0:0x8cbc8af35596ce72"],"When":"2024-12-7"},{"Name":"Sarah Barnes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV1ca2s2Ju78fXB3WcTna5eoONK6rtbXd-or7AsBLVFqiGf04UKIg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Had a reservation for 12:00pm and wasn't given a table till 12:30pm. Typical service of what you'd expect from a traditional dim sum restaurant. It's hard to flag someone down after you've ordered if you want drinks or hot sauce. Or anything really.

Food was delicious. Everything came out hot except the Taro birds nest. That seemed like it wasn't as fresh. Service for food was quick. As soon as you order, food starts coming out quickly.

Lots of free parking. Was harder to find the restaurant if you haven't been to the mall before. I would go again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOgb2y95oJJvdHYE_HlkSeRes9ZqGxKjmPeF4jg&fid=0x0:0x8cbc8af35596ce72"],"When":"2024-9-29"},{"Name":"Jessameen Dela Peña","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX9mRpmL8-ZJUG7UPFcnsjzRdxjABif-MswbO1rxgJyyWfns8Jd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We ordered the sautéed beef with Chinese broccoli, fried rice with pork and shrimp, and cream corn soup with minced chicken. Our favorite was the deep-fried crab claw with shrimp paste—it was unbelievably good! The portions were incredibly generous and could last for days. The service was exceptional; our server went above and beyond to ensure we had the best experience and made excellent dish recommendations. The place is very fancy but offers affordable prices.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMn2GKo_hM5okzMfSZClpBZbu_Dh1Jtjmyl545E&fid=0x0:0x8cbc8af35596ce72"],"When":"2024-8-24"},{"Name":"Allan Ng","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVNe78uSaiW7EBdh1XXTEeus_vpGIm93XhcgtH3d0ZMDq17341pmA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Not bad; they have all my staples, but most things I found to be a bit blander compared to other dim sum restaurants (notably the Wu Gok). But keeping in mind that this particular location is really convenient for parking or transiting to. If I’m just looking for low-hassle dim sum and don’t live in Vancouver, I’d definitely come back.

I will also add, though the other typical items were on the blander side for my liking, the Egg yolk lava steamed bun was sublime - they did that one dish so so well, I’d say better than the average restaurant I can go to for it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNtU_QLUQRPpB3cyiB6qGnOGckTsumilRfNwha9&fid=0x0:0x8cbc8af35596ce72"],"When":"2024-7-14"},{"Name":"Jessy J","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLHNRFw0Z_JgaU0TxGr1Pv5X-w9V6JzR0bnCuTDlGr_7pfsbx_k=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Had dim sum here today.

Food was decent however service was slow.

Had tour regular type of dim sum and portion size is average.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPppIrPrzOxtQc8_twj4FXtbZpa_17MutvxfcO2&fid=0x0:0x8cbc8af35596ce72"],"When":"2024-10-28"},{"Name":"Janey Roh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLOMxtxjDNxOF_r0IqfPlGA74SB-KY6cVB7tMqaAybYfIP2Ng=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We booked the private room for my parents anniversary lunch. We had 3 tables with 8 people per table and I think that was the ideal configuration. We had a 10 course banquet menu that included peking duck and king crab. I worked with the manager, Carol for our event and she was extremely helpful. My sister is gluten free and Carol was able to accommodate by creating a 3 course menu for her. On the day of the event, we were able to arrive early to set up some decorations and discuss the flow of the event with the Alex, one of the servers for our event. Each dish was fresh and delicious. The king crab is really something- so sweet and tender. The service during the meal was impeccable. Carol, Alex and another server (sorry! I didn't get his name) were just amazing- so attentive and checked in regularly to ensure everything was going smoothly. Everyone remarked at how great the food and service was. Thank you for making our event so memorable!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Adrienne","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKvS1YiBi1kAYmplCTkzo9NqyjbLMViYayHxaEQA-dKyQUyyA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We’ve been to Lee Garden several times now, and their food is always consistent. We always make a reservation as we’ve seen people line up outside to wait. Service is quick, and the food is flavorful. We’re happy with the portions, the food is a bit pricier than other places.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOwG2_Az5cq5OI3OpA0WaEUDJNRDggmPhCICaUx&fid=0x0:0x8cbc8af35596ce72"],"When":"2023-5-15"},{"Name":"Tammy Hoang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW-yEBkQVFHvEWZfuLZqbeoOB7DXxgT7uhpXL_VVia-4TbHCTg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Some dishes were tasty, some were just okay. Foods were served quickly shortly after order. Restaurant has very convenient location with lots of parking at the mall. Nice decoration and very clean, we love the atmosphere. It's definitely a great place for family gathering. The restaurant is packed on the weekend, better to make a reservation especially when you come with a big group.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNY0Wjqe_5Xary3HvT8sMk90xkuTHA31i_L0NU&fid=0x0:0x8cbc8af35596ce72"],"When":"2023-2-8"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"JP","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX90NeQebsEGfp9rJe7B7QdUfdncEkOmwFrEw8C0EIB0z7Jl9-uUg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is a must-try Korean-style Chinese restaurant. The food is incredibly tasty, and the broth of the jjambbong is clean and refreshing. Both the sweet and sour pork and the spicy garlic fried chicken were perfectly crispy, with delicious sauces that made the meal very satisfying. Plus, the prices are very reasonable.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"HYEWON LEE","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocImw2BV3gpBbuKJRFJyndnOLdUx52roq9Q8ll4TquJg0hNwng=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Awesome foods and nice service. Most favourite is spicy seafood noodle, which has a lot of seafood and perfect spiciness. When my parents don't have appetite, we place orders of deep fried spicy chicken and seafood scorched rice soup. The rice soup is very soft and delicate and spicy chicken has a perfect balance of crispy outside and tender inside. I highly recommend this restaurant for family dine-in.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP61jdct5gPQytDMdHPfQhPfCjuShmJpan19VB_&fid=0x0:0x76c34e41dc3dd317"],"When":"2021-3-24"},{"Name":"Francis Li","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWgfmbUHLwmxF3ATfQGv1RD5eZck6TDnyYt1IZAHB6YDFw4kfEYkg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food is great. This has become our regular place to get Korean food. The location is also clean and a good place to eat with 4-5 people. The seats are in booths so you will need to separate if you have a larger group.

Their khanpuggi (Korean fried chicken with sweet sauce) is my favourite and probably the best I’ve eaten so far.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNMfITN5SV912JFu-VXkNc8gJs4lMk8JJ0OwZRg&fid=0x0:0x76c34e41dc3dd317"],"When":"2022-10-30"},{"Name":"Joe Ong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWY0QkKOvXmXArCRzRQc2K62z7cyKngNEnzP-kHw0mhUaDX-VbO=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We drove by this place countless times. We new that Ruran was a new Chinese Style Korean restaurants. As the building is an old building, we noticed an old building smell immediately. There were not many people dining at this time. I'm guessing daytime business is much busier.

We quickly ordered a combo. It came with sweet and sour pork, black bean noodles and a spicy seafood noodle. The sweet and sour pork came first and I must say that it was crispy, juicy and flavorful. We had the sauce on the side so we dipped instead of drenched.

Black bean noodles and spicy seafood soup noodles were good. Very good price for Combo A. Great value.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNZjlZWy42PlZ5TiA0W8JhaAz6YORSYU1HZj-ph&fid=0x0:0x76c34e41dc3dd317"],"When":"2019-9-14"},{"Name":"Kim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVrftba3fmWixW5Rg8SO3N0tTHgu3sUj3by9VHuwz4x8TXWATfw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"So my Korean friends recommend us this place so many times and very first time visit here on Saturday:) This place is spacious and quiet 😊 in small old town this is a gem!!
What we order as my husband loves fried rice ordered it and I got spicy sweet pork . We both were super happy!!!! They brought us our childhood!! Will definitely come back again!!!😎❤️❤️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMrOmrWMCwLYkwpyhT8a2We0vdwOB1Y6tR7v_Ho&fid=0x0:0x76c34e41dc3dd317"],"When":"2022-7-3"},{"Name":"Jamie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIU1OPkdAYZ2-cX58b7PHdKmE9L8kdrxNfX8MisT-pu7cl-1mE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of the best Korean Chinese restaurants in Vancouver. Ordered combo-A for three people and it was more than enough. Tang-su-yuk was freshly made and perfect chewiness. Jjajangmyun and jjambong were the best!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPN0MYvkJ0YFEmHXPeWoi1fhP-6BHy4T62zMPud&fid=0x0:0x76c34e41dc3dd317"],"When":"2023-11-15"},{"Name":"Kristine Salva","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL7O2uIYZr4PZGpRXNs61iZ8-knWMylsARmkmvYkxWZVPz5Hg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I usually come back here to buy the chicken and fried rice. The taste is inconsistent sometimes its delicious and sometimes no taste. I was looking forward to buy take out today. What i got, chicken is soggy and the fried rice is good but no coleslaw missing in my order. Food has no taste or i might ordered the wrong choice. I put the chicken in air fryer hoping it will be crunchy but doesn't. No more take out for me its not worth $48.  May be dine in is worth it than take out and order the right food i may like. I might not come back here. Im so disappointed today.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP0I7gAa7mtytOTFc0NXovFxChtADI30efeVIha&fid=0x0:0x76c34e41dc3dd317"],"When":"2023-9-29"},{"Name":"v l","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUdZvJxBhGRMKAh6ZoV-1pNG0RsqEMX0Q7xeTmMWZiQ1-rLiRu7Rg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Not vegetarian friendly: just edamame and noodles with black bean sauce. The noodles were pretty good, though; a lot of onions!!
Other dishes were pretty good, Chinese Korean style. Dominant flavours: onion, spicy mustard (😋), black bean, rather than the usual Korean gochujang, kimchi tastes.

Large portions, shareable - for family-style dining.  Yellow pickled daikon and onions with black bean sauce for banchan.  Overall food was good.  Would like to go back to try other items on menu available.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNYpnJXFyhZVxgyf0eMqNRlJIooulpbKe0ox4zo&fid=0x0:0x76c34e41dc3dd317"],"When":"2020-7-20"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Jennifer Bee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFO0fgPBTIA1yxL3IXSghRJ6EmshLC1YB1a72b-xeg3kpjHx0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Took my MIL out to get her nails done and stopped by Ricky’s for lunch. It was noon and it took about ten minutes to get a table as it was quite busy. She loved her fish and chips and ate nearly all of it which is a good sign. My shrimp po’ boy sandwich was good too and a nice amount of heat.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNn3fUX6I6TQ2rUoNgX9hgrber9wPt9dhwe91SH&fid=0x0:0x6154d88775c17540"],"When":"2024-11-23"},{"Name":"Danial Dehghan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVXgDzaiKXT97_r82ZF9d2HsnV9L5L_dmiF-k12CY0fufyZgoVyUw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing experience! The burger was absolutely delicious, and the staff were super friendly and attentive. Everything was perfect from start to finish. Highly recommend!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMMx9Oqh4evkQTG8qqdUVy6aQbdtzhU1P_PWyqA&fid=0x0:0x6154d88775c17540"],"When":"2024-12-18"},{"Name":"J Roberts","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXZCK_Dwit38tgGB6wCDQgn_t0VvLEAlRjrv6_w2VfOSJRvoeNFrg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Stopped in for breakfast. Veggie omelet was stuffed with veggies and cheese. French toast was fresh tasting.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOhBQR6uQCkeFaPfeLlKem4kwdItdvfBpmGkhwl&fid=0x0:0x6154d88775c17540"],"When":"2024-11-14"},{"Name":"Jojit Bermudez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIYUoK5Gds0JkJtokCJz9kcAhoAJc6Hkp2QVUgUXDyhHKpnjQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Brought my parents with us for a weekend brunch. We enjoyed our visit at this location. Bam our server was awesome. He was friendly, polite and attentive. We are definitely coming back here soon.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPPJ615wqd2CrHXFNFYjjcgfZnyLiMPdyrFMFv9&fid=0x0:0x6154d88775c17540"],"When":"2024-11-16"},{"Name":"Maria M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIbAl3QqzjCkGeEfZrvLw1-pFOjmS4Pev33ZP0gmGTUa7cdX1E=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My hubby and I came in for a late dinner.  We were greeted by Anna with a cheerful smile, led to our table and after some talk she took our order.  We haven’t been to this location so she gave us some very good suggestions,  hubby took the original hamburger and I got the senior 3 course meal,  cream of mushroom soup, chicken strips with coleslaw and lemon meringue pie.  Glad we took her suggestions.  We enjoyed our meal.  Everything was cooked to perfection.  The ambiance was great and the restaurant was so clean.   It’s really amazing what you learn unexpectedly just by talking to people like Anna, who served us and the other young lady. And even though it was close to closing time, we did not feel rushed.  All in all we had a great experience and being creatures of habits, we will surely be back.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"John M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWItgijJKwgA0f52g38y2veJk-Ddfx32Y6n5pRa8jqM3m7RR0lStA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Very casual and cozy atmosphere similar to a pub.  Service was slow to begin with but ended up being good. Wasn't excellent per se but good.

Their omelette was cooked well. I like how their veggies had a bit of a crunch to them. Perhaps the peppers could have been cooked slightly longer but it was good. Shredded hash browns were not greasy which was good.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"K’s coffee lover","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW-385uQOflrqOxsV0QWsdIyhv-rxdZ7rLwLnLPmzpfPGzr9P6Z=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This is my first time here and it was not a pleasant experience. I have studied the menu ahead of time and was looking forward for my dinner gathering with one extra family. Not sure if our server is new to her job.  After taking our order and we all confirmed the detail. Number of things went wrong.  First we ordered a soup (meal size) with garlic bread. It came in a cup size instead (no bread). We also ordered a burger with lettuce wrap. This option was highlighted on their menu. We explained to the server few time and make sure she understands. She end up giving us a burger with bun. We asked for and exchange and it came back with literally just TWO pieces of lettuce 🥬
If you have a lettuce wrapped burger elsewhere  you should know how’s that should be (Very disappointed). We also ordered a kid meal. The server didn’t offer any drink until we remembered that was included. Overall the food was blend and the server knowledgeable need a big improvement.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMGZG4BlkpSSw-LeSXPzH0zwtq3X1vPWfh9cJ40&fid=0x0:0x6154d88775c17540"],"When":"2023-3-9"},{"Name":"Al So","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLumQHIv-5W9wXPr4ZbA1zWCVnPk2w1Kc3bjsO93-VMG-v7JQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of the few places in the area for  breakfast. Place was busy for a Saturday morning. This used to be an ABC restaurant but it closed, owner was ready for retirement and the Ricky's down the street closed and moved to this location. So even less options to eat out breakfast. Food was as expected and good options for kids. There is an interesting private room at the back good for parties and large groups. No issues I would eat here again,","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNxUWJfMLXiAJVaB7hhn8uxnbyOd8XorXIM4AT1&fid=0x0:0x6154d88775c17540"],"When":"2022-10-23"}]
