[{"Name":"Jessameen Dela Peña","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX9mRpmL8-ZJUG7UPFcnsjzRdxjABif-MswbO1rxgJyyWfns8Jd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"As a sushi fan, I was eager to try this place out. However, my visit in March was disappointing due to bland and dry food. I noticed they have been closed for almost a month or two. I'm curious if there has been a change in management since my last visit in March? It would be great to see improvements in both food quality and service.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOkBoy1q3ZTmnnz3vBVc55Xy0owCoDg9q2yruNY&fid=0x0:0x7315c3ddc35be1e7"],"When":"2024-6-13"},{"Name":"Cameron Luo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUNv4MBQjlc7mIVzxf9_EfHWHthxHa6geMMy3QWZ4s9TnJG2fWO1A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I loved this sushi place!!!
I came on a Saturday night, the food was amazing.
Also, their service is very good as well.
Would come back again when I visit the area - I felt welcomed when I dined here.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPT9pWQLy0GnHHCNsFEeT2a5J54L9Lhi7ZZW8R7&fid=0x0:0x7315c3ddc35be1e7"],"When":"2024-7-23"},{"Name":"Vitalie Veclici","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVn8kycEuyvgu8wcx5Mpwijp97INeeCs7xxytZNIaEQ_HzZHS2yeg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sushi Koo is a cozy, welcoming spot for sushi lovers, offering fresh and delicious Japanese cuisine. The menu includes a great variety of rolls, sashimi, and specialty dishes that are well-prepared and reasonably priced. The fish is always fresh, and the portions are generous, making it a good value for the quality. The staff is friendly and attentive, and the service is quick, even during busy times. Whether you’re dining in or taking out, Sushi Koo is a reliable choice for satisfying sushi cravings.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ads","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVwDyuvQtXP_VygmU1rNXhUJ0mc48E4h1QtDkdEfrlXmuS-mYhL=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Arigatou ありがとう !
I'm normally super fussy and strict on good sushi joints, this place makes the exception and my favorites around Greater Vancouver list no doubt. A plentiful portion of fresh Edamame 枝豆 and Agedashi Tofu 揚げ出し豆腐 were great, followed by a beautiful presented and perfectly prepared tray of Inari Roll 稲荷, Unagi Roll  ウナギ and Dynamite Roll 炸虾卷 were flawless. A phenomenal and incredibly tasty experience left me gagging for more and I had to delve into a couple of cheeky Inari Nigiri いなり寿司, Tamago Nigiri 玉子寿司 and Avocado Nigiri ネタ were phenomenal, big fat chowy yummy rolls.
The menu is one of the best I've seen, staff are super friendly and talented and the aesthetics are great, it's such a cosy vibes joint with a local home cooking kitchen feel. They also feature a unique purple rice option here at reasonable priced fare.
Support local businesses!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPKdi8mk0Fh3ap4R69GkSKDttRniyrD0Dyu-lhs&fid=0x0:0x7315c3ddc35be1e7"],"When":"2023-6-18"},{"Name":"Kelly B.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJkiKuJm4moehDFI36IJphpjRLNWxNWzBlehm-exa9sv2k-Ng=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It was my first time here, and I was very impressed by our experience. The service was the best I have had in years. They provide tea and water immediately upon being seated. Recommended dishes and told us there were pictures of food online, refilled water, cleared dirty dishes promptly, and offered extra ginger when they saw I liked it. The food was prompt, fresh, and delicious. The prices are average, keep in mind that every restaurant has raised prices due to covid losses and increased rent. Keep up the good work.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alex","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKeyFz2HjwN9xzz9AnNUP1f9FxIJz9s0PK8fDQoD1g82Jzc6w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an amazing experience at this sushi restaurant for lunch. The sashimi was exceptional, fresh, and full of flavor. The service was outstanding; my waitress treated me like I was in a five-star restaurant! I highly recommend this place for both the delicious food and the incredible service!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Faezeh Vahdatihassani","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV2bw-ymcu67hZtIwsDNrPQPJaoPY4lqCRiAu3XCWAdqpV5X3b7=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was obsessed with Sushi Koo. When they closed, we checked every day to see if they would reopen. Yesterday, after many months, I finally went there for lunch. I had fish and chips, and it was incredibly fresh. The fish had no unpleasant odor and was crispy without being greasy. The new owners are very friendly and respectful. Although the prices are a bit higher than before, the quality has greatly improved. Pay more and have higher quality and healthier food. Thank you, Sushi Koo team.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Christina K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXY44ToPfFNvS5cz96PYOxJzhEcZVC7MRcG4Ip4Xsn3W2MXZgty-w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I've been eating at Sushi Koo at least once a week for the past year. I was devastated when they closed down only to find out they were open again the next month. Didn't hesitate and ordered some basic rolls, oshi, dragon roll, the usual.
First, the prices are absolutely insane now. Yes, it's true the portions are a bit bigger, but it was bland and not comparable to the old place. I loved their salmon oshi and dragon roll, but they don't taste the same anymore. And I miss the happy combo :(
At this moment, nearby Shio is the cheaper and also tastier choice, and unless the menu and prices drastically change, I unfortunately don't see myself coming back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM9HnlxvPVjG1v7tlVJ8qV4C-TEaPKCrvUVUw3Q&fid=0x0:0x7315c3ddc35be1e7"],"When":"2024-1-26"}]

[{"Name":"Tyler Hazelman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVaOeOfMrKb93Y_IutfdRfQ5RnvS47tYfW1M-2iSLOIvO-Sl_d1=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This cozy spot in Coquitlam is perfect for a steaming bowl of ramen, offering plenty of options and add-ons. My go-to is the Double Double Chashu Tonkotsu with added Kakuni (pork belly)—an absolute home run! Do yourself a favor and stop by for lunch; you won’t be disappointed.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOi4M9zFpvrTZRL3MwFQwZTu2FtK3Bu5LwX6OJa&fid=0x0:0xedb6807f8baab6cd"],"When":"2024-11-11"},{"Name":"Jessameen Dela Peña","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX9mRpmL8-ZJUG7UPFcnsjzRdxjABif-MswbO1rxgJyyWfns8Jd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Been searching for the best ramen spots in the area, but this one didn’t quite live up to my flavor expectations. While it wasn’t for me, I still appreciate the experience and hope to find a better match next time!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOm4QHh43LMJEbyVIMPwt6RtPbDWVTv99tk8C22&fid=0x0:0xedb6807f8baab6cd"],"When":"2024-12-8"},{"Name":"Mikayla Cortan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXUSbVNbWxTmKX3pyqaMjVhNP6W7orlcHjVcPPcVICoFkwdwTLO=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely adore Shobu!! Ramen is always my favourite and is constantly my craving so I’ve tried a fair few of ramen places around metro Van and Shobu has always been the best!! My favourite is the Kakuni ramen, it’s absolutely to die for! Their prices are very comparable or even slightly less than most ramen places, the best broth and pork flavours too. I’ve even gotten my dad hooked on it and he was originally not a fan of pork broth. Absolutely recommend this time and time again to all my friends!
P.S. my girlfriend and I came so often one of the waitresses would always recognize us and remember our order and it was so sweet!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPS4hjkAdxyZfwmksDC-f9uJa1GOOnTlYc5ZnyJ&fid=0x0:0xedb6807f8baab6cd"],"When":"2024-10-28"},{"Name":"Thor Campbell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVh1pnkJmsn1D8awag9xC4L5eddyHFQgwiWuJifBf1DVM9IvsHo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sho Bu came up as a random spot for Ramen, I tried it, and it was so good!
The portions are actually fair, and the amount of protein and toppings in the ramen are loaded, too. Followed by fair prices and convenient location by Coquitlam Centre

The service was great, food came super fast and it brings me back to a legit ramen shop in Japan. Small little shop for something quick and easy just as it should be.
I would certainly return to support this small business around the Tri-Cities area!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOa6qib1zyeQB8go2Zru8Z45a8GzcbJVXuPGndc&fid=0x0:0xedb6807f8baab6cd"],"When":"2024-7-8"},{"Name":"Noah MacLeod","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXnGOTt69QkP-Odwlqd-UzHafm6Dj1VvbHDQiYOi-yrHDWH31aixQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really great spot, I will come back next time in town. The food was out impressively quickly, and I was very happy with the combo I got! Tasty, well portioned, and interesting balanced flavours.

I've been told that I don't know what good ramen is because I haven't lived in the city, which I do argue against... but my amateur taste buds, and wallet, give Sho Bu fivvveee stars!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM95x6j6OVVCQ8SMjraWVu8XB_N5pHCUbaoNr16&fid=0x0:0xedb6807f8baab6cd"],"When":"2024-5-27"},{"Name":"Evangeline Reymundo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJI1Nlu3hdQyr4eln6VfUWQFA-CRztL9qvZigMJlicalVY3cw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The food is good and affordable. I had the summer special(Zaru Soba), which was very refreshing. The server was very attentive and frequently checked to make sure that we were enjoying our meal.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMcomlVdUkVBNhqAsj3P509CB3fWslD7NFWPQqA&fid=0x0:0xedb6807f8baab6cd"],"When":"2024-7-22"},{"Name":"Rich B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVoQ-WXqpj4r3w8UAKcm_AnoI410Sm3LNTYN6x5shslunTgL988=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I stumbled upon this little hole in the wall near Lincoln sky train station and literally what a treat!!  The ramen broth is literally out of this world.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNQbkwr3cedaV0fmzuBQTOKtWBEW14JhvpdhKSt&fid=0x0:0xedb6807f8baab6cd"],"When":"2024-11-18"},{"Name":"Vanessa L.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWxblsEoXnos0OURVMxJHIKqi8429GoOvGK9m8yN-pYifX-rdV7dA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great people and great food. It was recommended by my family. Happy to have a new place to go to for ramen!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOPpJZMsmG_LYruyFrro60YjFKsosp_MASH26q_&fid=0x0:0xedb6807f8baab6cd"],"When":"2024-8-19"}]

[{"Name":"Nicky Choi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWdbrHfH4GFsTTqgK1b8FKEyHjbYNyqA15i6JBcGlTzjesmGsA3=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Doppio Zero Pizza truly lives up to its name when it comes to their pizza! The crust was perfectly thin and crispy, with just the right amount of chew, and the toppings were fresh, flavorful, and generously portioned.

As for the pasta, it was just okay. While it wasn’t bad by any means, it didn’t quite stand out the way their pizza did. It could use a little more flair to match the high standard set by their pizzas. I also didn’t like how the pasta noodle was too over done? 😬

The tiramisu was delicious as well.

One thing to have in mind as well is the parking.. if you go during a busy time.. you might need to park in the residential area up the street and walk..

Overall, Doppio Zero Pizza is a must-visit if you’re craving top-tier pizza. I’ll definitely be back for another round of their incredible pies!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMWz1qkXa_dRoPp1tDige938yd0NVrn7CaniteR&fid=0x0:0xd23db9fd5273683e"],"When":"2024-11-24"},{"Name":"Youngsoo Song","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU9KF6xNrz8Ca-06zFTT1f92qb4UuXywvQbI5TeswgCgRYyBqNnHA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Food was good and the server was friendly. I had the pizza and the burrata-- both were good and reasonably priced. I gave the food 4 because while the taste was good, the dough near the center of the pizza was so thin, the toppings kind of tore through it. Perhaps my toppings had too much moisture(?) but either way, I wish the middle had not torn.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO4lvZij57sk_m_zZG-bu8SmTU-NubQmz8Gv00S&fid=0x0:0xd23db9fd5273683e"],"When":"2024-12-13"},{"Name":"Cheestravels (Cheestravels)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUu90KHK59eES_iLdA-5e4hTpzDDtNybwcTzvnfRLjdEkfHdQ5Xbw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"A tad overpriced for what they give you. Pizza is great and gnocchi is amazing. Tried a few dishes and pasta was decent but not incredible for price. Desserts were underwhelming with canned whipped cream on the sides. Was disappointed that they charge an automatic 20% gratuity charge for groups or 8 or more.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMVfMFJNbu9g2OV8HWFRcI2fA01-Ha4oSxuV8kV&fid=0x0:0xd23db9fd5273683e"],"When":"2024-7-27"},{"Name":"Conor Finding Realtor","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWt3-qD1dIuKKhCigfciL6_hrPkCXppeVegMsaV8xEZkwNnNrs=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hands down best Pizza in tri-cities. Love this place and such great Atmosphere!

I ordered the Margarita and this pizza was made to perfection. The staff had such a welcoming vibe as soon as I came through the door.

I met the owners Giulia and Daniel who are outstanding people that clearly have put there all into this restaurant. There story moving here from Italy is the icing on the cake.

If you want truly authentic Italian food come to Doppio Zero!

Thank you so much for the great service and amazing food!

I will be coming here a lot more!

Conor Finding","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNECU47lUiUaAQU5C8wuyEQ1na0QMa0t_F1iu5J&fid=0x0:0xd23db9fd5273683e"],"When":"2024-9-6"},{"Name":"Swimming Lion","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIoNuKoBPU8hDsJrOBlEDRPQawlWHi3C9rUvrLYtz7paaZM0w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love this place !
Stone oven pizza so delicious the crust is thin, chewy and crispy
Love the carbonara  too the pork is very special hefty meat taste , fatty but not too fatty
Coffee was creamy and rich with dreamy aroma
affogato - rich and robust flavor with a pronounced coffee taste.
Servers are very friendly and attentive
Free parking lot
We went on Sunday evening around 8 pm the parking lot was pretty empty
We have party of 13 and when we pay server told us we don’t need to tip extra as for party over 8 they will automatically add 20% on top for gratuities","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOLr6M3r84e3yCErwyvFutgs65ZD7_DzQAmlugN&fid=0x0:0xd23db9fd5273683e"],"When":"2024-8-5"},{"Name":"NôMāR Åltïçłöś","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXKVyqW_kOlfqb-yGJ_Ks--LFkl55GXHpZ6S3YNX2dqaycCck_x=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nice, quaint Italian restaurant at Como Lake Ave., in Coquitlam. Very positive vibe once you enter the place. Impeccable service from start. The food was superb. One of my favorite place to go.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNKK--SEp02at22elf4GZcmkqg8v695mmOVKqwF&fid=0x0:0xd23db9fd5273683e"],"When":"2024-8-30"},{"Name":"Danial Dehghan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVXgDzaiKXT97_r82ZF9d2HsnV9L5L_dmiF-k12CY0fufyZgoVyUw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of the best Neapolitan pizzas in coquitlam with Wood fired oven  that I’ve tasted, if not the best. Dough is sourdough meaning healthy as well. Dough also was excellent, chewy yet perfectly baked. Place was great and cozy. Pizza taste was unique Considering the quality, price is fair as well. Open kitchen well depicts their cleanness and pizza craftsmanship.This is my new go-to.🍕","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOzpZBxs-lPZeno12i-7kpMiuuoOoeBWV2WbyXP&fid=0x0:0xd23db9fd5273683e"],"When":"2024-8-18"},{"Name":"Joshua Fang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVVYKjZadI3GLvYlhP8JzW1RAWYF0hYt7IB342AdEQBC7hNDQVNQg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Pretty crazy that this spot is in Coquitlam. One of the best pizza’s I’ve ever had and some great pasta as well. Service is good. Atmosphere is good. No frills, good food. What else can you ask for?","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNSLFB0woHceKwU2FmtnPWrRAu0B_YlvgrmJHPV&fid=0x0:0xd23db9fd5273683e"],"When":"2024-8-27"}]

[{"Name":"Gustavo Torres Lauria","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUgB5NGic5lsyx494iU5NEDDDei2vBk5Dik0XtIwHIOdAsln9HE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Sushi California is such a bad sushi place that you will regret it. I feel so upset I got to pay for this awful food: the Dynamite Roll was very weird tasting. Tons of lettuce (in a dynamite Roll!!? Like, really? Unheard of!) and on top of it, the lettuce was off, too mushy and well tasted rotten.. Long story short, terrible! We also got a Mr Prawn roll, soaked, but like really soaked in mayonnaise and a sweet sauce. Too rich, too fatty…too disgusting. Make yourself a favour and chose another sushi shop. Any other, it will be better hands down.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOwZl0kJgh9FrRr6Xxfk7XxyoCFpDyk1ocgNMz0&fid=0x0:0xeb1c795ce885c7de"],"When":"2024-6-22"},{"Name":"Mohammad_s Zare","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX0zvPgAwUepTiYIAUBS1yK_ACR_lBIpMWJx1RjPIgsoDnibPMz=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing Sushi and Generous Portions!
I recently visited Sushi California in Coquitlam with my wife, and it was an incredible experience. The food was absolutely perfect—fresh, flavorful, and beautifully presented. On top of that, the portions were huge, making it an excellent value for the price.

The restaurant had a great atmosphere, and the service was friendly and efficient. Whether you’re a sushi lover or just looking to try something new, this place is a must-visit. We’ll definitely be coming back soon!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPeI3Cs79Mlaxc-wMUOtW1bpURpme_tGfArB8bW&fid=0x0:0xeb1c795ce885c7de"],"When":"2024-11-25"},{"Name":"mackenzie jackson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVgC9tzVS7yRJwpcQ5nDzCNUvslbCgrhdSrEMgtr15St-UUo4Kg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love this place! They have the best Nigiri and Sashimi in town, their portions are big and fresh unlike other restaurants and the servers are kind and pretty.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPvl_iEnVk_yp3zyXO4YFzKFSGNuJAZjnaQnPXr&fid=0x0:0xeb1c795ce885c7de"],"When":"2024-9-6"},{"Name":"Daniel Jung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFE7g6vnjf23CW6mDeh4anchF8fxBs6O5Nsx0bvhepuO3MVzWa=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Update: Went in for dine-in at 5pm, true service was a little slow as they seemed understaffed, but it was still a decent dine-in (4/5 for Dine-in)

So happy they opened a Sushi Cali here! Not sure if it's because they just opened but the portion and flavor is 10x better than the other locations. I will most likely order here, minimum, once a week!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPUBxlTq8joKbn9Tatg_7Xlvx_uzxndzjI198rx&fid=0x0:0xeb1c795ce885c7de"],"When":"2021-12-12"},{"Name":"Cora","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU9YQmsmKhqCSvMVPAZKT18eImIWQ2QjEOLJi24FjTkNMSIg53C=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Finally a Sushi California has opened up here! I've always liked the one on North Road but the parking is atrocious so I never went. Tonight we tried out this new location and the service and food were great! The food came out quickly and the service was excellent! If you needed anything they were happy to help and refilled our tea often. The food was fresh and very large portioned. I'm glad a new location has been opened here in Coquitlam.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPtxlzQ69e1MqOiCqoDn76iexZBOuyDRl393O5v&fid=0x0:0xeb1c795ce885c7de"],"When":"2021-12-19"},{"Name":"VanGogh013","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJxFt4JIPmZ64ezhA6PUPFbMs3FhoBo_XeES_VgIT5n9E34NQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Normal sushi . Nothing special
Today Aug 31. We went again but wasn’t that good at all specially dark horse roll. It’s awful and other rolls are really bad.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNHTngwVVWmmWSmCHoaNmT3g-a8-Q9UYN1WKJVD&fid=0x0:0xeb1c795ce885c7de"],"When":"2024-7-26"},{"Name":"May Zhagro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU9KviWdU_UGm6yjKPv-6aFaljm1EC_ecrxYhnt_LO3duiyBNho=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Not busy at all when we went to Sushi California on Saturday night. Got enough food for 2 for both the meal and breakfast next day for $45. Prices were reasonable especially for the individual sushi. Vegas Roll was pretty good and had a small kick to the usual California Roll. The veggie sunomono came in a small bowl but the base was very flavourful and refreshing. The tuna from the BC Roll combo tasted fresh and not so fishy. The restaurant was playing mukbang videos which was an interesting choice. Small parking lot out front. Would come back again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPgPtL7fSgaGRiA6El5vY7FT51CBmNCzE-5cgrH&fid=0x0:0xeb1c795ce885c7de"],"When":"2023-4-29"},{"Name":"J Q","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWWLFaR2htiLNLIQAXB2-FbuNystyoB794RiAm0Uo82lJgg8OdK=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Update:

Visited again recently, food were even better then last time and the customer service got much improved!! Loved there Ton Katsu, it was crispy outside and soft & moist inside.
Never disappointed :):)

They have just right amount of rice on the nigiris, you will get LARGE portion of food than what you are paying. Great customer service and very clean :) I would come back for sure","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPyL9OzF-uKdBpBEJNlsr8Yx19y7hRVeKM13avr&fid=0x0:0xeb1c795ce885c7de"],"When":"2022-3-29"}]

[{"Name":"Valentina Herrera","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXZ7XlcJpLvK_YDmb_Ud57rBNg42U_aRNoKAu6mIfBQiMid6Oo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Visited BC for the first time and was recommended this restraunt. I can't stop recommending it myself. My family and I loved every dish. We will certainly visit when you come back.

Food is fast and fresh. Staff is polite and friendly.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO4xVUQdzNJshedrwv8fUXNQYaeVNsx0BplvSAV&fid=0x0:0xdf6b68ec77e84579"],"When":"2024-6-12"},{"Name":"Josh L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVomV4_Y_zk7wjQNBFHPicVGAVLUpU7FPKsDet970FZirM5QQQr=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great sushi here but only 4 pieces of chicken in the chicken teriyaki bento box. My disappointment is immeasurable, and my day is ruined. Still would come back tho","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM-7gVm2kMQDkQk2mfY1TXIPAtn0h1JiFPN9AR6&fid=0x0:0xdf6b68ec77e84579"],"When":"2024-11-26"},{"Name":"C L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWFSCt_t74XiqlEdz6jDYOHmtwc4pgb3Fve6nsF3wEBwwz9hl0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Low key authentic-style Japanese eatery with all the traditional favourites and chef-created special rolls.  The food tasted fresh, arrived quickly & sashimi portions were generous.  We saw many people doing take-out while we were dining so this must be a local haunt as the menu was reasonably priced","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPXgRr56pbczGaSjD4n7nWiiV_NZpKxiVy5QVAO&fid=0x0:0xdf6b68ec77e84579"],"When":"2023-7-24"},{"Name":"임예찬","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIyFEel7vyALHMzpn6C6Cq8-kba4Z_RkURgz7eRuP6QqvvjmQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"taste is awesome! I wanna visit here again!
and then all staffs are so kindly😊👍","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM_tRdePl3duzNCFv1wrbobi43cMK5m-jFGYkzS&fid=0x0:0xdf6b68ec77e84579"],"When":"2024-11-30"},{"Name":"Mingyuan Ren","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWY7nEuDRbKdGOcP9KUEFuTIhCoy_zXIvPqK78URJshjzUM9oo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We’ve ordered more than 10 times and never got disappointed. All of the dishes on menu are fantastic. Also great taste when you take it home. The oshi sushi is greeeeeeeat! Special rolls are amazing. And try their katsu! Udon! Highly recommend.
Still, something I do not like: tuna bite, yakisoba and yakiudon.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMyHUGERrJJoh0IN2rk7Bt0AugCkfwPzdzyuhXz&fid=0x0:0xdf6b68ec77e84579"],"When":"2022-7-3"},{"Name":"Ethel eh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWcZbZpeT9_dQ45cBTS5ThPY6RuQesAVvdjRBKD6-2KMiQYJdqi=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Still the best sushi I ever had. Veggie bento box. Very generous amount for under $20. Everything was delicious. Prompt friendly service. Free hot green tea while I waited. Well done !","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"JD","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXVFj7LNOTX4AOFSOmIlvZBDs4m0ZvbzGytwaTX7uYDSavNtj0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best BC roll I've ever had. Crunchy salmon skin with occasional meat, also with a delicious teriyaki sauce (no artificial crab meat, which i hate that a lot of other sushi places do). Then balance the sweetness with a spicy tuna/salmon roll or a spicy agadashi tofu.

Small little restaurant, seems to be family ran, servers are nice and the chefs don't look stressed out. Always a good experience when I eat here. Parking is not bad, there's more parking below towards Save-on.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNWESBNLIeUqoBdpmKKUHv0eiMBWj8I3hC9PlYx&fid=0x0:0xdf6b68ec77e84579"],"When":"2023-3-16"},{"Name":"Summer Denise","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXVLGlEjExYSI9TlDWJA5kTZkeVo9iNkfZ5Fa7s6qADcSesw6sxVg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Small and cozy, it’s nicely located near Mundy Park, one of my favourite places to hang. Unfortunately, my first dining experience here is also my last as ingredients used weren’t fresh. Rice was so stale that I could barely swallow the second piece of avocado sushi. They didn’t have enough avocado for the avocado roll and so they added cucumbers to it without first informing me of it. Salad, abundant but browning quickly as I ate along and my lunch lasted less than an hour. Batter on tempura was the right amount but sadly, not fresh, and neither was the spring roll. Terriyaki tofu on bean sprouts and cabbage was okay. Only tasty thing was their miso soup with wee cubes of tofu and no, not returning to the diner just for that or the great service I got from the server.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN7L9bWaWCIfdLpLQ5kruWiHQYI3hXPCQWiJkMQ&fid=0x0:0xdf6b68ec77e84579"],"When":"2024-3-8"}]

[{"Name":"Elmira Nazari","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUS8psOPde-fgvVYsglTVKj-j9hpNdB1347mGr_T9d11yAStREO4w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cute little Thai spot with very attentive service. They actually take the time to pack your food. Delicious and good portions.
- Spring rolls were jam packed with ingredients and incredibly crispy.
- Chicken wings had such a unique lemon/spicy and lemongrass taste
- Seadoo red Thai curry - sweet and spicy with coconut flavour. Served with rice.
- Pad Thai - large portion, well made.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPhf4jj_ordOfTlpBgCG1HHhBJm9h8cccQ4XSUU&fid=0x0:0xa680fed803c187a1"],"When":"2024-9-30"},{"Name":"Swapnil Kambli","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUdhhWN0KCMgQl8JxSlRxuwT7oQItuYRCMRTco9Mv-DKvRQLHe2=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We’ve dined here twice, and have found the dishes to be excellent, in terms of taste, quality and portions.
I’d easily highly recommend this Thai place, over many, cause of their authenticity and flavours.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPee8MUlEDDmW6qpcpri4m-4XLuD0d4IJYlg0Er&fid=0x0:0xa680fed803c187a1"],"When":"2024-10-29"},{"Name":"Liz Park","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJIuViSUslkGybLwzF5hJuKnwuKDgGhdfdvpLRCkLln5KJ6Gw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We discovered this hidden gem of a restaurant today and it was a hit!! We ordered veggie red curry, and rice and basil, and regular and coconut thai iced tea, and coconut shrimps. As you can see, their portion was more than enough and our tastebuds were satisfied! Our belly was satisfied, and we look forward to tasting more food from the menu in the future.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPgNn7gSB3UeOhmTbslc6I5LlGvGVY3roArCks2&fid=0x0:0xa680fed803c187a1"],"When":"2024-9-5"},{"Name":"Tara Elizabeth","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWafp5-DbmdXd42lrIMIaPpUa4TG8IACFTFef3W9rqO44JjPcQgRg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This was our first visit to this charming spot. The Thai food was exceptional. In particular, we loved the pineapple fried rice (chicken in there, too). We also really enjoyed the veggie spring rolls, and though it was very mild, we found the red curry tasty, too. Our only disappointment was there was no yellow curry. Our server was lovely and attentive without being too  intrusive. The decor was delightfully retro (see pic of 70s phone).  All in all, though it is tucked out of the way down Westwood Street, it is well worth a visit. The two of us ate for $50, including tip. It is hard to beat those prices. The restaurant closes daily at 8:30 so lots of time for a little later dinner hour(we like that)!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO3MkAuBqkfQID1HZL5cIqkSx2hcvXrZgyPvGE_&fid=0x0:0xa680fed803c187a1"],"When":"2024-5-22"},{"Name":"Jade Chin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLJWSVoZW1CCY-_xhdgdeWOnL28P_e39FAE_t38PKZ_hYo17g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ordered take out: chicken pad Thai and green curry with chicken. Personally, I'm not a fan of Thai food, but my husband chose tonight's dinner plan. Of all Thai places, this place did an outstanding job. The pad Thai was not too sweet, not too sour, not too salty, and smelt incredible. Good amount of chicken, big portion of noodles, good amount of tofu with bean sprout and the crushed peanuts on top was perfect. The curry was spicy despite mild, but manageable. Again, very tasty. Chicken was excellent, not dry and it was just right.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jessica Dhaliwal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXOeC5VCbc6g3HH3dxXpDS9bE993HEKMDVI3SjHX2aNdHbQOJHQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I would say Thai Coco is the biggest highlight of Coquitlam. The decor was so nice and it was cozy and the food was so great while dining in and even better as leftovers. Also this was the first time I ever experienced pasta or noodles that stay surprisingly nice and HOT because they were served on a hot plate! Loved the interesting menu too","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPhBe8YpmOUQfEqReIlDxMZtW7WFTShOKLL4Fgy&fid=0x0:0xa680fed803c187a1"],"When":"2024-8-29"},{"Name":"Shweta Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXtnc5g-DhlNFKBuVm-Ri3EJhNR7eysyJfm0HrPZFoOOsluh9pj=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A cute thai restaurant with great food, prices, and customer service! I read a couple reviews about the portions being a bit smaller, so my husband and I order 3 dishes. But we we're surprised by the quantity and the quality!! We had plenty. The portions were great. Our waitress was kind and quick to help. We were famished at arrival but left super full and with leftovers. We will definitely be coming back and be recommending to others.
We had the drunken chicken noodles, chilli chicken, and pineapple fried rice. All of them hot, fresh, and yummy. Try this place out if you're hesitant.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMmH3fPnITUAyOsmQwjgPlxztjt0Yy5IV34PKKy&fid=0x0:0xa680fed803c187a1"],"When":"2024-10-8"},{"Name":"Jhk 727","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXRlpzpCG0lmTiswrjxl92nKs9mapw2VnKHEXcy00upiXVnodNCJA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Amazing Tom Gha! Deep rich flavours that opens up your appetite perfectly. Red curry was flavourful while being not heavy - I could have had another bowl on its own.  Friendly staff with cozy modern atmosphere was a plus. Only knock I have was the portions - all dishes ordered were medium to small portioned. I would increase the portions by 10~15% and perhaps raise cost slightly to compensate - but that’s up to the owner’s business strategy:)
Overall, I’m glad to have found this place. Will be back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNSunyzuHZ8vtGGAmGtgFvTcTEv07fpipni41Kq&fid=0x0:0xa680fed803c187a1"],"When":"2023-12-10"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"A.J. Canadian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU0mITu_1OR_MuXzhVIkPjHjZnimy2Y-mI64r72OA1Zbucah6-N=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"A convenient Coquitlam restaurant serving drinks, bubble tea, share plates and delicious mains. More of a grab and go or quick stop kinda restaurant. Good food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOdXHVbm4tISC3oVOY17Fw9Rjte3DlkgNSHi7qz&fid=0x0:0x5c2ed58282bdcee3"],"When":"2024-12-15"},{"Name":"Eunice","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ2ALhqjwHhkNkSm6pXiyY4p5qQowzcr6jQE1ebfHzuWw2OswE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Went to buy the lunch bargain Bento.
For $14.95 only 3 slices of pork belly  and The box is full of rice.  Not worth it. Do not recommend to try.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOkEr-NhkrIqTLie9Mjy3sjLLJB14S17aoxaFp0&fid=0x0:0x5c2ed58282bdcee3"],"When":"2024-12-18"},{"Name":"John Seong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW0htFjeJaWzfoh1Wx3ky51rbanezwWv8SlRvcZ43DjNt3_9Xz8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Good Taiwanese food here with ordering available through either the app or in person. Dishes are generally good but a little bit too sweet. We tried the rice dish and their boiled curry. Good pick if you are trying to grab food and boba in the same restaurant.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPqFaLLwN1pPk88UFMWD_afKpM9HJlFZarycPXZ&fid=0x0:0x5c2ed58282bdcee3"],"When":"2024-4-18"},{"Name":"Mark","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLCap4roQc83_yZ-1MBmfeCbe_pnUK3r9NBKni5HgJlcUtNHA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"False advertising, makes this place hard to recommend. Sorry in advance for the long post.
I ordered the $14.95 3 sauce chicken bento box for pick up at around 8 pm. I get to the restaurant and grab my order go home open it and find just 3 sauce chicken, not a bento box.
Put the food back in the bag and go back down to the restaurant. My cell service can be spotty so figured maybe the phone did one of those things where a word is missed.
Get back to the restaurant, yes they didn't hear the bento part so I ask for it to be corrected. This is where it gets frustrating!
First I am told that they do not sell the $14.95 bento box after 5pm so I cannot get it. I point out their advertising doesn't say anything about "time specific" so then I am told they are "sold out". I ask if they sell any bento boxes at night and told no but would I like to order a side of white rice for my chicken?
Those are half the elements of a bento box right there!
So I just left with my chicken.
The food was good but shame on Bubble World for deceptive advertising tactics and for the outright lies.
I would forewarn anyone to be careful when looking at any advertised promotions at this restaurant.
Due to my work I eat at restaurants quite often and this is a first in any of my reviews.
I have attached the promotional poster for others.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNbtO_1ImM9lL6q-l4hl_w0y4wwU_3gNltydl-O&fid=0x0:0x5c2ed58282bdcee3"],"When":"2024-12-6"},{"Name":"Daniel Jung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFE7g6vnjf23CW6mDeh4anchF8fxBs6O5Nsx0bvhepuO3MVzWa=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Been enjoying their Dairy Free (Almond Milk) Bubble Tea specifically The Oreo Milk Tea!

When I'm lazy and don't want to try something new Bubble World is my best bet.

Mixing shrimp & Egg fried rice with Salt and Peppery Chicken Nuggets equals a happy belly.

Their Bubble tea has been #1 compared to anywhere else, I even prefer it over CoCo

Solid Bets:
Shrimp & Egg fried rice
Salt & Peppery Chicken Nuggets
Deep fried Squid Feet
Salty Peppery Squid roll
5 Spiced Beef in Chinese Pancake
Stirfried Noodles w/Beef & Green Onions","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOZ4vQf_AHXm9P8RswB5-4IyXJrdd8YV_rQep4r&fid=0x0:0x5c2ed58282bdcee3"],"When":"2022-1-16"},{"Name":"Sherry Ahmari","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUzZjpgnbFzMAdoLwNn-kzRLUMAt8kquABzgD2ac3X12G-Wogw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This is hands down the worst restaurant for service. They are not able to accommodate a group of more than four people and are so rigid to accommodate. Honestly our birthday event was made into a horrible experience.
Would not add a table because we were a group of six.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN7Zgdu_Vfw2otHQMAyxESPXFh418Zc5HSyT9NP&fid=0x0:0x5c2ed58282bdcee3"],"When":"2024-9-28"},{"Name":"Дарина Сніжна","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV627FxghGf4TOeVPZpUWXijbu7jcIHN9oro9ByB8LwCxlNoGFJZQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I can't say anything bad about the food, but I had to wait a long time for the waiter for the order and the bill. And maybe in general my impression would have remained neutral if the waiter had not put my umbrella in a dirty bucket. I find it disrespectful to have such a place for customers umbrellas.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM9G1yyg4iEB04yDLUiAVlpMZPiM3W8t8-B-JNX&fid=0x0:0x5c2ed58282bdcee3"],"When":"2024-6-27"},{"Name":"May Zhagro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU9KviWdU_UGm6yjKPv-6aFaljm1EC_ecrxYhnt_LO3duiyBNho=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Ate in at Bubble World and prices and portions were not too bad for this economy. The prices in-store is a bit lower than the one you can find on the website which is the opposite case for more restaurants. The rice dishes came with a good amount of side dishes and it was very filling to finish everything. The beef noodle wasn’t very Taiwanese but it was decent. The seating were booth formats and everyone had their own privacy. You scan a QR code to order your dish which directly goes into the kitchen. A server comes with the items you ordered on a receipt and checks it off as you get them.

There is a small parking lot where you can park but also a larger lot near the Old Navy / GAP.

Called Bubble World for take out. Food was packaged nicely. The popcorn chicken box didn’t have ventilation, so there was a lot of moisture collecting at the top of the box which wasn’t a pretty sight. However, the taste was there with the spices. The squid dish was spicy and chewy. The meal combo with rice had a good amount of variety to the dish. Lots of parking in the plaza. Within very close walking distance to Lincoln Station and Coquitlam Centre.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPgxJbP7xrVImriXVuTBYo40slurUQbgQS-eDqk&fid=0x0:0x5c2ed58282bdcee3"],"When":"2022-2-8"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Meghan Atkins","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWpn_HJKLz67oWun2TqZ53LpPOuwDcgytLe9I7rJRW9gkR5zUDI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I ordered take out tonight from Dinakis (through skip the dishes). Ordered my regular Greek dish, the chicken souvlaki. I often order from another restaurant but thought I would give Dinakis a try. Upon eating my chicken souvlaki skewer, I noticed the taste and texture of the chicken seemed off. To my surprise the chicken was raw in the middle. The restaurant was immediately called to inform them. They stated that we needed to contact skip for a refund (which is fine!) and said the chicken was raw due to how busy the restaurant was tonight. Unfortunately, I do not see this as a valid reason for serving undercooked meat. They offered to remake the meal and have me come and pick it up. Unfortunately with a baby in bed, leaving the house is not option which is why I ordered in.

I’ll no longer be order from Dinakis. Perhaps if the situation had been dealt with differently on their end I would. However, it’s all left a bad taste in my mouth - no pun intended.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPamzWqtMSJD_2lXqeftQ04VTeQ-qet20_AUo7c&fid=0x0:0x9aee5f46d48e0cd3"],"When":"2024-12-21"},{"Name":"Queenie Chao","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXZJZmSpZQRAFF9t6SoJ29KP7hdKen-l5gR8pgpgRf7-1s6aED9=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went here for my dad's birthday. Service was excellent! Food was great - the roast lamb, chicken marsala, and moussaka were all amazing, especially the lamb! The only exception was the steak, which was over cooked and full of gristle. To make up for it, they offered us a tiramisu cake which worked out well and was tasty too. Would definitely come back for the lamb and try other items too!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPUkbQOcVFipathRk-dHPJeXSBTX5g93Ke5HcNA&fid=0x0:0x9aee5f46d48e0cd3"],"When":"2024-10-14"},{"Name":"Jessica Tite","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVDIMc556UvdeCdK2q0SIDelAc_HJzjyapBYqP0A0CPBdyeWUex=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is the best Mediterranean food I've had! It's no wonder they have so many awards/accolades at the entrance way.
The food is incredible: well priced, fresh and great portions.
The restaurant is neat and clean, including the washrooms. It has a very cozy feel inside.
Service was excellent!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP2zKnmJCNiyvvJJiFSndVY5qI8Go-Dp0HU1Vdj&fid=0x0:0x9aee5f46d48e0cd3"],"When":"2024-2-11"},{"Name":"Al So","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLumQHIv-5W9wXPr4ZbA1zWCVnPk2w1Kc3bjsO93-VMG-v7JQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you’re in the Shaughnessy area in Poco and craving some Mediterranean magic, look no further than Dinakis Mediterranean Grill. Let me just say, the portions here are generously sized, so come prepared to feast!

The tzatziki is a standout—nice and fresh, with a flavor that’ll make your taste buds do a happy dance. It's the perfect companion to their delicious offerings.

Speaking of which, the Souvlaki Combo is a real treat. It comes with beef, chicken, and prawn souvlaki, each one cooked to perfection. The beef is tender, the chicken is juicy, and the prawns are succulent. It's a delightful trio that hits all the right notes.

We also tried the roast lamb, which was cooked to perfection. It wasn't fatty, and the meat just came off the bone. We thoroughly enjoyed it.

For those dining with little ones, you'll be pleased to know they offer kids' portions. These come with one skewer instead of two at a reduced price, making it great value. It’s the perfect way to keep the kids happy without breaking the bank.

Overall, Dinakis Mediterranean Grill is a great spot for hearty portions, fresh flavors, and good value. Make sure to bring your appetite—you won’t be disappointed!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNi-Vmmgslvmp-CsAb30_lQnluDK_dEqTU341G1&fid=0x0:0x9aee5f46d48e0cd3"],"When":"2024-6-30"},{"Name":"Patrick Laplante","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWEQ6rmzYgqU18BgeUeFbN3j9UzTXOfNOAqOLvy-TwFRIxBth-Q7g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Firstly, the service and the staff are absolutely fantastic. Secondly, the food quality is great, it's really great value, huge portions, and always fresh. And thirdly, great drink selection, and I was happy to hear that they can accommodate large parties as well. Whether for a cute date, family dinner, birthday celebration or quick lunch, I'd highly recommend!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMGEpDRCp2o6wFFn9ZB0lPz_oE8b1ckSu6JjaQG&fid=0x0:0x9aee5f46d48e0cd3"],"When":"2024-1-8"},{"Name":"Julian Sara Joseph","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWofxVvuCZOl3BWxzMUTJPVosg-yW0WoAuPTsW6aFO5_K2yZycmSg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The Greek food here was truly authentic and tasty. Souvlaki of all varieties was great. We had come back from a trek and all our tiredness was gone with the kind servers and their affordable but yummy food ❤️their portion sizes are quite large so it is filing. Loved the presentation too.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNJvrpsBh0Cgol4Hr9mDBGY6_JEDFnb7KJHbIEJ&fid=0x0:0x9aee5f46d48e0cd3"],"When":"2023-4-4"},{"Name":"Cheryl G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUQZ5krFYmB32nSSVZRn_5-zzzmWzMyLr7fQFLOSOH_4NttzFie=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Overall good experience. We had regular entrees but also ordered happy hour appetizers, portions was a little small. I also found that an automatic 18% gratituity was surprising for 7 people dining. But we enjoyed the food with our dining guests and I would recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Thom Slater","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVNyquzT0Ty5ga2cGbYXqVQ4Zp1mr8dSG4EejGqH4R5Eqad_PSB=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came in for an extended family dinner. Really generous portion sizes, the lamp chops were fantastic.
Other than the great food, what really made this a 5 star experience was the incredible service from Mariah.
She took our 12 person reservation last minute despite being solo, had such great energy the whole night, and really made it an enjoyable time for everyone. We'd come back just for her.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Linh L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVaB8qs_ygwwwpHNel9QXMXCKqxjoIZrWCW5N9kOTA3MUsIG0QWTg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Food quality has gone down quite a bit.  The service is still great and it's a clean place to dine at along with being able to accomodate larger tables.  I'd go again if it was the only option around here.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPVoOVfsz2IkZP8A7vFifm5tHHJIQd8T21GOmwQ&fid=0x0:0xb89aa5370ad1307a"],"When":"2024-12-17"},{"Name":"HW C.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUg-IQKwQu37rrt2uXrxPur2eFHVtEh0sof-QwsldNZaEygI2hK=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Been here twice, never again! Would have selected zero stars for food if that option was available. This isn't all the food we got. We also had a kid's meal and a onion soup. Super salty soup. Kid's meal was ok but pricey.
Basically everything in here is pricey yet quality is not up to par. Not an ordinary Hong Kong style cafe. Stay away!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMJAxe1MU5inKBYv7ViYQ-mxrXjCf2k4WieUwed&fid=0x0:0xb89aa5370ad1307a"],"When":"2024-10-11"},{"Name":"TERRY CHENG","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUsg-oI6sco7O5Go48_oGM2GdPS9ywAc_QfXDXDKM3uhrlF3VpMxg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Food is delicious. I had the chicken with salted fish fried rice. It was made perfectly with wok hay. You can taste the salted fish. The kitchen forgot my wife's order but unlike other typical Asian restaurant where the server just says it is coming, she apologized and went to follow up immediately. The atmosphere is loud and tables cramped. It is busy so you definitely need to wait. The washroom is 3/5 stars. Difficult to find any slippery floor.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPcw9bZT9QydmEGTIcGIKCSRHagLaVgqiZt-4Ml&fid=0x0:0xb89aa5370ad1307a"],"When":"2024-3-2"},{"Name":"Kevin S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWW-HoTH05SDyiEsT9u8Wd25Wyn-omXApiCGy1l-mOBxv_wj5xh=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A fine Hong Kong style restaurant.

I found the prices a bit on the higher side, but just slightly. The portions were generous, and the baked rice was quite creamy and delicious.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMnMqJR3qWP9PZWzBIUrCkSJrm8aqc7e1v_rq0_&fid=0x0:0xb89aa5370ad1307a"],"When":"2024-11-13"},{"Name":"Kanako Sakurada","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKYybgPjG_d3LYq66Ui47Ocd_2PMrfkKaju5V_L0IyVTR19lQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"HK style cafe with wide variety of food from western to asian to fusion! Great steak combo and 10% off ordering on line even when eating in. Food is more than decent and the portion size is large.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNN16kz7Zh95HdWI--Ik0AAwQ2Z7ETsd_sBB0GP&fid=0x0:0xb89aa5370ad1307a"],"When":"2024-10-2"},{"Name":"Munchica","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbQ6ACs51IPQJlRLrmnunOErED8bimOf5-y1uov4EWpuZvjQQjrA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Delicious and solid place for classic Hong Kong Cafe food. You can order online from your phone and they give you a 10% off discount if you order this way. There are plenty of combos that come with a drink and the menu is vast with both Western and Asian dishes. Highly recommend the tomato sauce baked ox tongue with a pasta of your choice. The tomato sauce was creamy, sweet, tangy, and savoury reminiscent of Campbell’s tomato soup. The lobster bisque was filled with lobster shell flavour. The red bean and grass jelly ice tasted delicious and refreshing serving as a dessert and drink at the same time.  Everything tasted delicious.

The portions for the fish and chips and pork and chicken cutlet and steak were good. There are comfy diner booth like seats to sit in and eat.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOOrZgPDR6-6MMRH7dQMHRUTXL89zevjiNTvoji&fid=0x0:0xb89aa5370ad1307a"],"When":"2023-11-5"},{"Name":"Linda Vu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW4Mt-fIM1ZKQuO_Y2ib9yo6xFV3B1mBRBjrbB_M80tp5QNaP0e=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best HK style cafe in Coquitlam.

Services and food are fast and efficient. The food is high quality and decently priced.

Breakfast ranges from $12-$14
Lunch ranges from $14-$18
Dinner set menus ranges from $19-$23","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN0PCRS9s3F_2r1xDSLsmEsNMEbJdi19UCaeY6C&fid=0x0:0xb89aa5370ad1307a"],"When":"2024-1-29"},{"Name":"ladan ghafouri","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVQKWEx_YV_Uj80v-xctgsLSGRY6V78hw5KMb4aNvRdZAaXJWti=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"My partner and I went there for brunch.We ordered Mexican and vegetarian omelet. We pick the French toast to come with. Also we asked for coffee. The menu was really rich and you will have variety of different opinions. We really loved the omelets. The French toast was perfect.  For the coffee I just prefer to have suger, milk and cream on the table like as every where else( they just asked us how many suger we want and put 4 milk on the table, not even in the plate). Overall I really liked it and we will go back to try lunch and dinner .","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNHNXWlB85awZcVo4LsFWw7YzcOUxmmYs4aAxUG&fid=0x0:0xb89aa5370ad1307a"],"When":"2024-4-8"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Sanjana Ranthilini","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX6POSb5GYlpUu6r8OK46uloIQlaxX1HTFGthMRpYIbdb6TmfXa=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food was great and the prices were really worth it. The servers were also super friendly and engaged. I loved their Biriyani.  It had so many flavors and spices; probably the best Indian Biryani I've ever tried in Canada.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPXTGY7-2nmj9Ngp5kyTGTs1U-WVcepCC8OBSuI&fid=0x0:0x587a7dd9814b3e2e"],"When":"2024-8-7"},{"Name":"Sathiyaseelan Suhashini","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWGCDhZwAvUF3Q8iMEpEx8TQCvKbwiXzYFJN0uOrenEt7v0wxGX=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A gem found in Coquitlam Centre, walking distance from sky train station.

Great taste and portions are reasonable for the price. They have great variety and mix of many dishes.

We tried Chicken Samosa, Lamp Tikka Masala, Garlic Naan, Onion Kulcha and Paratha.

They take a while to bring food, but I found it fresh and good in taste that is worth the time.

Customer service is attentive and good.

It would be around $20 without desserts and appetizers.

I found their dessert portion to be extremely unreasonable as it is way too small for $6.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNogZYG0qiPCt0JxZqa14zAKS2qGw2MpO4HCwZ3&fid=0x0:0x587a7dd9814b3e2e"],"When":"2024-8-8"},{"Name":"Nicky Choi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWdbrHfH4GFsTTqgK1b8FKEyHjbYNyqA15i6JBcGlTzjesmGsA3=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I must admit this place is pretty darn good! I haven’t had much Indian food in a restaurant t but this butter chicken curry was bang on! I got mine a little spicier and I loved it! The Samosa on the other hand was a little too salty for my liking, but it might differ for other people. Next time I’m wanting to try the vegetarian Samosa, hoping it has a lot of potatoes in it to even out the saltiness. 😅 all in all the server was really really polite and helpful and they came around several times asking if the food was good.They were trying to help us all the time and I appreciate it the quick response to all our requests. It got pretty busy during the evening but it’s definitely a place you should come on by if you’re in town.

Price: average - $16.99 for butter chicken curry doesn’t include naan or rice. Naan on the side is $2.99 + get  each person would be about $25 at least for dinner to be safe’","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNdI80T2Z7E1UZFnnPyr_bKYqpKzm18Ain0HVgU&fid=0x0:0x587a7dd9814b3e2e"],"When":"2024-1-29"},{"Name":"Jimmy Marse","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ6EabICLG0QSjGi0nBueVj96UcPn2rgpvZ0QCseNTv0rxJuA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was taken here the first time by my East Indian coworker and I started falling in love with this restaurant.  Then I brought my wife a week after, then my daughter 2 weeks after that.  The food was very delicious.  The service was so decent and comfortable that made me feel like eating at home.  Shout out to Simmer who has provided us the top notch service and we will definitely visit again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOTJAeyDX4zO9K5P9JaHHOWVKyTDUt-u18m0pl4&fid=0x0:0x587a7dd9814b3e2e"],"When":"2023-11-2"},{"Name":"marrina e","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXnp2QqU2IP2AgIC84yOheubXxBGmiXzONKBJBU40ZTC7pN3Qme=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great food, great prices!  Gagan was an amazing server. Ordered more but forgot to take photos","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNYVskaQhrORYoMOQzdd5lkIZ1JKICT5jxJ6Vx2&fid=0x0:0x587a7dd9814b3e2e"],"When":"2024-10-19"},{"Name":"Hashan Peiris","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXQS5tXYmTSP8F6gc8CzViRW9uUkD3rHwc2GCIQJ7tX0r6Ne1oo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I went there with my friends. The time taken to serve food was good as every one ordered different dishes. Their food was worth to share with someone. Specially the grill platter was delicious and the portion was large. Their naan and roti were fresh. The chai was refreshing. The staff was friendly and tried to make us comfort during the stay.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM3zu_pVMlPLhWlG7SWdPP3anp_GM5bae5_YduH&fid=0x0:0x587a7dd9814b3e2e"],"When":"2023-12-25"},{"Name":"Attila Szamoskozi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW2AAt3w8V6vnjRCqXfUE0xqvAqQuLl4Zs8C3rG6vUvIyME7FzU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had the lunch special curry chicken.  Very well executed.  The sauce on the chicken was very flavorful and spicy.  I ordered it hot, and it was definitely hot!  Chickpeas were great also.  Slightly different sauce on the chickpeas.  I felt like the rice could have used a bit more seasoning on it's own but paired with the curry sauce it was great.  Very friendly service.  Would definitely return!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN9-I7nRRrsiNtkPhy1aYk9MoeUxt1aEZXSE8kA&fid=0x0:0x587a7dd9814b3e2e"],"When":"2023-8-11"},{"Name":"Jade Fahimi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVwyVH8wWI2OG1btBbQUf9ggv7bcm5UFVEByiz_fVyLXbp1xFVr=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We ordered from Lazzez last weekend, and I was pleasantly surprised by the quality and portion sizes of the food. The sauce was thick, flavorful, and absolutely delicious. The portions were much larger compared to other restaurants, with so many pieces of chicken and paneer in the sauce—it really exceeded my expectations.

Overall, it was a fantastic experience, and we’ll definitely be regulars at this restaurant. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Monica Nguyen Ho","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUZBeMwSkt7l1K2HVfyeAFOoXFwnBn78IKEly42V3HGsujhC8gu=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time coming to this location but not my first time coming to Chicko Chicken 🙈.

I got half buldak and half snow chicken with shake shake fries. Buldak is definitely spicy and very yummy. I forgot the pickled radish this time but they are always good. Great combo with the chicken!

I ordered in person so I had to wait 30min for my order not bad since it was made fresh and there was only 3 workers (1 was even taking calls and packing orders for pickup and delivery). It was worth the wait though the food was amazingggg 🤤

I was also craving it for over a week too, pretty satisfied. If you do want to order, just make sure to order for pickup/delivery to skip the wait. I will definitely order for pickup next time 🤣","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipObb3li8YJmp4jeRZ5J8ZjVfUmsfrT_A0LuGQaC&fid=0x0:0x464057daf042c093"],"When":"2024-10-7"},{"Name":"Chris Wolfe","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWu8fbcvAdoID9Egy1yMAxykKuWztsrQaE5XfcgR9nw0KWwqKaZ1g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’m giving this restaurant 5 Stars because their chicken is out of this world.

Chicko’s Chicken has officially ruined all other food for me. The moment that crispy, juicy masterpiece hit my taste buds, I heard angels singing…and I don’t even go to church-es

The chicken is so good it made me reconsider every life choice that led me to NOT eat here sooner. The fries? Perfectly golden little sticks of joy. The sauces? Probably illegal in some countries because no one should be this happy.

Sure, I walked out of there with sauce on my shirt, grease on my fingers, and zero dignity left, but you know what? Worth it. Chicko’s, you’ve got me hooked harder than my uncle’s addictions.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Al","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXJke_H51lEVtqmQ6Mwhj0R5MqDW7L2xLlIdf0sg4kPFJFF0D9I=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What an excellent lunch to taste some Korean style fried chicken.
So tasty that makes you bite your finger!!!
Good pricing which half a size is enough for one person.
Tasty side pickles and drinks.
No dine in only take out. Lots of parking for free.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNDqJRewPdtulpaYON0iar_3OEapzYo0PsXRMxW&fid=0x0:0x464057daf042c093"],"When":"2021-2-23"},{"Name":"Pauline Li","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIRNG7TpX7rUc6XCTzrQAMxwHXV7kNiIeWY2TA0eCmZOWTgow=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Doesn't follow regulations and conditions of operations permit.  Doesn't allow customers to use washroom facilities which is a violation of BC Food Premises Regulation.  Received Permit to Operate from Fraser Health only for Take-Out but has obvious front of restaurant dining area for 18 diners. Makes me wonder what other short cuts they are taking in the kitchen?","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Priya Badhan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUUWrpdymoiG3drKefuP1fHuEVUxK_kqe7u0-JFka_xzidrhRw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love this place their chicken is always fresh & flavourful cooked at the perfect temperatures.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPOi0KavoK86_rgCSwcB4Znv2HSlDPQ2LXH6Jpj&fid=0x0:0x464057daf042c093"],"When":"2024-9-14"},{"Name":"Arjun Tyagi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWopm7CB27Brsn2nZf_ZcGMYA1rC2xZn0gFS2Ev_B4zUk8mX8MoIQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love this place, the chicken is always fresh and tasty. The app for ordering is precise, fast and easy to use. No complaints from any of the flavours and or dishes I’ve tried. My go to delight! My favourites would be the Yangyeom and Buldak ones, The recent addition of Haek is also nice.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMlsAYVBIwCMqkmQuWxhDb1nEo9wughmhSw-dyB&fid=0x0:0x464057daf042c093"],"When":"2021-1-21"},{"Name":"Ellen Sea","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUgyvw39gUnCgl6xsGC3h38EgAvDpICnxUdU619L8I4-wyV0VMy=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"**PLEASE DISREGARD THE DUMPLINGS, NOT PART OF THE ORDER**
I ordered the soy garlic bone-in chicken and it was very delicious. I didn't eat it right away because I wanted to get home first and watch a movie with my meal but even after the 45 minute transit, the chicken was still crispy. Of course the bottom was a bit soggy but that's not for them to blame. Knowing that my chicken was still relatively crispy after nearly an hour, I imagine it would've tasted spectacular straight out of the fryer. I made dumplings alongside (should've taken a photo before putting the dumplings in, but oh well!). The chicken came with a small side order of pickled radish. I personally LOVE pickled radish so next time I will order a bigger side pickled radish. All in all, definitely some of the best korean fried chicken I've had in Vancouver- highly recommend. Even the boneless chicken tastes amazing!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipONCk_af9v-W-pPAZRamFWWFPIvbpz4lV3BeWwM&fid=0x0:0x464057daf042c093"],"When":"2021-8-12"},{"Name":"Nathan Ozee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX082A1x_wj7AxxsD2GKy5bR5t4BkjbO2P7RKrD-PyQx-wdvkD1=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Radish and drink no longer complimentary with an insane price for half order….
Every Korean place had complimentary dishes but greed took over these guys.

It was previously a complete package.
no longer complete. Next non greedy place.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Lenny Pottier","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUxzZl5gT-cauJ3WfvWzNtU6dLIejZJz4545gK9rOohGI8c0kc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Bbq is my go too fro kfc, i love their cheeseling fries... i usually order from the port moody location and never been disapointed. Today i order from this location and received weird shaped fries mushy and barely edible. Yes it was free with my purchase but for the quality i will have prefer paid and get rhe real deal.... (see picture attached). Chicken was good but not as crispy as usually get in port moody. Will probably not order from this location again even though it is closer .","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOwJ1OtTgs7S3n5mfI5LJ9h1H_DuFFGlqgoLD9G&fid=0x0:0x616e899f573a2426"],"When":"2024-10-20"},{"Name":"Jennelle Stam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIWYGUfyG2dESbyA1fBLy08rntV4nEfvkAAwXniWbZmYxCYIw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Finally got the chance to dine here, after months of my friend recommending it (and sending lots of bragging pics). It did NOT DISSAPOINT. Not only am I planning on coming back here to make my way through the menu, I'll join my friend in singing it's praises. Food was awesome, and service was wholesome.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOK1D7wMftVr2zQ-SnWrQzZ8xwrydvMFLAIxHYB&fid=0x0:0x616e899f573a2426"],"When":"2024-8-29"},{"Name":"Blampin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUe_Zl-7bsR_k4aPN0CDrFm3JxQQaY2wgkXgNPVdZQs9NDoFTA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This spot was kind of easy to miss entering the plaza where H mart and Pomme are. The KFC Korean Fried 🍗 Chicken was absolutely amazing! Tou have no idea so many flavors ever Gangnam Style !!
Rhw server was super nice even though the kids were making a rawkus!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMljFLHZqn4SXfgxAlv9n7VzRvIazMUCtesYhyP&fid=0x0:0x616e899f573a2426"],"When":"2024-7-20"},{"Name":"Ellen Sea","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUgyvw39gUnCgl6xsGC3h38EgAvDpICnxUdU619L8I4-wyV0VMy=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Ordered the galbi q chicken and the assorted cheese balls with a pitcher.
The chicken was actually quite good and moist but it wasn't crispy at all, so I can imagine that the takeout orders wouldn't be crispy either. The assorted cheese balls were also really good but just know that they're filled with cream cheese and not the stretchy mozzarella!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMVhOBmL1dXlMrjKdvXJeEweA36IPC25MDmn-qE&fid=0x0:0x616e899f573a2426"],"When":"2024-7-2"},{"Name":"May Zhagro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU9KviWdU_UGm6yjKPv-6aFaljm1EC_ecrxYhnt_LO3duiyBNho=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delicious hot chicken straight from the deep fryer. Fast service and it only took less than 10 minutes from ordering to when we got our first dish. Lots of fried chicken options to choose from but we chose the golden fried which is this place’s signature dish. It was so flavourful despite looking very normal. The restaurant also has $5 happy hour 3-5 pm and 9-close every day. Lots of parking at the plaza.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOdBNPkj9lUhkiYlFXOCn5CmJyKztu4wSvXxjsz&fid=0x0:0x616e899f573a2426"],"When":"2023-4-15"},{"Name":"Lindsey Williamson Christy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUm0fBNIzlRgvO6bgjVqXgXmvR5p2HzkxHc09XqHLqCh77AS_a1fA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Awesome little Mom & Pop Korean Chicken place. We tried a few things and everything was great. It’s good little spot for a quick tasty meal","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOVDSwHj5NdWzjBydxx3Bp83sC3EjikOB47Bkxh&fid=0x0:0x616e899f573a2426"],"When":"2024-6-30"},{"Name":"P H (p p)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXJKZy9bt4M6XUHig_6VLAGdw5hO6Ek6ULZkNZOMB3D3bFiKF4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Service is good cause I just picked up not for here.
The secret source flavor is not good as Metrotown. I still remember that metrotown’s is more spicy and the amount of chicken is larger.

I could remember wrong for the amount but the taste must be right. Hope it will improve next time. Well I still love it anyway.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNifXAAchMK9-BVRuriRjlpbA5Rzsa8LWflCELG&fid=0x0:0x616e899f573a2426"],"When":"2024-4-21"},{"Name":"Fremy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWqXXZ5rKarOZyZdNvNUw-YcnDQL3N2JVFQewPrpwmHEPRYalMs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The honey garlic chicken was really succulent and crispy. The flavour of the garlic and honey harmonizes really well and its flavour was bursting the moment you take a bite into it. On the other hand, the mala hot chicken tasted more peppery rather than the signature flavour profile of mala. It has a really strong kick for people who are not accustomed to hot spices, such as myself. Overall, for less than $20/pax, their portion is just right.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPiPdaZa_WzdSiRuZctc9_11e4iWL0ills8MITc&fid=0x0:0x616e899f573a2426"],"When":"2023-2-12"}]

[{"Name":"Michael L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU7qHQHktTRAhS7s-EU8pajW0_P0nE3GRmSWs728jQssSrUsYyo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of the best pho places in Coquitlam, offering great portions of food at a good price. It's also one of the earliest to open and the latest to close in the area.
I came in very hungry just before closing one time, and the owner was very friendly and kind, insisted me to take the time to eat without rushing.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPsf7vlSSlvwWXCmfpKfWdt6fJ3FBqbJ8j3G00q&fid=0x0:0x2b766e3b9b7bf89b"],"When":"2024-9-12"},{"Name":"Naomi Pausche","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUUxTfwxXrEFiAyDLq3sgPk2P11B_V02GFw7mHgLpsAEcYYYPPVVQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Seat gripping experience, left me sweating and in a state of pure bliss. Please do yourself a favor and dine at this fine establishment. Music 10/10 Staff 10/10 Aura 10/10","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPqih8ntCzOw4GaC_cyBVOQaiVzFjljVUEv2AdO&fid=0x0:0x2b766e3b9b7bf89b"],"When":"2024-12-15"},{"Name":"Henry Thomas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWjbZBN0zYrViJlyvp7r8eiOhoIkkz4O-fiN3sJhBSqzvVWZweA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"My family (4) and I decided to have lunch here as it was early in the day and close by.
No sooner had we received our meals and began to eat they presented us with the check. We continued dining and within 5 minutes 3 employees approached us giving us the impression they wanted us to hurry so they could reuse the table.
We left feeling that they were more interested in taking our money than providing a welcoming atmosphere.
First and last time here.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amir Beheshtian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUJ6C_Bum8v5F39RUuKIpjJ_TP5q278YpYCRflkkdsQCBi_EyZ9=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It was soooo delicious one of the best noodle places I have ever experienced, highly recommended","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOQJeR7Nx9Ku2O1_5IaWYLDRXhNyfjDz9ppaDw8&fid=0x0:0x2b766e3b9b7bf89b"],"When":"2024-11-17"},{"Name":"Derek Hansen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXaBRm-VY_m99UwZ6UwdvGjzB7nw1EejvhcMIUbGB5N2HHxrZpHjw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Have been in a couple times before not bad but there are better options around for Vietnamese food. Definitely not my goto but if your in the area and wanting some quick pho will cover the basics.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPVlbYNd45_x00535rT3lHXj5UgexGHaStnVd0M&fid=0x0:0x2b766e3b9b7bf89b"],"When":"2024-6-18"},{"Name":"Roni Kury","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW8hnpD5szDElfgLyoB9jO1waARL7PsGNhrZuGm_O0A_sCj4FW7=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Outstanding benefits "stew" (really, egg noodle soup)!  Generous portions, plenty of meat & veggies in the broth (very flavourful);  usual Pho condiments offered.  Very reasonable prices for the portion size (huge) and quality.

I will definitely be a repeat customer, though I also want to try the other location of Schoolhouse, as it is closer to home.

My only complaint is that the menu, and the servers, are not descriptive enough.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"A.J. Canadian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU0mITu_1OR_MuXzhVIkPjHjZnimy2Y-mI64r72OA1Zbucah6-N=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hands down my favorite Pho restaurant over all these years. Friendly staff, clean facilities, always get great tasting food. Plenty of free parking and always child friendly. My recommendation if your in the area.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNdgfLic23fu56mA8Nhhq4yzgShN2paR-TS8rlK&fid=0x0:0x2b766e3b9b7bf89b"],"When":"2024-8-11"},{"Name":"Mahdad Nour","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLq5GqpFajc0Znw8mo90PS6wome53kTdEKYoi-WehAkn2r7VA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of the best pho’s . Large portions and friendly atmosphere. Quality of meals are really high! Like there so much 👌🏽","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMwZy1hg5k7jTq5bzZTLgFrgDshnA6t1ESbZB69&fid=0x0:0x2b766e3b9b7bf89b"],"When":"2024-5-12"}]
