user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Regie Sacdalan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLVDuCV38ynK6mxDdP-HlWdoPODHVpBYeLjIOghxaV1fgHRoA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It's no wonder why this place has such a high Google review rating! One of the best Peking Duck and Lettuce Wraps in Metro Vancouver and at a reasonable price.  The duck was plump and juicy. The lettuce wrap course had a perfect meat ratio. The best Deep Fried Squid I've had -- light, airy with just a hint of spice so my kids were able to enjoy it too. The squid at other places is often tough and this was not the case here. Everything tasted great and was high quality. Food was served hot. The servers were very attentive and kind. We will definitely be back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP45SWEE9L8SmkSTJFyrr_zJmSoMsRDskWEqo_J&fid=0x0:0x8b30f4df92938c89"],"When":"2024-8-13"},{"Name":"Joshua (ThickBurger_Bites)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUbIhhMlbxk7OIMpcaP-aSx2m75kt8-mqmXoXAJQ5K99gnxiff1zg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Newly opened Hong Kong style restaurant. We went there for lunch and were pretty happy with the quality and flavour of the food.

The portion sizes are quite big so I’d highly suggest getting a dish or two less as we were a group of 8 people and 6 dishes were too much for us.

Service however, could be improved as the kitchen forgot to bring out two of our dishes until we reminded them about 30 to 40 minutes after we were done with the others.

Price isn’t that bad. About CAD20 per person.

I’d recommend making a reservation in advance as the place does tend to get pretty busy and parking can be a pain to find.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMptKLVmoMm8826G-woKe7UTtGCTE6Z_UlJ5MMX&fid=0x0:0x8b30f4df92938c89"],"When":"2024-7-10"},{"Name":"Bob","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVkEC75mT1rTSBiWusD60B4Ypx_mMWrgo5mEAuPBQ7mgpfmDaoe4Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"When I went it was still considered a soft opening for the restaurant. The dim sum menu items were all very good. The seasoning was well balanced and not overwhelming. They were understaffed today and the customers were getting impatient, but there isn't much you could do. Come on guys. It's hard to hire people and they just opened.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP-M6i5DzCOlWPhn8UH4RjKHzD8CMfstAiJ0E6n&fid=0x0:0x8b30f4df92938c89"],"When":"2024-8-25"},{"Name":"Munchica","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbQ6ACs51IPQJlRLrmnunOErED8bimOf5-y1uov4EWpuZvjQQjrA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A wholesome Chinese restaurant good for family dinners with good portion sizes given for the dishes. The honey garlic spareribs and deep fried squid were well fried being crispy on the outside and moist on the inside. The Peking duck was standard. The complimentary choice of mango pudding or dessert soup at the end was nice. Solid place for standard Chinese food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPM7O1IwhE73us5iOTaBQDUKFzzcfIrATj9lDfY&fid=0x0:0x8b30f4df92938c89"],"When":"2024-8-5"},{"Name":"Tmo Jra","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKu-bLJQalUBeL5kjDEs0RopDiDGGJMUE6USX1nrCypwPJTfQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Newly opened dimsum restaurant that we decided to try on a whim. Very glad we did! The decor was nice, food was delicious, and the people there were quite friendly.
Also, the portions were huge! Got used to the small but pricey portions in most Vancouver restaurants, so was very pleasantly surprised with the size of the orders here. Our family of 3 ate till we were stuffed but only got through a 3rd of each order (we normally don't have enough left to take home).
Definitely get the bang for your buck here!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPtiSgEaA709o9eEKbxoIbV5FcseRz7ewMOhaXf&fid=0x0:0x8b30f4df92938c89"],"When":"2024-7-27"},{"Name":"Geraldine Sangalang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUcAsqfNVs6uRfmsJ5FtsU66GdsPGBE4zo_tn8DnG79e7VADqel9Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best dimsum in the area! Formerly known as Rainbow Butterfly, Yan's House is the updated version of a neighbourhood favourite.

Dimsum is fresh, hot and served quickly. Main dish portions are massive. We ordered fried rice and we're surprised at the size. One portion will serve 4-6 people.

The Deep Fried Squid is wonderful. Crispy, light batter. The squid is tender and cooked beautifully. We crave this dish.

Spicy String Beans with Minced Pork is so satisfying to eat. Savoury on its own or delicious with rice. It's a family favourite.

Dimsum is served all day. It's quite busy in the morning but the restaurant is quite large. Make sure to put your name on the list and you'll be seated asap.

Great space for a group, or small parties. Once seated, you're provided a carafe of hot tea. There's free wifi available.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPW9KvDGBCNNyd-yCe-Pda8deL6vOs2zEpruOf_&fid=0x0:0x8b30f4df92938c89"],"When":"2024-10-22"},{"Name":"Eveline Yu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKZ_kiKNY5YBfaLOhaLW3SLnIfYj072uzzapXDuzRiVxziOnO0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"First visit! Tried to come in the morning for dim sum but it was so busy, we decided to come for dinner instead. :)
Love the atmosphere - staff are friendly and helpful.
We had the 2 dish combo + a side of bbq pork.
Combo comes with soup, rice, and dessert. Such a great deal.

My kids liked the chicken cream corn soup.
Dessert was mango pudding.

We ordered the stir fried green beans & beef… pretty tasty… and big portions.
Broccoli, egg tofu, mushrooms was also yummy.

Overall, decent meal. Reasonably priced. Had leftovers to pack home. Will come again :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNeNsl4u7Ms7hOZM-A7umSD_YQU9soxfp434hDm&fid=0x0:0x8b30f4df92938c89"],"When":"2024-6-10"},{"Name":"Snoopy Kitchen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU3h-I-trbYva-Tzrs-UNhkQe4Nn1jgsblAcoQ0hPrnUWvugM3Y=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"It’s a good Chinese restaurant for stir fry instead of dim sum.

Black bean chicken chow mein and congee are very good.  Shrimp dumplings skin was broken when it got picked up.  Siu mai has corn inside which is a bit weird.  Chicken mushroom e fu noodles in cream sauce is like pasta but exceptionally good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM3_qnMWQVAsdNzG-__Hqhg8x2przBhr0AmAq0j&fid=0x0:0x8b30f4df92938c89"],"When":"2024-8-26"}]

user_reviews: [{"Name":"W P","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocILxAIkDJOMkU9eiOhUr1vp_EVknYE6-JpPp2DlzYH5UXNOLQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food at JFY is absolutely amazing! Every dish was full of flavor and beautifully presented. Highly recommend if you're looking for a great meal.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNX6Vqs_OyudkThAmeHarsQ8Us00FjV57PICm5g\u0026fid=0x0:0x741d98414591f8a2"],"When":"2024-8-22"},{"Name":"Cher Lin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKuJb4AXSXpx8-KCPDQBZHJ2K3rRI-J71p19_u0fIii9KOuBhQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I LOVE the food here and I believe the service and atmosphere will improve once they have more dine in customers! I’ve been looking for authentic Chinese food restaurant like this in Coquitlam especially with spicy cuisine but also the typical noodles, dumplings, etc… I was told the chef is from more northern China and the lady helped us is from Guang Dong and they have been in the restaurant business for decades, I didn’t ask too much about their stories but all I know is this is their newest adventure! I am glad!!!! I see people order for take outs and some people even order everyday but from 7:15 to 9:30 on a Saturday, there were only 4 dine in tables including us, so they do not have extra servers, which is totally understandable… therefore if you are looking for services like cactus club, it’s not going to happen any time soon… nonetheless, I rate the service 10/10 for their friendliness and knowledge of the food, suggestions, the only reason why I give 4 star on google is because I want to stay true to what to expect for the next customers, atmosphere is 3/5 because it is a little dated but to some people this could be a 5/5.. nostalgic feeling! Overall, this is a must try and if you are a local, you might make this restaurant a regular thing… I am going back to try more dishes! Everything we ordered were amazing! Not overly salty or oily and packed with the right amount of spices without being too spicy, we did ask for mild spice. 10/10 for food! Please go!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOYRx0aAchW6Be7b-wVxwYTWSPczodN3XwfU85Q\u0026fid=0x0:0x741d98414591f8a2"],"When":"2024-3-10"},{"Name":"Pej Namshirin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXt8TlEL2i2Xn40BjhRE9J4no4CShDCK1NmCQWJYbCcLJNbs-s8rQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A little bit quiet on a Thursday night, but we came in hungry and left completely satisfied with full bellies. Excellent service: as if we were guests in their home. Everything was tasty, nice portions, good value. Get the House Special Crispy Noodles. We'll be back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOHVvR21V2RyCPQ2Kgq5IyCxs5g1UwLpS-WTUxy\u0026fid=0x0:0x741d98414591f8a2"],"When":"2023-12-15"},{"Name":"Rob S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKl1FCoFebTKBGR8qu0CXJcgOpg1C_GaPiRgmFNkViRrR_-bA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came here for dinner.  Its a small place but got seated right away. Server answered a few questions which was nice. Ordered 5 dishes but forgot to take pictures of the other 3. A lot of other customers ordered a spicy hot pot. Next time I'll have to try that.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMRkJKK6IeEaXBZ3Hd9d-c7UyLkv-kUGZORMJc6\u0026fid=0x0:0x741d98414591f8a2"],"When":"2024-5-12"},{"Name":"Co","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXG4naUf_X253ZW_x8qkz7Uig_hfCxvqNh5uL6iGAWHlnMotds=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We love spicy food, and this place did not disappoint! The stir-fried kidney, pickle finish and other spicy dishes were bursting with flavor and perfectly spiced. Every bite was a delight. The service was friendly, and the atmosphere was cozy. We’ll definitely be back for more!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPnjHsZ7S12ig4C-lxuqyJYkSOqKSDXkdu-K0N-\u0026fid=0x0:0x741d98414591f8a2"],"When":"2024-6-23"},{"Name":"Adiarto Pranoto","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWGpDhMtiMDaaGt41IC1705uh4RhlaoTss7zAyJyY1-mSYu5O1azw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Truly a hidden gem! The food at JFY is absolutely delicious and they put extra care to use only the freshest ingredients. Highly recommended.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMfk1oM0bHeKrtwI6CwmmEd-e5vttjoJ0vgrFca\u0026fid=0x0:0x741d98414591f8a2"],"When":"2024-10-4"},{"Name":"james hong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIuUy2OG4Bplbxj_Ym7mbYDtZs9FWrEHXAQ_lSJQm4W1YCgQg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"the chef here is a master when I saw him. The fried rice noodle dish I had today was just like the best one you can have at Kirin or other good high quality places. This Chow-fun dish is simple, but very delicate to cook. Here, not oily, not salty, not mushy, noddle fried perfectly with all the ingredients, It's been a while to have a good take out Chinese dish. The Portions is just good for me. Prices are good on the menu and the place feels homey with warm greetings. I figured out why this chef has decades of cooking experience. Finally, good Chinese foods in the area. See you soon!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Soupie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIPo3MiiUq9w5p_rhCAyIVjl8rNLcE_4pEVJ-lVg7n0s8Q18A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time coming here and would definitely come again! Enjoyed the spices a lot, it really hit the spot. Awesome service as well, they explained the menu and gave us some great recommendations. Highly recommend this place, good for families and friends!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMAwIGQGSCoEb0keyUr5P0DQ-aWAhr13Hb5txwr\u0026fid=0x0:0x741d98414591f8a2"],"When":"2024-6-3"}]

We got: Unagi, Chopped Scallop and Dynamite Roll; And takoyaki and appetizer tempura. Was really delicious and well worth the price. The eel had no fishy taste at all and the scallops had a perfect amount every bite. Split between 2 people was just a little over 20$ each before tip. Will definitely be coming back here again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPccuqsq-BFQdSEQm6SGKnZrrv8IaPOrCjcv8JZ&fid=0x0:0x3171bd894a933bac"],"When":"2024-11-12"},{"Name":"Carmen Stewart","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVFXe4EoZzAOkubIcHiJU27Iuag1as2s1tPKSWcxV1AyervXGfM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"1st time customer, not the last. It’s by 7/11

Oh this place also has omakase!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMUwQSxkMWd60Ebckitd1pwxWKzwkrR42JZmIUR&fid=0x0:0x3171bd894a933bac"],"When":"2024-4-9"},{"Name":"Rajan Brar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVIjHk0yDRdF8YJTKikQj4pF49eAxqpVm-eZLrh6pOEhzJnkwZrsw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The service was excellent, and the food was outstanding. user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Nicky Choi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWdbrHfH4GFsTTqgK1b8FKEyHjbYNyqA15i6JBcGlTzjesmGsA3=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"! This cozy spot has been around forever, quietly serving up some of the most delicious homemade soups and sandwiches you’ll find anywhere. The owners, an older couple with a genuine love for food and people, bring such a warm, personal touch to every visit—it feels like stepping into a friend’s kitchen.

Their menu is simple but so satisfying, with fresh ingredients and flavors that taste like home. Whether you’re craving a hearty soup on a cold day or a made-to-order sandwich packed with goodness, this place never disappoints. Just a heads-up—they only accept cash and debit, but trust me, it’s well worth it. Also parking is a downer… might need to park elsewhere and walk ✌️

If you’re in the area and haven’t discovered Soup Plus yet, do yourself a favor and stop by. It’s a neighborhood treasure that we’re lucky to have!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOG0k3E34RIXaeskX_JjwDum-MPWj2SDjFjo9Kq&fid=0x0:0xc33a17c296eedd9"],"When":"2024-11-30"},{"Name":"Brittany","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUaTw3mnOK8l8haAjS6bfO1ye0bRyF4XKnDg89neYDPBoOw4QlgPQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delicious homemade soup and fresh sandwiches and fresh bread. Mushroom soup and veggies soup are remarkable - best I've ever had. My nieces were raving about it and it lived up to all the hype.

Mom and pop shop, owner operated. Come support and try this amazing little gem","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOyA7Of-qJDb7v2BeVFv7LxNV0rlGWx_iAgVMrp&fid=0x0:0xc33a17c296eedd9"],"When":"2024-12-21"},{"Name":"Kaveetha Ranasinghe","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU1NmpEWHhyELkiusQQfGjHBZJjt65z-zUPvX9oai9lHWo0qwbC=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I used to love the poor boy from this place conveniently located. However my last experience left my baffled and disgusted when I ordered a foot long to take home and found a hair embedded in the bread. Sick to my stomach I went the following day to tell the owner, I was trying to be respectful and didn’t want to cause a scene so I waited patiently till he served his hungry customers and then when I tried to explain the incident all he did was point to his head which was almost bald and then say ‘what to you want me to say’.. never will I recommend this place to anyone as the customer service is definitely a hit or miss and the owner did not handle the situation appropriately. He also over charges than that actual price listed and I never said anything cause I felt sorry for him.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPvHB2P1xYqXsjh2N92-0HfRv24v8miGTrm6TdK&fid=0x0:0xc33a17c296eedd9"],"When":"2024-12-6"},{"Name":"Jennifer Bee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFO0fgPBTIA1yxL3IXSghRJ6EmshLC1YB1a72b-xeg3kpjHx0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"First and last visit. Egg bagel tasted good, but this place is filthy. There are cobwebs on the walls, the light switch by the door was black with dirt, my bagel was cut with a dirty knife and his bare hands. I don’t know why I stayed and ate here but I was starving and had already ordered before I saw how dirty it is.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNpfgXFlbfEIiFxh9IHVVetYwqe_waR4Kqv_kga&fid=0x0:0xc33a17c296eedd9"],"When":"2024-11-23"},{"Name":"Sofia Kingsley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVscMfV773tiAinmQb8EmCQe8fupb_zckAC6DxPMjzxzAvwQEER=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"incredible hidden gem! my first time visiting a soup shop. owner is so friendly and has a great personality. sandwiches are super fresh and you can taste the effort and love that is put into them. real star was the mushroom soup. we also got teriyaki chicken and louisiana poor boy. i am looking forward to coming back and trying other menu items when i’m in the area. new fave spot!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP4m2xUjds5eAy9wxxFKeMhaxJoF0Xlo72YKm4l&fid=0x0:0xc33a17c296eedd9"],"When":"2024-7-10"},{"Name":"Kamil Chocimski","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJiqh1VSZRODqN-Djl6vCyrZVFOC1F520DSa-G8lhjPI6NkKSg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What a treat. Old fashion Bistro, incredible bread the owner makes. He is delightful.
We chatted for over an hour.
His small sized soup is like a large. Incredible price and oh so delicious.
A must stop. This will be my daily lunch place. Just tremendous. You must visit here. You won't be disappointed.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNl_II1ckLjKtwydAPYkYlggjLRXS30XurahsSm&fid=0x0:0xc33a17c296eedd9"],"When":"2024-6-25"},{"Name":"Kelly Toor","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVR_-44-cn0DUitwnM7uqyuE1tMmbvmOCy68MTB929uIbFoynoi4A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went to Soup Plus for the first time today and it was delicious. The broccoli soup was probably the best I’ve ever had. Ordered the BLT which has homemade fresh bread, it was so light but still filling. The couple who owns the shop was really funny and kind, felt like we were having lunch at our Grandparents house. Will go again and would recommend.

NOTE: They only accept debit or cash.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOBLdsXUGvjH0zj4Hhuk8lUjx9d-BTATKVb6-yW&fid=0x0:0xc33a17c296eedd9"],"When":"2024-5-29"},{"Name":"Ton V","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWb4h6oZDMjakZ7o0kpJmjp_i41AvhfJ62KCrl6wCnDvytBpv4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Pleasant surprise- place looks a bit dated and scruffy, but the soup and sandwiches are delicious.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPAQGpogWRz8rjch2psV7ofjmfVbgAraIopwfo&fid=0x0:0xc33a17c296eedd9"],"When":"2024-11-9"}]

[{"Name":"David Dizon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXPfQve4gHnIn7ck5uwi49Z0aTKTrEOrVFe67dbPCVUJQgSKH5d=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Walee Bistro is such a great find! The dry hot pot is seriously amazing—packed with flavor and such a good deal for the price. The portions are generous, and everything tastes so fresh. I loved how perfectly the spices were balanced; every bite was delicious. The staff are super friendly, and the vibe of the place is cozy and inviting. If you’re into bold flavors and want something that feels worth every penny, definitely check this place out!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPPk7X4fnY0i5pd08Hw6EYdQ0leHhleF40UKK_Y&fid=0x0:0xf589a877c69ef99"],"When":"2024-12-15"},{"Name":"Rong Zhang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUF4JvRjEmWEBaxR_Hb8Vj7FIX9fqZVly3W-J0rsoXVXL_20Io=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Here’s a polished version of your review:

We absolutely love this place! The food is incredibly delicious and perfectly suited to our taste. The restaurant is spotless, and the staff is always welcoming and friendly. The owners are very attentive and take the time to check in and ensure guests are enjoying their meals, which is such a nice touch.

We usually order takeout, but honestly, the food tastes even better when dining in. The portions are generous—we ordered one appetizer, a bowl of rice, a vegetable dish, and our favorite, Kong Pao Chicken, and still had leftovers to take home!

The only downside is that parking is limited, but luckily, it wasn’t busy today, so we didn’t have any trouble.

Overall, this is one of our favorite spots, and we’ll definitely keep coming back! Sorry about the photo, we were too hungry to take it before we started ;)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPDHbRblP2ApxddghgrMAWLGvF2iluyWVy37Oyw&fid=0x0:0xf589a877c69ef99"],"When":"2024-12-15"},{"Name":"Y. Cherski","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK-7SLlKKRW0Rqcp9wRXFlvt6gbh0rtI7PMIroLgxETtGiPwQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"This little plaza is packed with cafes, which is great for variety but can make parking a bit of a challenge. The atmosphere at this spot is super casual, with a laid-back food court vibe, and the staff are attentive. The noodle and dumpling selection is impressive, and I’m pretty sure they make everything in-house. What really stands out is their "build your own" combos with plenty of options, and at a very reasonable price. If you're a lamb fan, you'll be happy with the many choices they offer. While nothing blew my mind, it’s tasty food at a good price, definitely worth giving it a try.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPTRytCrbH3xzwd_I48O6gPYmGU_uFyl0RU4M-K&fid=0x0:0xf589a877c69ef99"],"When":"2024-10-19"},{"Name":"Julie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK6iqNbgJ99pEVigrdmqTpMQQRCYbL7zrrvCytBAxs45Tk47A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great experience, came here multiple times. Every time it’s great! cheap price! Great deal on the combo noodle! Definitely give it a try! Clean atmosphere and the beef in the noodle is super tender.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM1TrqLfp3XVdp_uk46SMCDM3LKaVB9XL1nzjGx&fid=0x0:0xf589a877c69ef99"],"When":"2024-7-25"},{"Name":"Nicole Chen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJbhYFsEt9S2xrJWKXlRYcufPKTQrboJr7AmyhIUsys_CP5DURV=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Their spicy stir-fried hot pot is highly recommended, and the other two Chinese dishes were also very authentic.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM_kY-LbGQMFWmM3sr2R0RdrXw3LxI3Cy3rp-jP&fid=0x0:0xf589a877c69ef99"],"When":"2024-12-14"},{"Name":"Chloe Wang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUypilqaCfFTLWfsuXOd4-sGcdINssz2wFi1Ho6TDg_uSXZ1Rhx=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love this place and their noodles and dumplings wontons. I followed them from Henderson mall, come here pretty much every week now. Good price and large portion, my kids love too.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNM2pOBm4KwlUiVyycF3LRpjvUmji41hm4d-wQh&fid=0x0:0xf589a877c69ef99"],"When":"2024-7-5"},{"Name":"Li-Ming Law","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVzJkCJpEps8ullfEeN8j_DCf3D7acE1BOTQh3dVoCu9_xarek4fw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had beef noodles. The soup was perfect, not too salty and had a good beef flavour. The noodles were tender yet chewy and went well with the optional side of pickled vegetables. The rice roll was also very good. New favourite spot!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOTzG9-vnSURw0Z-a3_mmUkTcPyPAyvy_9mrtzS&fid=0x0:0xf589a877c69ef99"],"When":"2024-10-21"},{"Name":"Aleah Lane","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXVVSYLY-YF1XtF1PryQwfGgBZdpKmSre2qZrhmSchFEqjpJ7g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing place. Really tasty and good prices.  I was thoroughly impressed by the Kung pan chicken rice bowl at this restaurant.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPoAYvIRIBoO9T1JFeoYoNTgXM9gL0S3MER1tfH&fid=0x0:0xf589a877c69ef99"],"When":"2024-12-24"}]

We ordered pistachio latte and pistachio cake and both of them tasted great. The cake tasted like heaven. The owners were very kind and made you feel welcomed. Our friends ordered Pennine and they were also satisfied. We had a great time here.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN36CPDmLHInapbVuZ1JRl4y8hlqdWbUU172JFp\u0026fid=0x0:0xd85181bca907f57d"],"When":"2024-12-16"},{"Name":"Juan Carlos “Juan Carlos Cornejo” Cornejo Alfaro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWK4DOcCHxY1jpQnKxnbwF-UesUsqTxeScFt7XgsrdyP9nM6xIb=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent services, atmosphere and the food is amazing! They have a variety of things, ideal to come with friends or dating! The service was as excellent as the coffee. If you are close to the mall come here and Peking near by!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMEupZ7f4TX74io9SNtcu2ynFCNExLIpYuZ-rzU\u0026fid=0x0:0xd85181bca907f57d"],"When":"2024-11-13"},{"Name":"Remmy Tisdall","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJJKl8uxtS7NXfyL9St3elxsX8KO_8NrJLtILjBfO25ruN_bXOB=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve always love going to local gems with a cozy vibe like Cafe Delitzi. I really like the atmosphere and of course with good coffee, and nice interior (cafe’s been redesigned inside) . This is a comfortable place to study or chill with friends also they have different board games and Jenga  you can use to play. Varieties of hot/cold drinks, tasty and healthy food options. If you’re up for a cafe  place that is not so intimidating to order,   with cute and home-like architecture then this is a must to visit. Plus  wheelchair and washroom (super clean)  accessible. Best perks of it you can get and earn points every time you come and you can use it to pay as a discount.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM_jm9ZgFRigYkL8Z5zXiYKWi-2SPwVM5t83IwP\u0026fid=0x0:0xd85181bca907f57d"],"When":"2024-9-13"},{"Name":"Kimiya Amini","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUwKhRqz6QFHK-mj1W1euew6tGICcNntPbUr7w4sT2byxpTiZ8T=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an amazing breakfast at Delitzi Café! The ingredients were fresh, the flavor combinations were spot-on, and the coffee was fantastic. The customer service was outstanding—everyone was so friendly. Despite being busy, the café was spotless, and I still received top-notch service. The prices are fair, and I highly recommend this spot. It’s the perfect cozy café to gather with friends or enjoy a relaxing weekend.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMENq1TarWLN32XEpb-Z-wodrHyj38dX3L5MLfU\u0026fid=0x0:0xd85181bca907f57d"],"When":"2024-10-1"},{"Name":"Paulina Pedrero Miranda","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXoiOld2vaC2Dv18bWNi8EDRiykD7MSCRsU3RK7RESh6xQghXxb=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great place to enjoy your afternoon, it has a calm atmosphere and the staff was very friendly and gentle, i ordered a london fog, my husband a smoothie and my friend another london dog, everything was really good!!, we also played UNO, they have more board games.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN2zl6T6dJEBK1ZxMu6f0UXiO557iZpIs7tXVZ2\u0026fid=0x0:0xd85181bca907f57d"],"When":"2024-12-9"},{"Name":"Liyarui Wang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU-w11e9UQ2EseIgcXos_yxM0RUQrlCG3pUCAa4UAzQGrLQylj7=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is the first time I’ve chosen to write a review about a cafe, unprompted, before even leaving - Cafe Delitzi was a beautiful, cozy surprise of a cafe to stumble upon. I was greeted by the most warm and kind staff ever, and my pistachio cream latte was phenomenal. Will be returning 1000% :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNzXrcdv9MNc_MsizFL4weDNuQs1z14R7PDLav7\u0026fid=0x0:0xd85181bca907f57d"],"When":"2024-10-13"},{"Name":"Yorka Olavarría","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ5om_Wne3RrFUbuooAfv9qqDlsqANmVgynyrj73ZuwqSNNlg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I bought 2 bags from too good to go (pic attached). The person was extremely rude and stated that \"all was fresh\" 30 minutes before closing time, so whatever you are buying tomorrow will not be \"fresh\". He mishandled two dirty ziplock bags to give me the most expensive croissants of my life.\n\nEdit: Although I appreciate this comment was not erased, I'd like to clarify that what you can see in the picture was $15. Scones were extremely stale and were not really edible, so it is technically $15 for 3 mishandled croissants. I apologize if my previous comment was not properly explained, and it is not my intention to argue.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNMCErNp6abZjbl09sKxlcOmHaNdMCPpWJgqW1v\u0026fid=0x0:0xd85181bca907f57d"],"When":"2024-8-30"},{"Name":"lida mir","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUYAkDf3J-a8GIawQEqO_y_U-GVvH2gA0zxqBN7-kFQWw1BQVE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Exactly customer service with great drinks and breakfast. Will come back again to try the other items in the menu🥰","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPhXhBgFnN7bh9tnCg-Fg_wpW3IhFjnaja6xEfq\u0026fid=0x0:0xc0a787d1e6fe6e2f"],"When":"2024-2-1"},{"Name":"Matchalun Ahn (Helena)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX2Bd8THUCtdw7ztqD6ief55FJ-ON2lSm6B1WgHBBqqrmyPPkai=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Good place. Would definitely recommend. Portion sizes are also pretty big.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOEml2YX6gPy5kKzTWBq3xG_6khb9Oldx7xG-u0\u0026fid=0x0:0xc0a787d1e6fe6e2f"],"When":"2024-1-5"},{"Name":"May Zhagro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU9KviWdU_UGm6yjKPv-6aFaljm1EC_ecrxYhnt_LO3duiyBNho=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delicious chicken cutlet with huge portions (2 large cutlets per order). Restaurant itself is not very big but has a decent number of seats. Parking on street or nearby at Coquitlam Centre parking lot.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPD8Gr4Peopux9Nf_46mpMlnLcZvvQYSB0zSg-z\u0026fid=0x0:0xc0a787d1e6fe6e2f"],"When":"2023-7-21"},{"Name":"J Cheung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWL0BZ5HaxRtwQYUfB73F38XNmwqlCBtIEfl5nLaJnfdzlxAdl2qA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very big and thick port cutlets. [{"Name":"Lauren Maxwell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWQciI-6gvWzRqJ1jOySgxy-T-F8sBeevM1LweLDQ4JgdFz334=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I absolutely love this little spot!

Quick, absolutely the best butter chicken I’ve had in a while. I got out of my way to stop in when I can.

I’ve had both dine in and delivery and the former is the best option for having it hot and fresh!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jonathan Gilder","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbNMXBfPwPeRno7mUL9WuGI3yA6G25USWWCsYOcT__JFbQC2CodQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a 12 pieces of boneless Tandoori served to us by Gagan who herself was extremely polite and courteous with a beautiful smile. The service was more than what we had expected and the food was really really good for the price. My friend and myself both liked the experience and since we always come for bowling, we are sure to visit again soon.
Thanks Gagan!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tianna Kayat","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKu300M-dBFFGl1UDt-MmHNX6KGhNJ49RRH88rnCcPu7VuE5fc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Ordered the prawn coconut curry and found a piece of glass in my food on my second bite. They tried to say it was plastic from the prawn casing, but it was a chunk of glass. I do not recommend trying this restaurant as this is not the first issue we have had with them.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPzf8GH-RFQKR8-UmYvLkok24-7YzNqkqBeXzIj&fid=0x0:0xb7c3c68028b6a96e"],"When":"2024-11-3"},{"Name":"Pia Orum","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXM-iCBZN7YEIcvwaSD6-3uiaE1AQzlwZqnEJDmyxj0VZcoYpv7=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My daughter had the Butter Chicken bowl, and I had the Samosa chaat. Both were so so good. The portion was generous. My daughter finished hers for breakfast 😂 she said that the chicken was tender and the curry was the perfect consistency not too thick not too thin. She also loved the naan.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Neal Thomas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUHCzfQtwP0oAsvL8BOjxlBVNv2nse1tmMD_wz2lBcLXAuuPsc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Tried the food for the first time. Indicated as such on my order notes. A very nice note on my order slip from the store stating 'we hope you enjoy our food' We certainly did! Chicken in both our dishes cooked superbly with outstanding mix of heat, spice and excellent flavor. We will be ordering again soon for sure. Excellent value for money. Thank you Team Tahn Door. Keep up the great work, you will go far.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNpzN1Z9yDcxxNK2hRefwhxGImv3Nl_Ggg5qQc&fid=0x0:0xb7c3c68028b6a96e"],"When":"2022-8-6"},{"Name":"Richard Chen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWL1jjCgwWcoepQ1SdSgBwCwyed0VshqfG5q14TYHxxERB25HQq=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Their tikki masala is a step above the rest, a must try. This time had the lamb vindaloo, the 17 dollar fee wasn't reflected in the portions especially concerning the potatoes, lamb was tender but I wouldn't say the sauce compliments rice.
The pakora was aromatic and a great appetizer.
Overall a sufficient place to eat","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP5j80MZmUs-etEWvNI5kVk4nGCe-QvproFj3Zh&fid=0x0:0xb7c3c68028b6a96e"],"When":"2023-7-11"},{"Name":"Kerrisan Lalande","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU0ihbN9nA61ZW_dyxjJHL9MxzBzo4te0ZqetqT_B6To93PKP46yA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Service was good, not great. My first time eating here and I would definitely come back! I ordered the dippin’ naans which were delicious. I can’t handle much spice, and I thoroughly enjoyed the butter sauce that it came with; it was flavorful and had enough spice to add depth to the taste without being unpleasant. It doesn’t come with a lot of naan bread, but I was happy to take the leftover sauce home to enjoy later.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPC6Pg7aPv9vMamAcHhXpF3HGQ7bVI9TWjoE-22&fid=0x0:0xb7c3c68028b6a96e"],"When":"2023-4-14"},{"Name":"Tracy Adina","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVO-sBtBThu_KsKgrmWEZfE_PesBHxKGxB3UqLxuw4aq9HVl_g0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Today we ordered the Tandoori Chicken + Garlic Naan. It was juicy and packed with flavour. I definitely recommend this dish.  We’ve been scoping out this spot for a little while now as we normally have to drive to Scott Road or Chilliwack for Indian food. So glad they’re finally open. I can’t wait to try their other dishes❤️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNW3cI2Sj_iWsgU3qVs_uuBu4RYtTKwrGDY022S&fid=0x0:0xb7c3c68028b6a96e"],"When":"2021-10-6"}]

There are so many items that we want to try.

We will definitely go back.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ally K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK20SxbQ29ElWudLMlWVmgifoTPMIKLn5ngtXDEReno3yju0Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Just had another amazing dinner at blue moon. We love the fish and chips. They are the best we have ever had! We also always order the butter chicken with Naan. They always make it fresh. This time we phoned in our order ahead of time and then dined in.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Navi Ahluwalia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW-COlFW-2Zh3HKusSNtOKzSbLHJPyazzE-uT_L6XZOG247BSQT=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I got blue moon to cater our company lunch and they provided excellent service and great food! Butter chicken and goat kurhi were both made perfectly with good spice, thank you guys for the service!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOhBdXdItlh2dgvj6b_MFeDR66tCVRmNpGfZyxr&fid=0x0:0x76800fbbe526d9f1"],"When":"2024-8-3"},{"Name":"wilsonjoshwilson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVPoK02al9DYZ9GLC0wDSU4FEAZAAPuuG6qlzOOh_26eyk877fT=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Tried Blue Moon a few days ago due to the rave reviews.

Personally I wouldn’t give it the five stars that others have based on my experience.

I ordered the butter chicken take-out special which came with rice, naan and salad.

Pretty good value for the price, although it wasn’t the biggest portion.

As for the food, the butter chicken sauce was creamy and had a decent flavour. The chicken in the sauce was chewy/dry and lacked any seasoning for my taste.(could have been day old chicken, potentially?) I also noticed a bit of a burnt flavour coming from either the sauce or the chicken. It was subtle, but noticeable enough to catch me off guard.

The naan wasn’t the best and the rice was standard.

To sum it up, for me personally this isn’t “five star” Indian food.Although some aspects of the meal were good, I wouldn’t say it’s more than 3 stars.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chad Wren","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKCCG_FRbbnU7tf1MYgoCRTcjvRGAFleK9J2qF5E_n0ESex6Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food here is excellent!  Our kids love the fish n chips and our daughter said it’s the best butter chicken she has ever had.  Naan bread and pakora are great too.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kimmi O'Sullivan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVLmbqspM_MvGR5i7Jp2CjOogNS5DQDy78_ehOCKq6lz-DdsxhK=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I'm not sure if all the five star reviews are just from friends/family trying to make the restaurant look good because it's new, but my experience was terrible.

I visited tonight and it was not busy at all--there were three other tables in the restaurant. One of the tables complained to the server about the food taking so long, and we ended up walking out after waiting over 45 minutes for our food. The server was not communicative and the atmosphere is non-existent.

There's so much other great Indian food within just a few blocks so unfortunately I won't be returning.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sundeep Mahil","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocImDDC_BiXlRgR1-zf1M5TJB0D081xc7eJJUI9qC9eOymte3w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food here is exceptional. We had the Chilli Chicken, Goat Curry, & Butter Chicken for dinner.

- All 3 of these dishes packed amazing flavour in each bite, I was licking my plate clean. Also had Mango Lassi which was made perfectly.

- The Service is awesome as well. We felt very welcomed the moment we stepped in.

Lots of food choices, we will definitely be coming back to try out the other dishes & drinks!","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Herman Ma","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUNkiZiWTHH4AMcQS5P0e7HeuuBX0dNeXwCFqQ9w2c9ob5i37E=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had family dinner here and I will definitely be back.  Food was very flavorful, portion sizes were good, and food came out quickly.  The servers gave food recommendations for dishes to try and the price was very fair.  I think they have dim sum during the day as well so will have to try that next time.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMonnMwhCPQ5-XwzFWgPNiomd-FGpNlwc-t7bnd&fid=0x0:0x6d2dd5cf087247d2"],"When":"2024-7-20"},{"Name":"Nathan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW6aOctokU9KmE5fwo6-6THfOky0imQyJSKP9b0jCAM3iXNSZtK=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Service has rapidly gone downhill over the years. We used to be regular customers here but found the owner becoming stingy and greedy. Gradually, prices got higher while the food portions got smaller (not enough broth in our takeout photo).

They also must have changed chefs, because the food isn’t the same. Noodles are often soggy, and the flavour is bland. I wonder if it’s because they’re trying to be cheap and not be generous with the sauce/portion in an attempt to save money.

Too bad. 1/5 stars due to bad service and low quality.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPjlS7Oxzhu2MyzUILv0QT8d_Z0I0FX_Amdwp7Z&fid=0x0:0x6d2dd5cf087247d2"],"When":"2024-10-13"},{"Name":"Ryan Gardner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocITFVXg73_7U2jrgVJP956L7ME6PdIgxrIx7_Y2WNfstwovYQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Our server Acknowledged that the chicken was raw in our "almond chicken", asked if we wanted to have it made fresh. We declined after losing our appetite eating half of it already. Charged us full price and refused to discount it or take it off the bill.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM9onc9XoaKGsH0gx-OZqBjqtK1odNMtkaRpz9B&fid=0x0:0x6d2dd5cf087247d2"],"When":"2024-7-28"},{"Name":"G W","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVG1FFo9GTnRGQNpjln74dhjBn3V4nGRQE_Yjur_OV6HYJsv04F_g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wow. Authentic Chinese cuisine. The Asian community was mostly the customers, telling me it's very good food because of the amount of customers here. The food was delicious. I am pescatarian and I ordered veg soya chow mein, garlic broccoli and  prawns and veggies. incredible flavour and portions. ordered three for two of us and took half home.
Service was right away taking care of you as you come thru the door. Greeted with a smile. Average is $20 per item but it's a fair amount served.
Simple open area with chairs and tables. Clean and Simple
Definitely recommend if your looking for a lovely Chinese dinner. They also deliver. Deliveries were flying out the door.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPUF5yRtUBjPGFCnYBY-h3xLv6R_D-g4cpbxSG5&fid=0x0:0x6d2dd5cf087247d2"],"When":"2024-5-20"},{"Name":"niya won","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKmwV9ujHyf266hG5NTci1Gc0JLSXKmgPbP7vaySC8bLv6tjA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"As a delivery driver, I often pick up orders from this restaurant. On several occasions, I needed to use the restroom during my work, but my request was denied. This not only caused inconvenience for me but could also lead to delays in delivering food to customers, as drivers are forced to find alternative facilities. I hope the restaurant can understand the challenges delivery drivers face and consider offering basic amenities. Supporting drivers in this way would benefit both the drivers and the customers who rely on timely deliveries.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Harrison Ens","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXy6nnUCtAVE291ykxHAR5AkhEKCNqUnONOVioWeL9fWaUVxpaY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Squid Congee had wonderful taste & portion size. The lady taking my money berated me for not tipping & a $1.25 card fee for under $50 purchases  is ludicrous.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOQTrkcUwPdFIpt-zTJV97ME6qSP-5z0jaCjoWK&fid=0x0:0x6d2dd5cf087247d2"],"When":"2024-8-29"},{"Name":"Chanelle D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXCEGtGi_rnAXcez2UGfi8tPvkrtnC3uoCyaDz_NpX-tJAfWp2A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This was a restaurant choice of my mom for her special day. For a new Chinese restaurant in the neighbourhood, we expected a much higher caliber of service. We were seated immediately because we made a reservation for about 10 people. We were quite disappointed by the service. We ordered several dishes to start but the dishes were served one at a time with 10 minutes in between. It was ridiculous! We ended up with one dish on the lazy susan making its rounds between 10 people for about 10 minutes before the next one was brought out.. then another dish. 10 minutes later, another dish. It was a painful and unbelievably slow service. Finally they brought out the main entrees after 45 minutes later. The restaurant was not at full capacity but we are guessing that the staff do not have a proper workflow. The dishes were OK. I would never recommend this place to anyone who wants good, reliable service.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO9nJ3DkW9F_LztkgcSm-Twy_-c2QvegygKatD9&fid=0x0:0x6d2dd5cf087247d2"],"When":"2019-5-13"},{"Name":"Henry Liu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWpG2mtSpUTo0L511zE_jfvNAiacFxGCQ9_Rt-Bqodv9L-Kg21JLA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Foods are good and delicious. Price are reasonable. Service good and courteous. The only funny point is when order food with free drinks, drinks cannot come latter.  The boss said they are too busy, if drinks come later, we have to pay extra as regular price. *This never heard or happened in any restaurants that I had visited* As a whole, the restaurant is worth to visit again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNQYbpq-CENX8zXL4Nyki8rNXq1d94Bfwg4m8iy&fid=0x0:0x6d2dd5cf087247d2"],"When":"2021-11-21"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Y S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWTmtWUtCZcs7qDdNKdjVbtcx5f5BcDfDU3YRp4zcFsXHKu1_WS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We came on a Saturday dinner around 6pm. The parking lot is very tiny and hard to find parking. There’s no other parking lot available nearby. The restaurant inside is spacious and the tables are not crowded together. The place can be noisy and I had trouble hearing what the person across from me was saying.

You order through a QR code and the food came very quickly. They have a small heat plate on the table to keep food warm.

Taste of the food was good. We liked the beef skewers. I don’t really like the tendon skewers because of the texture.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMm-pX5dlD9pMXI0FzAiGGywpJR6-RScI7s2spt&fid=0x0:0x17360df85a1e9142"],"When":"2024-10-13"},{"Name":"Mathew Wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVqr0VMvVacTdghzD4J4MfAhe6q5dMZ1b1Ki5_SYoFGvzKwiW0B=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Delicious bbq skewers (pig skin, beef roll w enoki, chicken gizzard)and cold noodle. Service was great, atmosphere was good nothing fancy, my only issue was floor was a bit slippery, perhaps mop water was greasy and needs more bleach. I would come here again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPHVW2maqSyKlLP-GolR3MZBsZ0g4sQoCvDBUw4&fid=0x0:0x17360df85a1e9142"],"When":"2024-12-20"},{"Name":"Evan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocItqym_b8p4Y-FW9783yYhbbkXgbWq5yo1i3Fyi_bB9_Q1tlIA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I wanted to eat skewers one day and uh this spot like does the job. Me and my friend ordered like a bunch of skewers and they were good but not fantastic. I really liked the BBQ pork skewers and if you gk I reccomend gettin that one it was 8/10. The lamb , beef and tripe were only like a 6/10 . I will be back for more skewers and maybe tk try the other stuff. The price is like okay it's like 2 to 2.5 for skewers and uoh order through some random website on your phone .

Ps. They give you yummy chips to eat while u wait for the food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMGfGItpaqmbsJl5twz57dC541_7HO_VMMx7f22&fid=0x0:0x17360df85a1e9142"],"When":"2024-7-30"},{"Name":"Y. Cherski","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK-7SLlKKRW0Rqcp9wRXFlvt6gbh0rtI7PMIroLgxETtGiPwQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I was intrigued by the concept of this restaurant but felt the dining experience could have benefited greatly from the guidance of someone more seasoned. Navigating the menu was a bit of a challenge, as some choices seemed less substantial, leaving us wishing we had ordered differently. The menu's focus on meats was clear, yet a greater presence of vegetables would have been welcome, as we only stumbled upon the option for a salad after noticing another table enjoying one. Another quirk was the timing of the soup service, arriving unexpectedly at the end of our meal rather than at the beginning, well after all other dishes were served. While the bill can add up quickly, familiarity with the menu could indeed turn a visit here into a more satisfying and rewarding experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNWH5sZ4xZB9c3y6UiKcGGnTPl9YW8md6Ua0hvi&fid=0x0:0x17360df85a1e9142"],"When":"2024-5-7"},{"Name":"TERRY CHENG","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUsg-oI6sco7O5Go48_oGM2GdPS9ywAc_QfXDXDKM3uhrlF3VpMxg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If all the meat on a stick BBQ restaurant this restaurant is number one. The portions are more than other restaurants for the same price. The selection is also better than other restaurants and the most important the taste is far better than other restaurants. The staff has been amazing not just on occasion but every time I have been there. The beer is also cheaper than other restaurants too. The atmosphere is perfect for what it is, a wonderful place for friends or family. My only complaint is that there is only one men's toilet and one women's toilet.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNMSgMmyQX51QvFhlzC8JdU2dNxQPcdpRQafAIY&fid=0x0:0x17360df85a1e9142"],"When":"2024-2-16"},{"Name":"Huang Recca","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIDF647f8wTC9xYKRRSNQV8CPkQJrc1Y81nFNPZerRiknh_jw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Used to be better but the standard seem to have dropped a bit. Some of the skewer arrived cold. Or overcooked. The lamb skewer used to be very good but today it seemed quite off. Portion of squid skewer shrank in size. Price can go up high if you dont watch what you are ordering.

Order via qr code using a smart phone. Some of the english menu appears to be done via online direct translation.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOm56CFLQnolpXXAW9_xZ5CDflNIGmIT_iBkCBx&fid=0x0:0x17360df85a1e9142"],"When":"2024-7-6"},{"Name":"Kevin Kurniawan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVwdtnJ5RbVf9X4FOyIvuW8Ujuf3XXqtUna-3fJWYoC7lMUEMXl=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Went here 3 times already. Food is great, service is also prompt. However with my last visit, which was yesterday, they served me one of the BBQ pork skewer which was undercooked.

I notified the staff, and what he did was just pulled away the rest of the BBQ pork skewers on our tray, heat it up again on the grill, and put it back.

Guy did not even say sorry, or take away the undercooked ones from my plate. Mistakes happen, but this is a very serious mistake. You don't want your customers to be ill after consuming your food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP-wef92gFp2yzDJr9A3iqEtZxxYvJUjdR34VWj&fid=0x0:0x17360df85a1e9142"],"When":"2024-8-19"},{"Name":"Triple Y","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWpOUu3KPS1-er6yleoWeyiUKtsRw4U7A4457Dg5vEpOaOkhJ5E=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The skewers were great, especially the lamb and beef. They were well seasoned. We also tried the cucumber salad, mung bean noodle and cold noodles. The service was the great, too! Highly recommend you to visit :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP4NpaspH8GH3T_Ikga4sqlPsl_2VGYFzUABcIn&fid=0x0:0x17360df85a1e9142"],"When":"2024-7-21"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Kristopher Susilo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJBtEhlXkRJMy2FnW55lvERwkpk2-F5eMFH_4N0FgO25PS_ew=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I can guarantee whoever gives this restaurant less than 5 stars either because they are not used to the typical “rude” but caring service by the aunties OR they just dont know what to order thats actually good.

First time here and I was impressed with the food taste. Ordered 4 item combo: shanghai style crispy chicken, fish & tofu hot/clay pot, greenbeans with beef and house special chowmein. Combo includes free rice, (lobak, carrots & beef) soup and dessert (mango pudding or red bean soup). It was too much for 4 of us and we had to pack some home.

Will definitely come back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPnhlxnsyLRRJEHh4fzVtiLgMOmMBDi22sds4lU&fid=0x0:0xd5411af39ffb3fa8"],"When":"2024-11-9"},{"Name":"Shirley Fung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXSf2s-kJuEfRzH7n0u0o-Ty-eDTJZIvAb-cR6BzmkEs9eHNYN_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"we had the 2 dishes dinner combo and it was so disappointing… the soup was the best thing about the meal. the crispy chicken was so bland. the server persuaded me to pay to upgrade the steamed fish to black cod but it was so disappointing. there’s no taste to it aside from few black beans on top. the sauce was watery and the texture of the fish was so mushy. you thought one thing you can count on for Chinese food is the saltiness of soy sauce, they didn’t even have that 🥲 the servers were generally nice but the cleanliness of one of the chefs and bathroom was bad.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO9FKinfJPsrJa8WvhmtHG9gBLSigOBIsDlKCi_&fid=0x0:0xd5411af39ffb3fa8"],"When":"2024-9-20"},{"Name":"EVAN ETHAN","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVUx4wFf5gaB1lR1A8XX5kn8xelbVXHG8-xFycDrpZ-n6j0ewpV=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"ORDERED BEEF FRIED RICE - $20 w tax - NOT WORTH IT! Better off ordering a beef dish.

Taste is OK but hardly any beef inside ( probably just 1 table spoon of TINY BITS of beef in one order).","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNypKE1WWfEfipQcw4XUmfNtSKtUTTkxRfhMFSD&fid=0x0:0xd5411af39ffb3fa8"],"When":"2024-12-5"},{"Name":"Ha Dinh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUcQG83kIM9L7VU9GS6J74J_TBMCdyvkYzp1C5XJSr_quttlO0V2A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really giving me the feeling of home-cooked meals. Tastes so similar to the food I had at home in Guangzhou. Dinner comes with soup and dessert. They keep rice warm in a small (red) bucket, really makes me reminisce the past. Portion is big, we ordered 3 dishes for 3 people, and still have enough for lunch the next day. Would totally come back 💛","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMvaLQtA4z_pvmNVnI8Kh1Z7qHpl_QKC50N4LrF&fid=0x0:0xd5411af39ffb3fa8"],"When":"2024-5-21"},{"Name":"Y. Cherski","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK-7SLlKKRW0Rqcp9wRXFlvt6gbh0rtI7PMIroLgxETtGiPwQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We ordered delivery from here before and decided to visit in person once in the area. The interior has seen its better days, so the interior vibe is drab. However, our waitress was friendly and communicative. We decided to go for a combo for two, and she recommended against one of the options we chose. I'm not sure what it was about, but our food was outstanding. I should mention that portions are huge. We got at least half of it to go. Prices are very reasonable, and there are many more options than listed in the delivery menu. If you are after nice looking interior and a cozy atmosphere, this place is not for you, but if you want yummy Chinese food for a very reasonable price, give it a chance.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP3Kz8AXC00TZcQEoR0U3SjODyiZU7llSsIe00y&fid=0x0:0xd5411af39ffb3fa8"],"When":"2022-8-9"},{"Name":"Daniel Li","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUAxFTfz_ZYgM60gsStYArKOb4YgmHuHArMEsVm-TJD2WcKuo33=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Had dinner here at Chinese New Year, service is consider good during this busy days.  The food is just average, the Deep Fried spicy squid and the deep fried lobster with spice chilli is a must try, others are mostly on average.  I would not recommend the hot and sour soup nor the
Singapore Stir-fried Noodles to anyone, their signature chicken are just fine as well.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOUZrsZslO2nY-auGLnWPWIk0Myi4-rLW0d4KVx&fid=0x0:0xd5411af39ffb3fa8"],"When":"2023-1-24"},{"Name":"Scott Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXHpW7vGME__Zs4wKjXR04Upnw88bkVVyz-H2288JsHocq9vI3r=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We had a great experience here! One of the better Chinese restaurants in the lower mainland.

I really liked their crispy squid and the sweet and sour pork. I also highly recommend their egg and shrimp! The egg was very silky and rich which perfectly complemented the shrimp. I want to try their Peking duck next time.

I recommend this place if anyone is around the area!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMJRfvhGAZpzBC7snM4pEnjwIvrGKpQzy8W21Cu&fid=0x0:0xd5411af39ffb3fa8"],"When":"2024-3-5"},{"Name":"Jaime Ricafrente","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXAJwwcGATN2RuHMthkyt1rjxVqb7NF_uxVYPAzS1OSfFJWO9Wn6g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It's my first time here.  I ordered the Crispy Chicken with Soy Sauce, Dp Fried Spicey Prawn, egg plant Clay Pot.  If you want a quick answer, EAT HERE ITS AMAZING!  Food is not salty, prawn not to coated, just AMAZING FOOD.  The Lotus soup was sooo good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP_dl1fR5wGDp97NMcI-nCS-1kz2NQOLv04voK2&fid=0x0:0xd5411af39ffb3fa8"],"When":"2023-12-18"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"DC G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKgEfP1mBKyycrif96oHS3qLSBdMNLaAdNHodByCKv_7ltcAG8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Incredible dinner with my friends! The flavors were bursting, and the presentation was top-notch. We will definitely come back again and again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMc-dp_ndyykYeZm-5FAlUAEAGob55LyQfy3vVI&fid=0x0:0x578fb8e94ebe9c76"],"When":"2024-12-22"},{"Name":"V C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLk2wwFONQqAunDwsj4VVYlkGmIB9ggQgBx879H-91jhcYS=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"There is a robot for delivering dishes which made my kids excited. Food is good. Less than $20 per person.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM-woEeQXqncYdhne092bvglRUfsgfGeIgO2f4&fid=0x0:0x578fb8e94ebe9c76"],"When":"2024-12-8"},{"Name":"kwokyin lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJDy1zFu9C8XXSdRNlEu20ovp7aSg7gDRBv_ulSBxkJzRweDw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I recently dined at a fantastic Shanghai restaurant and was thoroughly impressed. The Shanghai soup dumplings were a standout—delicate yet bursting with flavorful broth, the perfect balance of savory and satisfying. The Dan-Dan noodles were equally delicious, with a rich, spicy sauce that complemented the noodles perfectly. The dish had just the right amount of heat and depth. The service was attentive and friendly, making the experience even more enjoyable. The ambiance was cozy, adding to the overall charm of the place. It's definitely a spot I’d recommend for anyone craving authentic Shanghai cuisine.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cori Keating","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUnmeI3fd9na4O4qGDfgGzQuDnkeLouJovnhnGUIoneMCOCl_M=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Omgoodness!! Northern Dim Sum like we’ve never had before. Hearty, made in house wraps and sooo delicious, had the pork buns, hot chili wontons, soup dumplings and chive pockets! Added garlic green beans which were excellent. Generous portions, left overs were enough for dinner. Can’t wait to go back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM06S7U0dpMNukUyoeon59lCcchmsNKIyZwfnlQ&fid=0x0:0x578fb8e94ebe9c76"],"When":"2024-7-14"},{"Name":"May Zhagro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU9KviWdU_UGm6yjKPv-6aFaljm1EC_ecrxYhnt_LO3duiyBNho=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great value lunch deal with a dish, rice, and a drink for only $12.95 everyday. There are 7 dish options to choose from and their combo meals are also discounted during lunch hour too. Sometimes the food can fill you up for both lunch and dinner due to the quantity. When we went, there was only one person juggling the takeout orders, the dine in customers, and any phone calls so service may be a bit slow. Once we ordered though, the food was out within 10 minutes. Some of the dishes are spicy so make sure to note that you don’t want spice if you can’t handle it. On street parking is limited but you can park at Coquitlam Centre near the Walmart and walk over.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPg1hoqKmZT1WRdHvOjV_CFw-0A6oS0ltpj0uUW&fid=0x0:0x578fb8e94ebe9c76"],"When":"2023-4-15"},{"Name":"Eva Tong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUbdn1JwTeGwTMz4zaH_aM0s2MjqUg4f-ith9g4COdwAGXFieA4Ow=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My family came to visit, so I brought them to a Chinese restaurant. Their food is delicious and the portion is enough. My parents love the seafood and tofu soup and the fried fish fillet with sweet corn sauce. The fried fish is well fried and the corn sauce is a thick sauce instead of watery, so the sauce can stick to the fish. We have also ordered  green onion beef and sweet soy glazed spare ribs.

The only thing about the restaurant is that they don’t have round tables which my family is used to in a Chinese restaurant. As most of the seats were taken we have to sit very close to the area where they are standing all the time and tray of dirty dishes. Even though they do have something to block off the sight but it’s still very close.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM4VpNKHWo7un0-FiiC_r_FtsJtmC8ljFKvDI-7&fid=0x0:0x578fb8e94ebe9c76"],"When":"2023-4-11"},{"Name":"Regine A.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJu3rFf3mgxBA4mBu9iInDniuxdzfgKO1oQ5uTfVErzQD3BBe4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a fantastic experience at Legend House Restaurant! The Chinese dish we ordered was absolutely delicious—flavorful and perfectly cooked. Highly recommend this place, and we will definitely be coming back!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Katherine Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ_fbiyyufWMqoCFysCuKDQEuZRz-jR8Hk5G3BPhWwM2YISMQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Came for dinner on Sunday 6pm. Was seated immediately without waiting. Server did not provide printed menus but there was a sign at the table with a QR code for an online menu.

Ordered pork soup dumplings (XLB), dry fried spicy green beans, Legend fried rice, and scallion pancake beef shank roll. The XLB were exquisitely wrapped with a thin wrapper, lots of well seasoned pork filling, but only a bit of soup. Dry fried green beans were delicious but quite salty - would be good paired with white rice. Scallion pancake beef roll was crispy, flaky, flavourful, and delicious. The Legend fried rice was loaded with toppings like shrimp, Chinese sausage, corn; a bit oily (you can see it on the spoon in the pic) but very tasty. Overall, all of the food tasted good and was great value for price.

Service was amazingly fast. Bathrooms and tables were clean.

I can see this being a go-to spot for Coquitlam locals to catch a quick casual meal of Sichuan Chinese food. I'm looking forward to coming back to try their dry spicy hot pot and chili boiled fish!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNqip9WwvMx664_JHQLBQnmzF2qxDwFx6NYuSgS&fid=0x0:0x578fb8e94ebe9c76"],"When":"2023-6-12"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Melinda Ng","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUMsYIuruesNJ4fTjqy4yNevJthJq9c29QqfPxA8x09D9sg2sf9=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Really happy to see that Lucky Gate is still going strong. Have come here several times with family over the years and it’s always pretty solid every time we are back. The portions are very generous and they have pretty great pricing for what you get. I recommend the noodles as they are made fresh and although you may not get to see them working on pulling the noodles live anymore (maybe?) they still taste great!

I believe the place is still family run and the service seemed like it could be a bit shorter in staff but our food still came out pretty quickly.

Parking can be a bit tough but there’s definitely options around if you’re willing to walk a block down or from across the street.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPPnOMGANJo8pzJjrZkT8WZQR_RyL8W6C9TGCb-&fid=0x0:0xaccdb034586d1c2"],"When":"2023-6-23"},{"Name":"Gen Wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL0x4Eq9GRWvX9EA38H3GMWPqz4gj6UZw48zS61frnmQ0-oj3E=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Our first time here, nice little restaurant. We arrived just before 6pm on a Friday and there was only 1 other table besides us but was a full house by the time we left. We ordered the Dan dan noodles, Yangzhou fried rice, crispy fried egg rolls, pork & cabbage dumplings and lucky gate home-style steamed pork dumplings. We enjoyed everything except the dan dan noodles, there was no flavour just a peanut sauce. The dumplings and rice were delicious, the rice was light and not greasy at all. The egg rolls came with a plum sauce but not the typical commercial plum sauces you normally get, it seemed like a fresh plum sauce which I liked. Portions were a decent size too for all dishes we ordered.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOS27P4BQWVnSHMAnwA5wqppr5AdBBJUJsnmZTO&fid=0x0:0xaccdb034586d1c2"],"When":"2023-5-27"},{"Name":"Emmanuel Carino","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVJ9g6OsewbE5PvEJQG0W2MrejjY87xqZcS0O_-lbnLLATuQeGq=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lucky Gate Chinese Restaurant is a fantastic spot for anyone craving authentic and delicious Chinese cuisine. The menu offers a wide variety of classic dishes, from flavorful stir-fries to savory dumplings, all made with fresh ingredients and traditional recipes. The portions are generous, and each dish is packed with flavor, making it a great value for the price. The atmosphere is warm and inviting, perfect for both casual dining and special occasions. The staff is friendly and attentive, ensuring a pleasant dining experience. Whether you're dining in or ordering takeout, Lucky Gate Chinese Restaurant delivers consistently excellent food that keeps you coming back for more. Highly recommended for anyone who loves great Chinese food!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Fred Knupp","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUukGkp9y-x2yZPZA7UpSYDaw9shX_weiqhl3K6mxZFUB86kG1k9Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"First time visiting here and I must say that the portions are pretty big and filling. Came with our relatives and can say that we left with a food coma lol. Food tasted great too.  If you like spicy food, then you should definitely come here as they have a lot of really tasty spicy options.

Decor is rather dated and they could do with some updated furniture and table coverings and interior decorations, but that's about it.

Come here with an empty stomach and you'll be leaving here plump full.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO5h7HK0Jls9TeWZ_CN7AYJ14359C466YiC59-5&fid=0x0:0xaccdb034586d1c2"],"When":"2023-6-11"},{"Name":"Renee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWkzdRYtGC8A0TF24pm1Lc0U46vrj9wBR19gGcg-qACTmqRO0ZbaQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lamb. You come here and order their cumin lamb or lamb skewers. Pair it with an order of the hand rolled pancake in Shangdong style and hot and sour soup. Divine. Oh the deep fried fish is pretty good too!

If you enjoy refreshing xiao long bao, as in not heavily flavored with spices, salt and sugar, but just a light fresh soupy dumpling you dunk into black vinegar, this is the place to get it.

Very family style, all their Shangdong dishes hits home! Did I mention their cumin lamb and lamb skewers are amazing?","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM8DGOkHLaZiX5Rb_9P484kxeoFOQ4L5JCjZoGd&fid=0x0:0xaccdb034586d1c2"],"When":"2023-5-20"},{"Name":"J C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVRid-486EHf3vFFlqzxc7hc71kbL9n1FDLFiUelrs10b7uY4If=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"The adventure of finding the best hole in the wall resto continues and this unfortunately don’t measure up.  Maybe we ordered the wrong dishes but there really wasn’t any flavours outside of salt and pepper.  Don’t expect service as there usually is only one server.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPrW5KZ_mt9LNWaGpNqvIFnX_n0YZbijxm5bgpM&fid=0x0:0xaccdb034586d1c2"],"When":"2023-6-28"},{"Name":"Happy Heart","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIzxNDbSKqtfYHxkSt0sGCFHw-pDCXZ21NYpof7TRuf3xeLpw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I stumbled upon Lucky Gate Chinese restaurant in Coquitlam. Their north eastern Chinese food is very authentic and the dishes are mouth watering. This place has signature fulfilling hot pot with big pieces of meat and handmade dumplings are very delicious. I would recommend this place over and over again for a taste authentic Chinese food. Its warm welcoming environment feels like eating at home. The best Chinese food taste you can find in Coquitlam and Vancouver.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMHYmh_Cm20IKF_lrIOeXVoHZjcgZUCjC9TMKtI&fid=0x0:0xaccdb034586d1c2"],"When":"2019-11-8"},{"Name":"connie leung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWI_fB6SeIS1ikGv2RhsDMCQCtWDrdYAq-3-mCPCW07YzB6KIPIbQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The food was not bad. The skin of the siu long bao was pretty thin which was good. But the meat was on the bland side. And so was the green onion pancake, it looks perfect but they forgot to put salt or any taste in it. But the price of the dim sum is quite reasonable. The pan fried rice cake was bland too. The salty soy milk and lamb skewers was the two items that was really good and tasty. But the waitress do not speak English, but u can order by the number of the items.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPuOVzgHTJrYiKk0_2O0njg7EIEQZMrBkdq_Zks&fid=0x0:0xaccdb034586d1c2"],"When":"2021-11-28"}]
