user_reviews:
[{"Name":"leesa tran","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUWsWaHyhzcw7kKPh9V3HkvTK5TTa81TdmCDp9IylYllx4puXIy=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Ordered the lunch combo set and thought it was okay. The quality of the meat was okay and side dishes. I wasn’t a huge fan of the grill though because our meat got burnt very quickly and charcoaled. Also ordered the seafood pancake and thought it was also okay. I wasn’t a huge fan of how it fell apart really easily.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNoQI5xqma306X3Xj-tyh3h7T8B0a6EB3d-8ggy&fid=0x0:0x1091031f4479bc0b"],"When":"2024-12-16"},{"Name":"Leanna Cheung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW-SXyk3Kx1735OiIr1tgjifqKKjDGVUvlOKwRxhFYCtDjEz6O6zQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"It was good but nothing special. The premium set was tasty and enough food for 4 people. The meats were good quality and delicious. Everything was too spicy for our groups taste unfortunately and there's no option to adjust the spice level. Even the soup was spicy. Seafood pancake was very large and filling  but lacked ingredients. Marinated crab has nice flavour but was too mushy for my taste.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPajHsix8dfb9OGSgYQ-sXLBMZ5j72d8V7mWYRU&fid=0x0:0x1091031f4479bc0b"],"When":"2024-10-1"},{"Name":"Dongjun Yan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXzkf4xL8CHsYSdrMooQZRL1NM56MIZidM-scMuAvdhuaJcHD0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This barbecue restaurant is truly an exceptional dining experience! From the freshness and tenderness of the meat to the unique seasoning, everything left a deep impression on me. The meat is incredibly fresh and of top-notch quality, with every piece grilled to perfection and exuding a tempting aroma. The service is outstanding as well—attentive and thoughtful, with staff always ready to assist at just the right moment. Combined with a clean and comfortable environment, it’s the perfect place for a gathering with friends or family.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO3Lf8xMOWJg9muKBfkhJblYwGw_im1uBzkTakn&fid=0x0:0x1091031f4479bc0b"],"When":"2024-12-19"},{"Name":"R C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX0eD31csNo04JzXmFiGxOw6om-U7XoOcrwih3LN1YIW10DJFxa=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of the Best Korean BBQ Spots in the Lower Mainland!

If you’re looking for fresh, quality meats, this is the place. The beef and pork were outstanding, and we loved the clams bibimbap and corn cheese as well. The portions were generous—four of us were completely satisfied for around $60 per person, including some beers, which felt very reasonable.

A heads-up: reservations are strict! We were about 7 minutes late, and they do only allow a 5-minute grace period, so be sure to arrive on time. I’d definitely recommend booking a table 1-2 weeks in advance to be safe.

Highly recommend if you’re in the mood for authentic Korean BBQ!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN6x4IJpXMApkWRzoIXtRrpxgUvJMrp7QZKsgNi&fid=0x0:0x1091031f4479bc0b"],"When":"2024-10-26"},{"Name":"Aileen J","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIuWvzbfzO_jncgaSim3qZy7MJd3uK4aw634-6jwwEqoRXiGA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I visited 'Toedam' after for a while. We were second on the waiting list, and just as waiting the seat for the delicious juicy BBQ was starting to feel tough, we were finally seated. When I said, "I was starving...😂", the server kindly handed us a tablet and mentioned that we could order right away so our food would be ready sooner. Such amazing service—Korean BBQ Restaurant at its best! To top it off, they even gave us drinks on the house as a thank-you for waiting patiently. I was so touched! And the food? Absolutely delicious!

I WILL VISIT AGAIN THIS RESTAURANT!!!👍❤️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMewMIOzZ36BKgF3xgwFR4vyqwomB3xrtylUXCH&fid=0x0:0x1091031f4479bc0b"],"When":"2024-11-19"},{"Name":"Xiao","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIS_o-8XQcfu3J4J73uohpXess7RNYg9bt22TmDVZmInFoeZQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently dined at Toe Dam, and I must say, the experience was fantastic! The food was very good and exceeded my expectations. We ordered the combo for two, and let me tell you, it was more than enough to feed three people! For just $78, the value was outstanding.

The staff was incredibly kind and attentive, making our dining experience all the more enjoyable. If you're looking for a place with generous portions and delicious food, I highly recommend Toe Dam. I can’t wait to return and try more from their menu!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOp0sgha2dFdxnH68-Xu6_xipdi0tZkR85NbgAx&fid=0x0:0x1091031f4479bc0b"],"When":"2024-8-18"},{"Name":"Hangout CAN (出走加拿大)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXLsataZBHdbXdf5fvvtSixzA7_P_SmPgA4k4U2s2VVx5uk12E8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food is very fresh and delicious 😋
Love this BBQ restaurant!
And we tried soy sauce crab & shrimp, seafood pancake too, Surprisingly tasty! Love it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNm1gvEQamVqWFkt6AN3o_ul0E7T-sgRTJHsWXK&fid=0x0:0x1091031f4479bc0b"],"When":"2024-11-16"},{"Name":"Lucy Li","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVuwCjTEBDQem6hcfmmxSA0I0nNlJPkS88N0KyjwlMUZAjI_Jdm8w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I recently visited this restaurant with my friends, and the experience was terrible due to the poor service. I wouldn’t be fooled by the other good reviews this restaurant has. Our server was inattentive, failing to refill our water jug or check if we needed napkins. We also asked for gloves with the raw crab, but they never arrived. To top it off, at 10:20 pm, the server abruptly rushed us for the bill, even though the restaurant was supposed to close at 11:30 pm. When my friend chose not to leave a tip and selected the no-tip option on the payment machine, the server rudely informed us that tip was not included and repeatedly canceled the transaction and tried to force us to leave her a tip. As for the food, we ordered the raw crab, beef tartar bowl, bulgogi bowl, and clam bowl. The only dish worth noting was the beef tartar bowl; the rest of the items were disappointing. The raw crab lacked a strong soy sauce flavor, and the other bowls were not enjoyable. I will not be returning to this restaurant and strongly recommend looking elsewhere for a better dining experience!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNoJCNgvYB_ywjz6R0cZ75YKeGLpBPtBO3cKwnA&fid=0x0:0x1091031f4479bc0b"],"When":"2024-8-17"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Okpako Cyril","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLVaNHZta1jM7gqQ_JUpXZci94qOXc8zdUCpiRKYiqYtGgVcQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I went to Hi Five Chicken today and had a great experience. I was served by Zara, who is a trainee, and she did a fantastic job. Even though she’s still learning, she was super polite, attentive, and made sure I had everything I needed.

The food was delicious! The chicken was crispy, perfectly cooked, and really well-seasoned. The place was clean and had a nice, welcoming vibe, which made the meal even better.
Service was a little slow, but that’s totally understandable since Zara is still training. She was so friendly and handled everything really well, she gave me something to chew before my order ready so I didn’t mind waiting a bit.
Overall, I had a great time at Hi Five Chicken and would definitely recommend it. Shoutout to Zara for doing such a great job.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOK1hVhWdT4U9NXbhjOhASrX40hlNgERtIZZUQm&fid=0x0:0x224de8ba58afb063"],"When":"2024-12-4"},{"Name":"021 Rima Akter","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXpRbHZwUEZP3uYoGDv8yEC5E42IsVQEyVoc1nBO6tj0X-rKZDe=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been a regular customer here, and my experience has always been wonderful! Today, I was served by Parneet, who was incredibly sweet and generous, giving us more chicken than we ordered. Her kindness really stood out and made the visit special.

The fried chicken here is always fresh, crispy, and absolutely delicious.The staff is consistently friendly and attentive, which makes every visit enjoyable.

Highly recommend this place for amazing food and excellent customer service. Thank you, Parneet, and the entire team for your exceptional service!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNmXcP1zehh0kJrZS3pP3m1qHxrz_4bX6zgHcnG&fid=0x0:0x224de8ba58afb063"],"When":"2024-11-30"},{"Name":"Tannya Julieta Vasquez Barrientos","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUwq4ZPOvl-CKsAHqUINO4rrIpNESx_wX4Yl0iC0EmnT2wQBf4e=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food is very good, especially their sandwiches. The fried chicken combos are the best, and the extra crunchy fries are amazing. The service is truly incredible. They help you choose your menu if it’s your first time there. I would definitely go back to this place. Bonus points: you can play Street Fighter arcade!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOfsvW-wAweAy4K9lc_1hQ5IqfATtGs9Vnv6sia&fid=0x0:0x224de8ba58afb063"],"When":"2024-12-2"},{"Name":"Razaul Rezvi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKCmfltE13lupE0zk9NLPPvL2aUV0qFGroVaRQDYg3Dc4qacQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I had a terrible experience at this fried chicken place. I ordered a fried thigh, and it was hard, greasy, and smelled awful. It seemed like it was either days old or fried multiple times. The staff were unhelpful and defensive when I gave them feedback, insisting they always cook fresh food, even though I showed them the disgusting chicken.

When I asked for a replacement, the staff said it would take 30 minutes, then changed to 20 minutes, and finally said 13 minutes after checking the oven. Clearly, they don’t care about providing good customer service. They refused to give me a refund, and I had no choice but to accept two drumsticks instead of the thigh I originally ordered.

If you buy chicken from this place, be cautious. If it looks red like in the picture, do not buy it—demand a replacement. If it’s soft like the drumstick, then it’s safe to buy. This was a very bad experience, and it’s unfortunate because it’s my second time dealing with this. Last time, I arrived at the store to complain, but it was already closed. I hope they improve, but I won’t be coming back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMKtW3HEtXwcnyez8WHmOPC7sAmXcAtG0t5VzEd&fid=0x0:0x224de8ba58afb063"],"When":"2024-7-4"},{"Name":"Paul Afuto","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJVswcrHR4BuJWVdul9Az7Mss_8tRmCXwFULcVSaUvDMFvbrw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a great experience at this Hi-Five. Definitely my favourite throughout the lower mainland. Was serviced by Manpreet Kaur who went above and beyond for us. Clean and welcoming environment with games to play and all. Definitely recommend.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPbNAFaLYClsZIEiSMj-BR3xSo0NcjUycx5f6fJ&fid=0x0:0x224de8ba58afb063"],"When":"2024-12-17"},{"Name":"Bobby Bhinder","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFML71qLNE7mZP5JrN6_ihKr8qgI_idGbKQXHKs1WszTkagLhn=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Prices charged, not as advertised.  Had to point out mistakes to get corrected.

Staff is very nice but missing spoon with coleslaw so had to eat it with the lit , my makeshift spoon.

Requested the chicken meal without  drums and was told it was not possible but will see what he could do.. gave me 2 drums instead..

Chicken was greasy as expected, otherwise cooked. Added a pic of the one thigh I received of a 3 pcs meal besides the 2 drums

I received only one thin napkin, a bit pricy for what you get, a little disappointed, will not be visiting again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMtGoVb7vdMl0gdRkQeyQ-qfuOHnfN5cxeAWRgG&fid=0x0:0x224de8ba58afb063"],"When":"2024-10-3"},{"Name":"Day Seize","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK7pyDpYQ-O3mZSb0nH3LYIRDmLb6oS5KUInureHLnFD3zmYA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Staff Mohit is very friendly and has good service. I am happy about the food. Very yummy and chicken is juicy. Will come back for sure!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPm7bnSYqdX7x4VQMPZuuLH9SUiI0Y4MrkOtUeM&fid=0x0:0x224de8ba58afb063"],"When":"2024-12-9"},{"Name":"Daniel Kim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVTBPBX9lEW7yMRyvZBXFnAeGz7adZdDsqKaKZhsjiAAagemgEG=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"There is nothing better than receiving great service at a chain chicken restaurant. It was my very first time trying Hi-Five. The workers there were so friendly and nice, and the chicken was delicious. Also, try the special store-made hot sauce if you are a hot sauce fan—it’s worth trying! Honestly, most chain restaurants are similar in terms of taste; however, great service always makes a difference. If I crave Hi-Five again, this is the store I will go to. :)

P.S. Zara was really doing her best to provide exceptional customer service! Keep it up :)","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Julia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKlZQlbKxdyWxxx6y_tkUNVaZMN1w8TPA_y_sBMw9x58nJAjw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Everyting was plentiful and delicious! Especially their mala jjamppong is sooo good The smoky flavour makes it even spicier and more delicious The seafood pancake is amazing too and the prices are super reasonable compared to other Korean spots Honestly it’s the best Korean restaurant in Vancouver","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOimlhJoewRKTb_QPpVNJ2FhOJevn30QUbWiW_Q&fid=0x0:0xf6f1c00a0e0f8389"],"When":"2024-11-6"},{"Name":"Hyejin Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXxmpr7FWXMJqHRsBv5DODkOQBS3knAjvplMlXBCEswBGZElLIF=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I’ve been to BBONG three times now, and the experience has been inconsistent, to say the least. Every time I visit, the taste of the jjajangmyeon seems to change. On my most recent visit, the sauce was far too watery, which was really disappointing.

The rice was overly mushy, though I understand that might come down to personal preference, so I can overlook that.

The service, however, has been consistently poor. Whether it’s a male or female server, they are unfriendly and simply take orders and bring the food. If you need something during your meal, good luck getting their attention – I’ve had to get up and ask myself. There’s no mid-meal check-in, and you have to go to the counter to pay.

After being let down on multiple occasions, I don’t think I’ll be returning.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMTGzIaHO75rEKRmtXMVQzIjM0x7SwyIofJqR7Y&fid=0x0:0xf6f1c00a0e0f8389"],"When":"2024-10-16"},{"Name":"iPhone reviewer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVmGIoE2HgBiExZ87gC-H42hJO4cRpKNlIwK3By628OIt4LWoi2=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Consistency matters, without it there is no success! I have visited this restaurant couple of times and noticed that their customer service isn’t that great, however, the food is decent. I can clearly remember my last visit and which is the reason why I have decided to write this review. Gentlemen’s and ladies, what is the definition of tips? You leave a generous tip depending on your satisfactory towards service or quality of the food. Tips should be well given according to those manners. Expecting such a high tip for poor service should not be normalized. I am not judging, this is literal facts. Please control your emotions.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mia Duong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUPAUy0Htbh5FTHA7CrcyalmfPE1fNra4l4o1y3j6EQjpz6Sdhn=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We went for lunch and I love the prices for the lunch specials, $11.99 for jiajiang mian. They have 6 mini side dishes and that Sat’s pretty cool!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMmlw3UAa9VAmiGL8ogwg6erEy6Nyj5qZJyKkFd&fid=0x0:0xf6f1c00a0e0f8389"],"When":"2024-8-23"},{"Name":"Joce Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUGrFjNBgSTeUkB5TUuTFijs7_U6G7FKJaRg-dNPU8w7lk_6hJf=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time here! Trying to try all the restaurants in this plaza. Was craving for clams in noodle soup! Clams in noodle soup is absolutely delicious! Clean broth no sand in the clams. Ordered seafood pancake as well, crispy and loaded with seafood goodness. Tofu soup wasn't too spicy super tastey as well as the seafood and rice combo. Taste of wok flavour! Ordered enough food for 4 ppl and had to take the rest of the food home!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNBRDse9fLHIds8ny6GNaKVkkzC4jIF23cNBEeG&fid=0x0:0xf6f1c00a0e0f8389"],"When":"2024-3-25"},{"Name":"Youjeong Park","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJtzJGpSrpmPRXDdKNXTKSZoTCOByK8-BhMGahndBI58CKzRA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently had Jajangmyeon and Tangsuyuk, and it was absolutely delicious. The black bean sauce was perfectly rich and savory, coating the noodles beautifully. Every bite of the Jajangmyeon was full of flavor, with just the right balance of sweetness and saltiness. The noodles were cooked to perfection, neither too soft nor too firm, and had a wonderful texture.

As for the Tangsuyuk, it was fantastic—crispy on the outside and tender on the inside. The sweet and sour sauce had a delightful tang that complemented the fried pork so well. I loved how it wasn’t overly sweet, just the right mix to enhance the flavor of the meat.

The portions were also very generous, making it great for sharing. Both dishes brought me a lot of comfort, and I was genuinely impressed with the quality. I highly recommend this place to anyone craving some great Korean-Chinese food!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOAWWz16C1RXtxLo50X81UJOyY-1sgtf_q3NZWp&fid=0x0:0xf6f1c00a0e0f8389"],"When":"2024-10-3"},{"Name":"Michelle M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWeetN-W20mnzvtvgZG8vAeDlWwG6zd354oPCvc1I4B_3Cjy_PI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Portions are massive!! The sweet and sour pork was good, it wasn’t too sweet or sour. The spicy fried chicken was really crunchy and didn’t have much tender juicy meat in it. The black bean noodle was ok, it was flavourful but only had a few shrimps and cuttlefish in it.

It was hard to call the server because we were in one of the booths and the walls are quite high. This is a great place for value not really quality but I didn’t mind it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMgWgrtfS5bP-GGjDY9nXAwpQMzTc8ZXmnNNaSK&fid=0x0:0xf6f1c00a0e0f8389"],"When":"2022-2-13"},{"Name":"Vic Yung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJjSUFpvFSwHsCrywPzGZzN7WDhV8Ljlj3YECw07iwjqMR_leW5=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Went on a weekday evening for a group dinner. Made a reservation beforehand but the place was not busy upon arrival, so reservation may have been unnecessary. The staff gave plenty of time to look at the menu and we ordered four dishes in total to share.

The food arrived relatively quickly and they were all in large portions. It was just enough food for 8 people.

Our group was sat behind a divider, so it may have been difficult to see if we needed anything, so staff were a little less attentive than they could have been.

Overall, it was a good experience and the food, considering the price, was well worth it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOtmmhnj1Cj3EcIKjkw7daNcT10GwLPPbW-c98J&fid=0x0:0xf6f1c00a0e0f8389"],"When":"2023-7-4"}]

[{"Name":"Trina Whitsitt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXzPXgI6R8ydiXU8rLTfBo8AtaNVUjLUFgDXd1vE_leiLYPO6A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I was there on a Monday night, and it was not busy at all. The server was super nice but really slow. It took a long time to get our drinks and put a food order in. The food was okay. The chicken sandwich was over deep fried, it was a bit dry. The place itself had a cool vibe and it was playing football.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"TS OS","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIrxJ8Fjd3bGSI8mWbF186RbFWyg_DW73VTS3OIkFaxPfXFBEQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This pub is outside the residential area but is conveniently located near highway with plenty of parking spots.  Our server was very pleasant and nice.  She makes your experience better.  Food are quite alright, very reasonably priced too even to consider this inflation era.  Taco Tuesday was neat and tasty and we also tried their golden Brussels sprouts which were also pretty good.  There are many kinds of wings to choose from, and special deal on Wednesday.  This now is one of our go to pubs as children are also allowed.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN87lH3GXT1p4K4IxHWDfUQl7qY9BczmGifIZII&fid=0x0:0x463038a64e1c3b06"],"When":"2023-6-21"},{"Name":"Kelvin Chung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUK7ZMdBlhvlFPiSySdxIgCJsO71IZXbDpx391sCwTkzkHaCpIv=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"10 out of 10.  Went there without any expectation and it was better than many popular restaurants.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNf6lbWLIzN9KUR-RyKssqq9_fs3Wk7_g9MJxZK&fid=0x0:0x463038a64e1c3b06"],"When":"2024-12-3"},{"Name":"Jordan Hsieh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbyRrh7UlWzOsyT41qQtxTb1m2bLd_4-Pusobxgdazm1EeUfU04g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went to checkout Golden Parrots with a buddy during their happy hour to catch the basketball game and we had a fun time. Guinness tastes great as well as their Fat Tug IPA which didn't taste that bitter so I loved it.

We got their deep fried pickles which came with a bit of fries. They were so good so we decided to get the poutine as well.

The owners came around to check on everybody and they were super friendly. We had a chat with them and they are absolutely awesome people.

Would definitely come back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPxUYzcPv1Z4heht31dXjvvjvPPInzWeM1C03GF&fid=0x0:0x463038a64e1c3b06"],"When":"2023-5-17"},{"Name":"Sabrina Dean","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIsuNoq0NjIZsw7Q0s08xv-ogcv0ajmV0Oo0HaZ5E_raW8Y=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Been here a few times and always enjoyed the food. They allow children in the "restaurant" part of the pub, which we appreciate since we bring our 6 yr old. Tonight, we had exceptional service by Iona - friendly and fast. There was all day HH drinks (Thurs) and a $18.50 steak special that my child devoured. We also ordered the chicken pesto penne which was tasty. Only downside was the cigarette smoke that comes in, every time the doors open.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jennifer Wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJErGKqO7BCzy2XzklkyTf07vqCBU_uYCQXwxZNuIKr42BWbg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Consistent food with lots of menu items, daily food and drink specials and friendly staff. Hit and miss on timely service. Sometimes really quick and attentive and sometimes not but not really tied to business. Noticed a fair amount of take out on this weeknight dinner hour which maybe made the kitchen slow.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Fred Rivers","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWgSCi2q2xQIo8etBfYKiAM7XcBCTUa-DDDdV9iPxCRjF4O86trZA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We were greeted quickly and friendly.  Found a seat and the server had a menu for us right away. Took our drink order and was quick to return with our frosty beverages and took our food order. Chicken burger was tasty and wings were moist. Servers were all attentive and friendly.  Would highly recommend this place and will definitely be back.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Doug P","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLx6YpxAAaIZ7Cj9PSMphfRQfkkw46YLaNdEeYIQOo495lpxg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Unfortunately we must have visited on an off day. We used to come here quite regularly about 30 years ago. At that time the food was always good. This time the fries were delicious, but both our entrees were sub standard. The prime rib sandwich was bland. The meat was overcooked. The cod was soggy.
Service was fine. We were greeted immediately at the entrance. There is renovations in the dining area, but that didn't affect the pub section. Multiple TV's had a ballgame on and others had CBC French news??? Very entertaining 🙄
The prime rib sandwich order was related to their Saturday prime rib special, starting at 4pm. I was hoping to revisited soon, but that won't be happening now.
Other diners seemed to be enjoying themselves.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews: [{"Name":"Alex Borrisovski","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKscHxIUcTePI3B0hf5AcOoUDC6DPl_UJyjo0agQXSvGbdsCw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The new management have changed things. The food was great, the service was fantastic. It's too bad the hours are limited, but having come here for hockey for many years, this is the best this place has been in a long time. Worth a trip upstairs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kiara Pelletier","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVw5wFIRt-58eUJT28bMXW-_A1xWl5sIe2bSiREMFXtx_acLSIt=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This establishment has recently come under new management, and unfortunately, the change has not been a positive one. While I had no issues with the food or our server, the on-site manager, who I later learned is named Patricia, displayed a visibly hostile demeanor toward her staff. This kind of behavior not only creates an unpleasant work environment but also inevitably affects the guest experience. Once I became aware of the tension, it made the atmosphere uncomfortable. The manager appeared neither happy nor adequately trained for the role. As someone with experience in customer service, I strongly hope the management takes steps to address this issue, as such behaviour is both unprofessional and detrimental to the business.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Douglas Dykens","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXpykpVkqtjv0MqJuItxb6Lo4JCIsRiaf3W1yzgFWMMebHVJmY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is a great place to watch your Childs hockey practice or game. The staff is always extremely friendly and eager to provide good service! Wide selection of drinks and good bar food!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jackson Marsh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU3mkw9Aq2Mni14yKQWSLZoYdzU3NK2eNe4GZLZ7D_9erjD-MUg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"It took over 30 mins to get a beer at the self serve station.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Josh Shelley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ-u2KR2ltM-k7o6fpr9UQ45PGDaM7oO18o6KV1D86b1nU8Hg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Always the nicest, fastest, best service! All the staff is super friendly and my glass is always full. The food is always excellent! Come and have a drink and watch a game at a great place.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shawn Nixon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIumHKDqc_JzC62C4yB5i8Sr2Bo2is2gBUEKUkyQoFqg-7irw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Ordered food and waited and hour and a half before finding out they never put the order in. So I ordered nachos instead thinking it may be quick, the place was empty and they messed up my order and they took an hour before finally getting my nachos. They showed up cold, I’m not one to complain or write reviews but this was really bad. Definitely don’t recommend but the hockey game was good!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kelly\u0026Lana Coueslan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI_VEbyssnQ_Dp5CEkmVByMHdrZsP1DBL_DBSksKGYY1gvUHw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Being a hockey mom I get to visit most of the bars attached to rinks in the lower mainland.  Boomers by far is my favourite.  Love the varied menu, the \"Boomer\" burger being my latest favourite. More importantly, a decent wine menu for a sports bar! Staff super friendly and the manager always ready with a smile and suggestion off the menu!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kim T","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUuNnN2AN1A4S0bJdZTcCwOg5iTyoan1x5VhxaYJqSv4T5hQykItA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love Boomers. We make sure to come up here anytime our son is playing hockey here. The staff is so friendly and they make you feel welcome. The food is amazing and the drinks are even better!!! Thanks for everything!!!","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Thushan Dodanwala","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWS_aDjXUy-U3JADt5BUTq5yyJMYhOkFN2Mlsu2VrgDFcuEVsMe=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a fantastic lunch at Gordon Ramsay Burger with my wife. The food was delicious, and the service was outstanding. Our server, Kiyomi, was attentive, friendly, and made sure we had a wonderful dining experience. We ordered the Nashville burger with onion rings, Hell's Kitchen Burger, Hellfire Chicken Wings, and for drinks a Watermelon Lemonade and Mojito. For dessert, we really enjoyed the Sticky Toffee Pudding and also they accommodated my request made at Reservation to bring out an Ice Cream Sunday with a candle as it was my wife's birthday. Everything was perfect and the flavors were incredible. I highly recommend visiting this place for great food and excellent service. We'll definitely be back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMjZVjP-ljjBQc-9i8VcY2WRaDYrE6tr8bBYxYL&fid=0x0:0x949c4608707b7a90"],"When":"2024-12-21"},{"Name":"Earl Malvar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVIKiqglVXoT9nPmI192J6J7r6928JA2bFrsB4MMWVRLWvGQBQp=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Thank you very much to our dinner-date host, Mark, who was very personable and eager to assist for us to enjoy our Gordon Ramsay dining experience. All the staff members were happy to oblige and acknowledging during our dine-in and that kept the vibe fresh and cozy.

We had a 24-Hour Burger and a Hell’s Kitchen Burger. Both were distinct-tasting gourmet burgers with their merits. I must admit that I’m partial to In-N-Out burgers, but these belong to a different category of food. Gordon Ramsay’s burgers are good in their own way. The 24-Hour burger’s Bbq sauce kept this dish interesting imo, while the Hell’s Kitchen burger was not so-in-your-face, as its subtle flavors from its ingredients kept this a pleasant dish to enjoy through a chat. For our drinks, the Espresso Martini tasted like a chocolatey dessert and the Earl and the Empress was like an iced tea punch. Both were good enough drinks to pair with our burgers.

All in all, it’s at least worth a visit to try out the menu, but the price points may not be as appealing if you’re looking for heft or more generous serving sizes.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOq1McavZOXafsAfIX0lQP4i5lEYxGu3gUPU0jm&fid=0x0:0x949c4608707b7a90"],"When":"2024-12-1"},{"Name":"George Watson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWDDOfxretD35ARsdREF1AzgD2ndrlNCvaeJvYRp_CvcKbsfn0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’d come here just for the onion rings! SO good! I had the “Brunch Burger” and it was crazy good! The bacon is candied and cooked perfectly. The house side salad was a flavour explosion in my mouth with the raspberries and feta. Damn son!!! What can I say? I’m gonna come back and try every single thing on the menu!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMfj82P-z-gt5xKUZw2ZFNCZsRk3OUTHtDCOfJ3&fid=0x0:0x949c4608707b7a90"],"When":"2024-11-13"},{"Name":"Triple Y","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWpOUu3KPS1-er6yleoWeyiUKtsRw4U7A4457Dg5vEpOaOkhJ5E=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our waiter at the Gordon Ramsay restaurant, Vanessa, made our experience fantastic. She was friendly, sociable, and genuinely kind. I’ll definitely be returning—the hamburger tasted just like the one I had in Las Vegas earlier this year! They also surprised us with a complimentary birthday dessert, which was a lovely touch. The atmosphere was great, featuring many pictures of Gordon Ramsay, all in a classy yet simple setting.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMCPCiCYfHm4yURTL7vTdma4Z4y0Ou7xwa7WP2N&fid=0x0:0x949c4608707b7a90"],"When":"2024-11-2"},{"Name":"Leah-Ann Maybee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVMulsRVvripmeyJ0yWPz1sCxHKRTmTLYktUy8Q7KQNujw4624=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The host was wonderful and our server was friendly, prompt and informative! Today was a special day that my friend and I that haven’t seen each other in close to 20 years got to see each other in person. Drinks and food, including dessert were incredible. I’m happy I have leftovers. I honestly can’t say anything but good things about the visit (first ever to a Gordon Ramsay restaurant). I will definitely come back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOl_eQns2ny4lprfMujqIK5dJkVLFsHmBWXgCSW&fid=0x0:0x949c4608707b7a90"],"When":"2024-10-20"},{"Name":"Jennifer Ramirez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVAFq69iTIcaZDekD27us44d8ngDu8WdKsqDyyYnNu7GaC-OA8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"This place was alright. It’s unfortunate that the ketchup doesn’t taste good, nor the sauce that comes with the sweet potato fries. My burger was dry… the one thing I did enjoy was the truffle fries and my glass of wine. My boyfriend enjoyed his unlimited Pepsi 😅 … no Coke sadly. The waitress was super friendly tho!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNahmbfQmQ3sMJbXpf9gArja5QUgUuUbbHFXfm3&fid=0x0:0x949c4608707b7a90"],"When":"2024-10-2"},{"Name":"Geraldine Sangalang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUcAsqfNVs6uRfmsJ5FtsU66GdsPGBE4zo_tn8DnG79e7VADqel9Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a fantastic time at Gordon Ramsay Burger. The food was delicious, and the service was welcoming and prompt.

I wish we made a reservation. The restaurant was busier than expected, and I can understand why.

I'd highly recommend the Kettle Chip Nachos. The braised beef with the kettle chips are delicious.

The Blue Cheeseburger was also fantastic. So glad we didn't skip it! The Backyard Burger was also fantastic.

We also tried a Straight Up Dawg for kicks. But it was just ok.

Looking forward to our next visit!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOdaSsKuwS7YzJhGIeD9Q6x0zCdBtDdSRcDTWlj&fid=0x0:0x949c4608707b7a90"],"When":"2024-12-7"},{"Name":"Kirsten Anderson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVY2Ec4gYGj3899LMmpRLOZW0Bf3u8nXrFYPnjknNaI8LNqqssEgA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Best onion rings I've ever had!
Reason enough to go back. Our table of 7 had a wide variety of burgers and they were all delicious. Fries were just right. Wings were good too, however overpriced for the qty. Service (Michael) was 5 stars. Attentive, warm, and professional. Milkshakes were a better value than the $15 cocktails. Appreciated the birthday treat with a candle.
The waiting area between the restaurant and casino has more decor/atmosphere than the actual restaurant. I'm not sure what it needs but "something" to make it feel less "generic".
Went in with trepidation and left with expectations exceeded.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOYcLrehLGCWt3TxtSMNnZDKTyQVLR3yz8zYCcw&fid=0x0:0x949c4608707b7a90"],"When":"2024-8-20"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Sinyo ganteng","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVK6DhObLW3StVcJ_e9Ph42mdmAq5cSoW-d536hao-jSu7WAn8I=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"small cafe in the office and industrial area. try their soup, corn chowder, overly taste, too creamy. price is decent, for $5+. seems like a family owned restaurant. pretty clean, not bad for a quick lunch.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNiQo4DqXLR9V04yjZDEQzIs-Ff2PVIpJ7mvO_u&fid=0x0:0x2a2857896adc1231"],"When":"2024-12-17"},{"Name":"Patrick Wilkinson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYakHcvOGD9AcOA-_R-KQPKBzO69i7w3xLbLsb1CP3UOPDU9LogQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This cozy cafe has the best food in the whole area. At prices lower than you would expect for the quality! I absolutely love Kim’s cafe and stop in whenever I can. Sandwiches, lunch specials, burgers.. you name it. Extremely friendly staff, fast service.

Seriously this place is the definition of hidden gem. Incredible, fresh amazing food. I love it!

10/10.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP6wGK7i3z5zi2jm9yssKB-dMnQry9x8AnulkHo&fid=0x0:0x2a2857896adc1231"],"When":"2024-12-10"},{"Name":"Daehyun Kim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWIHxxz0drxXNhxABHkARE53of9eUDqUYMpgMl7k7eCkK24jniG=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We visited this restaurant 2 times in a month.
We had Hawaiian burger combo(burger, fries, coffee), bacon cheese burger, everything omelette.
Their burger bun was so perfect. It wasn't greesy, wasn't over cooked dry. And also the meat was perfectly cooked with very juicy and fresh tomato and lettuce.
The everything omelette was another perpect food. The vegetables( bell peppers) were grilled so that you can taste the fire with own flavours. The egg was perfect medium firmess. I said to my wife that the chef must have worked in a 5 star hotel before.
I will visit here soon again.
But you clean up after yourself. But also you are asked tip them. The tip is totally up to you. I was very happy with the food so i tipped them.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP_tIQvAXNYbojJ6nM_n35MYU2n4-dpaAlQcDCJ&fid=0x0:0x2a2857896adc1231"],"When":"2024-7-4"},{"Name":"Ronald Neufeld","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW3-UYUNJrMpFog9fj3pIFLK5tmoK0-LgL_hzRpH2SFmt6tHLqw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Mainly come here for their chicken curry katsu special on Tuesday. Great flavor and I usually order a bit extra sauce. Value is nice and service is quick.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMcamyhkXmfRnmHFdRfV9lg3R51sPMe9vznZKP7&fid=0x0:0x2a2857896adc1231"],"When":"2023-10-18"},{"Name":"Kay Bee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKmxcCu0a7Tl2EIwVjP2qrHq3Yql4NE9ewxjMr7ovKkKB3Rew=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Very bad experience here.  No one could even say hello or acknowledge we were there .  Took forever to order.  Dirty tables. No thank yous or anything.  Ok if you like mediocre food from a dirty facility with no customer service.  Avoid this, there has to be something better in the area.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Marta Szmilko","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ5cxLIqYW9CEaeY8Pk-Tk56SV38TRlVi8sTLyufepImTtZw98=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The hamburger is very tasty, the fries are divine. The staff is fast and friendly.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPghJKRjiO6K2T7y9oPUjjwK9lyf2fz1jk3PCUQ&fid=0x0:0x2a2857896adc1231"],"When":"2023-3-8"},{"Name":"Grace Xu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXAmY3gC_74HFyTtrGM9YMgQR3nvqGbAUqTOig9dL6vWfDc5Mfy=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Cute little dinner style restaurant serves breakfast and lunch, Korean fusion food, Western comfort food like chicken soup, hamburgers, etc.

I only come here for lunch because it’s close to work, and I like it here, friendly service, tasty food, nice and clean restaurant, no complaints!

They have also recently upgraded their menu and up their game in the social media network, yes they have an instagram account now! You can follow them and see what’s new on the menu!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP3FolAgK4QCMQSWbFotC-N17ICNKu3mjix_mfj&fid=0x0:0x2a2857896adc1231"],"When":"2019-11-28"},{"Name":"Kevin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLL8WdmmeXgGd14-pwts9OY5wJqKS1a-qMe0A4PK7ODpCo5wH4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It’s rare to come across a non-chain food place that sells sandwiches and wraps. I was pleasantly surprised by how great everything tasted. The quality of the food served here is easy to tell based on the freshness of the ingredients, and it’s quite clear that they put in the effort to make sure that everything is fresh and delicious. Their bread is what I think makes their sandwiches taste so great (I’m a sourdough fan myself). It’s not your typical grocery-store bought bread, and it plays a huge role in the flavor factor.
I was inclined to get the soup since a lot of the other customers at the time were getting them, and I can see why. It tastes homemade and fresh, which makes me consider trying all their soups.
They also serve daily specials like chicken teriyaki with rice which I also enjoyed. The portion was generous for the price, and the chicken was crispy which made it much more enjoyable than the typical soft/mushy chicken teriyaki from other places.
This café is in a secluded area and it’s one of the healthier available options for breakfast/lunch. It’s also nice to see how the staffs here know their regulars’ names and usual orders. This to me means that they are tasty enough to come back! I would recommend this place to anyone who is passing by and need a quick bite.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPwCsSIUWY4XzdvVSlTnZEnJ0Ubabs22REdsSGB&fid=0x0:0x2a2857896adc1231"],"When":"2019-2-4"}]

[{"Name":"S D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKJYsqsfylRWb2qB-xJh6bN2jntU-d5BqDo5FMP29y23P0aTA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing Dinner at Rumi’s Kebab & Grill

We had dinner at Rumi’s Kebab & Grill, and it was a great experience, from the moment we stepped inside, we were welcomed by a cozy, inviting atmosphere.

Very clean and well maintained restaurant.

They have a great selection of different cuisines Afghan, Persian and Turkish.
Every dish was packed with flavor and beautifully presented, you could tell the chefs put a lot of care into each plate.

You cannot visit this place and not try the Kabuli Tikka!! Trust me you will love it!!!

All in all, our dinner at Rumi’s Kebab & Grill was a great experience. The food was delicious and service was outstanding. If you’re looking for a place with amazing food and even better service, Rumi’s Kebab & Grill should definitely be on your list.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPYSNqSGcJpWEmIcdvajCh8IhBfodu1m6iFGQWi&fid=0x0:0xb645b5df0f288bfe"],"When":"2024-11-18"},{"Name":"Disha Rana","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW9RvTMXeP3KqSHfnATMTo2ic7srx022rxbo_TaCIeCacEG1IXQ0A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely loved the flavours and atmosphere of the place.
The food was delicious, with perfect seasoning,  the flavours are spot on! You can tell the ingredients are of high quality, and the portions were generous.
The ambiance of the restaurant was warm and inviting. Yousef was incredibly friendly and attentive, ensuring our meal was enjoyable.

If you're a fan of authentic flavors and excellent service, Rumis Kebab and Grill is a must-try.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOU3DB2Kw0nheOR6wdaTr91ItSr_zrUtGJ_Igvp&fid=0x0:0xb645b5df0f288bfe"],"When":"2024-12-21"},{"Name":"Albina Smishchenko","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKW-1yczTyBCGKI9JUS936Gi4bmhbmRzZRmqdOT0R09GfFUtA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The atmosphere is very cozy, with an authentic oriental interior that immediately takes you to Turkey. The service is at a high level - the staff is friendly, attentive and ready to help with choosing a dish.

The food is simply amazing! I especially liked the kebab - juicy, with perfectly selected spices.

I recommend this restaurant to anyone who wants to try real Turkish cuisine. I will definitely come back again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMjPss8kI6WsxXlGtdh-jDA5xPbLPaZOrp5VufE&fid=0x0:0xb645b5df0f288bfe"],"When":"2024-12-11"},{"Name":"Shah Babur Rais","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXfpy04fX8eU1SWBi1gGmmSfUYeKEsc_ozYdpzlC0WdiYmJpUog=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delicious food with great decor and atmosphere. It is truly an authentic afghan cuisine with a variety of dishes representing real afghan taste. Thank you for a great service and delicious food after a long day of work. I will definitely come here more often and would recommend it to anyone.

The food is so delicious and authentic that I had to eat the whole plate. I took a picture of my empty plate to show this for future foodies.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOsnQmhI5j6qjfCM1v8yPIX_zHVO5WF1E4NJXEa&fid=0x0:0xb645b5df0f288bfe"],"When":"2024-10-16"},{"Name":"Lise-Anne Bielak","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVlwZNw8zHw4_84s-ID1xXFCYqDrDxmOWGXXNg_SYvcZVngBLK-=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came twice for the brunch and each time was absolutely delicious. The mantu dumplings are super flavourful and would come back just for those. And the sujuk (Turkish sausage) would recommend you get extra!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPKM56V12-IAMTjdPp9ltCGAyMCB8f4WLyAkP9v&fid=0x0:0xb645b5df0f288bfe"],"When":"2024-12-14"},{"Name":"Narges Amirian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUM8zUxZ7t3xIXkqdR20aB3Re58yZTb9VHoU9Nv2RpaF6upqSc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We recently dined at this resturant, and the food was outstanding! Every dish was not only fresh but also packed with delicious flavors that truly showcased the best of Afghan cuisine. Each bite was a delight, from the aromatic spices to the perfectly cooked ingredients. The welcoming atmosphere and friendly staff only added to the experience. If you're in the area, don’t miss out on this gem for an authentic and tasty Afghan meal!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMwTDXTB4UDbrOm9mn4kt_y1NYTgnnzFVwyK0-o&fid=0x0:0xb645b5df0f288bfe"],"When":"2024-10-9"},{"Name":"Tomis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU5jFOkJ247NYbh_k4LmxmH66JB0yPwuwyoCPAVh9_W6x-N0Tk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Showed up at 5pm. Place empty. Ordered mixed kebab. Very good. Pulao rice definitely worth the extra charge. Talked myself into the baklava as well as Turkish tea. Definitely going back to try more dishes. Atmosphere only 3 stars as they were playing Christmas music and pop, would have been nice to hear real Turkish folk music.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOQvvjlEJRFLo7L-lbGjUvCaEEbOJbJeAajMAmZ&fid=0x0:0xb645b5df0f288bfe"],"When":"2024-11-28"},{"Name":"Свят Мысив","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX93F7wrB6Dc0ihsqMdg_UZCsT49nCSpKfsLxLjyzUVquEapYQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It was nice to visit this restaurant. Unlike other Canadian establishments, it is clean! This is good. The waiters are always attentive and ask if everything is okay with you. The food is not too spicy and very appetizing. I ordered lamb shashlik - it was great! Thank you for a pleasant time spent in this restaurant.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNeIU05X14Ie38BFyWhufcdQpqU5xnff4qd-n8T&fid=0x0:0xb645b5df0f288bfe"],"When":"2024-11-25"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Bianca Z","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKbna_-rUln88CEmv7uKXFkToIGuu_UGqgGuBzz7f9y77no-w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"f you're looking for a cozy spot with a homey vibe, Café Ibex is the place to be! This charming café offers an incredible brunch experience that you won’t want to miss. From hearty plates that satisfy your morning cravings to lighter options that are perfect for a relaxed midday meal, their brunch menu has something for everyone.

And while the brunch is the star of the show, let's not forget the desserts—deliciously crafted, they're the perfect sweet ending to your meal. The coffee? Simply divine. Whether you're a straight-up espresso lover or a latte aficionado, the coffee at Café Ibex hits all the right notes.

And the location? Stunning! Nestled in a beautiful spot, it's the perfect place to unwind, enjoy some great food, and soak in the surroundings. It’s the kind of place where you can relax, chat with friends, or even get some work done while savoring every delicious moment.

Highly recommend this gem to anyone looking for a delightful café experience! ☕🍰✨","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPohjpd3LsChWeMhL6sLAh7MHOZCYuAgMEX8HXh&fid=0x0:0x6d5c91495d5ac0d7"],"When":"2024-8-11"},{"Name":"Alvie Jane","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW2c9bDX5jNCznK5zCHqpdqZ-h1cSU95xqbr6CUly8Jngcz6Z3IjQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The location is nice, very spacious, and beautiful view.  The food is good.  We ordered fish tacos, chick pea suffle and mocha.

We got there at 10 am, ordered at 10:15, but we got our food at 11:15!  Omg! We ended up taking our food for to-go.  I only saw three staff working in there...  I dunno if there are more staff, but yeah... waited and hour to get our food.  😞","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNkXog7g7dPTf35GobEGs9qiOlqBCHnxXHAlsb4&fid=0x0:0x6d5c91495d5ac0d7"],"When":"2024-7-4"},{"Name":"Brandon L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJyHn7JV86qZm8CZqsqIks8GN6yWYEAQ6gvZcDyoNWS-KuZVg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wonderful eatery in Burke mountain area. The food and drinks were great, and the people were so nice. We even got to talk to the owners who were super friendly. Just an awesome neighbourhood cafe. Would definitely recommend.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMWDyFtP4MybybfBWP30YH9V0dWqIkIuVmuW-uw&fid=0x0:0x6d5c91495d5ac0d7"],"When":"2024-7-15"},{"Name":"Hayley V","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVAMZm2-sNxGCCFpIEkOztczqjSFDs0b95WxSG6JnJJ1HSCyhzW=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Nice spot to study with a good view. Underwhelmed by the French toast, thai tacos, and the blended chai special considering they were all quite pricey. Cold brew was good.

They also have EV parking spots which is convenient.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPk6QompzQEJFgU-IZAYngTVVdIwE--h02nrA44&fid=0x0:0x6d5c91495d5ac0d7"],"When":"2024-9-7"},{"Name":"tatiana machulis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIuHbOJwjVCQvHS0SQIHh02XrK0MKhe0iPkX-holPY6NvwiQA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Yes, the customer service is not the best... But the food and the nice atmosphere compensate for it. The food isn't cheap, but it was delicious! The bbq pulled pork and the margherita flatbread were amazing! The drinks were just ok, in the future I'll try something else. If you get to seat outside, the view is pretty nice :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMCCjgPqd7NfQf3884Ptt1gp_4GwBMrnMr_lcJ0&fid=0x0:0x6d5c91495d5ac0d7"],"When":"2024-7-14"},{"Name":"Anuj Bahri","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWT18lkBaeoQnNIFm_M330k_SNNhMs4bw7so2Nnyr04cr_0Ud9H=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If I could give 6 or more stars I would for sure! This place was worth the visit. Awesome food! Beautiful view, nice patio, courteous staff! Had a great evening on a weekend. Definitely worth trying!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNTGB6coceSoOBFFAp-WNcpQ2qnc-PFy7t6qNI8&fid=0x0:0x6d5c91495d5ac0d7"],"When":"2024-8-19"},{"Name":"Clarisse De Guzman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVIdORX9Pyiz3EihaWSGQDl7y-TmVuuWxntoNQ1HgcHLQ18Vfd1=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great cafe with beautiful lighting and yummy cheesecakes and coffee. I ordered the Caramel Carrot Cheesecake and it was amazing! It was super sweet though, so I’m glad I ordered a coffee to balance it out. The iced latte with oat milk I had was great. Loved the atmosphere here! Modern yet cozy, and a great place to enjoy patio dining on a sunny day. I’m hoping to try their savoury food next. Service was friendly too.

Important note: They only accept card payments! Not a problem for me personally since I rarely have cash on me. Just something to keep in mind before you go.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN8dadjlhiKCldXmedH86IZBcccLXQxBZ8E-1Tu&fid=0x0:0x6d5c91495d5ac0d7"],"When":"2023-6-19"},{"Name":"Sarah Sosnowski","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWJc-Dq28QyUJ7C8WWvNoOfH1zuw1otJKp0YnKhJ0bmB3XHevTY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Beautiful view and creative menu. I enjoyed the eggs benny, especially because it allowed me to try a new take on a bread free Benny. I enjoyed the vanilla oat milk latte  because it was so frothy. I enjoyed the view especially because it made me feel expansive. Thanks to Ibex cafe and kitchen. I’m grateful.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMJtVMos9G58lx1rlDIaMLGwpSviBdSLS8ohIo3&fid=0x0:0x6d5c91495d5ac0d7"],"When":"2024-3-28"}]

[{"Name":"Geraldine Sangalang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUcAsqfNVs6uRfmsJ5FtsU66GdsPGBE4zo_tn8DnG79e7VADqel9Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Very popular local breakfast and brunch spot. Be ready for a wait, but it's worth it if you're looking for generous portions and sweet rewards.

We ordered a few dishes to try:

Apples and Cinnamon were exactly that. Sweet and delicious with just enough tartness.

The Mexicasa Omelet was savoury and spicy. Wonderfully satisfying, and a huge portion.

We had a hard time deciding between The King Kong and Bowser. But the toasted coconut won, and we went with Bowser. Believe it or not, it wasn't too sweet. The flavour and texture of the pancake helped to balance the dish.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNtawtl5BET-xx7jUpEtFONFxkBUI9Bfsvlqihi&fid=0x0:0xaaebff47a4a99ef2"],"When":"2024-10-15"},{"Name":"Juan José Salaya","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX1Ln__1lVc-JSwJxu3Sudj7VGGpDHTTaI6ATzhk7kkdUk_WRTN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Amazing service from Shauna, fast en friendly.
I had the chocolate waffle, insane! And huge portions.
But the savory pancake not the best, hipster hash. The pancake was good but the side of hash and vegetables were not very good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPmaviqW2sU_R_MfMRdvFHaU01XhNLfVwSVCcOH&fid=0x0:0xaaebff47a4a99ef2"],"When":"2024-8-9"},{"Name":"Mar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWWTdC3Cu0qquRYQVKhOdWcOmJsma73tOEyPAbRghfK5B9Xyfw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Quiet and cozy place on weekdays. My favorite dish of all time is Veggie I Love You, which comes with a pancake. The veggies are always fresh and neatly sliced. The only drawback is the high price","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNoiGISJgSmJLSHz_XDKv3UeFGIR2oQ23GqinXJ&fid=0x0:0xaaebff47a4a99ef2"],"When":"2024-10-9"},{"Name":"Jeff Downer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXl3HQ-1C4N-_a7ykvhIi5aM883AB-cDQVYb1xeenCY7zekayvZ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I had high hopes for this place. The hash just didn’t deliver. Pretty average Sysco quality potato hash with premade tasting hollandaise that resembled cheese. One slice and a half of avocado : ( I just wish it tasted more homemade and less store-bought. The pancake was good! Sweet and caramelized. Not worth the price of the dish (Hipster Hash)
My partner’s chocolate banana waffles were a hit though. Very good and nice portion.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNtalSDrAz-3j5GtPKct2PF6onzeKeFu4j88AIk&fid=0x0:0xaaebff47a4a99ef2"],"When":"2024-8-11"},{"Name":"danakhatib","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVkw_MS-bFFQL-DqU_kCatDuVYGKImx-f2Z5AnYQHBCy9-uZ6_t=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Service was fantastic! They split our foods onto seperate plates (without us asking) because we wanted to share some dishes, which was very kind! Food was great, we got the chocolate waffle, which was delicious and the smoked salmon benny. I’ve had better hollandaise sauce but overall everything was awesome!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOcXsNe5b-w07YgnnqAfyFuObJiLP2t5VicwA1B&fid=0x0:0xaaebff47a4a99ef2"],"When":"2024-8-15"},{"Name":"Kiah Rose","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWTVXBfiLNTJ8gFd9zcQjhLGEsYxsifqJuzzyh3SEwJwRrMplme=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you’re looking for incredible food and an amazing atmosphere, The Big Flat Pancake is the place to be! The quality of the food is absolutely top-notch — everything is fresh, flavorful, and made with care. The pancakes are delicious, and the portions are generous!

What really sets this place apart, though, is the staff. They’re full of positive energy and always make you feel like part of the family. We shared lots of laughs, and their warm hospitality truly gave us a fantastic start to our Saturday!

I love supporting local, family-owned businesses, and The Big Flat Pancake is exactly the kind of place that deserves your attention. I highly recommend giving it a try!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMy6zOwu4HHfJ_gTbG6krgQtrhQd5D-xVfx0wsj&fid=0x0:0xaaebff47a4a99ef2"],"When":"2024-11-9"},{"Name":"Davina Johnsen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXOWfxjdUo4u1LYvAiA8xMOSJlaFjaSMXKmyFbVlITAYWYoqbeaXw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This was our second day in a row here because it was sooo delicious yesterday. I liked our server from yesterday better (purple haired girl- I think her name was Tasha?) she was great. The food here is out of this world. It’s a cozy little hipster place, great music. Clean washrooms. If you show up and there is a line up, please stay, because I promise it’s worth the wait!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNk5YdsWzVNzwwA_kkRWs6GwvBXaSg7LV_7oKIg&fid=0x0:0xaaebff47a4a99ef2"],"When":"2023-10-21"},{"Name":"Adam M.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXBezQ5u52QUPfNCS-XISW7oETfNlf5RvdoikJTFUzauPV7HEINiA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Big Flat Pancake has been one of our favorite restaurants since the day they opened. Whether with my family or just the two of us, we’ve enjoyed countless breakfasts here, including many Mother’s Day and Father’s Day celebrations. The restaurant's modern design and simplicity create an upscale breakfast experience, even though it maintains a casual and welcoming vibe.

Seating is limited, and I still recall waiting outside with social distancing protocols in place during the early post-COVID days. Last week, we visited again, and as always, I ordered my favorite: chicken waffles with whipped cream and strawberry topping on the side. My wife, on the other hand, loves trying something different every time we visit. The food arrived quickly, and as usual, it was very tasty.

However, (our visit on Nov 30th)  I do want to share one piece of feedback from this visit. My wife and I were enjoying our coffee after finishing our meal when the server brought the check—completely understandable, especially when tables need to turn over for waiting guests. But this time, there were four empty tables, and no one was waiting. Moments later, while we were still sipping our coffee, the server returned with the cordless payment unit and stood by our table. We were both caught off guard, thinking, “What…?” We paid because the payment unit was already there, and the server was waiting, but the interaction felt rushed.

Having owned a restaurant in downtown Vancouver, I understand the need to turn tables efficiently. That said, there’s an unspoken etiquette between servers and guests, and this instance felt a bit abrupt—particularly since the restaurant wasn’t busy.  It’s a small issue, and I’m sure it wasn’t intentional, but I wanted to share this experience in the hopes it’s not repeated for other guests.

Of course, we will continue visiting Big Flat Pancake because we love the food, atmosphere, and overall experience. This is just some constructive feedback for management or ownership to consider.

Thank you, and see you again soon!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN3DgZTp8jMRgeo2EOBKceMPW-1SSt0lYSYOwaO&fid=0x0:0xaaebff47a4a99ef2"],"When":"2024-12-10"}]

Owner claims the ramen were fresh and we asked the lady after we seen frozen ramen being brought in to make, AND WE ASKED THE LADY SERVER, SHE SAID YES WE DO MAKE RAMENS FRON FROZEN ONES. So I don’t know what you are trying to prove, or if workers are just being lazy and not doing their jobs. [{"Name":"Geraldine Sangalang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUcAsqfNVs6uRfmsJ5FtsU66GdsPGBE4zo_tn8DnG79e7VADqel9Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Quiet restaurant with plenty of seating. Within walking distance from Coquitlam Centre, the Coquitlam Aquatic Centre and LaFarge, it's a great spot to regroup with fresh sushi.

I tried the Salmon & Spicy Scallop Roll ($9.95), Avocado Roll ($3.25) and a Miso Soup ($1.50). Sushi rolls were prepared fresh, and the flavour was satisfying.

Very reasonable prices. Surprisingly beautiful tableware.

Perfect local cheap and cheerful spot. Next time, I'll try the Korean Chirashi Don.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOaPAinBXUUu3ilSaGH9s6s84yk_foIZfB7F_7O&fid=0x0:0x8fbdacf2df47aa40"],"When":"2024-10-13"},{"Name":"Jimmy Huang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVmaQe2WLp7herqsSS6Qbb3TdkPTjO2rKeO4tgMEL6Gag0kIT7k=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Inari (bean curd) nigiri sushi: good inari sushi, I liked it.
Chopped scallop with masago nigiri sushi: first time trying this and it’s quite delicious.

Miso soup: the server was very kind and offered me a second bowl of miso soup. It was decent.

Chicken teriyaki donburi: awesome dish! The portion was very generous and it tastes pretty good. Would recommend.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOTtGnweFoM8BOXJe_TVo9-7V78JMoAJTYoaNkf&fid=0x0:0x8fbdacf2df47aa40"],"When":"2024-10-5"},{"Name":"Maya Ushikubo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXJxE78gPCdJOshqUdmDjplgd5sCYNs7KC5rpdfRolyT7BeGidS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I usually order from Uber Eats. Every time I am increasingly more disappointed with the aesthetic & quality. Never ordering from here again. Seaweed is horrible quality, stale, damp, and hard to chew. When you order the party tray sushi in the middle is squished & barely have anything in there! This time was the WORST! And the sushi never stay together, it always falls apart! Ugh. If you’re a sushi restaurant you might as well perfect what is supposedly your speciality.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPxVwsw9WmsLxHId3u1c5CK18wiXpoPq5Bl1gah&fid=0x0:0x8fbdacf2df47aa40"],"When":"2023-7-9"},{"Name":"Rachel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ2CZgy0TVqtFKiLfsbPAZO_17b8OnxpihQm3eYlsYxIR57ZbI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sitting down for sushi at Hakone is akin to the feeling of coming home.
Great quality food, great prices, even better care and service by a family-owned small business. A must-visit in Coquitlam!
⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMHBfN5ufjL-H8bmX5AXnEGcnVIGaFwzKGHAVQ&fid=0x0:0x8fbdacf2df47aa40"],"When":"2024-2-5"},{"Name":"Bryan Hamilton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVT8h0PfMIgbjw04_aBjNfJzW0U66oxSAxm91LsnZ0QjC4eOTQX=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I did not score the atmosphere as I had my dinner delivered by Skip the dishes. The food was delicious and the presentation very good even for delivery. Another time I will need to sit in the restaurant and enjoy the experience. The salmon. As tender and tasty, the shrimp tempura nice and light and crunchy. The spicy tuna roll had just enough heat. And the salad was fresh and crunchy.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPfsCMrlSOE4uXC8UftX3vK-R1z7HMhcPqwxR0C&fid=0x0:0x8fbdacf2df47aa40"],"When":"2024-1-6"},{"Name":"Minipa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXLkpsoXCUt-uCoPDrB_Mv40ZqSioejOqdNEdMQaklHEBDE1W1x=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Another staple place for hangouts between friends. Hakone is a lowkey restaurant hidden in a mini-mall that is close to Coquitlam center. The service is quick, water is completely being refilled and the food is great for it's price.

I would definitely recommend bringing friends and family here :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN4301MVNEiKigNCBRKK0xCOC6ppSshmyRDBY2S&fid=0x0:0x8fbdacf2df47aa40"],"When":"2023-5-28"},{"Name":"Chris Khoo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUVswFIT6QEqI-75YXfE_hJY7j3l02kgKmoSxfj7DZFHoba0DWRug=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The sushi is very tasty and the presentation is really good. Really good value for money. Most of all, the service is amazing!

I will be coming back to this place again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMrw6UdRoMzFOjwmygXwD-vh0i9SFGOPOBdXD2K&fid=0x0:0x8fbdacf2df47aa40"],"When":"2023-2-1"},{"Name":"Grace Ni","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUVqcBTqiZHcIOQ7ny42hdLDrTV7OCPvX3BQu84I9AEELlTVVDT=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love this place! Great quality and portion sizes - they are always so sweet here and care so much about the quality of their food. My partner and I are regulars despite being surrounded by many many sushi spots - Hakone is certainly our favourite :)","Images":null,"When":""}]

This is an eatery so inside of the restaurant is fulled of the food smell so we decided to sit outside. It was more peaceful😗

The price of drinks are reasonable I think. The location is a bit hard for walking if you are not in neighborhood but there is a parking lot right in front of the cafe so it’s good for the people.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOCM3I3YqRSE2r3A6UoRBRLk5qthqs1w9dOPq7u&fid=0x0:0x842408b42802980e"],"When":"2024-7-20"},{"Name":"Brian Stewart","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJqikwf0-G731bGJ0EOoEgeqikki9ZtAPEZMJwAnQXsDoWAzw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I just left having a quick lunch. Americano and the club sandwich. It was so tasty. This is a neat little place tucked in a residential area. If you visit Port Moody this is worth the drive up the hill. Did I mention they also make pizza!! I'll be back.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"VFX Soup","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXdmaF5fr1PFwFHzqvp_4BNdCPaFDuEyKyQczQ4zVX_--sY35Cz=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I just had the best pizza of my life. This place is under new ownership and the food and drink selection is amazing! I had the Lamb pizza with banana peppers and it blew my socks off.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNbeb7bdpCM18rPJAMln9LoOWzzu26H34fXr6PP&fid=0x0:0x842408b42802980e"],"When":"2024-10-6"},{"Name":"Jordan Ellis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV6CEeIPS-loQURDvgAmkL1dRe7eqLm27RtfMqxJVA0n0p4cgv3=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The Beanery is a hidden gem! It’s a quiet and clean spot, perfect for relaxing or catching up on work. The staff were super friendly and welcoming. We shared a croissant, which was delicious, and both the latte and espresso were smooth and well-made. Definitely planning to come back!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Yoshiko C.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKtcsZOlyd8taDwX9F7EkmkehI4-UW_WG9O9oyFRNdwVNmFnuw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"A surprise to have found this little cafe in a residential area. Stopping by a Saturday afternoon, we were excited to explore it; however, the barista ignored us when he got a couple of orders and let us stood by the cashier for so long. When we asked some questions, staff didn't seem to be willing to answer so we ended up ordering two to-go coffee and left.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMtyUlKMVhVLZ6DrO23a8AxRMfAjKG6en1mjQS1&fid=0x0:0x842408b42802980e"],"When":"2024-6-9"},{"Name":"Ryan Pan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJnWku3j0CZMNCsei3m0vOrdZAdUfzVvR154Ojdba66S2a7XA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love this place, their pizza is superb! Freshly made with fresh ingredients. The sandwiches are fantastic as well. The small pizza is perfect for our 4 and 6 year old, while my wife and I shared the large pizza. Very friendly staff and great food, I will be back for sure. P.S. their latte tastes great as well, overall a very positive experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMDwZw82nr_Ax52636BANNN1-fPgq8IhhQ9aZ7f&fid=0x0:0x842408b42802980e"],"When":"2018-2-4"},{"Name":"Ads","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVwDyuvQtXP_VygmU1rNXhUJ0mc48E4h1QtDkdEfrlXmuS-mYhL=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I found this little hidden gem when going for a stroll around the area. Super cute, quaint coffee joint with an upbeat and laid back atmosphere, totally dig this place! The staff whip up a really yummy Maple Oat Latte for sure! Albeit quite expensive for a 16oz coffee, it was a great experience nonetheless.
Support local businesses!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMiKJvL1kXAYAeIu75Lj8xFXKnaRHBymoyAQVnS&fid=0x0:0x842408b42802980e"],"When":"2023-4-16"},{"Name":"dela de Youngster","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUDfbQ46vnRRuuLpyyuhZRepHVtgyPbeHaE2sw297s3wfIgxBLu=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Some of the best pizzas I've ever had.
